NK086(lu)003:1: // gu h+ya ma n+t+ra p+au r+b+aa ba r+t+ta na pu
NK086(lu)003:2: r+aa na sh+aa sa na bya ba s+tha pa na
NK086(lu)003:3: pra ti sam k+shee pa ta ka thi ta su
NK086(lu)003:4: b+h+aa shi t+aa lo ko t+sa ba n+aa ma bi
NK086(lu)003:5: ha ra ti //// gsang sngags snga 'gyur rnying ma
NK086(lu)003:6: pa'i bstan pa'i rnam gzhag mdo tsam brjod pa legs
NK086(lu)003:7: bshad snang ba'i dga' ston ces bya ba bzhugs so
NK086(lu)003:8: ha ra ti //// //// yo si d+d+ha ba r+y+aa
NK086(lu)003:9: sta pa d+aa ni m+aa tra ny+tsi t+r+aa d+ha ro
NK086(lu)003:10: b+aa k+pa bi bu d+d+ha sa rba ////
NK086(lu)003:11: gang zhig grub pa mchog brnyes go 'phang tsam //
NK086(lu)003:12: ngo mtshar 'dzin min rgyal kun gsung rdo rje ////
NK086(lu)003:13: tree lo kya ne t+aa gu ru k+aa ya dri
NK086(lu)003:14: sh+t+aa d+hi sh+tha n+tu pa d+m+aa ka ra go d+ha
NK086(lu)003:15: ri na //// srid gsum zil gnon rig 'dzin skur bzhengs pa //
NK086(lu)003:16: o rgyan rdo rje 'chang gis byin gyis rlobs //
NK086(lu)003:17: thabs mchog bde chen snang ba'i d+r+wa ba kun //
NK086(lu)003:18: shes rab stong nyid gnyug ma'i phyag rgyar sdom //
NK086(lu)003:19: brtan g.yo'i srog tu yongs bzhugs he ru ka /khyab bdag bla mas byang chub bar du skyongs //
NK086(lu)003:20: chos tshul dri med chu gter las skyes pa'i //
NK086(lu)003:21: legs bshad gtam gyi ut+pala mtshar sdug can //
NK086(lu)003:22: don bzang sbrang rtsi'i rdul phreng 'dzag pa na //
NK086(lu)003:23: dpyod ldan bung ba'i dga' ston ci yang 'phel //
NK086(lu)003:24: de'ang 'phags mchog 'jig rten dbang phyug gi zhing khams
NK086(lu)003:25: bsil ldan gangs ri'i ljongs su sprul pa'i chos rgyal
NK086(lu)003:26: mes dbon rnam gsum gyi thugs bskyed phrin las bla
NK086(lu)003:27: na med pa'i nyer len gyis /
NK086(lu)003:28: ston pa'i zhal skyin mkhan slob pan grub byang sems
NK086(lu)003:29: lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis bsgyur bshad 'chad nyan sgom
NK086(lu)003:30: sgrub kyis gtan la phab nas rgyal bstan gzhir bzhengs
NK086(lu)003:32: de las gnubs chen khu dbon zur pa mes dbon
NK086(lu)003:33: nyang rog rong klong sogs grub brnyes rig 'dzin rgyal
NK086(lu)003:34: ba dngos dang mtshungs pa grags med pa'i tshang chen
NK086(lu)003:35: po brdol te da lta'i bar bshad sgrub phrin las
NK086(lu)003:36: kyi rgyun mnyams par bzung bzhin bzhugs pa gsang sngags
NK086(lu)003:37: snga 'gyur rnying ma zhes yongs su grags pa 'di
NK086(lu)003:38: nyid kyi bstan pa'i lus rnam par gzhag pa snying
NK086(lu)003:39: por dril te mdo tsam 'chad par 'dod do //
NK086(lu)003:40: de yang thog mar spyir 'khor 'das kyi chos ngos
NK086(lu)003:41: 'dzin cing de'i mtshan nyid gtan la dbab par bya
NK086(lu)003:46: gang la dmigs pas zag pa dang bcas pa'i las
NK086(lu)003:47: kyis khams gsum du 'khor zhing sdug bsngal 'ba' zhig
NK086(lu)003:48: la spyod pa'i skyon gyi rang bzhin can ni 'jig
NK086(lu)003:49: rten pa'i chos kyi mtshan nyid /
NK086(lu)003:50: gang gis rgyud la brten pas sgrib gnyis 'jig cing
NK086(lu)003:51: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las skyobs par byed pa'i rnam
NK086(lu)003:52: dkar gyi yon tan mnga' ba ni 'jig rten las
NK086(lu)003:53: 'das pa'i chos kyi mtshan nyid de /
NK086(lu)003:55: sdug bsngal dag ni thams cad dang //
NK086(lu)003:56: sgrib kun sel byed dam pa'i chos //
NK086(lu)003:60: zhes pa'i byings las bsgrubs pa'i d+harma zhes bya ba'i sgra las don bcu 'dzin pa'am /
NK086(lu)003:63: thams cad 'dzin pas na d+harma ste chos so //
NK086(lu)003:65: don bcu ni rnam bshad rig pa las /
NK086(lu)003:66: chos ni shes bya lam dang ni //
NK086(lu)003:67: mya ngan 'das dang yid kyi yul //
NK086(lu)003:68: bsod nams tshe dang gsung rab dang //
NK086(lu)003:70: zhes 'byung ba ltar chos kyi sgra shes bya la 'jug pa ni dper na mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:71: chos gang la la 'dus byas sam /
NK086(lu)003:74: chos rnams thams cad de 'drar shes par gyis //
NK086(lu)003:75: zhes pa la sogs pa lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:77: dge slong dag log pa'i lta ba ni chos ma
NK086(lu)003:78: yin la yang dag pa'i lta ba ni chos yin
NK086(lu)003:79: no // zhes pa lta bu dang /
NK086(lu)003:81: chos la skyabs su song ba /
NK086(lu)003:87: btsun mo'i 'khor dang gzhon nu ma rnams dang lhan cig tu chos spyod /
NK086(lu)003:90: byis pa ni mthong ba'i chos gces par 'dzin pa yin /
NK086(lu)003:93: dge slong chos zhes pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:96: dbyangs kyis bsnyad pa'i sde dang /
NK086(lu)003:99: 'du byed kyi rdzas rnams ni de'i chos so //
NK086(lu)003:101: nga yang 'chi ba'i chos dang 'chi ba'i chos nyid las ma 'das so //
NK086(lu)003:104: dge slong gi chos bzhi zhes dang /
NK086(lu)003:105: dge slong dag srog gcod pa ni chos ma yin la /
NK086(lu)003:106: srog gcod pa spang ba ni chos yin no //
NK086(lu)003:109: yul chos dang rigs chos lta bu rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:110: de dag 'dzin pa'i sgra don dang ji ltar 'brel snyam na /
NK086(lu)003:111: shes bya rnams kyis ni rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:112: dper na sa ni sra ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:115: rlung ni yang zhing g.yo ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:116: zhes pa lta bu rang mtshan dang /
NK086(lu)003:117: 'dus byas thams cad ni mi rtag pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:118: zag bcas thams cad ni sdug bsngal ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:119: chos thams cad na bdag med pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:120: mya ngan las 'das pa ni zhi ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:121: zhes pa lta bu spyi mtshan 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:122: lam dang myang 'das kyis ni 'khor bar ltung ba las 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:123: yid yul gyis ni yid 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:124: bsod nams kyis ngan 'gror ltung ba las 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:125: tshe'am srog gis ni lus sam ris mthun 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:126: gsung rab kyis ni don phyin ci ma log par 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:127: 'byung 'gyur gyis 'byung rgyu'i chos de 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:128: nges pas nges par bya ba'i gzhi 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:129: lugs kyis ni rang dang mtshungs pa'i spyod pa 'dzin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:130: rig pas ni 'khrul pa'i phyogs las 'dzin pa lta bur rigs pas dpag par bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:131: gsum pa dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:134: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK086(lu)003:136: sbyin pa ni 'jig rten pa la'ang yod 'jig rten las 'das pa'ang yod do //
NK086(lu)003:137: de'ang 'jig rten pa'i sbyin pa gang zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:141: mi 'da' na 'jig rten pa'i sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:142: gang sbyin pa byin pas 'jig rten las g.yo /
NK086(lu)003:144: 'da' na 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:146: thabs gang gis mthar phyin par bsgrubs pas 'bras bu
NK086(lu)003:147: 'jig rten las 'phags nus mi nus kyi khyad par
NK086(lu)003:148: ro // de la'ang dang po 'khor ba'i chos la gsum /
NK086(lu)003:151: 'phros don ma rtogs log rtogs kyi lta ba bshad pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:153: 'khor ba'i chos rgyu ma rigs pa gsum mtshungs ldan du shar ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:154: bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa shes pa skyes
NK086(lu)003:155: pa de la de nyid du ma shes pa dang
NK086(lu)003:156: / lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas rang ngo
NK086(lu)003:157: ma shes pa de dang shes pa de gnyis lhan
NK086(lu)003:159: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas rang snang la
NK086(lu)003:160: gzhan du dpyad pa'i cha de gsum ngo bo gcig
NK086(lu)003:161: las ldog pa tha dad du shar bas gzhi las
NK086(lu)003:162: gzhi snang du shar ba de rang nyid las byung
NK086(lu)003:163: bar ma shes pas yul yul can du dpyod byed
NK086(lu)003:164: kyi ma rig pa gsum po rgyu'i rkyen /
NK086(lu)003:165: rang las gzhan du bzung bas snang yul me long
NK086(lu)003:166: la rang gi byad shar lta bu dmigs pa'i rkyen
NK086(lu)003:167: / nga dang nga yi bar 'dzin pa'i shes pa bdag po'i rkyen /
NK086(lu)003:168: gsum po dus mtshungs pas de ma thag pa'i rkyen te /
NK086(lu)003:169: bzhi po de 'dzom pa'i dmigs pa ma dag pa'i
NK086(lu)003:170: cha las snang ba dang shes pa gnyis nang dang
NK086(lu)003:171: phyi rol du gzung 'dzin gyi rnam char bzung bas
NK086(lu)003:173: 'khrul pa'i rgyu ni ma rig pa //
NK086(lu)003:174: ma rig pa ni rnam pa gsum //
NK086(lu)003:176: rgyu gcig byed med rtsa ba las //
NK086(lu)003:177: rang ngo yin par ma shes pas //
NK086(lu)003:181: lhun grub stong pa'i yul la shar //
NK086(lu)003:185: 'khrul pa de nyid 'khrul dus nyid nas rang ngo
NK086(lu)003:186: ma shes pa'i sgrib byed kyi rang rtsal la ma
NK086(lu)003:187: rig pa'i char kun gzhi dang /
NK086(lu)003:188: de la brten pa kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa'i sems dang /
NK086(lu)003:189: de las byung ba'i nyon mongs pa drug ste /
NK086(lu)003:190: shes rab kyi cha las 'khrul pa gti mug /skyed pa'i rim pa'i cha las 'khrul pa zhe sdang /
NK086(lu)003:191: lta ba'i cha las 'khrul pa nga rgyal /
NK086(lu)003:192: snang ba'i cha las 'khrul pa 'dod chags /
NK086(lu)003:193: ma rtogs pa'i cha las 'khrul pa phrag dog ste /
NK086(lu)003:194: de la sogs pa nyon mongs pa bsam pa rjes su 'dzin pa'i sems dang /
NK086(lu)003:195: dran pa rnams rjes su 'dzin pa'i yid dang /
NK086(lu)003:196: mtshams sbyor ba'i bag chags dang the tshom rnams kyi gzhir gyur pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:197: yul dang dngos por 'dzin pa'i cha la sogs pa
NK086(lu)003:198: rtog tshogs kyi rim pas brgyad khri bzhi stong ste
NK086(lu)003:199: / dug gsum ka cha mnyam pa la nyi khri
NK086(lu)003:200: chig stong du mchis pa rnams bag la nyal gyi
NK086(lu)003:201: char shar ba'i yid kyi rnam par shes pa dang
NK086(lu)003:202: / / sgo lnga'i shes pa byung zhing /
NK086(lu)003:203: de nyid yul la 'jug pa na lnga logs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:204: shes pa drug gang yang rung ba'i rgyun yod pa
NK086(lu)003:205: yul dang / de nyid skad cig gis de dang
NK086(lu)003:206: de'i rnam par 'dzin pa da lta'i shes pa dang
NK086(lu)003:207: yul dang / / de'i rjes la bde sdug bar
NK086(lu)003:208: ma gsum gang rung tshor ba ni reg pa'i tshor
NK086(lu)003:210: de ltar drug tshan gsum du dbye ba'i khams bco brgyad dang /
NK086(lu)003:211: rdul phra rab tshogs pa gzhig cing gzhom du rung ba'i gzugs kyi phung po /
NK086(lu)003:212: myong zhing srid pa 'byung ba tshor ba'i phung po /
NK086(lu)003:213: g.yo zhing yul la 'jug pa 'du shes kyi phung po /
NK086(lu)003:214: byed cing bag chags sogs pa 'du byed kyi phung po ste lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:215: rtog tshogs gang zhig skye zhing mched par byed pa'i
NK086(lu)003:216: yul gyi rnam pa las rang gi skad cig phyi
NK086(lu)003:217: logs kyi rgyun dang de nyid 'dzin byed kyi shes
NK086(lu)003:218: pa gnyis skye zhing mched par byed pa'i mig gis
NK086(lu)003:219: gzung yul gzugs sogs drug dang /
NK086(lu)003:220: shes pa'i rnam pa las skad cig phyir logs su
NK086(lu)003:221: skye zhing yul la mched rung du skye ba'i gzugs
NK086(lu)003:222: la gzugs su shes pa mig gi rnam shes la
NK086(lu)003:223: sogs drug ste bcu gnyis po dang /
NK086(lu)003:224: yul 'dzin pa la dbang byed pa'i mig gi dbang po sogs lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:225: rnam par rig byed shes pa dang po'i gzugs can
NK086(lu)003:226: gyi bdag po'i rkyen las byung ba yid kyi dbang
NK086(lu)003:231: dang po ni 'khor ba'i bde 'bras skyed byed dge bcu la sogs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:232: gnyis pa ni de las ldog pa'i las ngan 'gror 'phen byed /
NK086(lu)003:233: gsum pa ni khams gong mar 'phen byed kyi las so //
NK086(lu)003:234: de rnams ni nang sems kyis bsdus pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:235: de dag gi snang cha dang rten gzhir gyur pa
NK086(lu)003:236: phyi yul gyis bsdus pa'i khams 'byung ba chen po
NK086(lu)003:240: stongs pa bzhis rgyu dang rkyen dang rten dang dngos po byed la /
NK086(lu)003:241: de las yul snang sems kyi bag chags brtas pas
NK086(lu)003:242: rmi lam lta bur 'dod pa'i khams gling bzhi ri
NK086(lu)003:243: rab khor yug dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten dang /
NK086(lu)003:244: gzugs kyi khams 'od lnga rang gsal 'ja' tshom lta bu dang /
NK086(lu)003:245: gzugs med pa'i khams srid rtse'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK086(lu)003:246: cha las byung ba sogs mdor na khams gsum gyis
NK086(lu)003:247: bsdus pa'i snod bcud brtan g.yo'i bkod pa thams cad
NK086(lu)003:248: 'phags pa rnams kyi don dam pa'i gzigs ngor mi
NK086(lu)003:249: snang yang / sems can rnams kyi blo 'khrul pa'i snang tshul smig rgyu la chur 'khrul pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:250: thag khral sbrul du mthong ba'i shes pa phyin ci
NK086(lu)003:251: log tu gyur pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi dbang gi snang
NK086(lu)003:252: ste / mu tig phreng ba las /
NK086(lu)003:253: de ltar snang ba sna tshogs rnams //
NK086(lu)003:254: thag pa la ni sbrul mthong ltar //
NK086(lu)003:255: de ma yin la der bzung bas //
NK086(lu)003:256: phyi nang snod bcud gnyis su chags //
NK086(lu)003:257: de yang brtag na thag pa nyid //
NK086(lu)003:258: snod bcud ye nas stong pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:259: don dam kun rdzob gzugs can no //
NK086(lu)003:260: sprul mthong de nyid mthong bas bden //
NK086(lu)003:261: thag mthong yang dag nyid du bden //
NK086(lu)003:262: dper na tho la bya bzhin gnas //
NK086(lu)003:263: bden pa gnyis kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK086(lu)003:264: 'jig rten kun rdzob tsam du ste //
NK086(lu)003:265: yang dag nyid la 'brel ba med //
NK086(lu)003:266: stong pa nyid kyi dbyings las ni //
NK086(lu)003:267: de yi ngo bo thams cad grol //
NK086(lu)003:270: 'khor ba'i chos rnams thag khra la //
NK086(lu)003:271: sbrul ltar med pa nyid du 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:273: de yang 'khor ba bde sdug mtho dman sogs snang
NK086(lu)003:274: tshul mtha' dag pa rnams skyed mkhan ni kun nas
NK086(lu)003:275: nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa'i zag bcas kyi las
NK086(lu)003:276: gsum po ste / las kyis byas pa /
NK086(lu)003:278: las kyis rnam par smin pa /
NK086(lu)003:279: las kyis snang ba las gzhan du ma gyur pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:280: mdo sde las brgya pa las /
NK086(lu)003:281: 'jig rten sna tshogs las las skyes //
NK086(lu)003:282: bde dang sdug bsngal las kyis byas //
NK086(lu)003:283: rkyen rnams tshogs nas las byung zhing //
NK086(lu)003:284: las kyis bde dang sdug bsngal byas //
NK086(lu)003:287: sems nyid kyis ni sems can 'jig rten dang //
NK086(lu)003:288: snod kyi 'jig rten sna tshogs las la bgo //
NK086(lu)003:289: 'gro ba ma lus las las skyes par gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:291: gnyis pa 'jig rten pa'i theg pa'am sor bzhag lha mi'i theg pa bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:295: lha dang mi'i bde ba mthar thug pa'i bar du
NK086(lu)003:296: 'god pa'i thabs gang zhig 'khor ba las 'phags par
NK086(lu)003:297: mi nus pa'o // gnyis pa nges tshig ni /
NK086(lu)003:298: lha mi'i bde 'bras tsam la sbyor zhing 'god nus pa'i phyir theg pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:307: ngan song gsum sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin can du mthong nas /
NK086(lu)003:308: der skyes pa'i rgyu mi dge ba'i las sbong ba'i sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK086(lu)003:309: he ru ka gal po las /
NK086(lu)003:310: lha ma'i theg pas mi dge spang //
NK086(lu)003:312: de la mi dge bcu ni /
NK086(lu)003:313: lus kyi las srog gcod ma byin len /
NK086(lu)003:323: yang dag pa'i lta ba zhes bya ba 'jig rten pha rol dang /
NK086(lu)003:324: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:325: ched du brjod pa'i tshoms las /
NK086(lu)003:326: 'jig rten pa yi yang dag lta //
NK086(lu)003:327: chen po gang la yod gyur pa //
NK086(lu)003:328: de ni tshe rabs stong du yang /
NK086(lu)003:331: de las ldog ste log par blta bas srog gcod
NK086(lu)003:332: spangs pa sogs dge ba'i las gzhan la spyad kyang
NK086(lu)003:333: 'bras bu sdug bsngal du smin par 'gyur te /
NK086(lu)003:335: gang zag log par blta bas legs spyad kyang //
NK086(lu)003:336: thams cad rnam par smin pa mi bzad ldan //
NK086(lu)003:337: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir yang dag pa'i lta bas zin pa gal che'o //
NK086(lu)003:339: mi dge bcu spong ba'i tshul khrims las gzhan med do //
NK086(lu)003:340: de ltar na snga ma las /
NK086(lu)003:341: gso sbyong 'dod spyod lha lus yid 'ong ba //
NK086(lu)003:342: skyes pa bud med dag la stsol bar bgyi //
NK086(lu)003:343: zhes lha'i go 'phang bgrod par byed pa la yang
NK086(lu)003:344: dag par blangs pa las byung ba'i tshul khrims dgos
NK086(lu)003:345: par ma bshad dam zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:347: 'on kyang de ni khyad par can gyi dbang du byas nas gsungs kyi /
NK086(lu)003:348: tsam po la ni dgos par ma nges te /
NK086(lu)003:349: yang dag pa'i lta bas zin pa'i dge bcu'i las
NK086(lu)003:350: lam 'khor bcas kyis 'grub par bzhed pa'i phyir ro
NK086(lu)003:351: // gzhan yang nyer len gyi phung po la gtsang ba la sogs pa 'dzin cing /
NK086(lu)003:352: ngo tsha khrel yod kyis kun nas bslangs te lus
NK086(lu)003:353: ngag gi bya ba tshul dang mthun par sgrub pa
NK086(lu)003:354: la skye bo dam pa'am ya rabs dang /
NK086(lu)003:355: de las ldog pa la skye bo ngan pa'am ma rab zhes bya ste /
NK086(lu)003:356: lugs kyi bstan bcos dam pa'i rgyan las /
NK086(lu)003:357: bkur bar 'os pa legs bkur zhing //
NK086(lu)003:358: mgon med rnams la lhag par byams //
NK086(lu)003:359: byas la drin lan mi brjed pa //
NK086(lu)003:360: dam pa rnams kyi mdzad spyod yin //
NK086(lu)003:361: ngo tsha dor ba'i 'tsho ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:362: sdig dang 'dres pa'i longs spyod dang //
NK086(lu)003:363: mdza' bo bslu pa'i mnga' thang bas //
NK086(lu)003:366: skye bo ngan pa sdig la dga' //byas la drin du mi gzo ba //
NK086(lu)003:367: ngo tsha dgra bo bzhin du 'dor //
NK086(lu)003:368: rang don 'grub na ci yang byed //
NK086(lu)003:371: dkon mchog gsum la dad pa skyo ngal med par byed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:372: don dam par dam pa'i chos btsal ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:373: gtsug lag bzang po la mkhas par slob pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:374: ci la'ang dran zhing tshod zin par bya ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:375: ma bcol ba'i las la rtogs 'dod mi byed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:376: mig mtho sar blta zhing gong ma rnams kyi rjes bsnyeg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:377: dus gsum pha ma la drin lan bslan pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:378: phu nu dang pha tshan nang du shong yangs che ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:379: rim pas rgan pa la gzhon pas bkur sti bya ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:380: khyim mtshes la byams par bya ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:381: gnyen grogs kyi dge bshes la dka' las kyis phan 'dogs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:382: srid kyis 'brel ba'i nye rigs la chab gang mthar dbyung ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:383: rig byed bzo la mkhas pas gzhan la phan pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:384: ltos pa'i mi drin gyis skyabs 'og tu gzhug pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:385: ngan byed kyi gros bkag nas rgyal khams bde yangs kyi gros gzhi 'ding ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:386: las chos la gtad de phyi mar bu smad kyis byang chub kyi gzhi thob par bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:387: zhes gsungs pa ltar mi chos gtsang ma bcu drug la bslab pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:389: rang gi 'bras bu 'byin nus kyi bar du goms par byed pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:391: zag pa dang bcas pa'i dge bcu'i las lam 'khor bcas la spyod pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:392: de ni mi dge bcu spangs pa'i cha nas btags so //
NK086(lu)003:393: gzhan yang lus kyi las phyag sogs dang /
NK086(lu)003:394: ngag gi bstod pa sogs dang /
NK086(lu)003:395: yid kyi gzhan la phan 'dod kyi sems dge ba la sogs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:396: 'o na he ru ka gal por /
NK086(lu)003:397: lha ma'i theg pa'i skabs su yi ge 'dri mchod
NK086(lu)003:398: sogs chos spyod bcu la spyod dgos par gsungs pa
NK086(lu)003:400: 'dir yang sngar ltar khyad par can dang tsam po'i khyad do //
NK086(lu)003:402: dge ba'i las stobs che chung gis /
NK086(lu)003:404: 'dod lha rigs drug ste 'dod khams kyi mtho ris gnas bcur skye ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:405: de ltar yang rgyas pa las /
NK086(lu)003:406: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge sbong byed pa //
NK086(lu)003:407: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK086(lu)003:409: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim las /
NK086(lu)003:410: dge bcu dag la gtsor len cing //
NK086(lu)003:411: dge dang mi dge mi mnyam pas //
NK086(lu)003:412: lha dang mi yi skye gnas te //
NK086(lu)003:415: de'ang 'di'i 'dod pa'i bde ba mthar thug pa mi'i 'khor los sgyur rgyal dang /
NK086(lu)003:416: lha'i gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi bdag po'i bar du bgrod pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:417: lang gshegs su bgrod bya'i gtso bo'i sgras smos te lha'i theg pa zhes gsungs so //
NK086(lu)003:418: theg pa 'di ni lam rim las /
NK086(lu)003:419: gzhi yi theg pa'i dang por gzhag /ces pa ltar
NK086(lu)003:420: theg pa thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa'am sngon du
NK086(lu)003:422: gang yang dag pa'i lta bas ma zin pa dang
NK086(lu)003:423: dngos gzhi dge bcu'i las lam la mi spyod pa'i
NK086(lu)003:424: theg pa ni gang na'ang med pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:426: dge ba bcu las brtsam nas ni //
NK086(lu)003:427: de yi chos ni rab tu dbye //
NK086(lu)003:431: zhes gsungs pa'i tshangs pa ni tshangs ris la sogs pa gsum kho na ma yin gyi /
NK086(lu)003:432: brah+ma'i sgra las tshangs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:435: 'dod pa'i nyon mongs pas gtsang ba'am dag cing tshangs pas na /
NK086(lu)003:436: sgra yangs pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK086(lu)003:437: khams gong ma'i lha gzugs khams gnas ris bcu bdun dang /
NK086(lu)003:438: gzugs med khams pa'i gnas bzhi ste nyi shu rtsa
NK086(lu)003:439: gcig po thams cad la tshangs pa'i sgras brjod cing
NK086(lu)003:440: / der bgrod pa'i lam 'khor bcas la tshangs pa'i theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:442: rang rang gi sa 'og ma la rags par blta zhing /
NK086(lu)003:443: rang sa la zhib par blta ba'i lhag mthong bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis /
NK086(lu)003:444: sa 'og ma'i nyon mongs pa spangs pa zhig gong mar skye bar gsungs pas /
NK086(lu)003:445: rang rang gi sa 'og ma la chags pa bral
NK086(lu)003:446: byed kyi lam bsam gtan bzhi dang gzugs med pa'i
NK086(lu)003:447: snyoms 'jug bzhi'i dngos gzhi gang rung zhig ma thob
NK086(lu)003:448: na gong mar mi skye ba'i phyir bsam gzugs gnyis
NK086(lu)003:449: ni tshangs pa'i theg pa dngos dang /
NK086(lu)003:451: 'jig rten pa'i mngon shes lnga ni tshangs theg gi
NK086(lu)003:452: yon tan khyad par can gyi lam du bzhed do
NK086(lu)003:455: 'jug sgo dang tshul khrims mi dge bcu spong ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:456: spyod pa dge bcu la spyod pa sngar ltar gyi steng du /
NK086(lu)003:457: byams snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms te tshad med bzhi la spyod pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:462: 'dod pa'i tshor ba las yid 'byung ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi bsam gtan bzhi ste /
NK086(lu)003:464: rtog pa dang bcas shing dpyod pa dang bcas pa ni bsam gtan dang po'o //
NK086(lu)003:465: rtog pa med la dpyod pa tsam dang bcas pa ni bsam gtan gnyis pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:466: rtog pa yang med dpyod pa yang med pa'i yid la byed pa ni bsam gtan gsum pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:467: dga' ba sdud pa yid la byed pa ni bsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:470: bsam gtan bzhi'i 'du shes la yid 'byung ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi snyoms 'jug bzhi ste /
NK086(lu)003:471: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched kyi /
NK086(lu)003:472: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched kyi /
NK086(lu)003:473: ci yang med pa'i skye mched kyi /
NK086(lu)003:474: 'du shes med 'du shes med min gyi skye mched
NK086(lu)003:475: kyi snyoms 'jug ste srid rtse'i lam mthar thug pa'o
NK086(lu)003:476: // de dag kyang rgyas pa las /
NK086(lu)003:477: tshad med bzhi spyod mi g.yo sgom byed pa //
NK086(lu)003:478: tshangs gnas la sogs skye ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK086(lu)003:484: bsam gtan dang po'i dngos gzhi chung 'bring che gsum
NK086(lu)003:485: du sgoms pa las tshangs ris sogs gsum du skye
NK086(lu)003:487: so skye'i gnas bcu gnyis po la 'gre zhing /
NK086(lu)003:488: bzhi pa la 'phags pa'i zag med shes rab sbel
NK086(lu)003:489: zhing rim pa lngar bsgoms na mi che ba sogs
NK086(lu)003:490: gtsang gnas lngar skye ba yin no //
NK086(lu)003:491: de'ang gzugs la chags bral ma thob cing bsam gtan gyi ro la chags pas 'khor te /
NK086(lu)003:493: tshad med bzhi dang bsam gtan bzhi //
NK086(lu)003:494: rim las so sor bdag 'dzin cing //
NK086(lu)003:495: gzugs rnams kun la bdag tu rtog /
NK086(lu)003:496: 'di ni tshangs gnas rim par skye //
NK086(lu)003:499: lhag mthong gi shes rab kyi dben pas ming bzhi
NK086(lu)003:500: la ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bdag tu bzung
NK086(lu)003:501: bas gzugs med kyi lhar skye ste /
NK086(lu)003:503: mnyam dang gzugs med ma rtogs nas /
NK086(lu)003:504: ming bzhi med par ma shes te //
NK086(lu)003:505: skye mched bzhi la gnas gyur na //
NK086(lu)003:506: srid pa'i rtse mo'i sa ru skye //
NK086(lu)003:508: gsum pa 'phros don ma rtogs log rtogs kyi lta ba bshad pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:509: 'di la sngon gyi slob dpon rnams dgongs pa cung mi mthun te /
NK086(lu)003:510: slob dpon nyi 'od seng ge ni ma rtogs pa phyal rgyang mur stug gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:511: log par rtogs pa mu stegs par bzhed /
NK086(lu)003:512: slob dpon sgeg rdor ni ma rtogs pa phyal pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:513: log par rtogs pa mu stegs rtag chad gnyis la bzhed /
NK086(lu)003:515: ma rtogs phyal pa rgyang 'phen dang //
NK086(lu)003:516: log rtogs mur stug mu stegs dang //
NK086(lu)003:518: slob dpon chen po pad+ma'i man ngag lta phreng las kyang de ltar 'byung bas /
NK086(lu)003:519: 'dir yang de bzhin du 'chad pa la /
NK086(lu)003:521: log par rtogs pa gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:523: go ba dang dbye ba gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:525: so so skye bo grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba'i gang zag go //
NK086(lu)003:529: dang po ma rtogs pa dngos ni /
NK086(lu)003:535: las rgyu 'bras ye ma rtogs pas kun tu rmongs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:537: rten 'byung rgyu 'bras kyi chos yod med gang du'ang
NK086(lu)003:538: mi spyod cing spong len mi byed pa'i phyir phyal
NK086(lu)003:541: cir yang ma rtogs pa ni 'jig rten phyal pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:547: yon tan la thob blo med pa'i blo 'phang smad pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:550: gnyis pa zhar las byung ba'i ma rtogs pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:554: tshe snga phyi yod med du ma rtogs shing tshe
NK086(lu)003:555: gcig gi phan bde bag tsam sgrub pa'i blo can
NK086(lu)003:557: phyi ma rgyang du bor te tshe 'di'i btsan phyug
NK086(lu)003:558: dang mthu stobs sogs 'jig rten pa'i gsang tshig mo
NK086(lu)003:559: rmi rtsis sogs la brten nas bsgrubs pa'i phyir rgyang
NK086(lu)003:566: rkyen gyis chad pa gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:567: theg chen gyi grub mtha' 'dzin pas 'dod bya ma yin pas rgyas par gzhan las shes so //
NK086(lu)003:570: 'du shes can bzhi chags pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:571: gang la g.yeng dang ya nga can //
NK086(lu)003:572: mos pa can zhes grags pa bzhi //
NK086(lu)003:573: sa bon 'dzin pa'i zhing du snang //
NK086(lu)003:575: 'dod yul la chags sred 'bral mi phod pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:576: tshe 'di'i mi chos kyi bya bas g.yeng ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:577: btsan phyug sdig dang bsdos nas sgrub pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:578: mi dge bcu spong zhing thar pa la mos pa'i rigs can no //
NK086(lu)003:579: gnyis pa log par rtogs pa la /
NK086(lu)003:583: rten gyi gang zag gang zhig log pa'i grub mthas blo bsgyur ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:585: nang pa las phyi rol du gyur pa mu stegs
NK086(lu)003:586: pa'i slob dpon snga ma dag rtog ge sde lngar
NK086(lu)003:587: 'dod pa las / rtag lta sde bzhi'i dang po grangs can pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:588: skye dgu rnams tshe lo nyi khri pa'i dus su /
NK086(lu)003:589: drang srong ser skyas mu stegs pa'i dka' thub kyis
NK086(lu)003:590: grub pa thob ste bstan bcos mang du brtsams pas
NK086(lu)003:591: / grub mtha' 'dzin pa'i slob ma gnyis byung ste /
NK086(lu)003:594: b+ha ra d+h+aa dzas shes bya thams cad grangs nyi
NK086(lu)003:595: shu rtsa lngar 'dod pa'i rjes su 'brangs pa la
NK086(lu)003:597: chur lhung gi bus nyi shu rtsa lnga po'i gnas
NK086(lu)003:598: lugs kyang stong par 'dod pa las ser skya pa
NK086(lu)003:599: ste / ye shes snying po kun las btus pa las /
NK086(lu)003:600: grangs can pa rnams yon tan smra //
NK086(lu)003:601: ser skya pa rnams stong par 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:605: yon tan gsum pa zhes bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:606: gnyis pa dbang phyug pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:607: lha dbang phyug gi rgyud sde mang du gsungs pas /
NK086(lu)003:608: dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob ma gnyis byung ste /
NK086(lu)003:611: rkang mig gis brtsams pa rigs pa'i lta ba la brten pa'i rigs pa can dang /
NK086(lu)003:612: gzeg zan gyis brtsams pa'i bye brag gsal ba la brten pa'i bye brag pa gnyis so //
NK086(lu)003:613: 'dis sems can bcings grol thams cad dbang phyug gis byas par 'dod de /
NK086(lu)003:614: 'gro ba 'di dag shes pa yod min te //
NK086(lu)003:615: bdag gi bde sdug bdag la rang dbang med //
NK086(lu)003:616: dbang phyug gis btang yang na g.yang sa'am //
NK086(lu)003:617: mtho ris dag tu 'gro ba kho nar 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:623: khyab 'jug gis rigs byed kyi bstan bcos 'bum ste brtsams shing /
NK086(lu)003:624: lte ba pad+mo'i skye gnas las tshangs pa gdong bzhi pa byung ste /
NK086(lu)003:625: des snod bcud thams cad sprul nas /
NK086(lu)003:629: rig byed chen po bzhi dran nas bshad pa phyis drang srong rnams kyis bsdus te /
NK086(lu)003:630: khyab 'jug gi bstan bcos brda sprod ngag gi 'od zer la brten pa brda sprod pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:631: drang srong ag+na'i smra ba'i mtshon cha la brten pa'i tshad ma pa la rnam phug pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:632: drang srong bden smras kyi bsgom rim skor dgu la
NK086(lu)003:633: brten pa'i sgom sgrub pa la gsang ba pa dang
NK086(lu)003:634: / drang srong ngan slong gi rnam dpyod gsal ba
NK086(lu)003:635: la brten pa'i gzhung bshad pa la spyod pa ba
NK086(lu)003:636: / dang / drang srong rgyun shes kyi bu la
NK086(lu)003:637: sogs pa'i tsa ra ka 'bum sde la brten pa'i
NK086(lu)003:638: gso dpyad pa la tsa ra ka ba zhes bya
NK086(lu)003:639: / dang / ste lnga'o // 'di dag gis rigs byed bzhi tshad mar 'dod de /
NK086(lu)003:642: rigs byed pa zhes grags so //
NK086(lu)003:643: bzhi pa rgyal ba pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:644: lha chen po rgyal ba dam pas /
NK086(lu)003:645: srog dang zad pa sdom pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:646: nges par dga' dang 'chi dang las //
NK086(lu)003:647: sdig dang bsod nams thar pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:648: shes bya tshig gi don dgur nges //
NK086(lu)003:649: zhes tshig don rgyan gyi snang ba la brten pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:650: thar pa mdog dbyibs can dang /
NK086(lu)003:651: shing sems pa can du 'dod de /
NK086(lu)003:656: lnga pa chad lta sde gcig ni /
NK086(lu)003:657: sum cu rtsa gsum du phur bu la brten nas grub pa thob pa lha'i bla mas /
NK086(lu)003:658: lha rnams lha ma yin la 'thab pa la spro ba bskyed ba'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:659: thams cad la skur pa 'debs pa lta ba'i snying po zhes bya ba'i bstan bcos brtsams pa /
NK086(lu)003:660: phyis mi yul du grogs mkhar bas dar bar byas te /
NK086(lu)003:662: bzang mo ma shi bar la dga' mgur spyod //
NK086(lu)003:663: shi nas de yi spyod yul min //
NK086(lu)003:664: lus kyang thal ba bzhin song nas //
NK086(lu)003:665: slar skye ba dag ga la srid //
NK086(lu)003:666: ces skye ba snga phyi la skur pa 'debs shing /
NK086(lu)003:667: ji tsam dbang po'i spyod yul ba //
NK086(lu)003:668: skyes bu'ang de tsam kho nar zad //
NK086(lu)003:669: kye ma mang thos gang smra ba //
NK086(lu)003:670: slu byed spyang ki'i rjes dang mtshungs //
NK086(lu)003:671: zhes ma mthong ba'i 'gro ba la skur ba 'debs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:672: blo ni lus kyi bdag nyid dang /
NK086(lu)003:673: lus 'bras lus kyi yon tan dang /
NK086(lu)003:674: 'di ltar lugs gsum la brten nas //
NK086(lu)003:675: goms pa srid pa yod ma yin //
NK086(lu)003:676: ces lam goms pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas la skur pa 'debs dang /
NK086(lu)003:677: sgro btags 'dzin phyir tshad ma min //
NK086(lu)003:678: ces tshad ma la skur pa 'debs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:679: pad+ma'i ge sar su yis byas //
NK086(lu)003:680: rma bya'i ri mo su yis bris //
NK086(lu)003:681: tsher rtse rno ba su yis bdar //
NK086(lu)003:682: thams cad rgyu med ngo bos byung //
NK086(lu)003:683: zhes rgyu 'bras la skur pa 'debs pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:687: nam mkha'i yid can pa zhes so //
NK086(lu)003:688: ma rtogs log rtogs kyi lta ba bzhi po de
NK086(lu)003:689: ni ma rig pa kho na las byung ba'i phyir
NK086(lu)003:692: 'jig rten gyi khams na sems can phyin ci log
NK086(lu)003:693: gi lta ba grangs med pa'i mdo rnam pa bzhir
NK086(lu)003:699: 'di dag ni ma rig pa'i lta ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:701: de la ma rtogs pa gnyis ni grub mtha'i lta ba ma yin mod kyi /
NK086(lu)003:702: 'on kyang sems kyi gnas tshul bsdu ba'i phyir de'i zla la bshad do //
NK086(lu)003:703: log par rtogs pa'i lta ba gnyis ni grub mthas blo bsgyur ba'i lta ba yin kyang /
NK086(lu)003:704: chos nyid mtha' dang bral ba sgro skur gyi mthar zhen pas log par bsgyur ba'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:705: 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i thabs ma yin te /
NK086(lu)003:706: grub mtha' smra ba rnams kyi nang nas tha chad pa mur stug par ma zad /
NK086(lu)003:707: mu stegs pa'ang bdag 'dod pas 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bdag 'dzin gyis bcings pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:709: ji srid bdag la mngon chags pa //
NK086(lu)003:713: rtag chad gnyis la gang gis blo zhen pa //
NK086(lu)003:714: don gyi snying po nyid las gol bar gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:716: skabs 'dir rang rang gi 'dod gzhung sogs ma bris te /
NK086(lu)003:717: shes par 'dod na gzhan du blta bar bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:718: 'dir kha cig rgyal ba'i bka'i dbye ba 'chad pa'i
NK086(lu)003:719: skabs su phyi rol pa'i grub mtha' sogs 'chad pa
NK086(lu)003:720: ni shin tu mi rigs pa nyid do zhe na
NK086(lu)003:722: mu stegs rang rgyud pa'i dbang du byas na lam
NK086(lu)003:723: gyi ltung sa dang spang bya ngo shes nas 'das
NK086(lu)003:724: pa'i theg pa rang lam las mi 'gyangs pa'i dgos
NK086(lu)003:726: he ru ka gal bo las /
NK086(lu)003:727: mu stegs theg pa rab nges na //
NK086(lu)003:728: mi spyod spang phyir khyod la bshad //
NK086(lu)003:730: yang sprul pa pa'i dbang du byas nas //
NK086(lu)003:731: sngar gyi dgos pa dang ldan par ma zad kyi /
NK086(lu)003:732: 'di dag kyang gang la gang 'dul gyi rgyal ba'i phrin las yin par gsungs pa'i phyir te /
NK086(lu)003:733: byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje chos kyis mdzad pa'i
NK086(lu)003:734: bde 'dus kyi thugs rje dpyang thag gnas kyi lung
NK086(lu)003:735: las / thugs rje'i 'jug pa sna tshogs pas //
NK086(lu)003:737: phyi rol byed pa'i sde rnams la //
NK086(lu)003:738: de dang der snang ston pas gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:741: chad lta mur stug pa'i lta ba ni shin tu
NK086(lu)003:742: ya nga ba'i log lta yin pas de lta bu
NK086(lu)003:743: bskyed pa rgyal ba'i thabs mkhas su ji ltar rigs
NK086(lu)003:744: snyam na / de'ang rigs pa nyid de /
NK086(lu)003:745: mur stug pa'ang rigs pa du ma khas len pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:747: thal 'gyur rnam dag 'god mkhan gyi rgol ba dang 'phrad pa'i tshe /
NK086(lu)003:749: de rjes ldog phyogs kyi sgrub byed rnam dag mthong
NK086(lu)003:750: nas yang dag pa'i tshad ma skye bar 'gyur bas
NK086(lu)003:751: na / grub mtha' la ye ma zhugs pa'i blun
NK086(lu)003:752: po las yang dag pa'i lta ba skye ba la
NK086(lu)003:754: yang 'di dag lha mi'i theg pa las 'phros te 'chad pa gang zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:755: lha dang mi'i theg pa gnyis kyis bgrod par byed
NK086(lu)003:756: pa'i rten gyi gang zag ni phyi nang gnyis ka
NK086(lu)003:757: la yod pa'i phyir smos te /
NK086(lu)003:758: phyi pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK086(lu)003:760: khyod kyi bstan la mi phyogs pa'i //
NK086(lu)003:761: skye bo ma rig gis ldongs pa //
NK086(lu)003:762: srid rtsi'i bar du song nas kyang //
NK086(lu)003:763: sdug bsngal yang 'byung srid pa bsgrub //
NK086(lu)003:765: nang pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK086(lu)003:766: dkon mchog gsum la bya ba byed par mos pa'i
NK086(lu)003:767: sgo nas skyabs su 'dzin yang thar pa don gnyer
NK086(lu)003:768: gyi blo med par 'jig rten pa'i lam nyid la
NK086(lu)003:769: gnas pa'i dbang du mdzad de /
NK086(lu)003:771: mos pa rnams kyi dbang mdzad nas //
NK086(lu)003:772: skyabs gsum rnam par bzhag pa yin //
NK086(lu)003:774: gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa bshad pa la gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:775: phyi rol pa las 'phags pa'i tshul /
NK086(lu)003:776: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par 'chad pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:778: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las skyob par byed pa myang 'das dam pa'i chos te /
NK086(lu)003:779: de ni chos thams cad kyi rab dang /
NK086(lu)003:781: phul du gyur cing gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas na dam pa zhes pa'i sgras brjod pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:782: de'ang dkon mchog gsum skyabs gnas su bzung nas /
NK086(lu)003:783: lta ba bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi khas len pa'am /
NK086(lu)003:785: yang dag pa'i bslab pa gsum la slob pas /
NK086(lu)003:786: 'bras bu srid rtse las brgal nus pas 'phags te /
NK086(lu)003:787: phyi rol pa'i lam na de dag med pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:788: de la skyabs 'gro ni lam gyi gzhi rten la med du mi rung ste /
NK086(lu)003:789: de sdom pa'i rgyu myang 'das kyi bsam pa rten byed nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:790: skyabs su ma song ba la sdom pa mi skye la /
NK086(lu)003:791: sdom pas ma bsdams na yang dag pa'i lam med pa'i phyir te /
NK086(lu)003:793: dge bsnyen gsum la skyabs 'gro ba //
NK086(lu)003:794: de ni sdom brgyad rtsa ba yin //
NK086(lu)003:796: sdom pa kun la yong mod kyi //
NK086(lu)003:797: skyabs su ma song ba la med //
NK086(lu)003:800: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pa /
NK086(lu)003:801: zag bcas thams cad sdug bsngal ba /
NK086(lu)003:802: chos thams cad bdag med pa /
NK086(lu)003:803: mya ngan las 'das pa zhi ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:804: bslab pa gsum la slob pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:807: shes rab gsum la thos bsam bsgom gsum gyi sgo
NK086(lu)003:808: nas bslabs pas thog mtha' bar gsum du dge ba
NK086(lu)003:810: bslab pa gsum ni rab ston cing /
NK086(lu)003:811: phyag rgya gsum dang yang dag ldan /
NK086(lu)003:812: thog ma bar dang mthar dge ba //
NK086(lu)003:813: sangs rgyas gsung du mkhas pas rtogs //
NK086(lu)003:815: 'bras bu srid rtse las brgal nus pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:817: khyod kyi bstan pa'i rjes 'gro ba //
NK086(lu)003:818: bsam gtan dngos gzhi ma thob kyang //
NK086(lu)003:819: bdud kyi mig ras btsa' bzhin du //
NK086(lu)003:820: srid pa dag ni ldog par bgyid //
NK086(lu)003:822: gnyis pa de'i rang bzhin rgyas par 'chad pa la gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:824: ston pa'i dam chos rnam gnyis te //
NK086(lu)003:825: lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK086(lu)003:827: brjod bya rtogs pa'i chos dang /
NK086(lu)003:828: rjod byed lung gi chos so //
NK086(lu)003:829: dang po rtogs pa'i chos la'ang gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:830: 'phags pa rnams gang du gshegs pa'i 'gogs bden bsam
NK086(lu)003:831: brjod kyi yul las brgal ba'i myang 'das chen po
NK086(lu)003:832: gnyis snang gi mtshan ma thams cad nub pa'i dbyings
NK086(lu)003:833: su snyoms par zhugs pa rtogs pa'i yon tan gyis
NK086(lu)003:834: thob pa gang yin pa de dang /
NK086(lu)003:835: gang gis gshegs pa'i lam bden rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK086(lu)003:836: par dag pa'i 'od gsal ba'i snying po can so
NK086(lu)003:837: so rang gis rig par bya ba'i spyod yul sgrib
NK086(lu)003:838: pa'i gnyen por gyur pa'i zag med kyi ye shes
NK086(lu)003:839: 'khor bcas rtogs pa'i ngo bor gyur pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:840: snga ma ni 'phags bzhi'i thugs rgyud kyi spang bya
NK086(lu)003:841: spangs pa'i zad mi skye'i ye shes te chags bral
NK086(lu)003:843: phyi ma ni gang gis spong byed chags pa dang
NK086(lu)003:844: bral bar byed pa'i gnyen po'i ye shes kyi rang
NK086(lu)003:845: bzhin te / 'phags pa ma pham pas /
NK086(lu)003:846: bsam med gnyis med rtog med pa //
NK086(lu)003:847: dag gsal gnyen po'i phyogs nyid kyis //
NK086(lu)003:848: gang zhig gang gis chags bral ba //
NK086(lu)003:849: bden gnyis mtshan nyid can de chos //
NK086(lu)003:850: chags bral nyid ni 'gog pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:851: lam gyi bden par dag gis bsdus //
NK086(lu)003:853: gnyis pa rjod byed lung gi chos la'ang gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:854: legs par gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK086(lu)003:855: de'i dgongs pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos so //
NK086(lu)003:856: dang po la gsum gyis 'chad de /
NK086(lu)003:860: dang po bka'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK086(lu)003:861: rang gi thun mong ma yin pa'i bdag rkyen ston
NK086(lu)003:862: pa sangs rgyas la brten nas byung ba'i khyad par
NK086(lu)003:863: bzhi lngan gyi rgyal ba'i gsung rab gang zhig mdo
NK086(lu)003:865: de dang lung gi chos 'khor don gcig ming gi rnam grangs so //
NK086(lu)003:867: brjod bya don dang ldan pa /
NK086(lu)003:868: brjod byed ngag tshig dri ma med pa /
NK086(lu)003:869: byed las khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa spong ba /
NK086(lu)003:870: 'bras bu zhi ba'i phan yon ston pa dang bzhir lhag bsam bskur ba'i mdo las gsungs pa ltar /
NK086(lu)003:872: gang zhig don ldan chos dang nyer 'brel zhing //
NK086(lu)003:873: khams gsum kun nas nyon mongs spong byed gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:874: zhi ba'i phan yon ston par mdzad pa gang //
NK086(lu)003:875: de ni drang srong gsung yin bzlog pa gzhan //
NK086(lu)003:877: yang brjod bya bslab pa gsum ston /
NK086(lu)003:878: rjod byed ngag tshig dri med /
NK086(lu)003:879: sgrub byed tshad ma gsum ldan /
NK086(lu)003:880: 'bras bu thog mtha' bar gsum du dge ba dang bzhir bshad de /
NK086(lu)003:881: bslab pa gsum ston ngag tshig dri ma med //
NK086(lu)003:882: tshad ma gsum ldan thog mtha' bar dge ba //
NK086(lu)003:883: de ni chen por gsungs pa rgyal pa'i bka' //ldog pa gzhan gyi gzhung du shes par bya //
NK086(lu)003:885: gnyis pa bka'i sgra don ni /
NK086(lu)003:886: su b+h+aa shi ta zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK086(lu)003:891: legs ba lnga la 'jug pa las 'dir legs pa /
NK086(lu)003:892: b+h+aa shi ta gsungs pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:893: legs par gsungs pas na bka'o //
NK086(lu)003:894: ji ltar legs par gsungs snyam na /
NK086(lu)003:897: ji ltar legs par gsungs pa yin zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:898: rnam pa bcu dag gis te /
NK086(lu)003:899: yang dag par bslang ba nyid kyis dang /
NK086(lu)003:900: dbang du mdzad pa nyid kyis dang /
NK086(lu)003:902: rab tu bstan pa nyid kyis dang /
NK086(lu)003:903: rab tu dbye ba nyid kyis dang /
NK086(lu)003:905: ko bar mdzad pa nyid kyis dang /
NK086(lu)003:908: yon tan yongs su 'dzin pa nyid kyis so //
NK086(lu)003:910: gsum pa bka'i dbye ba la lnga /
NK086(lu)003:915: dbang po'i sgo nas dbye ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:916: dang po bdag rkyen gyi sgo nas dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:917: zhal nas gsungs pa dang byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:918: rjes su gnang ba'i bka' dang gsum las /
NK086(lu)003:919: dang po zhal nas gsungs pa la'ang gnyis kyi /
NK086(lu)003:920: ston pas mdun bsus nas gsungs pa ni sdud pa lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:921: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor bzhi po de
NK086(lu)003:922: dag yang dag par rab tu dga' bar mdzad pa'i
NK086(lu)003:923: phyir / yang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di ston cing /
NK086(lu)003:924: de'i tshe chigs su bcad pa 'di dag bka' stsal to //
NK086(lu)003:926: 'khor gyis zhus nas gsungs pa ni 'jam dpal mtshan brjod lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:927: rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK086(lu)003:929: dpag med rnams kyis dgyes pa yis //
NK086(lu)003:930: rab gsungs gang lags bshad du gsol //
NK086(lu)003:932: gnyis pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' la gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:933: ston pa'i phyag rdo rje snying po dang rnam grol
NK086(lu)003:934: zla ba'i spyi bor bzhag pas 'chad pa dang zhu
NK086(lu)003:935: ba'i spobs pa skyes nas mdo sde sa bcu pa
NK086(lu)003:936: gsungs pa lta bu skus byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka'
NK086(lu)003:938: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po
NK086(lu)003:939: rnams kyi shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa
NK086(lu)003:940: las brtsams te / ji ltar byang chub sems dpa'
NK086(lu)003:941: sems dpa' chen po rnams shes rab kyi pha rol
NK086(lu)003:942: tu phyin pa las nges par 'byung bar 'gyur ba
NK086(lu)003:943: de bzhin du khyod spobs par byos shig /ces gsungs
NK086(lu)003:944: pas rab 'byor gyis brgyad stong par sher phyin bshad
NK086(lu)003:945: pa lta bu gsung gis byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka'
NK086(lu)003:946: las brtsams te / dang / thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' la gsum las /
NK086(lu)003:947: ston pas zab mo snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK086(lu)003:948: mnyam par bzhag pa'i mthus sh+aa ri'i bu dang spyan
NK086(lu)003:949: ras gzigs gnyis kyis dri ba dri lan gyi sgo
NK086(lu)003:950: nas gsungs pa sher snying lta bu thugs ting nge
NK086(lu)003:951: 'dzin gyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' dang /
NK086(lu)003:952: yang sangs rgyas kyi mthus nam mkha' dang bya dang
NK086(lu)003:953: ljon shing sogs las kyang chos kyi sgra byung bar
NK086(lu)003:954: lta bu thugs bden pa'i stobs kyis byin gyis brlabs
NK086(lu)003:955: pa'i bka' dang / sangs rgyas kyi mthus nyan thos
NK086(lu)003:956: dang gnod sbyin sogs kyis smras pa'i 'bras bu khyad
NK086(lu)003:957: par can 'byin nus kyi sngags tshig bkar bsdus pa
NK086(lu)003:958: lta bu thugs rje'i stobs kyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:959: pa'i bka' dang / bka' zhes bya'o // gsum pa rjes su gnang ba'i bka' ni /
NK086(lu)003:960: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:962: nga yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og tu bsdu ba byed pa'i tshe /
NK086(lu)003:963: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK086(lu)003:965: bar du mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig /mthar bcom ldan 'das
NK086(lu)003:966: kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do zhes bya
NK086(lu)003:967: ba'i bar gyis sdus shig /ces gdams pa bzhin du
NK086(lu)003:968: sdud pa po rnams kyis de ltar bcug pa'i ngag
NK086(lu)003:969: tshig rnams bkar bsdus pa lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:970: gnyis pa dus kyi sgo nas dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:973: gnyis pa mtshan nyid med pa'i /
NK086(lu)003:974: gsum pa don dam rnam par nges pa'i chos 'khor ro //
NK086(lu)003:975: gsum pa sde tshan gyi sgo nas dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:976: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis sam dgu ste /
NK086(lu)003:979: mdo sde dbyangs bsnyad lung bstan dang //
NK086(lu)003:980: tshig bcad ched brjod rtogs pa brjod //
NK086(lu)003:981: de lta byung dang gleng gzhi dang //
NK086(lu)003:982: shin tu rgyas dang skyes rabs bcas //
NK086(lu)003:983: gtan phab rmad du byung ba'i sde //
NK086(lu)003:984: de ltar rnam pa bcu gnyis ni //
NK086(lu)003:985: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis so //
NK086(lu)003:990: gtan la phab pa'i sde gsum ma gtogs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:991: de ltar yang tshig gsal las /
NK086(lu)003:992: sangs rgyas rnams kyi mdo sde la sogs pa //
NK086(lu)003:993: bden pa gnyis brten bstan pa rnam pa dgu //
NK086(lu)003:995: bcu gnyis po'ang sde snod gsum du 'du ste /
NK086(lu)003:997: mdo yi sde dang dbyangs su bsnyad pa'i sde //
NK086(lu)003:998: lung bstan tshigs su bcad pa'i sde dang ni //
NK086(lu)003:999: ched du brjod pa lnga ni mdo sder bsdus //
NK086(lu)003:1000: gleng gzhi'i sde dang rtogs pa brjod pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1001: de lta byung ba'i sde zhes bya ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:1002: skyes pa rabs dang bzhi ni 'dul bar bsdus //
NK086(lu)003:1003: shin tu rgyas dang rmad du byung ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:1004: gtan la phab pa gsum ni mngon par bsdus //
NK086(lu)003:1007: snga rabs phal cher zhig gis 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa
NK086(lu)003:1008: zhes bya ba rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las shin
NK086(lu)003:1009: tu rgyas pa chen po byang chub sems dpa'i sde
NK086(lu)003:1010: snod phal po che gsungs pas shin tu rgyas pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1012: mkhas pa snar ston seng ge 'od ni gtan la
NK086(lu)003:1013: phab pa'am rmad du byung ba'i sde yin gsungs so
NK086(lu)003:1014: // bzhi pa gnyen po'i sgo nas dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:1015: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong ste /
NK086(lu)003:1016: lha mo bzhis zhus pa las /
NK086(lu)003:1017: thub pa chen pos chos rnams kyi //
NK086(lu)003:1018: phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong la //
NK086(lu)003:1023: dug gsum cha mnyam las gyur pa nyi khri chig stong re re'i gnyen por 'dul ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:1026: rig pa 'dzin pa sngags kyi sde snod rnams nyi khri chig stong re re gsungs pa yin te /
NK086(lu)003:1027: mi zad pa'i gter bston pa las /
NK086(lu)003:1028: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang //
NK086(lu)003:1029: dug gsum cha mnyam spyod pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1030: nyi khri chig stong gnyen po ni //
NK086(lu)003:1031: chos kyi phung po de snyed gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:1033: de las gzhan du pan chen bi ba la mi tras rdzogs pa chen po dung yig can du /
NK086(lu)003:1034: sde snod las mngon pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:1035: zhes pas sngags mngon pa'i sde snod du bsdu bar mdzad pa ltar /
NK086(lu)003:1036: skyi nyi ma rdo rje sogs kyang mngon pa'i sde
NK086(lu)003:1037: snod la phyi nang gnyis las sngags nang gi mngon
NK086(lu)003:1039: slob dpon sh+aan+ti pa dang snar ston seng ge 'od
NK086(lu)003:1040: sogs zab mo'i don mdor bsdus te ston pas sngags
NK086(lu)003:1041: ni mdo sde'i sde snod de /
NK086(lu)003:1042: de kho na nyid bsdus pa'i rgyud las /
NK086(lu)003:1043: mdo sde 'di ni legs bshad pa //
NK086(lu)003:1046: mdo sde 'di ni nyan byed na //
NK086(lu)003:1048: rang lugs mngon pa dang mdo sder bsdu ba sogs
NK086(lu)003:1049: ni rgyud gzhung phyogs re ba dang bstun pa de
NK086(lu)003:1050: dang der 'jog par mdzad pa yin pas mi 'gal
NK086(lu)003:1051: yang / rgyud sde spyi'i dbang du byas na rig
NK086(lu)003:1052: pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod dam sde snod bzhi pa
NK086(lu)003:1053: zhes sde snod rkang thub pa gcig tu bzhag na
NK086(lu)003:1056: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:1057: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:1059: dpung bzang gi zhus pa las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:1060: bye ba phrag gsum dang ni 'bum phrag lnga //
NK086(lu)003:1061: rig 'dzin sde snod du ni rgyal bas gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:1063: yang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK086(lu)003:1064: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK086(lu)003:1067: de gsum ston byed nyan thos dang /
NK086(lu)003:1069: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod ces gsum du bsdu tshul gcig dang /
NK086(lu)003:1071: sde snod dag ni gsum mam gnyis kyang rung //
NK086(lu)003:1072: bsdus pa'i phyir te rgyu ni dgus 'dod do //
NK086(lu)003:1074: chos kyi phung po thams cad bsdu na 'dul ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:1076: mngon pa'i sde snod gsum mam /
NK086(lu)003:1078: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod de /
NK086(lu)003:1080: de la 'dir gsum du bsdu ba'i dbang du byas nas /
NK086(lu)003:1081: der grangs nges pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK086(lu)003:1082: rgyu dgus sde snod gsum du bzhag ste /
NK086(lu)003:1085: shes bya la ltos nas gsum gsum mo //
NK086(lu)003:1086: de la spang bya la ltos nas gsum du bzhag pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:1087: the tshom gyi gnyen por mdo sde /
NK086(lu)003:1088: mtha' gnyis la sbyor ba'i gnyen por 'dul ba /
NK086(lu)003:1089: rang lta mchog 'dzin gyi gnyen por mngon pa'i sde snod rnams gsungs /
NK086(lu)003:1090: bslab bya la ltos nas mdo sdes bslab pa gsum bshad /
NK086(lu)003:1091: 'dul bas lhag pa tshul khrims dang sems sgrub /
NK086(lu)003:1092: mngon pas lhag pa'i shes rab sgrub pa yin no //
NK086(lu)003:1093: shes bya la ltos nas chos dang don mdo sdes bshad /
NK086(lu)003:1095: mngon pas 'bel ba'i gtam rnams par gtan la dbab pa la mkhas par 'gyur ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:1096: rgyu dgu po 'dis sde snod gsum du bzhag la /
NK086(lu)003:1097: de ltar bzhag pa'i dgos pa'ang /
NK086(lu)003:1098: sde snod gsum la thos pas sems la bag chags 'jog /bsam pas don rtogs par byed /
NK086(lu)003:1099: bsgom pas zhi gnas kyis nyon mongs pa zhi zhing
NK086(lu)003:1100: lhag mthong gis de kho na nyid rab tu rtogs
NK086(lu)003:1101: pa'i sgo nas rnam par grol bar byed pa ste
NK086(lu)003:1103: de ni bag chags rtogs dang zhi ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:1104: rab tu rtogs pas rnam par grol bar byed //
NK086(lu)003:1107: s+au tra'i sgra las mgo smos pas na mdo zhes bya ste /
NK086(lu)003:1109: gnas rnams dang ni mtshan nyid dang //
NK086(lu)003:1110: chos don smos phyir mdo yin no //
NK086(lu)003:1112: a b+hi ni mngon pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:1113: mu khya la sogs pa'i yi ge gzhan bsnan pas mngon du gyur pa sogs su 'gyur te /
NK086(lu)003:1114: mngon du'i phyir dang yang yang phyir //
NK086(lu)003:1115: zil gnon rtogs phyir mngon pa'i chos //
NK086(lu)003:1117: bi na ya zhes pa 'dul ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:1118: yi ge dbre bsnan gyis ltung ba sogs su 'gyur bas /
NK086(lu)003:1119: ltung dang 'byung dang ldan pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1120: nges par 'byung dang gang zag dang //
NK086(lu)003:1121: bcas pa dang ni rab dbye dang //
NK086(lu)003:1122: rnam par nges phyir 'dul ba nyid //
NK086(lu)003:1124: sde snod ces pa bi ta ka'i sgra las drangs na bin+di ka bsdus pa'i gong bu dang /
NK086(lu)003:1125: bi ta ka pre bo che la 'jug pas shes bya'i don thams cad brjod byar bsdus pas sam /
NK086(lu)003:1126: 'di dag gi nang du brjod bya mang po 'dus pa'i phyir sde snod do //
NK086(lu)003:1127: lnga pa dbang po'i sgo nas dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:1128: spyir y+aa na'i sgra las theg pa zhes bya ba
NK086(lu)003:1129: bzhon pa la 'jug pa ltar 'dir lam gong nas
NK086(lu)003:1130: gong du bgrod par byed pas de dang 'dra ba'i
NK086(lu)003:1131: phyir theg pa'o // de ltar yang sdud pa las /
NK086(lu)003:1132: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen te //
NK086(lu)003:1133: dga' skyed bde ba mngon par thob byed theg pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1134: mchog /de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya
NK086(lu)003:1136: dbye na rnam grangs 'di kho nar nges zhes mtha' gcig tu nges pa bzung du med de /
NK086(lu)003:1137: gdul bya'i blo dang mtshams par sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes gang la gang 'dul du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:1138: de ltar yang lang+kara gshegs pa las /
NK086(lu)003:1139: sems can rnams ni yongs drang phyir //
NK086(lu)003:1140: theg pa mtha' dag ngas bshad de //
NK086(lu)003:1141: 'di zhes dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK086(lu)003:1143: de yang cung zad bsdus te brjod na /
NK086(lu)003:1145: theg pa gcig ste theg pa gsum du med //
NK086(lu)003:1146: ces pa lta bu la dgongs te mthar thug theg pa gcig tu sgrub pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1147: yang theg pa chung ngu dang chen po'i rgyu 'bras kyi dbye ba gnyis dang /
NK086(lu)003:1148: nyan rang byang sems kyi theg pa gsum mam /
NK086(lu)003:1150: kun 'byung 'dren dang dka' thub rig /dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:1153: theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la //
NK086(lu)003:1154: theg pa gcig gis 'bras bur gnas //
NK086(lu)003:1155: zhes rgyu'i theg pa gsum 'bras bu'i theg pa dang bcas bzhi dang /
NK086(lu)003:1156: yang de bzhi'i lam stegs su mngon mtho'i theg pa
NK086(lu)003:1157: gcig tu byas pa bsnan pas theg pa lnga ste
NK086(lu)003:1159: lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1160: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1161: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1162: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1163: bla na med pa'i theg pa /
NK086(lu)003:1165: yang kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa la nyan rang byang sems gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:1166: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa la bya spyod rnal 'byor gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:1167: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa la ma h+aa anu
NK086(lu)003:1168: a ti gsum du phye bas theg pa rim pa
NK086(lu)003:1170: yod ni gcig las med pa la //
NK086(lu)003:1171: byung ni theg pa dgu ru byung //
NK086(lu)003:1173: mdor na ji srid blo'i rim pa ma zad kyi
NK086(lu)003:1174: bar de srid du theg pa'i mthar la'ang thug pa
NK086(lu)003:1175: med pas bsam gyis mi khyab par gsungs te /
NK086(lu)003:1177: ji srid 'dul shes yod kyi bar //
NK086(lu)003:1178: theg pa'i mtha' yang thug pa med //
NK086(lu)003:1180: gang la brten nas 'gro ba'i lam dang gang gis
NK086(lu)003:1181: 'gro ba la sogs pa blo ngo bo nyid kyis
NK086(lu)003:1182: dag pa'i ngo nas theg pa zhes pa'ang dmigs su
NK086(lu)003:1183: med de / sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na //
NK086(lu)003:1184: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK086(lu)003:1186: kha cig gis rdo rje snying 'grel du /
NK086(lu)003:1187: sangs rgyas pa la bzhi pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1188: lnga pa thub pa'i dgongs pa min //
NK086(lu)003:1189: zhes gsungs pa'i don gyis theg pa gsum las grangs gzhan mi 'thad par dam 'cha' yang /
NK086(lu)003:1190: lung de'i don ni nyan rang dang byang chub sems
NK086(lu)003:1191: dpa'i theg par gsang sngags kyang don gyis bsdus nas
NK086(lu)003:1192: skabs der spyi tsam du de ltar bstan nas /
NK086(lu)003:1193: bye brag tu sangs rgyas pa la zhes pa'i tshig
NK086(lu)003:1194: gi nus pas phyi rol lta ba la log pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1195: rtsa ba'i grub mtha' lnga sogs grangs mtshungs 'gog pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1196: ched du dgos dbang gis de skad gsungs pa yin
NK086(lu)003:1197: la / gal te theg pa gsum las grangs gzhan nges par 'gog pa yin na /
NK086(lu)003:1199: lha yi theg dang tshangs pa'i theg /nyan thos kyi dang de bzhin du //
NK086(lu)003:1200: de bzhin gshegs dang rang rgyal gyi //
NK086(lu)003:1201: theg pa de dag ngas bshad do //
NK086(lu)003:1202: zhes theg pa lngar gsungs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1204: theg pa sna tshogs thabs tshul gyis //
NK086(lu)003:1205: 'gro ba'i don la brtson pa po //
NK086(lu)003:1206: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK086(lu)003:1207: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK086(lu)003:1208: zhes gsungs pa'i theg pa gcig 'di gang la ngos 'dzin /
NK086(lu)003:1209: nyan rang 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba gang
NK086(lu)003:1210: zhig gdod theg chen gyi bsam sbyor rgyud la skyes
NK086(lu)003:1211: nas rnam mkhyen sgrub pa la bsams na mi rung
NK086(lu)003:1212: ste / theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung zhes bshad pa'i phyir dang /
NK086(lu)003:1213: byang chub sems dpa' mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung
NK086(lu)003:1214: bas rgyu'i theg chen rang lam gyis sangs rgyas 'phags
NK086(lu)003:1215: pa'i go 'phang mngon du byed pa la bsams na
NK086(lu)003:1216: theg pa gsum gyi rjes su theg pa gcig bkar
NK086(lu)003:1217: nas gsungs pa la don gyis dben par 'gyur te
NK086(lu)003:1219: gnas skabs su theg pa du ma'i rnam gzhag mdzad
NK086(lu)003:1220: pa'ang de dang de'i gnas skabs dang gtso che chung
NK086(lu)003:1221: dbang gis gdul bya drang ba'i thabs su bstan nas
NK086(lu)003:1222: / de rnams rang rang gi lam gyi 'bras bu
NK086(lu)003:1223: rjes mthun re thob tu zin kyang da dung de'i
NK086(lu)003:1224: gong du sangs rgyas thams cad kyis gang du bgrod
NK086(lu)003:1225: pa gcig pa'i lam rdo rje'i theg pa mchog bstan
NK086(lu)003:1226: du yod pa la dgongs pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:1227: gzhan rnams de nyid la bkri ba'i lam stegs tsam
NK086(lu)003:1228: du bstan cing rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi bar du
NK086(lu)003:1229: bgrod bya'i lam rnams skas kyi gdang bu ltar gnas
NK086(lu)003:1231: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK086(lu)003:1232: skas kyi gdang bu lta bur bstan //
NK086(lu)003:1235: drang srong rnams kyi theg pa gsum bstan pa //
NK086(lu)003:1236: rnam 'dren rnams kyi thabs la mkhas pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:1237: theg pa gcig las gnyis su yod ma yin //
NK086(lu)003:1238: bkri ba'i don du theg pa gsum bstan to //
NK086(lu)003:1241: srid pa'i lam gyis dub pa rnams //
NK086(lu)003:1242: ngal gso'i don de de nyid min //
NK086(lu)003:1244: gzhan yang theg pa gsum kho nar bzhag pas ma khyab ste /
NK086(lu)003:1246: 'od srung theg pa ni gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:1249: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:1250: de bas na rang lugs 'dir nyan rang byang sems
NK086(lu)003:1251: sngags kyi theg pa ste bzhir grangs nges pa'i phyi
NK086(lu)003:1252: ma la rgyud sde 'og ma gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:1253: bla med la bskyed rdzogs gsum du dbye bar mdzad
NK086(lu)003:1254: nas de theg pa'i rim par bzhag pa la 'gal
NK086(lu)003:1255: bar 'du ba'i cha shas tsam yang gnas pa'i skabs
NK086(lu)003:1256: med de / sangs rgyas kyis sa bsdus pa'i chos
NK086(lu)003:1257: thams cad la spyir theg pa gcig gi sgra sbyar
NK086(lu)003:1258: ba'am bye brag ji snyed pa la theg pa so
NK086(lu)003:1259: so'i sgra sbyar kyang rung ste thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1260: bar du bgrod byed kyi lam yin pas so //
NK086(lu)003:1261: de'ang dang po phyi mtshan nyid kyi theg pa gsum pos rim bzhin dgra bcom pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1262: ne tso'am bse ru lta bu'i rang sangs rgyas dang /
NK086(lu)003:1263: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyis mthar 'degs pas na theg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1264: gnyis pa phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa gsum
NK086(lu)003:1265: pos rim bzhin rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa
NK086(lu)003:1266: dang / rigs bzhi mkha' la spyod pa'i sa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1267: rigs lnga stug po bkod pa'i sar 'degs par byed pas na theg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1268: gsum pa nang pa thabs kyi rgyud rnam pa gsum
NK086(lu)003:1269: gyis rim pa bzhin yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK086(lu)003:1270: gyi sa dang / bde ba chen po'i sa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1271: ye shes bla ma'i sar 'degs par byed pas na theg pa'i sgra bshad bzhag la /
NK086(lu)003:1272: 'di la dgongs nas lang gshegs su //
NK086(lu)003:1273: ji srid sems can 'jug pa'i bar //
NK086(lu)003:1274: theg pa dag la thug pa med //
NK086(lu)003:1275: ces gsungs pa sems kyi rnam par rtog pa ji
NK086(lu)003:1276: snyed pa dang rjes su 'tshams par theg pa'i sgo
NK086(lu)003:1277: yang de snyed du yod par gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:1278: skabs 'dir dbang po 'bring dang rnon po dag la'ang
NK086(lu)003:1279: dbye ba gsum gsum du phyes pa gdul bya'i blo
NK086(lu)003:1280: tshod la dgongs nas sngags kyi theg pa gong 'og
NK086(lu)003:1281: rnams de dang mtshungs par bstan te rang rang gi
NK086(lu)003:1282: gzhung lam du lta sgom spyod 'bras tshar re tshang
NK086(lu)003:1283: bar lam so sor rang rkya thub pa'i don tsam
NK086(lu)003:1284: du bshad nas / mthar phyin pa blo zad chos
NK086(lu)003:1285: zad 'phags pa'i lam bden sgra ji bzhin pa'i mthar
NK086(lu)003:1286: thug par bzhag pa yin te /
NK086(lu)003:1287: der ma zad nyan rang theg pa'i myang 'das ni gnas skabs tsam las mtha' thub ma yin cing /
NK086(lu)003:1288: des rnam par grol ba'i myang 'das 'thob par byed
NK086(lu)003:1289: pa la rang lam gyi 'bras bu mngon du byas
NK086(lu)003:1290: nas gdod theg chen la 'jug dgos pa'i phyir theg
NK086(lu)003:1292: rgyu'i theg chen dang rgyud sde 'og ma gsum du
NK086(lu)003:1293: 'bras bu'i rnam gzhag rnam grangs pa re bstan kyang
NK086(lu)003:1294: de dag tu 'bras bu bde bgrod byed kyi lam
NK086(lu)003:1295: sbas don zab mo khyad par ba rnams ma bstan
NK086(lu)003:1296: la / 'bras bu dngos la'ang yongs su rdzogs pa dang ma rdzogs pa'i khyad par che zhing /
NK086(lu)003:1297: bla med kyi theg par ni thabs yongs su rdzogs par bstan pa'i phyir dang /
NK086(lu)003:1298: 'go ma rnams kyi lam dang 'bras bu'i tshul thams cad kyang 'di nyid la tshang zhing /
NK086(lu)003:1299: bla med kyi thun mong min pa'i chos rnams de
NK086(lu)003:1300: dag la med cing de dang de'i dod thub kyang
NK086(lu)003:1301: gzhag tu med pa'i phyir der 'du la /
NK086(lu)003:1302: bla med la'ang bskyed rdzogs gnyis po lam gang zhig
NK086(lu)003:1303: sgrub tshul blos byas las ma 'das pas bsgrub bya
NK086(lu)003:1304: 'du byas su 'gyur bas ye shes mthong ba la
NK086(lu)003:1305: khyad par shin tu che ste /
NK086(lu)003:1306: rdzogs pa chen po ni blos byas kyi chos kyis
NK086(lu)003:1307: reg pa'i skabs med pas chos nyid kyi bden pa
NK086(lu)003:1308: gnas lugs ltar rtogs pa'i stobs kyis thob pa 'phags
NK086(lu)003:1309: rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i lam bden zag pa med pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1310: ye shes te / lam 'og mas mngon du bya
NK086(lu)003:1311: rgyu rnam grangs mang pos bstan pa'i chos nyid ma
NK086(lu)003:1312: nor ba 'dir mngon sum du mthong bar 'gyur ba'i
NK086(lu)003:1313: ye shes te / phyir / theg pa ma lus
NK086(lu)003:1314: pa theg pa chen po bla na med pa 'dir
NK086(lu)003:1315: 'du ba yin pas de'i phyir 'di la ye shes
NK086(lu)003:1316: kyi theg pa zhes bshad pa'ang yin te /
NK086(lu)003:1317: sangs rgyas phal po che'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:1318: ye shes kyi theg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1319: theg pa chen po la rab tu gzhol ba'i sems
NK086(lu)003:1320: kyis dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag yongs su bsngo'o
NK086(lu)003:1322: lha'i bu rab rtsal sems kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:1323: theg pa chen po'i theg pa 'di //
NK086(lu)003:1324: sangs rgyas theg pa bsam mi khyab //
NK086(lu)003:1325: sems can gyi ni go skabs 'byed //
NK086(lu)003:1326: theg pa chen po bla na med //
NK086(lu)003:1327: theg pa ji snyed ci yod pa //
NK086(lu)003:1328: 'di ni de yi mchog tu dgongs //
NK086(lu)003:1329: de phyir theg pa chen po las //
NK086(lu)003:1330: theg pa thams cad bar du dbye //
NK086(lu)003:1332: 'phags pa rtogs chen phyag rgya las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:1333: theg pa ni gcig kho nar nges te //
NK086(lu)003:1334: gnyis dang gsum du ma mchis so //
NK086(lu)003:1337: de yang gdul byar theg pa gsum gyis 'dul ba la nyan thos dang /
NK086(lu)003:1339: theg pa chen po bstan to //
NK086(lu)003:1340: yang dag par theg pa gcig ste 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:1343: rab 'byor theg pa ni gcig kho na ste /
NK086(lu)003:1344: bla na med pa sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:1347: theg pa gcig las gnyis pa yod ma yin //
NK086(lu)003:1348: gsum pa nam yang yod min 'jig rten na //
NK086(lu)003:1349: sna tshogs 'gro ba 'dul bar mdzad ma gtogs //
NK086(lu)003:1350: zhes pa la sogs skabs 'gar theg pa gcig tu gsungs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1351: yang kha cig tu gnyis dang gsum dang lnga sogs
NK086(lu)003:1352: su grangs kyi mtha' ma bkag par gsungs pa'ang yod
NK086(lu)003:1353: de / byis pa rnams ni drang ba'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:1354: theg pa tha dad ngas bshad do //
NK086(lu)003:1356: lha yi theg dang tshangs theg dang /
NK086(lu)003:1357: sogs sngar smos pa bzhin dang /
NK086(lu)003:1358: la lar grangs med par yang gsungs te /
NK086(lu)003:1359: ji srid sems ni 'jug gi bar //
NK086(lu)003:1360: zhes sogs gsungs pa dang gnas lugs ma 'khrul ba
NK086(lu)003:1361: mthong ba'i gang zag la dgongs nas theg pa med
NK086(lu)003:1364: sems ni rab tu gyur pa na //
NK086(lu)003:1365: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK086(lu)003:1366: sa gsungs pa bzhin dgos pa'i dbang gis de lta
NK086(lu)003:1367: bur bstan pa rnams la mtha' gcig tu 'di tsam
NK086(lu)003:1368: zhig yin la 'di tsam zhig min no zhes rnam
NK086(lu)003:1369: gzhag 'grigs 'grigs ltar smra ba'ang yang dag pa'i gnas
NK086(lu)003:1370: la blo gros kyi 'jug pa ma phyogs pa'i rtags
NK086(lu)003:1372: 'dir re zhig theg pa'i rim pa dgur grangs nges par mdzad pa ltar na /
NK086(lu)003:1373: rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud las /
NK086(lu)003:1374: mdo dang rgyas pa chen po dang //
NK086(lu)003:1375: shin tu rgyas pa chen po'o //
NK086(lu)003:1376: shin tu rgyas pa chen po ni //
NK086(lu)003:1377: brgyad khri bzhi stong bsam mi khyab //
NK086(lu)003:1378: rgya che grangs mang chen po ste //
NK086(lu)003:1379: bsam gyis mi khyab gzhal du med //
NK086(lu)003:1381: rgyas pa chen po 'di ltar te //
NK086(lu)003:1382: dbye ba rnam pa dgur 'dod do //
NK086(lu)003:1383: nyan thos dang ni rang rgyal dang //
NK086(lu)003:1384: de bzhin byang chub sems dapa'o //
NK086(lu)003:1385: kri ya dang ni u pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1386: de bzhin yo ga'i theg par bshad //
NK086(lu)003:1387: ma h+aa a nu yo ga dang //
NK086(lu)003:1388: de bzhin rdzogs chen a ti'o //
NK086(lu)003:1389: de ltar rnam pa dgur bshad de //
NK086(lu)003:1390: chos kyi bstan pa chen po yin //
NK086(lu)003:1392: gdul bya dbang po dman 'bring mchog gi gnas skabs
NK086(lu)003:1393: la gsum gsum du dbye bar 'dul byed kyi theg
NK086(lu)003:1394: pa'ang de dang mtshungs par ston par mdzad de /
NK086(lu)003:1395: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK086(lu)003:1396: nga yi bstan pa'i chos rnams ni //
NK086(lu)003:1397: sems can blo yi rim pa las //
NK086(lu)003:1398: che dang chung gi khyad pa gyis //
NK086(lu)003:1399: rim pa gnyis kyi tshul du bstan //
NK086(lu)003:1400: rang rang lta dang sor bzhag go //
NK086(lu)003:1401: zhes gsungs pa'i rang rang gi lta ba la phyin
NK086(lu)003:1402: ci log dang yang dag pa gnyis su dbye ba'i
NK086(lu)003:1403: phyi ma ni / de nyid las /
NK086(lu)003:1404: yang dag pa ni rim gsum ste //
NK086(lu)003:1405: chung ba'i blo dang chen po dang //
NK086(lu)003:1406: de bzhin 'bring po'i blo can la //
NK086(lu)003:1407: rim pa gsum gyi tshul du bstan //
NK086(lu)003:1408: chung ba'i rim pa rnam gsum ste //
NK086(lu)003:1409: de yi blo dang mthun pa'i chos //
NK086(lu)003:1410: rtog pas sbags la nyan thos so //
NK086(lu)003:1411: 'du shes can la rang rgyal te //
NK086(lu)003:1412: rtog 'dzud can la byang sems so //
NK086(lu)003:1413: 'bring po gsum la bstan pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:1414: rab tu dman la bya ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:1415: dman pa rnams la spyod pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:1416: rnam shes can la rnal 'byor nyid //
NK086(lu)003:1417: chen po'i rim lngan gsum dag la //
NK086(lu)003:1418: sems yas pa la bskyed pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1419: sems bcud can la rdzogs pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:1420: mchog gsang rab la rdzogs pa che //
NK086(lu)003:1421: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:1422: gnyis pa dgongs 'grel bstan bcos kyi rnam gzhag bstan pa la gsum /
NK086(lu)003:1427: gtso bor bstan bcos rtsom pa'i bsam pas kun nas bslangs te /
NK086(lu)003:1428: rang gi zhe 'dod grub mtha' gzhan la ston pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1429: phyir du bsdebs pa'i lung gi chos de bstan bcos
NK086(lu)003:1431: gang zhig khyad chos bzhi dang ldan pa de bstan bcos rnam dag gi mtshan nyid /
NK086(lu)003:1432: khyad chos bzhi po gang rung dang bral ba de bstan bcos ltar snang gi mtshan nyid do //
NK086(lu)003:1434: rtsom pa po rnam g.yeng med pa'i yid can gyis
NK086(lu)003:1435: tshig don rtogs pa'i shes rab dang gzhan la phan
NK086(lu)003:1436: 'dod kyi snying rjes kun nas bslangs pa bsam pa
NK086(lu)003:1438: sdeb sbyor dag pa'i tshig 'brel chags pa rjod byed tshig gi khyad par /
NK086(lu)003:1439: thar pa don gnyer gyi gdul bya la nye bar
NK086(lu)003:1440: mkho ba'i thabs ston pa brjod bya don gyi khyad
NK086(lu)003:1441: par / tshig de la thos bsam byas pas thar
NK086(lu)003:1442: pa thob pa'i nus pa yod pa dgos pa byed
NK086(lu)003:1445: gang zhig rgyal ba ston pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK086(lu)003:1446: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK086(lu)003:1447: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK086(lu)003:1448: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK086(lu)003:1451: shastra'i sgra las sh+aa ba na 'chos pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:1452: rgyu nyon mongs dug gsum las bslab pa gsum ldan du 'chos pa'i phyir dang /
NK086(lu)003:1454: 'bras bu ngan 'gro dang srid pa'i sdug bsngal las
NK086(lu)003:1455: skyob pa'i phyir 'chos skyob kyi yon tan dang ldan
NK086(lu)003:1458: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1459: ngan 'gro'i srid las skyob byed gang yin pa //
NK086(lu)003:1460: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK086(lu)003:1461: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK086(lu)003:1463: gsum pa bstan bcos kyi dbye ba la //
NK086(lu)003:1466: rtsom byed gang zag /ji ltar brtsams tshul /
NK086(lu)003:1468: brjod bya don gyi sgo nas dbye ba dang drug las /
NK086(lu)003:1469: dang po byed las mchog dman gyi sgo nas dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:1470: bde 'dus kyis gcod tshoms kyi chings las /
NK086(lu)003:1471: bstan bcos don med don dman dang //
NK086(lu)003:1472: don log don ldan bzhir shes bya //
NK086(lu)003:1474: don med pa bya rog so brtag gi bstan bcos lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1475: don dman pa thun mong gi rig gnas bzhi'i bstan bcos lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1476: don log pa phyi rol mu stegs pa'i bstan bcos lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1477: don dang ldan pa sangs rgyas pa'i nang rig pa'i bstan bcos lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:1478: sa sde las dgur bshad de /
NK086(lu)003:1479: don med don log don dang ldan //
NK086(lu)003:1480: ngan g.yo brtse bral sdug bsngal spong //
NK086(lu)003:1481: thos rtsod sgrub pa lhur len pa //
NK086(lu)003:1482: bstan bcos rnam pa dgu yin no //
NK086(lu)003:1484: snga ma gnyis bstan bcos ltar snang ba ste dman pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1485: phyi ma re re bstan bcos yang dag pa ste mchog yin no //
NK086(lu)003:1486: gnyis pa dgos pa byed las kyi sgo nas dbye ba la /
NK086(lu)003:1487: bka'i don rgya chen po sdud pa'i bstan bcos /
NK086(lu)003:1488: 'khrugs pa go rim bsdebs pa'i bstan bcos /
NK086(lu)003:1489: zab mo rnam par 'byed pa'i bstan bcos gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:1490: mtshan gzhi rim bzhin mngon pa kun las btus /
NK086(lu)003:1493: gsum pa rtsom byed gang zag gi sgo nas dbye ba la lnga ste /
NK086(lu)003:1494: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa la bstan bcos
NK086(lu)003:1495: su byas pa rdo rje chos kyis mdzad pa'i bde
NK086(lu)003:1497: byams chos sde lnga lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1498: dgra bcom pas gsungs pa las bstan bcos su byas pa mngon pa sde bdun lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1500: chos kyi phung po sh+aa ri'i bus //
NK086(lu)003:1501: gdags pa'i bstan bcos mong+gala bus //
NK086(lu)003:1502: khams kyi tshogs ni gang pos byas //
NK086(lu)003:1503: rnam shes tshogs ni lha skyed kyis //
NK086(lu)003:1504: ye shes la 'jug ka t+ya'i bus //
NK086(lu)003:1505: rab tu byas pa dbyig bshes kyis //
NK086(lu)003:1506: yang dag 'gro ba'i rnam grangs ni //
NK086(lu)003:1507: gsum po che yis byas zhes grags //
NK086(lu)003:1509: de la bye brag tu smra ba rnams kyi lugs ltar na /
NK086(lu)003:1510: ston pas yul dus gang zag tha dad la thor
NK086(lu)003:1511: bur gsungs pa rnams sh+aa ri'i bu sogs kyis bsdus
NK086(lu)003:1512: pas ched du brjod pa'i tshoms bzhin du bka' yin
NK086(lu)003:1513: pas / dgongs 'grel gyi thog ma ni bye brag bshad mdzod yin no zhes zer /
NK086(lu)003:1514: mdo sde pa ltar na mngon pa sde bdun ni
NK086(lu)003:1515: nyan thos so skye dag gis byas nas ston pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1516: gsung dgra bcom pas bsdus par kha 'phangs par 'dod
NK086(lu)003:1517: pas dgongs 'grel gyi thog ma sde bdun yin no
NK086(lu)003:1518: zhes zer ro // de la dogs pa 'di 'dra zhig 'jug ste /
NK086(lu)003:1519: theg pa chen po la mngon pa'i sde snod logs
NK086(lu)003:1520: na yod pa zhig tu nyan thos la'ang 'byung dgos
NK086(lu)003:1521: pa dang / sde snod gzhan gnyis glegs bam tha
NK086(lu)003:1522: dad du 'byung zhing mngon pa la de ltar mi
NK086(lu)003:1523: 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan yang med dam snyam pa'i dogs
NK086(lu)003:1524: pa dang / pa 'di skye'o // des na bye
NK086(lu)003:1525: brag tu smra ba'i lugs de 'thad 'thad 'dra ba
NK086(lu)003:1526: pa dang / pa 'di skye'o // zhig snang rung
NK086(lu)003:1527: / slob dpon chen po dbyig gnyen ni mdo sde
NK086(lu)003:1528: pa'i 'dod pa dang mthun par bzhed ces mkhas mchog
NK086(lu)003:1529: pa dang / pa 'di skye'o // zhig snang rung
NK086(lu)003:1530: / rnams gsung pas / 'dir dgra bcom pas mdzad
NK086(lu)003:1531: pa'i bstan bcos kyi mtshan gzhir bzung ba yin la
NK086(lu)003:1532: pa dang / pa 'di skye'o // zhig snang rung
NK086(lu)003:1533: / rnams gsung pas / / gzhan du brdol thabs
NK086(lu)003:1534: su smra ba kha cig /sde bdun bka' ma yin
NK086(lu)003:1535: pa dang / pa 'di skye'o // zhig snang rung
NK086(lu)003:1536: / rnams gsung pas / / te / nor ba
NK086(lu)003:1538: sh+aa ri bu la sogs pas byas pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:1539: zhes zer ba ni shin tu blun pa'i gtam ste /
NK086(lu)003:1540: ston pa nyid kyis rnam par 'phrul pa las byung
NK086(lu)003:1541: ba'i dgra bcom chen po mchog zung lta bus bka'i
NK086(lu)003:1542: don log par 'grel ba yin na dbang gyur skye
NK086(lu)003:1543: bo phal cher zad pas na /
NK086(lu)003:1544: dbang du gyur ba'i skye bo ngos 'dzin rgyu ma dmigs pa'i phyir dang /
NK086(lu)003:1545: dgra bcom pa rnams kyis kyang de nyid ma mthong
NK086(lu)003:1546: na nyan thos kyi lugs la de nyid mthong ba'i
NK086(lu)003:1547: gang zag mi srid par thal ba'i phyir snyam du
NK086(lu)003:1548: sems so // yang byang sems 'phags pas gsungs pa
NK086(lu)003:1549: la bstan bcos su byas pas gsum pa la gnas
NK086(lu)003:1550: pa 'phags pa thogs med kyis mdzad pa'i rgyas pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1551: bstan bcos sa sde lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:1552: bsdus pa'i bstan bcos sdom rnam gnyis lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1553: yi dam lha'i lung bstan thob nas brtsams pa la
NK086(lu)003:1554: bstan bcos su byas pa phyogs kyi glang po'i tshad
NK086(lu)003:1555: ma kun las btus pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1556: kun mkhyen chen po'i gsungs rab mdzod bdun lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1557: rang gi grub mthas zlos shing gzhan gyi log rtog
NK086(lu)003:1558: sun 'byin pa la mkhas pa so skyes pan+di tas
NK086(lu)003:1559: brtsams pa la bstan bcos su byas pa mkhas mchog
NK086(lu)003:1560: dbyig gnyen gyis mdzad pa'i pra ka ra na sde
NK086(lu)003:1562: rtsom byed gang zag gi sgo nas dbye na lnga po der 'dus so //
NK086(lu)003:1563: bzhi pa ji ltar brtsam tshul gyi sgo nas dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:1564: bka' nyid la 'grel par btags pa'i bstan bcos dang /
NK086(lu)003:1565: bka'i don rang rgyud du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos gnyis su yod /
NK086(lu)003:1567: tshig don gnyis ka zhib tu gtan la 'bebs pa ni rgya cher 'grel te /
NK086(lu)003:1568: so thar gyi mdo'i 'grel pa bam po lnga bcu pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1569: dus 'khor 'grel chen dri med 'od lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1570: tshig gi cha spros pa dang bcas nas 'chad pa ni tshig 'grel te /
NK086(lu)003:1571: ched du brjod pa'i tshoms kyi 'grel pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1572: snying 'grel phyogs bcu mun sel lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1573: go bka'i gnas rnam par 'byed pa ni dka' 'grel te /
NK086(lu)003:1575: don gyi gtso bor bsdus te gtan la 'bebs pa ni bsdus don gyi 'grel ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:1576: bi ma la'i snying 'grel pan+di r+tha dang /
NK086(lu)003:1577: rong zom chen po'i le lag gi sa ma 'grel lta bu rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:1578: gnyis pa bka'i don rang rgyud du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos la'ang gsum las /
NK086(lu)003:1579: bka' gcig gi don rdzogs par ston pa'i bstan bcos ni 'dul ba mdo rtsa ba /
NK086(lu)003:1581: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i sgyu 'phrul lam rim lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1582: bka' thor bu'i don ston pa'i bstan bcos ni dge tshul gyi k+aa ri k+aa lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1583: bka' mang po'i don ston pa'i bstan bcos ni zhi ba lha'i bslab btus dang /
NK086(lu)003:1584: kun mkhyen 'jigs med gleng pa'i yon tan mdzod lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:1585: lnga pa bshad bya bka'i sgo nas dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:1586: bka' spyi 'grel par byed pa la /
NK086(lu)003:1587: tshig gi cha 'grel par byed pa brda sprod pa'i bstan bcos ka tsa na lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1588: don gyi cha 'grel bar byed pa tshad ma sde bdun mdo dang bcas pa lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1589: bye brag so so'i dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos la /
NK086(lu)003:1593: lta spyod zung 'grel du gtan la 'bebs pa'i bstan bcos gsum las /
NK086(lu)003:1594: dang po ni mngon pa mdzod lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1595: lus rnam gzhag sngon du 'gro bas gnas brgyad kyi /
NK086(lu)003:1596: dang po shes par bya ba'i yul phung khams skye mched /
NK086(lu)003:1597: gnyis pas dbang po'i rang bzhin dang 'dus byas kyi skye tshul rgyu rkyen 'bras bu dang bcas pa /
NK086(lu)003:1598: gsum pas sdug bden snod bcud kyi 'jig rten kun 'byung bden pa /
NK086(lu)003:1600: lnga pas nyon mongs pa'i rnam bzhag /drug pas lam
NK086(lu)003:1601: dang gang zag bstan pas lam nyams su len tshul
NK086(lu)003:1602: / bdun pas 'bras bu yongs shes thob tshul /
NK086(lu)003:1603: brgyad pas sngar drug par bstan pa'i gnyen po lam
NK086(lu)003:1604: bden gyi rten du bsam gtan gyi snyoms 'jug sogs
NK086(lu)003:1605: dgos pas de'i rnam bzhag bstan no //
NK086(lu)003:1606: gnyis pa spyod pa'i cha ston pa ni 'dul ba mdo rtsa ba lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1607: gzhi bcu bdun las rab byung gi gzhi dang por bstan nas /
NK086(lu)003:1609: gzhi bcu drug rnams gzhir byas pa la /
NK086(lu)003:1610: gzhung dam pa'i 'dul ba 'dul 'byed sogs phran tshegs
NK086(lu)003:1611: kyi skabs nas 'byung ba rnams ji ltar rigs pa
NK086(lu)003:1613: me tog phreng rgyud lta bu ni rnam 'byed gzhir
NK086(lu)003:1614: byas pa la gzhan rnams ci rigs par sbyar nas
NK086(lu)003:1615: 'chad do // gsum pa lta spyod zung 'brel du
NK086(lu)003:1616: ston pa ni bye brag bshad mdzod chen mo lta
NK086(lu)003:1617: 'chad do // bu ste / de la bye brag
NK086(lu)003:1618: tu bshad pa'i don ni zhib mor bshad pa'i don
NK086(lu)003:1620: ni nyer sbas kyi dus su dgra bcom pa rnams
NK086(lu)003:1621: spyi mthun du brtsams zer ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:1622: kha cig grags pa dang thams cad 'dod sogs kyis mdzad par 'dod /
NK086(lu)003:1623: bod rnams gtam de gnyis bsres te thams cad 'dod
NK086(lu)003:1624: dang sgur po sogs dgra bcom pa lnga brgyas byang
NK086(lu)003:1625: phyogs ri bo 'bigs byed gar mkhan gyi gtsug lag
NK086(lu)003:1627: don la dgra bcom pa de dag gi gsung rgyun
NK086(lu)003:1628: phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs pa gnas brtan rnams kyi rna
NK086(lu)003:1629: ba nas rna bar brgyud pa phyis yi ger bkod
NK086(lu)003:1631: yang chos 'khor bar pa'i dgongs 'grel la'ang /
NK086(lu)003:1634: lta spyod zung 'brel du gtan la 'bebs pa'i bstan bcos gsum las /
NK086(lu)003:1635: dang po ni klu sgrub kyi dbu ma rigs tshogs lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1636: bsgrub bya spros pa'i mtha' 'gog pa'i rigs tshogs rtsa ba shes rab /
NK086(lu)003:1640: sgrub byed rtog ge'i rigs pa 'gog pa'i rigs tshogs zhib mo rnam 'thag bcas rigs tshogs lnga'am /
NK086(lu)003:1641: de'i steng du don dam par rang bzhin med kyang
NK086(lu)003:1642: kun rdzob tu tha snyad 'thad cing grub par ston
NK086(lu)003:1643: pa tha snyad sgrub pa bsnan pas rigs tshogs drug
NK086(lu)003:1645: tshig gsal gyi dgongs pa ltar na rigs tshogs lngar 'thad ces gsung /
NK086(lu)003:1646: gnyis pa spyod pa ston pa ni zhi ba lha'i spyod 'jug lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1647: le'u bcu yis byang sems phan yon dang //
NK086(lu)003:1648: sdig bshags gtsor ston byang chub sems yongs bzung //
NK086(lu)003:1649: bag yod shes bzhin bsrung dang bzod pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1650: brtson 'grus bsam gtan shes rab bsngo ba'o //
