NK086(lu)003:1652: gsum pa lta spyod zung 'brel du ston pa ni mngon rtogs rgyan lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1653: shes rab pha rol phyin pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:1654: dngos po brgyad kyis yang dag bshad //
NK086(lu)003:1659: dngos brgyad don bdun cus gtan la 'bebs par byed do //
NK086(lu)003:1660: yang chos 'khor gsum pa bka' tha ma'i dgongs 'grel las /
NK086(lu)003:1662: lta spyod zung 'brel du gtan la 'bebs pa'i bstan bcos gsum las /
NK086(lu)003:1663: dang po ni rgyud bla ma dang 'byed gnyis lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1665: sangs rgyas chos tshogs khams dang byang chub dang //
NK086(lu)003:1666: yon tan sangs rgyas phrin las tha ma ste //
NK086(lu)003:1667: bstan bcos kun gyi lus ni mdor bsdu na //
NK086(lu)003:1668: rdo rje yi ni gnas bdun 'di dag go //
NK086(lu)003:1669: zhes pas dkon mchog gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:1670: de'i rgyu khams bde gshegs snying po /
NK086(lu)003:1671: 'bras bu byang chub dang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan
NK086(lu)003:1672: drug cu rtsa bzhi dang phrin las bdun rnams gtan
NK086(lu)003:1675: yod med dam rtag chad kyi mtha' bsal nas dbu ma'i lam ston par byed /
NK086(lu)003:1676: chos dang chos nyid rnam 'byed ni /
NK086(lu)003:1678: chos nyid mya ngan las 'das pa'i rnam dbye ston par byed pas na /
NK086(lu)003:1679: de gnyis rnam par 'byed pa'i gzhung ngo //
NK086(lu)003:1680: gnyis pa spyod pa ston pa ni sdom pa nyi shu pa lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1681: byang sems dbang 'bring gi rtsa ltung bzhi nyes byas
NK086(lu)003:1682: zhe drug dang bcas pa gtan la 'bebs pa'i gzhung
NK086(lu)003:1683: ngo // gsum pa lta spyod zung 'grel du ston pa ni mdo sde rgyan lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1684: theg chen bka' sgrub sogs skabs nyi shu rtsa gcig gis /
NK086(lu)003:1685: rigs dang chos la mos pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1686: zhes sogs don tshan bcu'i sgo nas gtan la 'bebs par byed do //
NK086(lu)003:1687: de bzhin du sde snod bzhi pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod la'ang /
NK086(lu)003:1688: rgyud sde bzhi'am drug gi dgongs pa 'grel bar byed pa'i bstan bcos rnams te /
NK086(lu)003:1690: lta ba ston pa'i bstan bcos slob dpon chen po pad+ma'i lta phreng dang /
NK086(lu)003:1691: ska ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim snang ba bcu bdun pa lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1692: spyod pa ston pa'i bstan bcos sgeg pa rdo rje'i dam tshig gsal bkra lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:1693: lta spyod zung 'brel du ston pa'i bstan bcos slob
NK086(lu)003:1694: dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i sgyu 'phrul lam rnam bkod
NK086(lu)003:1696: drug pa brjod bya don gyi sgo nas dbye ba la /
NK086(lu)003:1697: ji snyed pa ston pa'i bstan bcos /
NK086(lu)003:1698: ji lta ba ston pa'i bstan bcos /
NK086(lu)003:1699: thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa thob thabs ston pa'i bstan bcos dang gsum /
NK086(lu)003:1700: de'i dang po ji snyed pa ston pa'i bstan bcos de la'ang /
NK086(lu)003:1704: 'jig rten pa'i lugs kyi bstan bcos skye bo gso ba'i thig pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1705: tsa ra ka rgyal po lugs kyi bstan bcos lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1706: de dag kyang dngos su mngon mtho'i rgyu yin mod /
NK086(lu)003:1707: brgyud nas thar pa'i rten du'ang 'gro srid pa yin te /
NK086(lu)003:1709: mi yi chos lugs legs spyod na //
NK086(lu)003:1710: lha yul bgrod pa thag mi ring //
NK086(lu)003:1711: lha dang mi yi them skas la //
NK086(lu)003:1712: 'dzegs na thar pa gam na 'dug /ces dang /
NK086(lu)003:1713: gzhan yang brtag pa brgyad ni /
NK086(lu)003:1714: rin chen sa gzhi gtso bor gtan la 'bebs pa'i bstan bcos rnams te /
NK086(lu)003:1715: drin lan bsab pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:1716: gal te byang chub sems dpa' rig pa'i dngos po
NK086(lu)003:1717: lngar ma bslab na nam du'ang bla na med pa
NK086(lu)003:1718: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu thams cad
NK086(lu)003:1719: mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob par mi nus so //
NK086(lu)003:1720: de lta bas na bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK086(lu)003:1721: thob pa'i phyir rig pa'i dngos po lnga bslab par
NK086(lu)003:1724: rig pa'i gnas lnga gang zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:1728: gtan tshigs kyi rig pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1730: bzo'i las kyi gnas rig pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:1732: de'i nang nas rig gnas dang po bzhi la sbyangs pa'i dgos pa yang /
NK086(lu)003:1733: rgyal tshab ma pham mgon gyis /
NK086(lu)003:1734: de lta bas na gzhan dag tshar bcad rjes bzung dang /
NK086(lu)003:1736: gzhan dag tshig dang don la log par rtog pa
NK086(lu)003:1737: tshar gcod par byed pa la sgra dang tshad ma
NK086(lu)003:1738: / dgos dgu spyi dang bye brag tu nad med
NK086(lu)003:1739: pa don du gnyer ba rnams rjes su 'dzin par
NK086(lu)003:1740: byed pa bzo dang gso ba rig pa gnyis so
NK086(lu)003:1741: / // de la bzo rig pa'i nang du gzhan
NK086(lu)003:1742: gsum 'dubs na bzo rig pa thog mar 'chad pa
NK086(lu)003:1745: lus ngag gtso bor byed dang mi byed las //
NK086(lu)003:1746: lus ngag yid kyi bzo zhes gsum du dbye //
NK086(lu)003:1748: yid dang 'brel ba'i lus kyi g.yo ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:1749: ngag gi brjod pa gtso bor gyur pa la lus ngag gi bzor 'jog cing /
NK086(lu)003:1750: de gnyis dang ma 'brel bar yid kyis bsam pa
NK086(lu)003:1751: tsam gyi dbang du byas pa la yid kyi bzo
NK086(lu)003:1752: zhes bya'o // rgyu mtshan des rgya che rol pa
NK086(lu)003:1753: dang lung phran tshegs kyi 'grel par bshad pa'i sgyu
NK086(lu)003:1755: bye brag rtogs byed du bshad pa'i bzor btags pa sum cu /
NK086(lu)003:1756: gar mkhan dang bro sogs rol mo'i bye brag bco brgyad /
NK086(lu)003:1757: bar ma dang drang srong sogs klu dbyangs kyi nges pa bdun /
NK086(lu)003:1758: sgeg pa sogs gar gyi cha byad dgu /
NK086(lu)003:1759: mdo sde las bshad pa'i bzo sbyangs bco brgyad dang /
NK086(lu)003:1760: brtag pa brgyad sogs dgos dgu sgrub pa'i thabs mtha' yas shing /
NK086(lu)003:1761: khyad par lus bzo mchog ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1762: sku gsung thugs kyi rten brten par bcas pa bzhengs
NK086(lu)003:1763: tshul dang / ngag bzo mchog rgyal ba mchod pa'i bstod dbyangs la sogs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1764: yid bzo mchog thos bsam sgom pa la sogs pa
NK086(lu)003:1765: bsam byung gi shes rig khyad par can rnams yin
NK086(lu)003:1766: cing / de dag ston pa'i gzhung lugs sh+aa ris bus zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK086(lu)003:1768: sdom 'byung sogs gsungs rab 'grel bar bcas pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1769: drang srong e tre'i bus byas pa'i chag tshad kyi
NK086(lu)003:1770: yi ge dang gser 'gyur la sogs pa bzo'i bstan
NK086(lu)003:1771: bcos rnams so // yang rig gnas gnyis pa gso ba rig pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:1772: dpal ldan rgyud bzhi'i dgongs pa g.yu thog pas bkral ba lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1773: de yang yan lag bshad rgyud las /
NK086(lu)003:1774: 'gro drug gtso bor gyur pa mi lus la //
NK086(lu)003:1775: mi na gnas dang na ba gso ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:1776: tshe ring chos nor bde ba sgrub pa'i phyir //
NK086(lu)003:1777: gso ba rig pa'i don rnams mdor bsdu na //
NK086(lu)003:1778: gso bya gso byed ji ltar gso ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:1779: gso ba po dang rnam pa bzhi ru bshad //
NK086(lu)003:1780: ces pas gso bya nad dang nad pa /
NK086(lu)003:1781: gso byed spyod lam zas dang sman dpyad /
NK086(lu)003:1782: ji ltar gso ba nad med reng du 'tsho ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:1784: gso bar byed pa po sman pa dang nad g.yog rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:1785: yang na dpa' bos yan lag brgyad du bsdus nas bstan pa rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:1786: yang rig gnas gsum pa sgra rigs pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:1787: p+aa ni pa'i 'grel par bshad pa ltar 'phags yul du grags pa sgra mdo chen po brgyad dam /
NK086(lu)003:1788: khyad par bod 'dir nyi zla lta bur grags pa
NK086(lu)003:1789: k+aa la pa dang tsan+da b+y+aa ka ra na'i bstan
NK086(lu)003:1790: bcos man ngag dang bcas pa lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1791: de'i brjod bya thun mong ni /
NK086(lu)003:1792: smra ba rgyan gyi me tog las /
NK086(lu)003:1793: ngo bo tsam dang khyad par ston //
NK086(lu)003:1794: de gnyis rten du gyur pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:1795: ming dang tshig dang yi ge yin //
NK086(lu)003:1797: ming tshig yi ge gsum yin la /
NK086(lu)003:1798: brjod bya khyad par ba ni /
NK086(lu)003:1799: brdal sprod snying po gsal ba las //
NK086(lu)003:1800: rang bzhin rkyen dang rnam 'gyur rnams //
NK086(lu)003:1801: brda spyod gzhung gi brjod bya yin //
NK086(lu)003:1803: rkyen gyi dbang gi rnam 'gyur sna tshogs su sgrub
NK086(lu)003:1804: par bya ba'i gzhir gyur pa ni rang bzhin te
NK086(lu)003:1806: rang bzhin byings dang ming de la'ang //
NK086(lu)003:1807: thog ma'i rang bzhin bya ba'i don //
NK086(lu)003:1808: rtags gsum dbyangs dang gsal byed mtha' //zhes so //
NK086(lu)003:1809: sgra'i rang bzhin gnyis po de ming tshig dbyangs gsum
NK086(lu)003:1810: gang rung du sgrub par byed pa sgra'i yan lag
NK086(lu)003:1811: gi rkyen te / de la'ang byings rtags su sgrub pa /
NK086(lu)003:1817: rtags tshig tu sgrub pa ste rkyen bdun dang /
NK086(lu)003:1818: de las kyang gnyis pa dang bdun pa gnyis ni rkyen dang rnam dbye'i gzhi mthun te /
NK086(lu)003:1819: gnyis pa ti sogs kyi byings tshig tu sgrub pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1820: sgo nas dus dang don rnam par 'byed par byed
NK086(lu)003:1821: pa'i phyir / rang bzhin dang rkyen nam yi ge
NK086(lu)003:1822: phan tshun 'brel ba'i dbang gis bsgyur pa dang dbyi
NK086(lu)003:1826: yi ge tsam dang 'brel ba yi //
NK086(lu)003:1827: bsgyur dang dbyi ba rnam 'gyur te //
NK086(lu)003:1831: prit+ta sogs kyis mdo'i rtsa ba bstan la /
NK086(lu)003:1832: yan lag ni byings mdo dang /
NK086(lu)003:1834: u na la sogs pa rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:1835: yang rig gnas bzhi pa gtan tshigs rig pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:1837: mngon sum dang ni rjes su dpag /ltar snang bcas pa bdag rig byed //
NK086(lu)003:1838: sgrub pa dang ni sun 'byin dag /lta snang bcas pa gzhan rtogs byed //
NK086(lu)003:1840: rtog ge'i tshig don brgyad du bshad de /
NK086(lu)003:1842: rjes dpag sgrub dag /thal 'gyur bzhir re re la'ang /
NK086(lu)003:1843: yang dag dang ltar snang gnyis su nges pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:1845: rang gis gzhal bya rtogs pa'i thabs dang /
NK086(lu)003:1846: rtogs nas gzhan rjes su 'dzin pa'i thabs gnyis su 'du /
NK086(lu)003:1848: mtshan nyid bslu med can shes pa //
NK086(lu)003:1850: tshad ma'i mtshan nyid rang gi 'jug yul la gsal du mi bslu ba'i rigs pa zhes 'byung bas /
NK086(lu)003:1851: bre tshad srang tshad ltar 'jal byed tshad ma zhig la 'jog /gzhal bya la gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:1856: gzhal bya mngon gyur 'jal byed la mngon sum gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:1860: lkog gyur gyi 'jal byed dang sgrub byed ni /
NK086(lu)003:1861: dngos stobs rjes dpag gi gtan tshigs gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:1864: ma dmigs pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK086(lu)003:1865: gzhal bya shin tu lkog gyur gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK086(lu)003:1866: mngon sum dang dngos stobs kyi gtan tshigs gnyis kas mi 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:1867: dpyad gsum dag pa'i lung nyid la brten dgos pa yin no //
NK086(lu)003:1868: de yang tshad ma'i bstan bcos ni slob dpon phyogs kyi glang pos mdzad pa'i tshad ma mdo dang /
NK086(lu)003:1869: de'i dgongs 'grel du dpal ldan chos kyi grags pas mdzad pa'i sde bdun lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1870: de la rab tu byed pa sde bdun ni /
NK086(lu)003:1873: bsdus pa rig thegs te gtso bo lus lta bu'i bstan bcos gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:1874: de las 'phros pa gyes pa yan lag lta bu'i bstan bcos bzhi ni /
NK086(lu)003:1875: rang don rjes dpag las 'phros pa gtan tshigs thig pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1877: gzhan don rjes dpag las 'phros pa rgyud gzhan grub pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1878: rtsod pa'i rig pa ste bzhi'o //
NK086(lu)003:1879: de yang mkhas mchog la la dag tshad ma'i bstan
NK086(lu)003:1880: bcos rnams mngon pa'i sde snod yin pas nang rig
NK086(lu)003:1881: pa'i bstan bcos yin zhes gsungs pa yod na'ang mi
NK086(lu)003:1883: tshad ma kun las btus su /
NK086(lu)003:1884: tshad ma dang gzhal bya nyer bar brjod pa nyid
NK086(lu)003:1885: kyis mu stegs pa'i 'dod pa snying po med pa'i
NK086(lu)003:1886: phyir / der zhan pa rnams bzlog pa'i don du 'di brtsams pa yin gyi /
NK086(lu)003:1887: 'di tsam gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i bstan pa la gzhug pa'i don du ni ma yin te /
NK086(lu)003:1888: de'i chos ni rtog ge'i yul ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:1890: gang zhig rtog ge'i lam nas chos nyid la khrid na /
NK086(lu)003:1891: de ni thub pa'i bstan las ches bsrings nyams pa yin /
NK086(lu)003:1892: zhes bya ba la sogs pa mang du gsungs pa'i phyir snyam mo //
NK086(lu)003:1893: yang 'phros don bzo rig pa'am sgra rig pa'i yan
NK086(lu)003:1894: lag tu gtogs pa rig pa'i gnas chung ba lnga
NK086(lu)003:1895: ni / skar rtsis snyan ngag sdeb sbyor dang //
NK086(lu)003:1896: mngon brjod zlos gar 'di lnga la //
NK086(lu)003:1897: rig gnas lnga zhes 'phags yul na //
NK086(lu)003:1898: grags pa'i ba dan rlung ltar sgrogs //
NK086(lu)003:1901: gang la longs spyod pa'i gzhi yul gyi dbang du byas te skar khyim gyi go la dang /
NK086(lu)003:1902: dus kyi dbang du byas te lo zla zhag gsum dus tshod dang bcas pa /
NK086(lu)003:1903: gang gi longs spyod par byed pa po gza' bcu /
NK086(lu)003:1904: des ji ltar spyod tshul brtag pa'i longs spyod dang /
NK086(lu)003:1905: rkang pa'i longs spyod dag par byed pa'i cho ga /de ltar spyod pa'i lag rjes la /
NK086(lu)003:1906: 'khor tshul gyi dbang du byas te mkha' la dus sbyor 'char rtsis dang /
NK086(lu)003:1908: rang rang gi rkang pa'i dbang gis gza' rnams kyi 'char nub /
NK086(lu)003:1909: skor phyogs kyi dbang gis nyi zlar sgra gcan 'jug pa /
NK086(lu)003:1910: rang rang gi longs spyod la spyad pa'i dbang gis nges pa 'pho sdud skye tshul bshad pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:1913: brtsi byed gnyis su 'dus pa yin no //
NK086(lu)003:1914: de ltar ston pa'i bstan bcos thun mongs ma yin
NK086(lu)003:1915: pa dus gdan gyi rgyud 'grel sogs rjes su 'jug
NK086(lu)003:1916: pa'i skar rtsis kyi bstan bcos rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:1917: phyi rol dang thun mong pa g.yul las rnam par
NK086(lu)003:1918: rgyal ba'i rtsis gzhung la sogs pa rnams yin la
NK086(lu)003:1919: / de las gzhan du bdag rig pa brtag pa
NK086(lu)003:1920: la shin tu mkho ba rgya nag po las byung
NK086(lu)003:1921: ba'i 'byung rtsis sam nag rtsis su grags pa ni
NK086(lu)003:1922: / / brtsi bya 'byung ba lnga'i skor mgo la /
NK086(lu)003:1923: brtsi byed rang bzhin gzhi'i gtsug lag dang /
NK086(lu)003:1927: 'dzin pa sems kyi gab rtse bzhir bsdus pa'i ma
NK086(lu)003:1928: rig 'khrul snang gi gtsug lag gnyis kyi sgo nas
NK086(lu)003:1930: khams lo sme ba spar kha dang //
NK086(lu)003:1931: zla zhag dus tshod gza' skar ro //
NK086(lu)003:1932: zhes don rnam pa dgur bsdus te 'chad pa'i bstan bcos rgyud du grags pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:1933: de dag gi man ngag gsal sgron ma bu la sogs pas bstan pa lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:1934: snyan ngag gi bstan bcos ni /
NK086(lu)003:1935: dan+di 'i me long lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1936: de yang sngon gyi slob dpon rnams kyis snyan ngag
NK086(lu)003:1937: gi brjod bya thams cad 'dod pa'i don sgrub par
NK086(lu)003:1938: byed pa / lus bcad lhug spel ma gsum mdzes
NK086(lu)003:1939: par byed pa'i sbyor ba khyad par can gyi chos
NK086(lu)003:1940: gnyis su bsdus nas bshad de /
NK086(lu)003:1942: de dag gis ni snyan ngag gi //
NK086(lu)003:1943: lus dang rgyan yang rab tu bstan //
NK086(lu)003:1944: lus ni re zhig 'dod pa yi //
NK086(lu)003:1945: don gyi rnam bcad tshig gi 'phreng //
NK086(lu)003:1946: de yang tshig bcad lhug pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:1947: spel ma rnam gsum nyid du gnas //
NK086(lu)003:1949: snyan ngag mdzes par byed pa yi //
NK086(lu)003:1950: chos rnams rgyan zhes rab tu brjod //
NK086(lu)003:1953: lam rnam par dbye ba thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyan dang /
NK086(lu)003:1954: thun mong gi rgyan gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:1957: dpe gzugs sogs don rgyan sum du so lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:1958: zung ldan bya daka'i khyad par dang /
NK086(lu)003:1959: dbyangs sogs nges pa'i bya dka' la /
NK086(lu)003:1960: rnam grangs dbye ba du ma yod /
NK086(lu)003:1961: ces pa ltar sgra rgyan dang /
NK086(lu)003:1962: gab tshig gi rgyan bcu drug rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:1963: sdeb sbyor gyi bstan bcos ni /
NK086(lu)003:1964: slob dpon sh+aan+ti pa'i rin chen 'byung gnas lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:1965: de'ang spyir sdeb sbyor gang la bya ba'i gzhi la /
NK086(lu)003:1966: chos rje sa skya pan+di tas sdeb sbyor gyi tshoms
NK086(lu)003:1967: zhes bya ba'i rjes su 'brangs nas rgyun chags rkang
NK086(lu)003:1968: pas ma bcad pa'ang bzhed pa ni rin chen 'byung
NK086(lu)003:1971: brjod pa tshig sdud ma po nyid //
NK086(lu)003:1972: 'di ni lhug pa dag gis gsos //
NK086(lu)003:1973: tshigs bcad la yang lho phyogs pa //
NK086(lu)003:1974: min pa 'di nyid gcig pu bzhed //
NK086(lu)003:1975: de la lci dang yang ba rnams //
NK086(lu)003:1976: mang dang nyung ba nyid spel ba //
NK086(lu)003:1977: mtho dman gyis ni rnam pa de //
NK086(lu)003:1978: brjod pa la sogs rnams la mthong //
NK086(lu)003:1979: zhes gsungs pa dang dgongs pa mthun nam snyam pas /
NK086(lu)003:1980: de 'dra'i rnam bzhag snyan ngag gi gzhung 'dir ma
NK086(lu)003:1981: smos zhes gsung mkhan byung 'dug pa la'ang dpyad pa
NK086(lu)003:1983: rin chen 'byung gnas su gsungs pa ni tshig bcad
NK086(lu)003:1984: kho na'i sdeb sbyor gyi dbang du mdzad pa'o zhes
NK086(lu)003:1986: de'i dbang du byas na sdeb sbyor gang la bya ba'i gzhi tshigs su bcad pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:1988: dz+aa ti gnyis sor de ltar yang //
NK086(lu)003:1989: tshigs bcad rkang bzhi de yang ni //
NK086(lu)003:1990: prit+ta dz+aa ti rnam gnyis dbye //
NK086(lu)003:1991: yi ge bgrang ba prit+ta yin //
NK086(lu)003:1992: phyi mo bgrang ba dz+aa tir 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:2001: mnyam pa'i dz+aa ti dang gsum yod do //
NK086(lu)003:2002: mngon brjod kyi bstan bcos ni /
NK086(lu)003:2004: de yang sgra gcig la don du ma 'jug pa go sgra lta bu dang /
NK086(lu)003:2005: don gcig la ming du ma 'jug pa nyi ma
NK086(lu)003:2006: la rta ljang can dang tsha zer can la sogs
NK086(lu)003:2007: pa ming brgya lhag pa 'byung ba lta bu ste
NK086(lu)003:2009: mngon brjod du ma'i don la ming gcig nyid //
NK086(lu)003:2010: 'jug pa dag phyogs pa dang 'od zer dang //
NK086(lu)003:2011: phyugs sog bcu la go sgra nyid 'jug dang //
NK086(lu)003:2012: don gcig nyid la du ma'i ming 'jug pa //
NK086(lu)003:2013: nyi ma nyid la rta ljang tsha zer can //
NK086(lu)003:2014: nam mkha'i nor bu pad+ma'i gnyen sogs so //
NK086(lu)003:2016: zlos gar gyi bstan bcos ni /
NK086(lu)003:2017: b+ha ra ta dang klu kun tu dga' ba lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:2018: de'i don ni tshig bcad lhug spel mar yod pa
NK086(lu)003:2019: gang zhig /skad rigs bzhi bsres pa'i sgo nas ston
NK086(lu)003:2020: pa'o // de yang mtshams sbyor gyi yan lag sgo la sogs pa lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:2022: rab tu snang byed sogs bcu drug tu phye ba
NK086(lu)003:2023: 'jug pa'i yan lag can dbyangs bdun la sogs pa
NK086(lu)003:2024: rnams dang / rgyan 'byed dang yi ge 'dus pa sogs mtshan nyid sum rtsa drug dang /
NK086(lu)003:2027: mtshams sbyor gzhan rnams kyi yan lag sogs sgyu rtsal gyi rigs rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:2028: gnyis pa ji lta ba ston pa'i bstan bcos ni /
NK086(lu)003:2029: bdag med gnyis gtso bor gtan la 'bebs pa dbu ma'i bstan bcos lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:2030: gsum pa thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa thob pa'i thabs ston pa'i bstan bcos ni /
NK086(lu)003:2031: byang sa dang spyod 'jug lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:2032: de lta bu'i bstan bcos rtsom byed slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid ji lta bu snyam na /
NK086(lu)003:2033: rab chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong ba'i slob dpon
NK086(lu)003:2034: dpal mgon klu sgrub dang 'phags pa thogs med lta
NK086(lu)003:2035: bu yin la / 'bring ni yid dam gyi lhas
NK086(lu)003:2036: dngos su gnang ba thob pa'i slob dpon phyogs kyi
NK086(lu)003:2037: glang po dang tsan+d+ra go mi lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:2038: tha ma'ang rig pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas shing bla
NK086(lu)003:2039: ma brgyud pa'i man ngag yod pa ste slob dpon
NK086(lu)003:2040: dpal spas dang sh+aakya blo gros lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:2041: de yang brgyud pa'i man ngag yod pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:2044: ngas ni man ngag sbyin par bya //
NK086(lu)003:2045: de la man ngag 'di yin te //
NK086(lu)003:2046: dgos pa sdud pa'i don bcas pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:2047: tshig don bcas dang brgal lan bcas //
NK086(lu)003:2048: mtshams sbyor bsnyan de bshad par bya //
NK086(lu)003:2050: yang na sgron ma gsal bar //
NK086(lu)003:2051: rgyud 'di'i ming ni ci zhig yin //
NK086(lu)003:2052: su yi don du 'di nyid mdzad //
NK086(lu)003:2053: su zhig byed po 'di'i tshad ci //
NK086(lu)003:2054: 'di yi dgos pa'ang ci zhig yin //
NK086(lu)003:2055: zhes gleng bslang ba lnga gsungs pa dang rjes su
NK086(lu)003:2056: mthun par rtsis sgo lnga'i sgo nas bshad par bya'o
NK086(lu)003:2058: snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa rin po
NK086(lu)003:2059: che'i rnam gzhag legs bshad snang ba'i dga' ston ces
NK086(lu)003:2060: bya ba las / spyir 'khor 'das kyi chos ngos
NK086(lu)003:2061: bzung zhing de'i mtshan nyid gtan la dbab pa'i chams
NK086(lu)003:2062: bya ba las / te / skabs dang po'o //
NK086(lu)003:2063: de ltar 'khor 'das kyi chos so sor ngos bzung
NK086(lu)003:2064: zhing dam pa'i chos kyi rnam gzhag rags pa tsam
NK086(lu)003:2065: spyir smos nas / de ni dam pa'i chos zab
NK086(lu)003:2066: mo de nyid gang las byung ba'i gzhi rgyal ba
NK086(lu)003:2067: sku gsum gyi ston pa'i rnam gzhag bstan pa la
NK086(lu)003:2068: spyir smos nas / bzhi ste / gdod ma'i mgon po chos kyi skur mngon par byang chub tshul /
NK086(lu)003:2069: de'i rnam 'phrul rdo rje 'chang gis zhing 'dir zhib brnyes tshul /
NK086(lu)003:2070: de las gsungs sku gnyis kyi sprul pa snang tshul /
NK086(lu)003:2071: rgyu 'bras theg pa'i sku dang ye shes kyi khyad par dbye ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:2073: spyir theg dman rnams kyi 'dod par 'o skol gyi
NK086(lu)003:2074: ston pa 'di lta bur yang so so skye bo
NK086(lu)003:2075: grangs med gsum du thar pa cha mthun bsags pa
NK086(lu)003:2076: zhig srid pa tha ma par gyur pa zhig byang
NK086(lu)003:2077: chub snying po rdo rje'i gdan du srod la bdud
NK086(lu)003:2078: btul / gung la bsam gtan bzhi'i dngos gzhis sbyor lam rgyud la bskyed nas /
NK086(lu)003:2079: tho rangs skya rengs 'char ka'i skad cig gcig la
NK086(lu)003:2080: pha rol tu phyin pa drug mngon du mdzad nas
NK086(lu)003:2081: chos dang gzugs sku'i bdag nyid can du sangs rgyas
NK086(lu)003:2082: te / kun shes nas rab bzang gi bar chos
NK086(lu)003:2083: kyi 'khor lo bskor ba sogs las sku gsum gyi
NK086(lu)003:2084: rnam gzhag tshang bar khas mi len la /
NK086(lu)003:2085: theg chen gyi mdo sde rnams su gsungs pa'i sku gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:2086: sngags la'ang phyi nang gi mngon byang lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:2090: yid khams bdud rtsi chos kyi sku /
NK086(lu)003:2091: snying po ye shes rlung ngo bo nyid kyi sku
NK086(lu)003:2092: sogs gdul bya dbang po rno rtul dang lam pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2093: rnal 'byor pa'i mos pa'i dbang gis de ltar bstan
NK086(lu)003:2095: 'dir theg mchog bla na med pa 'od gsal rdo
NK086(lu)003:2096: rje snying po thun mong ma yin pa'i lung ltar
NK086(lu)003:2097: 'chad na / 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das
NK086(lu)003:2098: pa gnyis gang du'ang dbyer mi 'byed pa kun gyi
NK086(lu)003:2099: sngon rol du srid zhi yongs la mnga' dbang sgyur
NK086(lu)003:2100: ba'i ston pa kun tu bzang po nyid dbyings bde
NK086(lu)003:2101: bar gshegs pa'i snying po gdod ma'i gzhi las gzhi
NK086(lu)003:2102: snang du shar ba'i skad cig la rang snang du
NK086(lu)003:2103: ngo shes pas rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid rang
NK086(lu)003:2104: sar grol bas dus gsum mtha' dbus thog mtha' sogs
NK086(lu)003:2105: shes bya thams cad la rnam par mi rtog pa
NK086(lu)003:2106: rang byung gi ye shes su sangs rgyas pa ste
NK086(lu)003:2108: thog ma dbus mtha' med cing rnam dbyer med //
NK086(lu)003:2109: gnyis med gsum bral dri med rnam rtog med //
NK086(lu)003:2111: 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:2112: rnam par rtog med lhun gyis grub //
NK086(lu)003:2113: dus gsum sangs rgyas las byed pa //
NK086(lu)003:2114: sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med //
NK086(lu)003:2115: dang po'i sangs rgyas ris med pa //
NK086(lu)003:2117: de'ang don la med kyang 'khrul snang blo bur pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2118: sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa rang ngo la
NK086(lu)003:2119: yongs su dag pas spang ba chen po /
NK086(lu)003:2120: shes dang shes bya gnyis su med pa'i ye shes
NK086(lu)003:2121: chen pos srid zhi ris su ma chad pa kun
NK086(lu)003:2122: khyab tu gzigs pas rtogs pa chen po /
NK086(lu)003:2123: de dag gi mthus 'gro ba thams cad kyi don
NK086(lu)003:2124: dmigs pa med par rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2125: phrin las mdzad pa ni sems chen po ste /
NK086(lu)003:2127: sems can kun mchog nyid sems dang //
NK086(lu)003:2128: spangs dang rtogs dang gsum po la //
NK086(lu)003:2129: chen po gsum gyi rang byung gi //
NK086(lu)003:2130: ched du bya ba 'di shes bya //
NK086(lu)003:2132: de nyid ci yang mi dmigs pa spros pa'i mtha'
NK086(lu)003:2133: thams cad dang bral ba chos kyi dbyings kyi ye
NK086(lu)003:2134: shes dang / 'khor 'das bzang ngan med pa mnyam
NK086(lu)003:2135: pa nyid du gzigs pas srid bzhi'i mtha' la mi
NK086(lu)003:2136: gnas pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes te /
NK086(lu)003:2137: ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes la dbang 'byor
NK086(lu)003:2138: pas rgyu'i theg pa dag gis 'jug pa thams cad
NK086(lu)003:2139: chos kyi dbyings su zhi ba'i 'gog pa dam pa
NK086(lu)003:2140: la gnas pa bshad pa'i stong rkyang tsam las 'das
NK086(lu)003:2141: pa ste / de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi so
NK086(lu)003:2142: so rang gi ye shes kyis gzigs pa'i yul sa
NK086(lu)003:2143: bcu'i dbang phyug rgyal sras rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:2144: gdul bya'i tshogs la gzugs sku mig la snang ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2145: gsung rna bar thos pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2146: 'phags pa'i tshul khrims kyi dri snom pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2147: chos kyi ro myong ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2148: ting nge 'dzin bde ba'i reg bya snang ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2149: rtog dpyod kyi shes rab kyis chos la 'jal ba
NK086(lu)003:2150: sogs kyi gazhi'am rgyur gyur pa'i thim la ma rmugs
NK086(lu)003:2151: pa'i ye shes phra ba'i rang bzhin nang gsal gzhon
NK086(lu)003:2152: nu bum pa sku'i zhing khams chen por shel 'od
NK086(lu)003:2153: nang du bsdus pa'i tshul can du bzhugs so //
NK086(lu)003:2154: de'i byin rlabs las rang snang zhing khams lhun grub
NK086(lu)003:2155: stug po bkod pa bsam brjod dang mtshan ma'i yul
NK086(lu)003:2156: las ring du song ba rgya ma chad cing phyogs
NK086(lu)003:2158: sangs rgyas nyid kyi ye shes kyis bsdus pa'i rang
NK086(lu)003:2159: snang longs spyod rdzogs sku'i dkyil 'khor nges pa lnga
NK086(lu)003:2160: ldan gyi bdag nyid can rigs lnga'i ston pa rnams
NK086(lu)003:2161: kyang sku dang ye shes tha mi dad kyi rol
NK086(lu)003:2162: pa chen por bzhugs pa las /
NK086(lu)003:2163: dus gzhan du gdod ma'i gzhi las gzhi snang du
NK086(lu)003:2164: shar ba'i rtsal rang ngo ma shes pas rmi lam
NK086(lu)003:2165: lta bu'i sems can rnams 'khrul pa'i rgyu med bzhin
NK086(lu)003:2166: du 'khrul pa ltar snang ba'i sdug bsngal gyi 'khor
NK086(lu)003:2168: brtse ba'i thugs rje skyes nas de dag gi don
NK086(lu)003:2169: du zhing khams kyi bkod pa rgya chen po sprul
NK086(lu)003:2170: pa ni rang snang longs spyod rdzogs sku ye shes
NK086(lu)003:2171: rigs lnga gangs chen mtsho'i phyag rgya'i gnas rnams dang
NK086(lu)003:2172: / ba spu'i khung bu re re la'ang 'byung ba
NK086(lu)003:2173: bzhi'i rdul phra rab ji snyed pa'i go thams cad
NK086(lu)003:2174: na zhing khams chen po dbyib dang tshad dang thog
NK086(lu)003:2175: tha la sogs par brjod pa'i yul thams cad las
NK086(lu)003:2176: 'das pa kho nas rgyas par gtams shing /
NK086(lu)003:2177: de dag kyang rnam pa tha dad pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2179: rnam pa gzhan du skye zhing 'gyur ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2181: rdzas gzhan gyis gos pa cung zad med par zhing
NK086(lu)003:2182: dang sku rgyal mtshos chos kyi dbyings gang bar gyur
NK086(lu)003:2183: ste / sdong po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:2184: spu yi rtse mo gcig la yang //
NK086(lu)003:2185: zhing rnams bkod pa bsam mi khyab //
NK086(lu)003:2186: sna tshogs dbyibs kyang tha dad med //
NK086(lu)003:2187: de dag 'dres par gyur pa med //
NK086(lu)003:2189: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:2191: nam mkhas ji tsam khyab pa de tsam du //
NK086(lu)003:2192: de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhing dang skus khyab bo //
NK086(lu)003:2194: de dag kyang sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi so so'i
NK086(lu)003:2195: zhing khams mi 'dra ba gsum du bkod pa ni
NK086(lu)003:2196: chos sku'i dus su 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i
NK086(lu)003:2197: zhing dang / rang snang longs sku'i dus su tshangs pa rnga sgra'i zhing dang /
NK086(lu)003:2198: sprul sku'i dus su tshangs chen gyi bskal pa zhes bya la /
NK086(lu)003:2199: de dag rnams su gdod ma'i mgon po nyid kyi
NK086(lu)003:2200: sprul pa'i sangs rgyas rgya mtsho dus gsum du byon
NK086(lu)003:2201: pa rnams dang / sems can gyi khams rgya mtsho
NK086(lu)003:2202: yang yod de 'byung ba bzhi dang nam mkhas khyab
NK086(lu)003:2203: tshad thams cad tshangs chen bskal pa 'di'i khongs su
NK086(lu)003:2204: pa rnams dang / 'du la / der ma dag pa'i sems can rnams 'chi 'pho ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2206: sangs rgyas rnams mya ngan la 'da' ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2209: lam sgrub pa la sogs bde sdug gi snang ba sna tshogs la spyod pa'i tshul dang /
NK086(lu)003:2210: de ltar rdul phran re re'i na'ang ri gling rgya mtsho sogs zhing khams tshad med pa snang zhing /
NK086(lu)003:2211: der ma zad rdul gcig gi steng gi 'jig rten
NK086(lu)003:2212: de'i rdul phra rab gcig la'ang sems can gyi khams
NK086(lu)003:2213: tshad med pa gnas pa rnams bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2214: rnam 'phrul dang / byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi
NK086(lu)003:2215: zhing sbyong ba'i smon lam gyi mthu chen po dang
NK086(lu)003:2216: rnam 'phrul dang / / sems can rnams kyi 'khrul
NK086(lu)003:2217: snang gis las kyi tshogs mngon par 'du bgyis pa
NK086(lu)003:2218: rnam 'phrul dang / / dang / chos nyid kyis
NK086(lu)003:2219: rab tu thob pa la sogs pa'i rgyu dang rkyen
NK086(lu)003:2220: gyis rab tu tshogs pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2221: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK086(lu)003:2222: sangs rgyas ye shes yul ni bsam yas pas //
NK086(lu)003:2223: byin rlabs rnam 'phrul de dag 'di lta bu //
NK086(lu)003:2224: zhing khams rgya mtshor bstan pa mtha' dbus med //
NK086(lu)003:2225: rnam par snang mdzad chos kyis yongs su sbyangs //
NK086(lu)003:2226: byang chub sems ni kun gyi bsam pa bzhin //
NK086(lu)003:2227: smon lam rgya mtsho bsam yas rnams sbyang shing //
NK086(lu)003:2228: sems can las rnams rgya mtsho bsam yas pas //
NK086(lu)003:2229: phyogs kun zhing rnams rgya mtsho thams cad 'byung //
NK086(lu)003:2230: byang chub sems dpa' kun gyi rnam 'phrul dang //
NK086(lu)003:2231: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid la 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK086(lu)003:2232: smon lam rgya mtsho thams cad mngon bsgrubs shing //
NK086(lu)003:2233: nam mkha'i dbyings la 'byams klas zhing 'byung ngo //
NK086(lu)003:2234: spyod pa rgya mtshos mtha' dang dbus med rnams //
NK086(lu)003:2235: spyod cing tshad med bde gshegs yul la 'jug /phyogs kyi zhing rnams rgya mtsho kun byang zhing //
NK086(lu)003:2236: bskal pa thams yas zhing rnams re rer sbyong //
NK086(lu)003:2237: sems can bsam dbyings bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK086(lu)003:2238: las kyi zhing rnams rgya mtsho thams cad 'byung //
NK086(lu)003:2241: skra tsam khyon la dus gsum tshad snyed kyi //
NK086(lu)003:2242: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho zhing rnams rgya mtsho dang //
NK086(lu)003:2243: bskal pa rgya mtsho spyod cing rab tu 'jug /ces so //
NK086(lu)003:2244: de dag kyang don la med pa gsal snang yin
NK086(lu)003:2245: te chos kyi dbyings la kun rdzob pa rnams gdod
NK086(lu)003:2246: nas grub ma myong pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:2247: gnyis pa de las zhing 'dir rdo rje 'chang gis sangs rgyas bsnyes tshul ni /
NK086(lu)003:2248: zhing 'di'i gdul bya'i don du thog ma'i sangs rgyas
NK086(lu)003:2249: kun tu bzang po nyid kyis thabs la mkhas pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2250: rnam 'phrul chen pos so skye rang ga mas sems
NK086(lu)003:2251: bskyed pa ltar bstan nas sangs rgyas pa'i tshul dang
NK086(lu)003:2252: mdzad pa'i rol pa bkye ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:2253: tshul de lta bu ni thun mong gi theg par yang grags te /
NK086(lu)003:2254: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:2255: dpa' bo chen po thabs mkhas te //
NK086(lu)003:2256: sems can yongs su smin bya'i phyir //
NK086(lu)003:2257: bye ba phrag brgyar rgyal ba nyid //
NK086(lu)003:2258: sangs rgyas nyid du bstan gyur kyang //
NK086(lu)003:2259: da dung du yang 'dren pa khyod //
NK086(lu)003:2260: sangs rgyas mdzad pa mang ston mdzod //
NK086(lu)003:2263: byang chub rgya mtsho rab bsnyes gyur nas kyang //
NK086(lu)003:2264: sems can rgya mtsho rab tu min bya'i phyir //
NK086(lu)003:2265: byang chub sems bskyed rgya mtsho ston mdzad cing //
NK086(lu)003:2266: mi 'grib spyod pa rgya mtsho dus kun ston //
NK086(lu)003:2267: bde gshegs rnams kyi rnam 'phrul de 'dra'o //
NK086(lu)003:2269: 'di nas bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol
NK086(lu)003:2270: du zhing khams rang bzhin rnam par bkod pa zhes
NK086(lu)003:2271: bya bar / thog ma'i mgon po'i rnam par 'phrul
NK086(lu)003:2272: pas sangs rgyas me tog mdzes pa chen po la
NK086(lu)003:2273: gser gyi rdo rje gcig phul nas dang po byang
NK086(lu)003:2275: de nas skye ba gnyis nas khyim bdag legs sbyin
NK086(lu)003:2276: gyi sras nor bu'i phreng ba zhes par gyur nas
NK086(lu)003:2277: sangs rgyas 'khor lo legs par spyod pa'i drung du
NK086(lu)003:2278: chos mnyan / de nas glog gi 'od ces bya
NK086(lu)003:2279: ba'i sras bram ze'i khye'u legs byin ces par gyur
NK086(lu)003:2280: te sangs rgyas dge ba'i blo gros la chos nyan
NK086(lu)003:2281: cing lo bdun tu ting nge 'dzin la gnas shing
NK086(lu)003:2282: chos mnyan / / bdun cu rtsa lnga'i mthar gyis
NK086(lu)003:2283: rin po che'i phung po rnam par bkod pa zhes
NK086(lu)003:2284: bya ba'i ri bo'i rtse mor mngon par rdzogs par
NK086(lu)003:2285: sangs rgyas pa'i tshul bstan nas chos sku'i dgongs par
NK086(lu)003:2286: bskal chen gcig tu bzhugs shing /
NK086(lu)003:2287: longs spyod thams cad rdzogs pa'i sku rgyan dang kha
NK086(lu)003:2288: dog gi 'khor lor rang byon cing de nyid kyi
NK086(lu)003:2289: ngang las rang snang gi rgyal ba rigs lnga'i dkyil
NK086(lu)003:2290: 'khor grangs las 'das pa rang byung la /
NK086(lu)003:2291: snang cha las mtshan dang dpe byad yongs su rdzogs
NK086(lu)003:2292: pa rdo rje 'chang gi skur byung ba ni thugs
NK086(lu)003:2293: bskyed pa'i rten rdo rje phul ba las byung ba'o
NK086(lu)003:2294: // de dag kyang sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK086(lu)003:2295: rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i mdzad pa sum cu rtsa drug
NK086(lu)003:2296: la dbang 'byor pa ste snyiing thig gi 'chad tshul
NK086(lu)003:2298: don la gong du bshad pa ltar thog ma'i mgon
NK086(lu)003:2299: po'i thabs la mkhas pa'i sgyu 'phrul tsam las tha
NK086(lu)003:2300: mi dad cing / gsang sngags kyi rgyud phal cher ston pa'i rdo rje 'chang dang /
NK086(lu)003:2301: snying thig yang gsang gi rdo rje gnas zab mo ston pa la kun tu bzang po dang /
NK086(lu)003:2302: gzhan du dam pa dang po'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK086(lu)003:2303: rdo rje sems dpa' sogs mtshan gyi rnam grangs du mas bsnyad pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2305: rab tu dag pa kun gyi mchog /gdod nas grol ba de bzhin gshegs //
NK086(lu)003:2306: kun tu bzang po kun gyi bdag /byang chub sems nyid nges pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:2308: sems dpa' thog ma tha ma med //
NK086(lu)003:2309: rdo rje sems dpa' dga' ba che //
NK086(lu)003:2310: kun tu bzang po kun gyi bdag /rdo rje snying po gtso bo'i gtso //
NK086(lu)003:2311: gdod ma tha ma med phyir yang //
NK086(lu)003:2312: dam pa'i dang po zhes 'dod de //
NK086(lu)003:2313: 'khor lo kun gyi gtso phyir na //
NK086(lu)003:2314: dam pa dam pa'i dbang phyug yin //
NK086(lu)003:2316: gsum pa gzugs sku'i sprul pa snang la tshul gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:2320: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim las /
NK086(lu)003:2321: lhun rdzogs rig pa rang snang ba'i //
NK086(lu)003:2322: zhing dang gzhal yas gdan khri rgyan //
NK086(lu)003:2323: 'od zer du mar snang ba ste //
NK086(lu)003:2325: chos kyi sku chen po nang gsal chos nyid kyi
NK086(lu)003:2326: ngang du bzhugs pa de nyid man shel gyi nang
NK086(lu)003:2327: 'od kha dog lnga nyi zer gyi rkyen gyis gsal
NK086(lu)003:2328: ba ltar / rang snang gi yul la phyi gsal
NK086(lu)003:2329: mched pa'i ye shes kyi snang cha sku dang zhing
NK086(lu)003:2330: khams tshad med pa la longs su spyod pa'i gnas
NK086(lu)003:2331: ba ltar / su / sprul pa'i bkod pa rnam
NK086(lu)003:2332: par snang mdzad gangs chen mtsho'i phyag gi mthil na
NK086(lu)003:2333: pad+ma'i sdong po skyes pa'i 'dab ma dang ze 'phos
NK086(lu)003:2334: rnams la zhing khams nyi shu rtsa lnga re brtsegs
NK086(lu)003:2335: ba ltar / su / mar gnas shing / zhabs
NK086(lu)003:2336: kyi skyil krung man chad las spos chu'i rgyun 'beb
NK086(lu)003:2337: pa dag tu'ang zhing khams bcu drug re yod pa
NK086(lu)003:2338: de rnams su rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas nges pa lnga
NK086(lu)003:2339: ldan gyi rang bzhin mtshan dang dpe byad rgya mtsho'i
NK086(lu)003:2340: bdag nyid rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor longs spyod
NK086(lu)003:2341: pa bgrangs kyis mi lang bar bkod pa de dag
NK086(lu)003:2342: ni ye shes gsang chen mtsho'i zhing dang sku'i bkod
NK086(lu)003:2343: pa longs sku chen po'i mtshan gzhi ste /
NK086(lu)003:2344: de dag rdul gcig gi steng na rab 'byams rgya
NK086(lu)003:2345: mtsho'i rdul snyed kyi zhing yang mi 'gal zhing sku
NK086(lu)003:2346: gcig la rab 'byams rgya mtsho'i sku 'du ba dang
NK086(lu)003:2347: / sku re res kyang zhing rab 'byams rgya mtshor
NK086(lu)003:2348: khyab pa sogs sgyu 'phrul rdo rje rol mo gsang
NK086(lu)003:2349: ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas su shes par
NK086(lu)003:2350: / bya ste / gsang ba snying po las /
NK086(lu)003:2352: dbyings nas dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod //
NK086(lu)003:2355: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed sangs rgyas dag /ces sogs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:2356: zhing khams de dag la mnga' dbang mdzad pa'i ston
NK086(lu)003:2357: pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku de'ang rang bzhin bdun
NK086(lu)003:2358: gyi khyad par dang ldan pa yin te /
NK086(lu)003:2359: de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i rang bzhin /
NK086(lu)003:2360: yon tan ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK086(lu)003:2361: ye shes mtha' dbus dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK086(lu)003:2362: 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad kyang rang gi ngo bo bstan du med pa'i rang bzhin /
NK086(lu)003:2363: mnyam pa nyid mngon du mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK086(lu)003:2364: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i rang bzhin /
NK086(lu)003:2365: dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK086(lu)003:2366: bdun gyi bdag nyid chen por lhun gyis grub pa
NK086(lu)003:2367: nyid gdul bya'i dbang gis sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan
NK086(lu)003:2368: ma sna tshogs par snang ba'i rnam 'gyur gyi cha
NK086(lu)003:2369: las mtshan dang dpe byad kyi rnam pa 'bar ba'i
NK086(lu)003:2370: gzugs kyi sku la phyag zhabs 'khor los mtshan pa
NK086(lu)003:2371: sogs mtshan bzang po so gnyis dang /
NK086(lu)003:2372: sen mo zangs mdog sogs dpe byad brgyad cu rnams te thun mong gi mtshan dpe rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:2373: ston pa'i thugs ye shes bzhis phye pa'i rtsal las phyi'i mtshan dpe /
NK086(lu)003:2374: rtsa 'khor rnams dag pa'i cha las nang gi mtshan dpe /
NK086(lu)003:2375: khams byang chub kyi sems rnam par dag pa'i cha las gsang ba'i mtshan dpe ste /
NK086(lu)003:2376: longs spyod rdzogs pa chen po la rtsa khams rnam
NK086(lu)003:2377: par dag pa bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin du
NK086(lu)003:2378: ro mnyam pa ni rgyan gyi nang nas mdzes byed
NK086(lu)003:2379: mchog tu gyur par bshad de /
NK086(lu)003:2381: a li ka li bde ba gnyis //
NK086(lu)003:2382: phan tshud ma 'dres gcig par shes //
NK086(lu)003:2383: bcu drug ngos gnyis mtshan dang ldan //
NK086(lu)003:2384: phyogs gcig ye shes lnga ldan pa //
NK086(lu)003:2385: brgyad cu'o bzod sogs rgyu las 'phags //
NK086(lu)003:2387: rtog tshogs las shin tu 'das pa'i zag pa dang
NK086(lu)003:2388: bral ba'i rnam par grol ba'i ye shes gzigs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2389: phung po dang / tshul khrims kyi phung po /
NK086(lu)003:2392: rnam par grol ba'i phung po lnga po yang de
NK086(lu)003:2393: bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK086(lu)003:2394: lnga'i bdag nyid chen po rnam snang /
NK086(lu)003:2403: dam tshig sgrol mar rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK086(lu)003:2404: pas mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po dang rnam
NK086(lu)003:2405: kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa nyid kha sbyor du
NK086(lu)003:2420: khro mo sogs rol pa rmad du byung ba'i 'khor
NK086(lu)003:2421: lo'i bkod pa rnams kyang yul yul can las 'das
NK086(lu)003:2422: pa'i ye shes rang snang gi yul kun tu longs
NK086(lu)003:2423: spyod pa'i cha nas bzhag pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2424: mthong thos snom myong bzhi yang rim bzhin /
NK086(lu)003:2429: yul gzugs sgra dri ro bzhi yang /
NK086(lu)003:2437: ljags te dbang po bzhi yang /
NK086(lu)003:2445: ma nges pa'i dus bzhi po yang /
NK086(lu)003:2450: gzhan yang rdo rje btsun mo dang snyoms par 'jug
NK086(lu)003:2451: pa'i gsang ba'i yul dang rnam shes gsum 'dus kyi
NK086(lu)003:2454: reg shes kyis dga' ba chen po'i ro nyams su
NK086(lu)003:2455: myong ba yang mthar byed kyi chen po bzhi dang
NK086(lu)003:2456: / rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi yang khro mo chen
NK086(lu)003:2457: mo bzhi'i rang bzhin dang ldan pa sogs mtha' yas
NK086(lu)003:2458: pa'i 'khor gyi rnam pa rnams kyang ston pa nyid
NK086(lu)003:2459: kyi rol pa dkyil dang 'khor gyi tshul du snang
NK086(lu)003:2460: ba mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo las gzhan du
NK086(lu)003:2463: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK086(lu)003:2468: bzhugs pa dkyil dang 'khor gyi tshul //
NK086(lu)003:2470: de dag kyang sangs rgyas rang snang gi ye shes
NK086(lu)003:2471: rnam pa thams cad pa'i bdag nyid sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK086(lu)003:2472: ba'i rol pa rnam pa kun tu zhing dang /
NK086(lu)003:2474: kun tu gzhal med khang dang /
NK086(lu)003:2486: dbang po re res kyang dbang po thams cad kyi
NK086(lu)003:2487: bya ba byed pa ste ye shes kyi rtsal 'gag
NK086(lu)003:2488: pa med pas chos kyi dbyings mtha' klas par khyab
NK086(lu)003:2491: kun tu bzang po'i zhal ni phyogs bcur gzigs //
NK086(lu)003:2492: kun gzigs kun bzang sku la mdun rgyab med //
NK086(lu)003:2493: phyogs bcu gang ba spyan gyis rnam par gzigs //
NK086(lu)003:2496: thams cad nas ni phyag dang zhabs //
NK086(lu)003:2497: kun nas spyan dang dbu dang zhal //
NK086(lu)003:2498: kun nas gsan ldan 'jig rten mtha' //thams cad khyab par bzhugs pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:2500: sangs rgyas kyi yul de ni sangs rgyas kho na'i
NK086(lu)003:2501: rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i phyir sa bcu'i dbang phyug rnams
NK086(lu)003:2503: sgrib pa mtha' dag las ma grol zhing ji lta
NK086(lu)003:2504: ba dang ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK086(lu)003:2505: spyan rdul dang bral ba ma brnyes pa'i phyir te
NK086(lu)003:2507: ngag yul min phyir don dam gyis bsdus phyir //
NK086(lu)003:2508: rtogs gnas min phyir dpe las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK086(lu)003:2509: bla na med phyir srid zhis ma bsdus phyir //
NK086(lu)003:2510: rgyal yul 'phags rnams kyis kyang bsam mi khyab //
NK086(lu)003:2512: gang du 'jig rten las 'das pa'i zhing khams phun
NK086(lu)003:2513: sum tshogs pa de rnams kyang rang snang gzhi'i 'od
NK086(lu)003:2514: gsal chen po'i snang cha dag pa rab 'byams kyi
NK086(lu)003:2515: 'khor lo'i snod bcud du shar ba rmi lam dag
NK086(lu)003:2517: gang gi tshe gzung 'dzin bag chags cha bcas rnam
NK086(lu)003:2518: par byang ba'i gnas skabs der snang ba las phyogs
NK086(lu)003:2519: gzhan shing du rdul rdzas rang mtshan du grub pa
NK086(lu)003:2520: zhig yod par mi bsams te /
NK086(lu)003:2522: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK086(lu)003:2523: bde chen zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK086(lu)003:2524: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pa na /
NK086(lu)003:2525: ngan song gnas kyang 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK086(lu)003:2527: gnyis pa sprul pa'i sku ni /
NK086(lu)003:2528: de yang gdul bya rang rgyud kyi bder gshegs snying
NK086(lu)003:2529: po la sgrib byed kyi dri ma ma dag pa
NK086(lu)003:2531: shin tu dag pa gsum gyi go rim la ltos
NK086(lu)003:2532: nas 'dul byed kyi ston pa yang de ltar snang
NK086(lu)003:2533: ba yin te / shin tu dag pa chos kyi
NK086(lu)003:2534: sku la 'khor 'das ro mnyam chen po nyid kyi
NK086(lu)003:2535: phyir don dam pa'i dbyings las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK086(lu)003:2536: gzugs kyi sku ni rtsol ba med pa'i thugs rjee
NK086(lu)003:2537: chen po'i rnam 'phrul 'gag pa med pa'i rol pa
NK086(lu)003:2539: gdul bya 'dul byed gnyis ltar snang ba'i gzhan dbang
NK086(lu)003:2540: gi tshul du mos pa'i chu snod rnyog pa med
NK086(lu)003:2541: pa ji snyed du sprul pa'i zla gzugs de snyed
NK086(lu)003:2544: ji ltar beed+aura sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK086(lu)003:2545: lha dbang lus kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK086(lu)003:2546: de bzhin 'gro sems sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK086(lu)003:2547: thub pa'i dbang po'i sku yi gzugs brnyan 'char //
NK086(lu)003:2550: rgyal ba'i chos nyid lus med rab zhi ba //
NK086(lu)003:2551: gnyis med rang bzhin med par thugs chud nas //
NK086(lu)003:2552: gzugs sku bzang po mtshan gyis brgyan pa yis //
NK086(lu)003:2553: 'gro ba ma lus bkang zhing ston par mdzad //
NK086(lu)003:2555: de la dbye na gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:2559: dang po rang bzhin sprul pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:2560: gong gi dbyings snang longs sku chen po'i ston pa
NK086(lu)003:2561: de nyid ji ltar dwangs shel la gzugs brnyan 'phos
NK086(lu)003:2562: pa ltar cung zad dag pa'i gdul bya sa bcu'i
NK086(lu)003:2563: dbang phyug rnams la snang ba ni 'di ltar rang
NK086(lu)003:2564: bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams dbus na 'og min dang
NK086(lu)003:2565: / phyogs bzhir rim pa bzhin mngon par dga' ba /
NK086(lu)003:2569: ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa gzugs kyi rgyal po
NK086(lu)003:2570: la sogs pa lnga po mtshan dang dpe byad rgya
NK086(lu)003:2571: mtsho'i bdag nyid can zhi ba dang khro bo'i rnam
NK086(lu)003:2572: 'gyur dpag tu med pa'i skus chos rnams 'jal zhing
NK086(lu)003:2573: ston pa dang / gdul bya'i nyon mongs pa lnga'i gnyen por che ba'i zhing khams lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:2576: ye shes lnga la sogs pas brjod du med cing
NK086(lu)003:2577: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK086(lu)003:2578: ba de nyid / ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku
NK086(lu)003:2579: dang 'khor rgyud gzhan gyis bsdus pa'i phyir phyed snang
NK086(lu)003:2580: rang bzhin sprul pa zhes nyi zla kha sbyor chen
NK086(lu)003:2581: po'i rgyud las phye bar mdzad pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:2582: de dang mtshungs par dbu ma pa chos kyi bshes gnyen gyis /
NK086(lu)003:2583: byang sems mthong lam pa yan chad la snang ba'i
NK086(lu)003:2584: longs sku btags pa bar bshad pa sku 'di dang
NK086(lu)003:2585: smon lam / tshogs kyi 'phen pa'am bzhed pa tsam
NK086(lu)003:2586: gyis phye ba'i 'og min gyis gnas gcig kho nar
NK086(lu)003:2587: mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya ba'i phyir rnam pa
NK086(lu)003:2588: rab tu mang po'i longs spyod rdzogs sku 'og min
NK086(lu)003:2589: rnams na gnas pa'i sprul pa'i sku 'ba' zhig rgya
NK086(lu)003:2590: chen por snang bar zad do //
NK086(lu)003:2593: 'dod pa'i kham dang gzugs med du //
NK086(lu)003:2594: sangs rgyas rnam par 'tshang rgya mi //
NK086(lu)003:2595: gzugs kyi khams kyi 'og min du //
NK086(lu)003:2597: zhes pa la sogs kyis mi yul du mchog gi
NK086(lu)003:2598: sprul sku sangs ma rgyas pa'i gong rol du 'og
NK086(lu)003:2599: min du 'tshang rgya bar shad pa'i lung don skabs
NK086(lu)003:2602: de nyid kyi ngang las 'gro ba 'dul ba'i sprul
NK086(lu)003:2603: pa'i sku ni 'jig rten gyi khams ma lus par
NK086(lu)003:2604: gdul bya'i tshogs yongs su smin par mdzad pa'i phyir
NK086(lu)003:2605: thabs la mkhas pas rnam par rol pa bsam gyis
NK086(lu)003:2606: mi khyab pa'i tshul ston pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2608: khams rnams kun tu sna tshogs shing //
NK086(lu)003:2609: dpag med bsam yas sprul pa yis //
NK086(lu)003:2610: sems can kun gyi don sgrub pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:2612: dga' ldan gyi gnas na bzhugs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2617: byang chub snying po gshegs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2618: bdud kyi dpung bcom pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2619: mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2620: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2621: yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2623: chos nus pa ston pa la mkhas pas dus gcig
NK086(lu)003:2624: tu phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams rab 'byams su
NK086(lu)003:2625: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul ston pa mchog gi
NK086(lu)003:2627: de re re la'ang gdul bya rigs drug so so'i
NK086(lu)003:2628: dbang shes la rang rang gi rigs dang mthun pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2629: 'dul byed rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug tu
NK086(lu)003:2630: sprul nas don mdzad pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2631: glang po'i rtsal lta bu'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:2632: 'jam dpal 'di la byang chub sems dpa' chen pos
NK086(lu)003:2633: pad+mo chen po zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK086(lu)003:2635: sems can dmyal ba'i gnas yongs su bzung ba'ang yongs su 'dzin te /
NK086(lu)003:2636: de lta'i bde ba cung zad yod pa de dag thams cad de na myang bar byed do //
NK086(lu)003:2637: sems can de dag kyang de dmyal bas dmyal ba mthong ste /
NK086(lu)003:2638: de cha lugs des sems can dmyal ba pa'i sems
NK086(lu)003:2639: can de dag dmyal ba dang bral bar gyur pa
NK086(lu)003:2642: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK086(lu)003:2644: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa ni tshad med de /
NK086(lu)003:2645: 'gro ba gang dang gang 'dul ba de dang de'i
NK086(lu)003:2646: gzugs dang kha dog dang ming gis don mdzad do
NK086(lu)003:2648: 'o na 'gro ba drug gi gnas der thub pa ji lta bus 'gro don mdzad ce na /
NK086(lu)003:2650: lha yi gnas na brgya byin mgon //
NK086(lu)003:2651: lha ma yin la thag bzang ris //
NK086(lu)003:2653: yi dwags gnas na kha 'bar te //
NK086(lu)003:2654: byol song seng ge nyid du smra //
NK086(lu)003:2655: dmyal ba las kyi gshin rje mgon //
NK086(lu)003:2657: de ltar gnas rigs drug po ni gong du bshad
NK086(lu)003:2658: pa'i ye shes gangs chen mtsho'i zhing khams rdul snyed
NK086(lu)003:2659: kyi dbus kyi phyag mthil pad+ma'i snying po la gnas
NK086(lu)003:2660: pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams rgyud nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK086(lu)003:2661: brtsegs mar yod pa'i bcu gsum pa mi mjed 'jig
NK086(lu)003:2663: de la mi mjed ces pa bzod pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2664: rtul phod pa ste zhing 'di'i sems can rnams 'dod chags la mi mjed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2665: zhe sdang la mi mjed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2666: gti mug la mi mjed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2667: nyon mongs pa'i 'ching ba rnams la mi mjed pa zhes bshad pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2668: s+aa ha'i sgra ni bzod pa'am nus pa la 'jug pa'i phyir de skad du grags so //
NK086(lu)003:2669: 'gro ba so so'i las snang yang /
NK086(lu)003:2671: las kyi bye brag bsam mi khyab //
NK086(lu)003:2673: gshin rje'i 'jig rten s+n+rel zhi ste //
NK086(lu)003:2674: byol song lha min gyen thur 'gro //
NK086(lu)003:2677: mgo gyen bstan du 'gro ba mtho ris /
NK086(lu)003:2679: mthar bstan gyis 'gro ba dmyal ba dang yi dwags te /
NK086(lu)003:2680: de drug po stong gsum 'jig rten gcig gi nang du tshang ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:2682: stong gsum gcig la chags tshul drug /sprul sku gcig gi zhing du grags //
NK086(lu)003:2684: rlung dkyil nas 'og min gyi bar gling bzhi ba'i 'jig rten khams te /
NK086(lu)003:2685: de stong phrag gcig tu bgrangs pa khor yug gcig gis bskor ba stong dang po dang /
NK086(lu)003:2686: de 'dra ba stong la stong bar ma ste mu khyud gnyis pas bskor ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2687: stong bar ma de 'dra ba stong la stong gsum
NK086(lu)003:2688: pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams mu khyud gsum pas bskor
NK086(lu)003:2689: ba dang / de lta bu bye ba phrag brgya la rab 'byams mtshams sbyor /
NK086(lu)003:2690: de nyid bye ba phrag brgya la rab 'byams rgyud /
NK086(lu)003:2691: de yang bye ba phrag brgya la rab 'byams rgya mtsho'i 'jig rten gyi khams /
NK086(lu)003:2692: de 'dra ba dung phyur phrag bcu la gzhi dang
NK086(lu)003:2693: snying po me tog gis brgyan pa'i zhing gcig ste
NK086(lu)003:2694: mchog gi sprul sku gcig zhing du bshad cing /
NK086(lu)003:2695: gnas de dag tu gdul bya'i khams dbang spyod tshul
NK086(lu)003:2696: ji snyed pa de snyed du 'dul byed kyi sgron
NK086(lu)003:2697: ma rnam par bkod nas 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis
NK086(lu)003:2698: sems can gyi don la spyod pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2699: de yang sku bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba /
NK086(lu)003:2701: rdzul 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul ba /
NK086(lu)003:2702: gsung rig pas 'dul ba dang bzhi las /
NK086(lu)003:2704: ston pa sprul pa'i sku'i mdzad pa'i tshul ni bsam
NK086(lu)003:2705: gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas yin pas grangs sogs mtha'
NK086(lu)003:2706: gcig tu nges bzung byar med cing theg chen gyi
NK086(lu)003:2707: mdo sde rnams su'ang mang nyung ci rigs 'byung ba
NK086(lu)003:2709: 'dir gtso che ba dag bsdu bas /
NK086(lu)003:2717: yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba rnams ni sku bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:2718: de dag dngos su mthong ba'i gdul bya rnams bsod
NK086(lu)003:2719: nams tshad med pa dang ldan pa'i phyir de ltar
NK086(lu)003:2720: du brjod do // gnyis pa thugs mngon sum pas 'dul ba ni /
NK086(lu)003:2721: dus gsum la ma chags ma thogs pa'i ye shes
NK086(lu)003:2722: kyis shes bya thams cad la 'jug pa nyid kyis
NK086(lu)003:2723: dus gsum so sor mi rtog bzhin du /
NK086(lu)003:2724: kun tu sgrib pa med par dus mkhyen pa'i mngon shes /
NK086(lu)003:2725: kun tu ma bsgribs par gzhan sems mkhyen pa'i mngon shes /
NK086(lu)003:2726: thams cad kun tu gzigs pa spyan gyi mngon shes /
NK086(lu)003:2727: thams cad kun tu gsan pa snyan gyi mngon shes /
NK086(lu)003:2728: kun tu sems can gyi don la spyod pa cho ga'i don spyod pa'i mngon shes /
NK086(lu)003:2729: sgrib pa dag pa zag zad kyi mngon shes drug po ni thugs kyi rjes su 'gro zhing /
NK086(lu)003:2730: shes bya thams cad mngon sum du gzigs shing dbang bsgyur ba'i phyir thugs mngon sum pas 'dul ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:2731: gsum pa rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul ba ni /
NK086(lu)003:2732: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2733: kun tu gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2734: kun tu thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pas gdul bya'i don mdzad pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2735: lha rnams la tshangs pa dang dbang phyug /mi rnams la 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po /
NK086(lu)003:2736: lha ma yin la thags bzang ris sogs dang /
NK086(lu)003:2737: de bzhin du bya rnams kyi ched du shing rta mo dang /
NK086(lu)003:2738: ri dwags rnams kyi ched du seng ge'i rgyal po
NK086(lu)003:2739: yi dam brtan pa sogs 'gro ba gang 'dul ba
NK086(lu)003:2740: de'i rigs mthun du sprul pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2741: gzhan yang zhal gyi dkyil 'khor zhi ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2743: phra men la sogs pa rang snang dang mthun pa'i ston pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2744: rang rang gi skal pa dang rjes su mthun par skye zhing 'pho ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2746: gshegs shing bzhugs pa la sogs dus ma nges par ston pa sku'i gsang ba /
NK086(lu)003:2747: gdul bya de dang de'i blo rtog dang rjes su
NK086(lu)003:2748: 'tshams par 'jug pa'i chos ston pa'ang so so'i skad
NK086(lu)003:2749: dang brda' yi tshul gyis go bar mdzad pa ste
NK086(lu)003:2751: lha yi skad dang klu dang gnod sbyin skad /
NK086(lu)003:2752: grul bum dag dang mi yi skad rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:2753: 'gro ba kun gyi sgra skad ci tsam pa /
NK086(lu)003:2754: thams cad skad du bdag gis chos ston to //
NK086(lu)003:2755: zhes gsungs pa ni gsung gi gsang ba /
NK086(lu)003:2756: zag pa thams cad dang bral ba'i ye shes kyis
NK086(lu)003:2757: gdul bya'i blo rgyud ji lta bar mkhyen pa'i tshul
NK086(lu)003:2758: gyis kun tu mthun par 'jug pa thugs kyi gsang
NK086(lu)003:2759: ba ste / de gsum po rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:2760: bzhi pa gsung rig pas 'dul ba ni /
NK086(lu)003:2761: rigs can lnga'i gdul bya rnams kyi 'du shes dang mthun pa'i theg pa lnga'i sgo nas mdor bstan /
NK086(lu)003:2762: nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por
NK086(lu)003:2763: chos kyi phung po brgyad bzhi stong gsungs te rgyas
NK086(lu)003:2765: dbang po'i rim pas mjug bsdu ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:2766: thams cad kyang sgra tshig rang mtshan las 'das pa
NK086(lu)003:2767: nyid sems can gyi khams la de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2768: byin gyis rlabs kyi mthus rnam rig dang mthun par
NK086(lu)003:2769: go bar 'gyur ba ni gsung rig pas 'dul ba
NK086(lu)003:2770: ste / nges don gyi mdo sde las /
NK086(lu)003:2771: nga yis 'di kun bstan pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:2772: tshig 'bru gcig kyang bstan pa med //
NK086(lu)003:2774: gsum pa sna tshogs sbrul pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:2775: sems can rnams la gang phan pa chen po'i gzhir gyur to cog rnams te /
NK086(lu)003:2776: 'di ltar rang bzhin dang 'du byed las byung ba gzugs kyi sku dang /
NK086(lu)003:2780: mya ngan gyi thang la grong khyer du sprul pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2787: sman sogs bem po'i dngos po dang /
NK086(lu)003:2788: mu ge'i tshe nya bo che /
NK086(lu)003:2789: nad kyis gdungs pa la srog chags nges pa /
NK086(lu)003:2790: srin mo'i gling du cang shes b+ha la ha /
NK086(lu)003:2791: 'dam khrod du gser gyi bung ba la sogs bzo
NK086(lu)003:2792: dang skye ba'i sprul pa sna tshogs par ston pa
NK086(lu)003:2793: ste / dkon mchog sgron me'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:2794: de dag snyan ngag mkhan rgyal snyan ngag sbyor //
NK086(lu)003:2795: gar mkhan rnga mkhan gyad dang rol mo mkhan //
NK086(lu)003:2796: bzhag mdzes rgyan phreng thogs nas gar byed dang //
NK086(lu)003:2797: sgyu ma mkhan po gzugs mang kun tu ston //
NK086(lu)003:2798: grong pa grong dpon kha lo sgyur bar 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:2799: de bzhin tshong dpon ded dpon khyim bdag 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:2800: rgyal po blon po mdun 'don pho nya dang //
NK086(lu)003:2801: sman pa 'jig rten bstan bcos cho ga mkhan //
NK086(lu)003:2802: de dag dgon pa ljon shing chen por 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:2803: sman dang rin chen mi 'dzad gter rnams dang //
NK086(lu)003:2804: yid bzhin nor bu 'dod 'byung sdong po dang //
NK086(lu)003:2805: lam gol dong ba rnams la lam ston 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:2806: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:2807: bye brag rdzogs chen thun mong min pa'i sprul pa'i sku'i 'chad tshul phyogs gcig la /
NK086(lu)003:2808: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i snang cha de nyid las gnas
NK086(lu)003:2809: ris bcu gnyis su sprul pa'i sku ston pa bcu
NK086(lu)003:2810: gnyis sprul pa de dang dus mtshungs par sku gsung
NK086(lu)003:2811: thugs kyi sprul pa'i bstan pa chen po gsum du
NK086(lu)003:2812: snang bas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2813: 'dzam bu'i gling 'dir chos sku'i bstan pa dngos rdzogs
NK086(lu)003:2814: pa chen pos byin rlabs las rang shar ba rin
NK086(lu)003:2815: po che brgya rtsa las 'khrungs pa'i rdo rje phyag
NK086(lu)003:2816: gang ba dang / longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par
NK086(lu)003:2817: spyod pa'i bstan pa dngos rang byung ba bstan pa
NK086(lu)003:2818: bu gcig pa'i byin rlabs las rang shar ba rin
NK086(lu)003:2819: po che brgya rtsa gcig las 'khrungs pa'i glegs bam
NK086(lu)003:2820: sor bzhi ba chos nyid kyi rang sgra sgrogs pa
NK086(lu)003:2821: gang ba dang / / sprul pa'i sku ston pa
NK086(lu)003:2822: bcu gnyis kyi byin rlabs las rang shar ba rin
NK086(lu)003:2823: po che brgya rtsa gcig las rang byung ba'i sku
NK086(lu)003:2824: gzugs 'gro ba'i lus bongs dang mnyam pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:2825: de gsum ni 'dus ma byas pas skye 'jig med
NK086(lu)003:2826: cing byin rlabs las rang byung du shar bas rdzu
NK086(lu)003:2827: 'phrul dang yon tan dpag tu med pas gang dang
NK086(lu)003:2828: 'phrad pas 'jig rten gyi khams sum byon dang 'byon
NK086(lu)003:2829: gyur gyi sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku rnams kyi sku
NK086(lu)003:2830: gsung thugs kyi bstan pa 'phel bar byed pa'i rten
NK086(lu)003:2831: yin la mthong thos reg pas rdos bcas rang dengs
NK086(lu)003:2832: su 'gro ba'i phrin las kyi bdag nyid can zhig
NK086(lu)003:2833: go // de yang rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lo'i
NK086(lu)003:2834: rang bzhin can te gang du bzhugs pa'i gnas ni
NK086(lu)003:2835: sku gsung thugs kyi bstan pas 'dul ba'i dus kyi
NK086(lu)003:2836: dbang gis gnas so sor bzhugs shing /
NK086(lu)003:2838: sku'i bstan pa'i dus su o rgyan gyi yul rgya
NK086(lu)003:2839: mtsho'i gling na bzhugs shing 'od dang sgra dang dge
NK086(lu)003:2840: slong rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa'i sprul pa grangs med
NK086(lu)003:2842: gsung gi bstan pa'i dus su ri ma la ya
NK086(lu)003:2843: lag na rdo rje'i gnas su gnod sbyin gyi rgyal
NK086(lu)003:2844: po rnams kyis phyag byed do //
NK086(lu)003:2845: thugs kyi bstan pa'i dus su rdo rje gdan gyi steng gi nam mkha' la gnas so //
NK086(lu)003:2847: sku'i bstan pa'i dus su rdo rje gdan gyi steng
NK086(lu)003:2848: du dpag tshad lnga brgya 'phags pa'i nam mkha' la
NK086(lu)003:2849: d+aa ki ma rnams kyis bzung nas gnas so //
NK086(lu)003:2850: gsung gi bstan pa'i dus su 'di nyid dang lhan cig tu gnas so //
NK086(lu)003:2851: thugs kyi bstan pa'i dus su rab tu khros pa drang srong gi phug bar gnas so //
NK086(lu)003:2853: sku'i bstan pa'i dus su 'di nyid kyi byin rlabs kyis sangs rgyas kyi sku dngos dang /
NK086(lu)003:2854: de nyid kyi sprul pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:2857: de dag gi zhal gyi dkyil 'khor dang dngos su spyod pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:2858: gsung gi bstan pa'i dus su gcig tu ma nges par 'dzam gling kun tu 'khor bar gnas te /
NK086(lu)003:2859: lha dang mi'i 'du ba khyad par can rnams kun gyis mchod pa'i gnas su 'gyur zhing /
NK086(lu)003:2860: skabs su bstan pa'i gnod pa byung ba'i tshe sku las 'od 'byung /
NK086(lu)003:2862: spyan nas ye shes kyi me 'byung ngo //
NK086(lu)003:2863: thugs kyis 'dul ba'i bstan pa la sum cu rtsa
NK086(lu)003:2864: gsum pa'i lha rnams kyi gzhal med khang lag na
NK086(lu)003:2865: rdo rje'i khang ba rtsegs kyi yang thog na mnyam
NK086(lu)003:2866: pa'i rang bzhin dpa' chen po zhes bya bas phyag
NK086(lu)003:2867: mdzad cing cho 'phrul rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid du bzhugs
NK086(lu)003:2868: so // de dang dus mtshungs par sprul pa'i sku
NK086(lu)003:2869: ston pa bcu gnyis kyang gnas ris bcu gnyis su
NK086(lu)003:2870: so // byon te / gdul bya'i gnas bskal pa
NK086(lu)003:2871: dang po la dga' ldan brtsegs pa zhes bya bar
NK086(lu)003:2872: so // byon te / / ston pa khye'u snang ba dam pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK086(lu)003:2873: 'khor sangs rgyas stong rtsa gcig /bstan pa kun gyi rtsa ba sgra thal 'gyur /
NK086(lu)003:2874: sdud pa po lha'i dga' byed dbang phyug /grogs lha'i bu nyi ma rab tu snang byed /
NK086(lu)003:2875: sems can rnams tshe lo dpag tu med pa thub pa'i dus na'o //
NK086(lu)003:2879: bstan pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyud lnga /
NK086(lu)003:2880: dus tshe lo bye ba'i dus na'o //
NK086(lu)003:2881: gnas drod gsher 'dus pa 'od kyis spungs par /
NK086(lu)003:2882: ston pa dpal 'jigs pa skyob pa'i yid /
NK086(lu)003:2883: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' 'bum phrag drug /bstan pa 'khor ba dong sbrugs dang /
NK086(lu)003:2885: dpal 'byung bzhi zad pa'i rgyud rnams /
NK086(lu)003:2886: dus tshe lo 'bum pa'i dus su'o //
NK086(lu)003:2887: gnas chags 'byung mngal du snang bar /
NK086(lu)003:2888: ston pa gzhon nu rol pa rnam par rtse ba /
NK086(lu)003:2889: 'khor gnod sbyin dang srin po stong phrag gcig /bstan pa sems sde rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:2890: yan lag gi rgyud drug /dus tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus su'o //
NK086(lu)003:2891: gnas 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i ldum rar /
NK086(lu)003:2892: ston pa drug pa rdo rje 'chang /
NK086(lu)003:2893: 'khor sangs rgyas rabs bdun la sogs pa /
NK086(lu)003:2894: bstan pa pha rol tu phyin pa drug sogs /
NK086(lu)003:2895: dus tshe lo bdun khri'i dus su'o //
NK086(lu)003:2896: gnas gsang chen rol pa dur khrod me ri 'bar bar /
NK086(lu)003:2897: ston pa gzhon nu dpa' bo stobs ldan /
NK086(lu)003:2898: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' sprin gyi shugs can bdun /
NK086(lu)003:2899: chos pha rgyud ma rgyud la sogs pa rgyud sde du ma /
NK086(lu)003:2900: dus tshe lo drug khri'i dus su'o //
NK086(lu)003:2901: gnas srin phug ru lu'i sgra dang ldan par /
NK086(lu)003:2902: ston pa drang srong khros pa'i rgyal po /
NK086(lu)003:2903: 'khor srin po bye ba gcig la /
NK086(lu)003:2904: chos rags pa 'dul ba'i rgyud bcu la sogs pa /
NK086(lu)003:2905: dus tshe lo khri'i dus na'o //
NK086(lu)003:2906: gnas bya rgod phung po'i rgyal po'i khab na /
NK086(lu)003:2907: ston pa dgra bcom pa gser 'od dam pa /
NK086(lu)003:2908: 'khor 'phags pa nyan thos rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa dpag tu med pa la /
NK086(lu)003:2909: dam pa'i chos 'dul ba khri phrag dpag tu med pa /
NK086(lu)003:2910: dus tshe lo lnga stong thub pa'i dus su'o //
NK086(lu)003:2911: gnas sogs po g.yu'i smin ma can byang chub kyi shing rnam par rgyal ba'i drung du /
NK086(lu)003:2912: ston pa brtse bas rol pa'i blo gros /
NK086(lu)003:2913: 'khor sa brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la /
NK086(lu)003:2914: chos phra brgyud bdun pa la sogs pa /
NK086(lu)003:2915: dus tshe lo stong gi dus su'o //
NK086(lu)003:2919: dam pa chos mdo sde dang /
NK086(lu)003:2921: lung a nu'i chos khri phrag brgyad la sogs pa /
NK086(lu)003:2922: dus tshe lo lnga brgya pa'i dus so //
NK086(lu)003:2923: gnas rdo rje gdan byang chub 'byung ba'i shing drung du /
NK086(lu)003:2924: ston pa yab mngon rdzogs rgyal po /
NK086(lu)003:2926: chos nges pa'i don 'ba' zhig /dus tshe lo sum brgya pa'i dus so //
NK086(lu)003:2927: gnas mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' bar /
NK086(lu)003:2930: chos bden pa rnam pa bzhi'i 'khor lo lan bcu gnyis su bskor /
NK086(lu)003:2931: dus tshe lo brgya ba'i dus na'o //
NK086(lu)003:2932: de ltar na gnas bcu gnyis su byon pa de
NK086(lu)003:2933: dag la phun sum tshogs pa lnga re bsdoms pas
NK086(lu)003:2934: chos kyi rnam grangs drug cu 'byung zhing /
NK086(lu)003:2935: mdzad pa phrin las kyi sgo yang /
NK086(lu)003:2936: sku'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis ni gnas mi 'dra ba bcu gnyis su /
NK086(lu)003:2937: ston pa nyid sku mdog phyag mtshan mi 'dra ba bcu gnyis su sprul nas byon pas /
NK086(lu)003:2938: gdul bya rigs mi mthun pa bcu gnyis kyi tshogs
NK086(lu)003:2939: mi 'dra ba dpag tu med pa'i don mdzad pa
NK086(lu)003:2940: mi 'dra ba bcu gnyis mdzad pa'i mdzad pa zhes
NK086(lu)003:2941: sku'i gzi mdangs la bstan nas sku'i bstan pa 'phel
NK086(lu)003:2943: sku de dag gi dus su gsung chos kyi 'khor lo mi 'dra ba bcu gnyis gsungs pas /
NK086(lu)003:2944: 'gro ba'i ngag gi bcings pa mi 'dra ba bcu
NK086(lu)003:2945: gnyis las grol bar mdzad pa'i mdzad pa zhes gsung
NK086(lu)003:2946: gi bstan pa 'phel ba'i don du byung ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:2947: gsung de tsam zhig gi tshe na thugs kyi dgongs pa mi 'dra ba bcu gnyis kyis /
NK086(lu)003:2948: 'gro ba'i rigs mi 'dra ba rnams kyi rtog pa
NK086(lu)003:2949: bcu gnyis las grol bar mdzad pa'i mdzad pa zhes
NK086(lu)003:2950: thugs kyi bstan pa 'phel ba'i don du byung ba
NK086(lu)003:2951: ste / de ltar bstan pa nges pa'i sprul pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2952: sku gcig la chos kyi rnam grangs dgu bcu rtsa
NK086(lu)003:2954: de dag dang ldan pa ni bstan pa'i bdag po zhes bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:2955: gal te mi ldan na sangs rgyas 'jig rten du
NK086(lu)003:2956: byon pa khol bu'i bstan pa zhes bya ste de
NK086(lu)003:2957: dag kyang sngon gyi sems bskyed rdzogs pa las byung
NK086(lu)003:2958: ba'o // zhes khyad par du ma dang bcas pas bshad cing /
NK086(lu)003:2960: phyi la sogs pa dgu yis ni //
NK086(lu)003:2961: mdzad pa'i bye brag dgos par 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:2962: zhes mdzad pa la'ang sku gsung thugs la phyi nang gsum rer dbye ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:2963: de re re la'ang bzhi bzhir dbye ba sogs mang du gsungs kyang 'dir mi spro la /
NK086(lu)003:2964: de dag rnams kyang khyad par gyi dgongs pa'i phyogs
NK086(lu)003:2965: gcig tu mngon cing bde bar gshegs pa thabs la
NK086(lu)003:2966: mkhas pas gdul bya'i zhing khams rab 'byams rgya mtsho'i
NK086(lu)003:2967: rdul gyi grangs dang rjes su mthun par 'tshams pa'i
NK086(lu)003:2969: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ston pa ni tshul gcig
NK086(lu)003:2970: la tha dad pa dag kyang 'gal bar mi bsam
NK086(lu)003:2971: te sangs rgyas kyi rnam 'phrul ni bsam gyis mi
NK086(lu)003:2972: khyab pa'i gnas yin pa'i phyir so skye lta zhog
NK086(lu)003:2973: 'phags chen rnams kyi blo'i spyod yul kyang ma yin
NK086(lu)003:2974: la / dus dang gdul bya sogs mtha' gcig tu
NK086(lu)003:2975: nges gzung ma mchis pas phyogs gcig mthong bas gcig
NK086(lu)003:2976: shos la smad par mi bya ste /
NK086(lu)003:2977: 'di ltar 'phags pa chos thams cad yang dag par sdud pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:2978: 'jig pa'i bskal pa 'chags pa'i bskal par mos na'ang
NK086(lu)003:2979: 'jig pa'i bskal pa 'chags pa'i bskal par 'gyur te
NK086(lu)003:2980: / sems can de dag gis kyang 'chags pa'i bskal par shes so //
NK086(lu)003:2981: 'chags pa'i bskal pa 'jig pa'i bskal par mos na
NK086(lu)003:2982: yang 'chags pa'i bskal pa 'jig pa'i bskal bar 'gyur
NK086(lu)003:2983: te / sems can de dag gis kyang 'jig pa'i bskal par shes so //
NK086(lu)003:2984: 'jig pa dang 'chags pa yang gzhan du 'gyur ba ma yin te /
NK086(lu)003:2985: mos pa de ltar yang 'gyur ro //
NK086(lu)003:2986: de bzhin bskal pa gcig snga dro tsam du mos
NK086(lu)003:2987: na yang de na sems can de dag gis bskal
NK086(lu)003:2988: pa gcig snga dro tsam du shes so //
NK086(lu)003:2989: snga dro bskal pa tsam du mos na yang de bzhin du 'gyur te /
NK086(lu)003:2990: de nas sems can de dag gi de bzhin du shes te /
NK086(lu)003:2991: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i mos pa las byung ba'i rdzu 'phrul zhes bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:2993: de ltar sku gsum po de sku lngar dbye ba la 'chad tshul gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:2994: zur gyi mkhas pa rnams ni /
NK086(lu)003:2995: sku gsum po de'i snang cha ma 'dres pa'i cha nas mngon par byang chub pa'i sku dang /
NK086(lu)003:2996: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha nas rdo rje'i
NK086(lu)003:2997: sku ste lngar bzhed pas chos sku longs sku sprul
NK086(lu)003:2998: sku gsum ni sku mtshan nyid pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:2999: gzhan gnyis rnam pa'i ldog cha dang ngo bo dbyer
NK086(lu)003:3000: mi phyed pa'i cha nas bzhag pas sku btags pa
NK086(lu)003:3001: bar bzhed / kun mkhyen klong chen pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:3002: chos sku mngon byang rdo rje'i sku gsum po sangs rgyas rang snang gi sku mtshan nyid pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3003: longs sprul gnyis ni gdul bya gzhan snang gis bsdus pa'i phyir sku btags pa bar bzhed /
NK086(lu)003:3004: gang ltar bshad kyang 'gal bar ma mthong med kyi
NK086(lu)003:3005: 'on kyang mtshan nyid kyi sgo nas rnam par bzhag
NK086(lu)003:3006: na / gdod nas dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK086(lu)003:3007: dag pa grol sa'i ka dag chen po sangs rgyas
NK086(lu)003:3008: thams cad gang du dbyings gcig pa'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:3009: lam thams cad kyi bgrod pa mthar phyin pa'i chos
NK086(lu)003:3010: nyid de ni rnam pa kun tu mi 'pho zhing
NK086(lu)003:3011: mi 'gyur bas rtag brtan 'dus ma byas pas mi
NK086(lu)003:3013: gdod nas dri ma dang bral bas rang bzhin rnam dag dang /
NK086(lu)003:3014: glo bur sgrib gnyis cha bcas shin tu rnam par
NK086(lu)003:3015: byang bas na dag pa gnyis ldan gyi sangs rgyas
NK086(lu)003:3018: dbyings kyi dag pa rdo rje'i sku //
NK086(lu)003:3021: dag pa gnyis ldan de nyid ngang las snang cha
NK086(lu)003:3022: mkhyen pa'i ye shes ma 'gag pa'i rtsal gyis bral
NK086(lu)003:3025: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad /
NK086(lu)003:3026: thugs rje chen po la sogs mkhyen brtse nus pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3027: yon tan rnams mnga' pa'i cha nas mngon par byang
NK086(lu)003:3028: chub pa'i sku zhes bya ba ma 'dres pa'i chos
NK086(lu)003:3029: thams cad kyi 'char gzhir gnas pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:3031: dri ma bral phyir byang ba ste //
NK086(lu)003:3032: yon tan rgyas pas chub pa nyid //
NK086(lu)003:3034: mngon par byang chub skur brjod do //
NK086(lu)003:3036: ye shes kyi sgo nas bzhag na /
NK086(lu)003:3037: chos dbyings ye shes ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK086(lu)003:3038: ye shes phyi ma bzhi po rten brten pa'i cha
NK086(lu)003:3039: nas ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes su bshad
NK086(lu)003:3040: cing / phyis kyi nges don smra ba'i mkhas pa
NK086(lu)003:3041: chen po dag gis kyang chos kyi dbyings kyi ye
NK086(lu)003:3042: shes ni don dam pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3043: phyi ma bzhi po la kun rdzob kyi cha ci
NK086(lu)003:3044: rigs par 'dres par bshad pa dang don gcig la
NK086(lu)003:3045: / ye shes de dag kyang snga ma ni /
NK086(lu)003:3047: thog ma dbus mtha' med cing rnam dbyer med //
NK086(lu)003:3048: gnyis med gsum bral dri med rnam rtog med //
NK086(lu)003:3049: ces sogs gsungs pa ltar chos kyi sku dang /
NK086(lu)003:3050: phyi ma bzhi po rim bzhin /
NK086(lu)003:3052: me long ye shes nga yi med //
NK086(lu)003:3053: yongs su ma chad rtag tu ldan //
NK086(lu)003:3054: shes bya kun la ma rmongs la //
NK086(lu)003:3055: rtag tu de la mngon phyogs min //
NK086(lu)003:3056: ye shes kun gyi rgyu mtshan phyir //
NK086(lu)003:3058: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyid //
NK086(lu)003:3060: mnyam nyad ye shes sems can la //
NK086(lu)003:3061: bsgom pa dag pa la 'dod do //
NK086(lu)003:3062: mi gnas zhi bar bzhugs pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:3063: mnyam nyid ye shes yin par 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:3064: dus rnams kun tu byams pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:3065: thugs rje chen pos dag dang ldan //
NK086(lu)003:3066: sems can rnams la mos pa bzhin //
NK086(lu)003:3067: sangs rgyas sku ni nges par ston //
NK086(lu)003:3069: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes ni //
NK086(lu)003:3070: shes bya kun la rtag mi thogs //
NK086(lu)003:3071: ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs rnams kyi //
NK086(lu)003:3072: gter dang 'dra ba kho na yin //
NK086(lu)003:3074: 'byor pa thams cad kun tu ston mdzad pa //
NK086(lu)003:3075: the tshom thams cad gcod pa yi //
NK086(lu)003:3076: chos chen char ni rab tu 'bebs //
NK086(lu)003:3077: zhes longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang //
NK086(lu)003:3078: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni //
NK086(lu)003:3079: khams rnams kun tu sna tshogs shing //
NK086(lu)003:3080: dpag med bsam yas sprul pa yis //
NK086(lu)003:3081: sems can kun gyi don sgrub pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:3082: zhes pa ni sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK086(lu)003:3084: chos dbyings mnyam nyid gnyis gnas lugs gzigs pa'i cha nas ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK086(lu)003:3085: ye shes gzhan gsum po 'char gzhi dang /
NK086(lu)003:3087: 'gro don mdzad pa'i cha nas ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes su bshad de /
NK086(lu)003:3089: ji ltar mkhyen pa'i dngos po yis //
NK086(lu)003:3090: gnas lugs rang gi don du shes //
NK086(lu)003:3091: ji snyed pa yis gdul bya yi //
NK086(lu)003:3092: bsam pa ji ltar gnas pa shes //
NK086(lu)003:3093: de ltar thugs rje'i 'char tshul las //
NK086(lu)003:3094: gdul bya'i 'gro ba tha dad la //
NK086(lu)003:3095: 'dul byed sku yang de tsam mo //
NK086(lu)003:3097: de ltar sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid chen
NK086(lu)003:3098: po'i go 'phang de nyid rgyu'i theg chen gyi lam
NK086(lu)003:3099: lnga sa bcu mthar phyin pa'i rgyun mtha'i bar chad
NK086(lu)003:3100: med lam la brten pa'i byang chub sems dpa' 'tshang
NK086(lu)003:3101: rgya ka ma de la phyogs bcu rab 'byams kyi
NK086(lu)003:3102: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis 'od zer chen po'i
NK086(lu)003:3103: dbang bskur bar mdzad pa mdo las gsungs pas rang
NK086(lu)003:3104: sa'i sgrib pa gnyis byang bar gyur kyang /
NK086(lu)003:3105: dkar dmar rlung gsum la brten pa'i 'gyur ba de
NK086(lu)003:3106: myong ba'i snang gsum 'pho ba'i bag chags phra ba
NK086(lu)003:3107: 'dod chags chen po'i dbang bskur la ma brten par
NK086(lu)003:3108: sbyong ba'i thabs med par sngags bla med kyi rgyud
NK086(lu)003:3109: dang 'grel ba rnams su ci rigs par bshad pa
NK086(lu)003:3110: / 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:3111: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung gi //
NK086(lu)003:3112: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK086(lu)003:3113: zhes pa'i dgongs pa dang yang 'byor ba'i phyir rgyu'i
NK086(lu)003:3114: theg pa'i mthar thug sngags la brten nas 'grub dgos
NK086(lu)003:3115: pa ni rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa so so'i ming
NK086(lu)003:3117: 'o na rgyu'i theg chen du 'bras bu'i rnam gzhag gsungs pa don med du 'gyur ro snyam na /
NK086(lu)003:3119: dbang rtul rgyu'i theg par mos pa dag gi ngor
NK086(lu)003:3120: de ltar bstan du zin kyang mdo'i nges don mthar
NK086(lu)003:3121: thug pa sngags su gnas shing /
NK086(lu)003:3122: der rang bzhin yongs grub dang /
NK086(lu)003:3124: dam pa'i bdag sogs spyi tsam zhig gsungs nas /
NK086(lu)003:3125: gnas lugs shin tu rgyas pa chen po dang de
NK086(lu)003:3126: nyid rtogs pa'i thabs kyi sgo yongs su rdzogs pa
NK086(lu)003:3127: sngags su bstan pa'i phyir sngags kyi sangs rgyas de
NK086(lu)003:3128: nyid mdo lam gyi sangs rgyas ma yin par mi
NK086(lu)003:3129: 'gyur te / lam ring ba'i sne nye lam dang
NK086(lu)003:3130: 'phrad pa zhig la de gnyis gang nas phyin kyang
NK086(lu)003:3131: don gyi gnas su gcig pa bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:3132: 'o na sngags ma gtogs mdo'i lam bstan pa don med do snyam na /
NK086(lu)003:3134: bgrod thag shin tu nye yang ngam grog dang /
NK086(lu)003:3135: g.yang sa'i lam la skyes bu lus dang blo stobs
NK086(lu)003:3136: che ba ma gtogs 'jug mi nus pa bzhin sngags
NK086(lu)003:3137: kyi gdul bya dbang rnon blo stobs che ba ma
NK086(lu)003:3138: gtogs khe nyen che ba'i phying dang /
NK086(lu)003:3139: bgrod thag ring yang ngam grogs sogs kyi 'jigs pa
NK086(lu)003:3140: med par lus dang blo stobs nyams dma' bas 'jug
NK086(lu)003:3141: pas dal bus phyin pas khe nyen chung ba ltar
NK086(lu)003:3142: mdo'i ring lam bstan pa'ang thams cad mkhyen pa thabs
NK086(lu)003:3143: la mkhas pa'i phyir chos ston tshul bla na med
NK086(lu)003:3144: pa nyid du shes par bya ba gnad dam pa
NK086(lu)003:3145: yin la / de ltar ma yin na rgyu 'bras
NK086(lu)003:3146: kyi theg pa gnyis dgongs gzhi 'gal ba can du
NK086(lu)003:3147: 'gyur zhing mthar thug theg pa gcig tu mi 'du
NK086(lu)003:3148: yin la / ba dang / nges don gyi phyogs
NK086(lu)003:3149: kyang gnyis su 'gyur ba sogs kyi skyon chen po
NK086(lu)003:3150: gnas pa'i phyir rgyal ba'i phrin las chud mi gsan
NK086(lu)003:3151: pa la mkhas par bya dgos so //
NK086(lu)003:3152: bzhi pa rgyu 'bras theg pa'i sku dang ye shes kyi khyad par ston pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:3153: sngon gyi mchog gzigs mkhas pa chen po dag rgyu
NK086(lu)003:3154: 'bras theg pa'i khyad par dang blo gros rnam 'byed
NK086(lu)003:3155: kyi ched du mdo dang sngags su bshad tshod kyi
NK086(lu)003:3156: sangs rgyas la khyad par 'di ltar dpyad de /
NK086(lu)003:3159: byin rlabs kyi khyad par dang gsum las /
NK086(lu)003:3161: mtshan nyid theg pa'i chos sku spros pa dang bral ba'i stong nyid nam mkha' lta bu yin te /
NK086(lu)003:3163: shes bya'i bud shing ma lus skam po dag /bsregs pas zhi des rgyal rnams chos sku ste //
NK086(lu)003:3164: de tshe skye ba med cing 'gag pa med //
NK086(lu)003:3165: sems 'gags pa de sku yis mngon sum mdzad //
NK086(lu)003:3167: sngags kyi chos sku ni dbyings dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin snang stong zung du 'jug pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:3169: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK086(lu)003:3170: snang ba nyid na dngos po med //
NK086(lu)003:3173: mtshan nyid theg pa'i chos sku stong pa'i mthar lhungs la /
NK086(lu)003:3174: sngags kyi chos sku ni snang stong gnyis su med pas rtag chad kyi mthar ma lhung ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:3176: mtshan nyid kyi chos sku las byin rlabs gzugs sku gnyis las mi 'char /
NK086(lu)003:3177: sngags kyi chos sku ni dbyings dang ye shes snang
NK086(lu)003:3178: stong zung du 'jug pa'i byin rlabs las sku lnga
NK086(lu)003:3179: la sogs pa ci rigs par 'char ro //
NK086(lu)003:3180: de bzhin du longs sku dang sprul sku'i khyad par yang 'di ltar yod de /
NK086(lu)003:3181: rgyu mtshan nyid kyis gzugs sku gnyis rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed par 'dod la /
NK086(lu)003:3182: sngags kyi gzugs sku ni rgyu dang rkyen gyis bskyed par ma byung ste /
NK086(lu)003:3184: rgyu rkyen rag lus med pa'i phyir //
NK086(lu)003:3189: longs sku'i khyad par la'ang gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:3190: longs su spyod pa'i khyad par ni /
NK086(lu)003:3191: mtshan nyid theg pa'i longs skus dkar po'i phyoogs la
NK086(lu)003:3192: longs spyod pa las nag po'i phyogs la mi spyod
NK086(lu)003:3193: / sngags kyi longs sku ni gnyis ka la longs spyod /
NK086(lu)003:3194: spyod byed thabs kyi khyad par yang /
NK086(lu)003:3195: mtshan nyid theg par nag po'i phyogs la longs spyod pa'i thabs med /
NK086(lu)003:3196: sngags la dkar nag gnyis kar longs spyod pa'i thabs yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:3197: sprul sku la'ang khyad par gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:3198: gdul bya yul gyi khyad par ni /
NK086(lu)003:3199: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sprul skus dkar phyogs kyi gdul
NK086(lu)003:3200: bya 'dul ba las nag phyogs kyi gdul bya mi
NK086(lu)003:3201: 'dul / sngags kyi sprul sku'i gdul bya la phyogs ris med pa'o //
