NK086(lu)003:3202: 'dul byed thabs kyi khyad par yang /
NK086(lu)003:3203: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi sprul sku la nag phyogs 'dul ba'i thabs med /
NK086(lu)003:3204: sngags kyi sprul sku ni gdul bya dkar nag gi phyogs gnyis ka 'dul ba'i thabs dang ldan pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:3205: gzhan yang chos sku la mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i
NK086(lu)003:3206: bde ba chen pos khyad par du byas pa dang
NK086(lu)003:3207: / longs sku nges pa lnga ldan kyang zhing dang
NK086(lu)003:3208: ston 'khor thams cad rang snang gzhi'i 'od gsal chen
NK086(lu)003:3209: por lhun gyis grub pa'i snang cha las gzhan snang
NK086(lu)003:3210: gis bsdus pa min pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3211: sprul sku yang 'dul ba rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas
NK086(lu)003:3212: phrin las rnam pa bzhi rab 'byams ci yang rung
NK086(lu)003:3213: ba la mnga' dbang bsgyur nas gdul bya'i don mdzad
NK086(lu)003:3214: pa la dbang 'byor pa sogs khyad par gzhan yang
NK086(lu)003:3216: de nyid kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa de yang /
NK086(lu)003:3217: gang gi tshe de bzhin gshegs pas thams cad mkhyen
NK086(lu)003:3218: pa'i go 'phang mngon du mdzad pa na rang gi
NK086(lu)003:3219: ngo bo'i cha las gdul bya sems can gyi khams
NK086(lu)003:3220: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dang 'dul byed thabs kyi khyad
NK086(lu)003:3221: par de snyed kyang thugs rje chen po'i rol pa
NK086(lu)003:3222: las gzhan du ma gyur ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:3223: thams cad ro gcig par 'bad med lhun grub tu gnas pas gdul bya'i bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK086(lu)003:3224: rgyal ba'i thugs bskyed kyi khyad par sogs rgyu dang
NK086(lu)003:3225: rkyen la ma ltos par sems can thams cad kyi
NK086(lu)003:3226: sems kyi rang bzhin gang yin pa de dang sangs
NK086(lu)003:3227: rgyas kyi ye shes bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po
NK086(lu)003:3228: chos nyid kun khyab kyi rang bzhin 'gro 'ong 'pho
NK086(lu)003:3229: 'gyur med par til gyi khams la snum gyis khyab
NK086(lu)003:3230: pa bzhin rnam par dbyer med pa'i bdag nyid can
NK086(lu)003:3231: du bzhugs pa ni gshis lugs su khyab pa'i phrin
NK086(lu)003:3232: las 'dus ma byas pa'i ngo bos rtag pa dang
NK086(lu)003:3234: lhun gyis grub pa'i mtshan nyid can te /
NK086(lu)003:3235: dad pa'i stobs bskyed pa 'jug pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:3236: 'jam dpal phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams rab 'byams
NK086(lu)003:3237: thams cad na mu stegs can gyi gnas thams cad
NK086(lu)003:3239: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i las bya ba thams cad
NK086(lu)003:3240: gang ci 'byung ba de dag thams cad ni de
NK086(lu)003:3241: bzhin gshegs pa'i lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes kyis
NK086(lu)003:3242: 'byung ngo // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:3243: ma 'dres pa'i chos dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:3246: gzhan gyi dbang gis nges 'byung dang //
NK086(lu)003:3247: bdag dang sems can mtshungs gzigs dang //
NK086(lu)003:3248: mdzad pa yongs su ma rdzogs phyir //
NK086(lu)003:3251: de ltar nam mkha'i mtha' klas kyi //
NK086(lu)003:3252: 'gro ba rtag tu lhun grub par //
NK086(lu)003:3253: thogs med blo ldan de yis ni //
NK086(lu)003:3254: sems can don ni yang dag 'jug /ces khyab pa dang lhun gyis grub pa'i don dang /
NK086(lu)003:3255: mdo sde las brgya pa las /
NK086(lu)003:3256: rgya mtsho chu srin gnas kyi rlabs //
NK086(lu)003:3257: dus las yol bar 'gyur srid kyi //
NK086(lu)003:3258: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la //
NK086(lu)003:3259: sangs rgyas dus las yol mi mnga' //zhes gsungs pa
NK086(lu)003:3260: bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las de nyid gdul
NK086(lu)003:3261: bya so so'i rgyud la skal ba dang 'tshams par
NK086(lu)003:3262: sad tshul la ltos nas myang 'das kyi rgyud kyis
NK086(lu)003:3263: bsdus pa'i 'bad rtsol dang rnam par mi rtog bzhin
NK086(lu)003:3264: du gshegs snying gi rtsal 'khor ba ltar shar ba
NK086(lu)003:3265: glo bur gyi chos dang 'dzom pa las /
NK086(lu)003:3266: rnam grol gyi lam ston pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang /
NK086(lu)003:3268: lam gyi rnam par shar ba dri ma sbyong ba'i gnyen por 'gro bas /
NK086(lu)003:3269: byang chub kyi myu gu smin zin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3271: smin par 'gyur ba'i thabs tshul ni bde bar gshegs
NK086(lu)003:3272: pa'i phrin las dang thugs rje'i rol pa rmad du
NK086(lu)003:3273: byung ba ste / sgyur 'phrul rgyas pa las /
NK086(lu)003:3274: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK086(lu)003:3275: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK086(lu)003:3276: 'gro ba'i phrin las bsam mi khyab //
NK086(lu)003:3277: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang //
NK086(lu)003:3278: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyis //
NK086(lu)003:3279: gdul bya rnams ni chud mi gson //
NK086(lu)003:3280: ngan song sbyongs shing byang chub zhing //
NK086(lu)003:3281: ye shes tshogs rdzogs kun tu ston //
NK086(lu)003:3283: gzhan du mnyam gzhag gi ye shes la g.yo ba
NK086(lu)003:3284: med bzhin du rjes thob kyis sems can gyi don
NK086(lu)003:3287: mi rtog pa dang de yi ni //
NK086(lu)003:3288: rjes thob de ni ye shes 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:3290: gdul bya'i dkar po rnam par 'phel ba'i rgyu dang
NK086(lu)003:3291: sangs rgyas kyi sngon gyi smon lam gyi rkyen las
NK086(lu)003:3294: zhing sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal gyur pa //
NK086(lu)003:3295: yid bzhin nor bu ji bzhin rnam mi rtog /
NK086(lu)003:3296: 'gro sgrol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /
NK086(lu)003:3297: 'di ni spros dang bral la snang ba yin //
NK086(lu)003:3298: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyang thun mong gi gdul bya
NK086(lu)003:3299: la ltos pa'i 'chad tshul phyogs re tsam las nges
NK086(lu)003:3301: snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa rin po
NK086(lu)003:3302: che'i rnam gzhag legs bshad snang ba'i dga' ston ces
NK086(lu)003:3303: bya ba las / rgyal ba sku gsum gyi ston
NK086(lu)003:3304: pa ji ltar byon pa'i tshul bshad pa'i tshoms te
NK086(lu)003:3305: bya ba las / / skabs gnyis pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:3306: de ltar mi mjed 'jig rten gyi khams su rgyal
NK086(lu)003:3307: ba sku gsum gyi ston pa ji ltar byon pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3309: da ni ston pa de dag gis chos kyi 'khor lo ji ltar bskor ba'i tshul las /
NK086(lu)003:3310: thog mar rgyu'i chos 'khor gsum gyi rnam gzhag 'chad pa la gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:3311: go don spyir dbye ba'i sgo nas smos pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3312: skabs don bye brag tu bsdus te 'chad pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:3314: de yang thog mar thub pa mchog gi sprul skus
NK086(lu)003:3315: rgyu'i theg pa'i chos 'khor gsum rim pa can du
NK086(lu)003:3316: bskor te / dang po bden pa bzhi las brtsam pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3317: gnyis pa mtshan nyid med pa /
NK086(lu)003:3318: gsum pa legs pa rnam par phye ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:3320: ston pas chos kyi 'khor lo thog mar bskor ba
NK086(lu)003:3321: gang zhig /yongs su ma dag pa'i sems can gyi
NK086(lu)003:3322: khams gzigs nas / mi rtag pa /
NK086(lu)003:3326: mi sdug pa sogs yid 'byung ba'i gtam gyis bskul nas /
NK086(lu)003:3327: 'khor ba la mngon par chags pa'i blo 'dor bar
NK086(lu)003:3328: byed pas don dam bden pa mthong rung du bsgrubs
NK086(lu)003:3329: pas theg chen gyi lam stegs su 'gyur ba la
NK086(lu)003:3330: dgongs te / yul w+aa ra n+aa si drang srong lhung ba ri dwags kyi nags tshal du /
NK086(lu)003:3335: 'gog pa bzhi po lan gsum du bzlas nas chos
NK086(lu)003:3336: kyi tshul ston pa theg dman nyan rang gi sde
NK086(lu)003:3337: snod lung sde bzhi la sogs pa rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:3339: ston pas chos kyi 'khor lo bar pa bskor ba
NK086(lu)003:3340: gang zhig /chos kyi 'khor lo dang po bskor ba
NK086(lu)003:3341: de tsam gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i brtson 'grus kyi
NK086(lu)003:3343: de'i 'og tu chos thams cad stong pa nyid dang /
NK086(lu)003:3345: smon pa med pa'i tshul rgya chen po'i gtam gyis
NK086(lu)003:3346: sangs rgyas kyi tshul khong du chud nas bdag 'dzin
NK086(lu)003:3347: bzlog pa'i phyir spros pa'i phyogs gcig 'gog pa rnam
NK086(lu)003:3348: grangs pa'i don dam bden pa rtogs pas theg chen
NK086(lu)003:3349: gyi lam dngos gzhi la dgongs te /
NK086(lu)003:3350: rgyal po'i khab kyi bya rgod phung po'i ri sogs su /
NK086(lu)003:3351: gtso bor byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun rnams la /
NK086(lu)003:3352: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen bar gyi chos rnams rang gi
NK086(lu)003:3353: ngo bos shin tu dben pa'i smra bsam brjod med
NK086(lu)003:3354: de bzhin nyid kyi tshul rgya che bar ston pa
NK086(lu)003:3355: theg chen byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod de /
NK086(lu)003:3356: rgyas pa sher phyin bye ba phrag brgya pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3358: 'bring po nyi khri lnga stong sogs dang /
NK086(lu)003:3359: bsdus pa brgyad stong pa la sogs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3360: de las 'phros pa bsam gyis mi khyab par shes par bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:3362: ston pas chos kyi 'khor lo mtha' ma bskor ba
NK086(lu)003:3363: gang zhig /chos kyi 'khor lo gnyis pa bskor ba
NK086(lu)003:3364: de tsam gyis de bzhin gshegs pas brtson 'grus kyi
NK086(lu)003:3366: de'i 'og tu phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i gtam
NK086(lu)003:3367: dang 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i gtam gyis sems
NK086(lu)003:3368: can de dag sangs rgyas kyi yul la 'dzud par
NK086(lu)003:3369: byed pas yod med la sogs lta ba'i gzhi thams
NK086(lu)003:3370: cad bzlog nas rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam
NK086(lu)003:3371: bden pa dngos su ston pa theg pa chen po'i
NK086(lu)003:3372: lam gyi snying po la dgongs te /
NK086(lu)003:3377: snying po'i gdul bya byang chub sems dpa' chen po'i tshogs la /
NK086(lu)003:3378: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen bar gyi chos rnams kun tu brtag pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3380: yongs su grub pa gsum du legs par phyes shing /
NK086(lu)003:3381: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i tshul du gtan la phab nas
NK086(lu)003:3382: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i gnas lugs rgya che
NK086(lu)003:3384: shin tu rgyas pa chen po'i mdo sde 'dus pa chen po bye ba phrag brgya dang /
NK086(lu)003:3385: sangs rgyas phal po che dang /
NK086(lu)003:3387: rgyan stug po bkod pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3388: yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po dang /
NK086(lu)003:3389: dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba la sogs pa rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:3390: de'ang bye brag smra ba rnams kyis lung gi chos
NK086(lu)003:3391: 'khor la mthong lam kho nas khyab pa 'dod cing
NK086(lu)003:3392: / mdo sde pas mthong sgom mi slob gsum char la chos 'khor du 'dod /
NK086(lu)003:3393: theg chen pas lam lnga po thams cad la chos 'khor du bzhed pa yin no //
NK086(lu)003:3394: rgyu'i theg pa de la grub mtha'i sgo nas dbye na gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:3397: dang po la'ang bye brag smra ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:3399: dang po nyan thos bye brag tu smra bas shes bya thams cad gzhi lngar 'dod pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:3403: ldan pa ma yin 'du byed kyi gzhi /
NK086(lu)003:3404: 'dus ma byas kyi gzhi ste lnga las /
NK086(lu)003:3406: rdul phra rab 'dus pa'i bdag nyid can gyi rags
NK086(lu)003:3407: pa'i dngos po bcom pa'am blos so sor bsal ba
NK086(lu)003:3408: na / der 'dzin gyi blo 'dor rung gi chos su dmigs pa kun rdzob bden pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK086(lu)003:3409: bcom pa'am blos bsal bas der 'dzin gyi blo 'dor
NK086(lu)003:3410: du mi rung ba don dam bden pa'i mtshan nyid
NK086(lu)003:3412: gang la bcom dang blo yis gzhan //
NK086(lu)003:3413: bsal ba de blo mi 'jug pa //
NK086(lu)003:3414: bum chu bzhin du kun rdzob tu //
NK086(lu)003:3415: yod de don dam gzhan yin no //
NK086(lu)003:3417: 'dis kun rdzob bden pa dam du ma grub kyang
NK086(lu)003:3418: bden grub tu 'dod de dngos po thams cad la
NK086(lu)003:3419: bden grub kyis khyab par khas blangs pas so //
NK086(lu)003:3421: sgo lnga yid dang bcas pa'i rnam shes kyis phyi'i don mthong ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:3423: tshor ba 'du shes sogs sems byung lnga bcu rtsa
NK086(lu)003:3424: gcig po thams cad gtso bo rnam shes dang lhan
NK086(lu)003:3425: cig yul la 'jug pas dmigs pa mtshungs pa dang
NK086(lu)003:3429: rdzas mtshungs pa'i sgo nas dbang pos don la bltas pas rnam shes rtogs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3430: sems byung gis kyang don gyi khyad par rtogs pa
NK086(lu)003:3431: gzung 'dzin dus mnyam du skye bar 'dod pas sems
NK086(lu)003:3432: dang sems byung gnyis ka phyi rol gyi don rig
NK086(lu)003:3433: pa ma gtogs rang rig pa med par 'dod la
NK086(lu)003:3435: snyoms 'jug sogs dang ming tshig yi ge sogs dus gsum rdzas su yod pa dper na /
NK086(lu)003:3436: bum pa bum pa'i 'das pa'i dus su yod la /
NK086(lu)003:3438: da lta'i dus su'ang yod pa lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:3439: las gang byas pa'ang chud mi za bar rdzas su thob par 'dod /
NK086(lu)003:3442: so sor brtag 'gog /so sor brtag min 'gog gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:3444: yid kyi rnam shes 'khor bcas zag med yin la /
NK086(lu)003:3445: lhag ma rnams ni zag bcas su 'dod do //
NK086(lu)003:3446: gnyis pa mdo sde pa'i 'dod pa phal cher bye smra dang mtshungs la /
NK086(lu)003:3448: bye smras gzugs su 'dod pa rig byed ma yin
NK086(lu)003:3449: pa'i gzugs spong sems rgyun chags pa la sogs pa
NK086(lu)003:3450: yin kyang / gzugs la brten nas 'byung bas gzugs
NK086(lu)003:3451: btags yod tsam dang dus gsum yang rdzas grub tu
NK086(lu)003:3452: yin kyang / mi 'dod cing / dbang po rnams rnam shes kyi bdag can yin pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3453: yul rnams kyang shes pa la rnam pa gtod byed kyi dmigs pa'i rkyen du 'dod /
NK086(lu)003:3454: sems dang sems byung gi gzhi sgo lnga'i rnam shes
NK086(lu)003:3455: dang 'khor sems byung gzugs la sogs pa yul la
NK086(lu)003:3456: dmigs te gzugs sgra la sogs phyi rol gyi yul
NK086(lu)003:3457: mthong ba med kyang me long la rang gi bzhin
NK086(lu)003:3458: dang 'dra ba'i rnam pa gtad pa ltar /
NK086(lu)003:3459: skad cig da lta'i snga logs su gzugs sogs kyi
NK086(lu)003:3460: don gyi rnam pa gtod byed phag na mos gtad
NK086(lu)003:3461: pas / skad cig da lta ba la gzugs sogs de dang de'i rnam par shar ba yin cing /
NK086(lu)003:3462: skad cig de'i ma 'ongs pa la da lta'i gtong
NK086(lu)003:3463: byed kyi phyi logs su rnam pa gtod pas shes
NK086(lu)003:3464: pa phyi rol gyi rnam par shar te yul du
NK086(lu)003:3465: dmigs pas gzung 'dzin yul can du gyur pa la
NK086(lu)003:3466: don rtogs so zhes btags pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:3468: 'dra ba nyams su myong ba la //
NK086(lu)003:3469: don myong zhes ni rnam par brjod //
NK086(lu)003:3471: snang ba shes pa'i ngo bo yin yang rnam pa
NK086(lu)003:3472: gtod byed phyi rol na med pas 'khrul pa yin
NK086(lu)003:3473: la / shes pa thams cad gsal bar myong ba rang rig pa ni ma 'khrul pa'o zhes 'dod /
NK086(lu)003:3474: ldan min 'du byed rnams kyang gzugs dang /
NK086(lu)003:3476: sems byung gi gnas skabs tsam las rdzas gzhan du
NK086(lu)003:3477: mi 'dod cing 'dus ma byas gsum ni mo gsham
NK086(lu)003:3478: gyi bu ltar rdzas su med pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:3480: de ltar nyan thos rigs nges rnams kyis spyod pa
NK086(lu)003:3481: so thar brgyad gang rung la gnas shing bden pa
NK086(lu)003:3482: bzhi la mi rtag pa sogs bzhi re bsgoms pas
NK086(lu)003:3483: gang zag rang rkya thub pa'i rdzas yod kyi bdag
NK086(lu)003:3484: gis dben par rtogs shing de nyid goms pas dug
NK086(lu)003:3485: gsum sa bon dang bcas pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3486: nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa'i mi shes pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3487: sgrib pa gnyis lam lnga mtha' phyin pa na sgom
NK086(lu)003:3488: lam rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bcom
NK086(lu)003:3489: ste theg pa chad pa'i tshul gyis spangs te lhag
NK086(lu)003:3490: bcas dang lhag med kyi dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu
NK086(lu)003:3491: mngon du byed pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:3492: rang sangs rgyas rnams kyis bden bzhi mi rtag sogs
NK086(lu)003:3493: la rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i tshul bcu gnyis
NK086(lu)003:3494: bsnan nas bsgoms pas lam bgrod tshul spyir snga ma
NK086(lu)003:3495: dang mtshungs mod / nyan thos pas 'dzin pa gang
NK086(lu)003:3496: zag gi bdag spang bar 'dod kyang gzung ba yul
NK086(lu)003:3497: gyi dngos po rdul phran cha med don dam du
NK086(lu)003:3498: 'dod pa gang zhig /rang sangs rgyas rnams kyis phyi'i
NK086(lu)003:3499: don bslus pa sems snang tsam las don dam du
NK086(lu)003:3500: mi bden par 'dod kyang nang 'dzin byed kyi shes
NK086(lu)003:3501: pa bden par 'dod pa sems tsam pa dang phyog
NK086(lu)003:3502: dang mtshungs mod / mtshungs te / mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK086(lu)003:3503: gzung don rtog pa spang phyir dang //
NK086(lu)003:3504: 'dzin pa mi spang phyir du ni //
NK086(lu)003:3505: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
NK086(lu)003:3506: yang dag bsdus par shes par bya //
NK086(lu)003:3508: de lta bus tshogs lam chen po man chad du
NK086(lu)003:3509: bdag med pa bsgoms nas sbyor lam drod nas mi
NK086(lu)003:3510: slob lam gyi bar stan thog gcig tu mngon du
NK086(lu)003:3511: byed pas dbang po rno rtul gyi dbang gis nyan
NK086(lu)003:3512: rang gnyis theg pa tha dad du 'byed pa yin
NK086(lu)003:3513: la / bsam pa dang rtogs rigs la khyad par
NK086(lu)003:3514: cher med cing de'i dbang gis sde snod kyang gcig
NK086(lu)003:3515: la / go // gnyis pa theg chen byang chub
NK086(lu)003:3516: sems dpa'i theg pa la'ang grub mtha'i sgo nas gnyis
NK086(lu)003:3517: la / go // te / rnam rig smra ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:3520: bye brag smra bas 'dod pa'i shes pa dus cha
NK086(lu)003:3521: dang rdul phran phyogs chas gzhig na mi rnyed pa
NK086(lu)003:3522: mdo sde pas bkag pa ltar don la ma reg
NK086(lu)003:3523: cing phag na mo'i rdzas kyang dam bca' tsam ste
NK086(lu)003:3524: / de'i phyir na ting nge 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:3525: kye rgyal ba'i sras dag khams gsum po 'di ni sems tsam mo //
NK086(lu)003:3526: zhes bka' stsal pa ltar chos thams cad sems kyi
NK086(lu)003:3527: snang cha tsam du 'dod pa'i phyir rnam rig smra
NK086(lu)003:3529: 'dis kyang 'khor lo tha ma'i lung gi rjes su
NK086(lu)003:3530: 'brangs nas chos thams cad kun tu brtags pa dang
NK086(lu)003:3532: yongs su grub pa gsum gyi rnam par gzhag pa khas len pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:3534: rnam grangs pa'i kun brtags dang /
NK086(lu)003:3535: mtshan nyid yongs su chad pa'i kun brtags gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:3536: snga ma ni tha snyad gdags pa'i phyir chos rnams
NK086(lu)003:3537: kyi ngo bo nyid dam bye brag tu ming dang
NK086(lu)003:3538: brdar btags pa don la med bzhin du blos sgro
NK086(lu)003:3540: phyi ma ni bdag gnyis lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:3541: gzhan gyi dbang la'ang gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:3542: ma dag pa'i gzhan dbang dang /
NK086(lu)003:3545: chos rnams rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:3546: ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed byung /
NK086(lu)003:3548: sdug bsngal gyi phung po chen po 'ba' zhig 'di byung par gyur ro //
NK086(lu)003:3549: zhes pa'i bar gsungs pa ltar zag bcas nyer len gyi phung po lngas bsdus pa rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:3551: shin tu dag pa'i rgyal ba rnams kyi sku dang ye shes zhing khams la sogs pa rnams te /
NK086(lu)003:3552: snga ma las dang bag chags kyi rkyen gzhan dang /
NK086(lu)003:3553: phyi ma ni sgrib pa bral stobs kyi rkyen las byung bas na de ltar btags pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:3554: yongs su grub pa'ang gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:3558: gnas lugs kyi don chos dbyings 'gyur med rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'i snying po can te /
NK086(lu)003:3559: rgyan stug po bkod pa las /
NK086(lu)003:3560: snying po de la kun gzhi'i sgras //
NK086(lu)003:3561: rab tu brtag par gyur pa yin //
NK086(lu)003:3564: zag pa med pa'i lam mthar phyin nas 'bras bu'i
NK086(lu)003:3565: dam pa kun gzhi'i steng gi nyon mongs pa cha
NK086(lu)003:3566: dang bcas pa rnam par byang bas snying po de
NK086(lu)003:3567: nyid phyin ci ma log par mngon du gyur pa
NK086(lu)003:3568: la bshad do // sems tsam pa'i grub mtha' 'di la dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:3571: snga mas sngon por 'dzin pa'i mig shes la sngon
NK086(lu)003:3572: po sngon por snang ba ltar grub par khas len
NK086(lu)003:3573: / phyi mas ni sngon por snang ba sogs thams
NK086(lu)003:3574: cad don dang blo gnyis ka'i ngo bor med de
NK086(lu)003:3575: ma rig pa'i bag chags la sgro btags nas de
NK086(lu)003:3576: ltar snang ba blo ma rig pa'i /
NK086(lu)003:3577: slad pa zhugs pa'i shes pa las rdzas gzhan ma
NK086(lu)003:3578: yin par 'dod pa snga ma las cung zad 'phags
NK086(lu)003:3579: shing / de la dbye na gzung 'dzin grangs mnyam pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3581: sgo nga phyed tshal pa sogs yul shes gnyis kyi sa dbye bas tha dad pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3582: rnam rdzun pa la'ang sems kyi ngo bo ma rig
NK086(lu)003:3583: pa'i bag chags kyi dri mas bslad pa dang ma
NK086(lu)003:3584: bslad par 'dod pas dri bcas dri med gnyis su
NK086(lu)003:3585: dbye la / gzung 'dzin grangs mnyam pa la rnam shes tshogs brgyad smra ba gnyis so //
NK086(lu)003:3586: sna tshogs gnyis med pa la tshogs drug 'dod pa
NK086(lu)003:3587: dang rnam shes gcig pur 'dod pa gnyis sogs dbye
NK086(lu)003:3589: 'di nyid nyan rang gi theg pa las cung zad
NK086(lu)003:3590: 'phags kyang yongs grub don dam pa'i bden pa ji
NK086(lu)003:3592: rnam bden rdzun gnyis kas phyi rol yul gyi rnam
NK086(lu)003:3593: pa bden med du rtogs kyang gnyis su med pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3594: shes pa rang rig rang gsal don dam par bden
NK086(lu)003:3595: pa dang yongs grub tu khas blangs pa'i phyir ro
NK086(lu)003:3596: // gnyis pa dbu ma pa la gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:3597: rags pa phyi'i dbu ma ngo bo nyid med par smra ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:3598: phra ba nang gi nges don dbu ma chen po'o //
NK086(lu)003:3600: rang rgyud smra ba'i dbu ma dang /
NK086(lu)003:3603: bye mdo sems gsum gyi grub mtha' ni dngos por
NK086(lu)003:3604: 'dzin pa'i mthar lhung ba'i phyir 'dzin zhen gyi spros
NK086(lu)003:3606: 'dir chos thams cad mtha' gnyis gang du'ang ma lhung
NK086(lu)003:3607: ba'i dbus ma nyid khas blangs pa'i phyir dbu ma
NK086(lu)003:3608: ste / de yang chos thams cad kun rdzob blo 'khrul pa'i shes ngo la yod cing /
NK086(lu)003:3609: don dam par blo ma 'khrul pa'i rig shes su
NK086(lu)003:3610: med par 'dod pa gang zhig rang rgyud smra ba'i
NK086(lu)003:3613: snang la don byed nus pa yang dag kun rdzob dang /
NK086(lu)003:3614: snang la don byed mi nus pa log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis dang /
NK086(lu)003:3615: don dam la'ang myu gu bdag las mi skye ba
NK086(lu)003:3616: sogs spros pa phyogs re gcod pa rnam grangs pa
NK086(lu)003:3617: dang / myu gu bdag las mi skye gzhan las
NK086(lu)003:3618: kyang mi skye ba sogs mtha' bzhi'i spros pa rnams
NK086(lu)003:3619: gcod pa rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam gnyis
NK086(lu)003:3620: dang / su 'dod la / mtshan nyid ni /
NK086(lu)003:3621: dpyod byed kyi rig pas dgag par nus pa la dpyad mi bzod pa kun rdzob dang /
NK086(lu)003:3622: rig pas dgag mi nus pa la dpyad bzod pa zhes don dam bden pa'i mtshan nyid de /
NK086(lu)003:3623: 'di ltar chos can kun rdzob kyi snang ba thams
NK086(lu)003:3624: cad dgag bya med pa la med par rtogs par
NK086(lu)003:3625: bya ba'i phyir / bden dngos med pa la med
NK086(lu)003:3626: par shes par byed pas phyi rol gyi don dang
NK086(lu)003:3627: shes pa'i dngos po gnyis kas stong ste yod med
NK086(lu)003:3628: kyi sgro skur gang du'ang ma phye ba'i ye shes
NK086(lu)003:3629: tsam zhig khas len pa yin te /
NK086(lu)003:3631: so so rang gi rig pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK086(lu)003:3632: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin dang /
NK086(lu)003:3633: dgag bya 'gog byed kyi rigs pa yang /
NK086(lu)003:3634: rgyu la dpyod pa rdo rje'i zegs ma /
NK086(lu)003:3635: 'bras bu la dpyod pa yod med skye 'gog /gnyis
NK086(lu)003:3636: kar dpyod pa mu bzhi skye 'gog /ma yin dgag
NK086(lu)003:3637: gtan tshigs su bkod pa rten 'brel chen po /
NK086(lu)003:3638: med dgag gtan tshigs su bkod pa gcig dang du
NK086(lu)003:3639: bral la sogs gtan tshigs dang rigs pas bsgrubs pas
NK086(lu)003:3640: bsgrub bya sgyu ma la sogs yongs dpyod ma yin
NK086(lu)003:3641: par dgag pa ma yin cing bden pa'i dngos po
NK086(lu)003:3642: bkag pa tsam gyi rnam dpyad med dgag bsgrubs pa
NK086(lu)003:3643: yin te / rig shes rjes dpags kyi rang bzhin
NK086(lu)003:3644: skye med nam mkha' lta bu spros bral don dam
NK086(lu)003:3645: bden pa'i mtshan nyid du dbu ma rang rgyud pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3647: 'dis don dam par med la kun rdzob tu yod
NK086(lu)003:3648: par bsgrubs pas rtag chad kyi skyon gnas shing blos
NK086(lu)003:3649: dpyad pa'i rig shes kyi spros bral med dgag tsam
NK086(lu)003:3650: rtogs pa'ang nges pa'i don du mi gnas la spros
NK086(lu)003:3651: pa 'gog pa'i rig shes kyang spros pa'i bye brag
NK086(lu)003:3652: las mi 'ada'o // gnyis pa thal 'gyur ba ni /
NK086(lu)003:3653: blo 'khrul pa dang ma 'khrul ba gnyis kyi dbye bas bden pa gnyis su 'byed de /
NK086(lu)003:3655: sangs rgyas kyi rnam pa kun tu mkhyen pa'i ye
NK086(lu)003:3656: shes kyi yul du shes dang shes bya yul yul
NK086(lu)003:3657: can gyi gzung 'dzin du snang ba gang yang med
NK086(lu)003:3658: de dper na gnyis du ma log pas rmi lam
NK086(lu)003:3661: dper na gnyid log gnyid dbang gis //
NK086(lu)003:3662: bu dang bud med gzhal yas khang //
NK086(lu)003:3663: gnas la sogs pa mthong gyur na //
NK086(lu)003:3664: sad nas de yis mi snang ltar //
NK086(lu)003:3665: de bzhin kun rdzob shes pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:3666: blo gros mig ni bye gyur zhing //
NK086(lu)003:3667: mi shes gnyid dang bral gyur nas //
NK086(lu)003:3668: sad pa'i tshe na mi gzigs so //
NK086(lu)003:3670: yul can ye shes kyi 'jug pa'ang nye bar zhi ba zhes bya la /
NK086(lu)003:3671: gang gi tshe sems dang sems las byung ba'i spros
NK086(lu)003:3672: pa thams cad rgyun chad cing 'gag nas bsam brjod
NK086(lu)003:3673: thams cad dang bral ba'i chos dbyings zhi ba chen
NK086(lu)003:3674: po'i 'gog par gnas pa de la blo ma 'khrul
NK086(lu)003:3675: pa'i chos nyid ces bya ste /
NK086(lu)003:3677: gang phyir chos nyid skye med yin phyir blo yang skye ba dang bral la //
NK086(lu)003:3678: de phyir de rnams brten la de yis de nyid rig pa lta bu ste //
NK086(lu)003:3679: gang phyir sems ni yul gyi rnam par 'byung bas de yi yul //
NK086(lu)003:3680: de rab rigs pa de bzhin tha snyad brten nas rig pa yin //
NK086(lu)003:3682: shes bya'i bud shing skam po ma lus pa //
NK086(lu)003:3683: bsregs nas zhi ste rgyal rnams chos sku ste //
NK086(lu)003:3684: de tshe skye ba med cing 'gag pa med //
NK086(lu)003:3685: sems 'gag pa de sku yis mngon sum mdzad //
NK086(lu)003:3686: ces bshad pa'i gnas de don dam pa'i bden pa
NK086(lu)003:3687: rtogs pa zhes btags te de'i yul ni gshis kyi
NK086(lu)003:3688: gnas lugs chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnams par
NK086(lu)003:3690: mthong ba rdzun pa blo 'khrul pa ni so skye
NK086(lu)003:3691: ma rig pa'i bag chags kyis bslad pas ji ltar
NK086(lu)003:3692: mig nad can gyis rab rib dang skra shad 'dzag
NK086(lu)003:3693: pa la bden par zhen pa ltar /
NK086(lu)003:3694: 'di ltar 'gro ba drug gi gnas dang longs spyod
NK086(lu)003:3695: bde sdug mtho dman sna tshogs su snang ba 'khrul
NK086(lu)003:3696: pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi rnam pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3697: 'phags pa rnams kyis rjes thob tu gzhan dang mthun
NK086(lu)003:3698: mong du snod bcud la sogs par snang ba'i rnam
NK086(lu)003:3699: pa gnyis / dbang po skyon can gyi rnam pa
NK086(lu)003:3700: dang skyon med pa gnyis ltar kun rdzob gnyis su
NK086(lu)003:3701: pa gnyis / bzhag ste / 'jug pa las /
NK086(lu)003:3702: mthong ba rdzun pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK086(lu)003:3703: dbang po gsal dang dbang po skyon ldan no //
NK086(lu)003:3704: skyon ldan dbang po rnams kyi shes pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:3705: dbang po legs gyur la ltos log par 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:3707: de'i dbang gis 'khor ba'i chos sems dang sems las
NK086(lu)003:3708: byung ba yul gyi rnam par snang ba dang bcas
NK086(lu)003:3709: pa thams cad kun rdzob yin la /
NK086(lu)003:3710: sa thob kyang sems dang sems byung ma 'gags pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3711: cha yul ma dag pa'i gzugs sogs tshogs drug snang
NK086(lu)003:3712: ba dang bcas pa mdor na spang bya gyur to
NK086(lu)003:3713: cog kun rdzob kyi phyogs su bslan nas 'khrul par
NK086(lu)003:3714: bzhag ste / kun rdzob de'ang dbang po skyon can la snang ba log pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK086(lu)003:3715: skyon med kyi yul du snang ba yang dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:3716: snga ma ni 'jig rten shes ngo la snang yang
NK086(lu)003:3717: mi bden par grags pa zla ba gnyis dang rmi
NK086(lu)003:3719: phyi ma ni 'jig rten shes ngor snang la bden
NK086(lu)003:3720: par grags pa zla ba gcig tu snang ba la
NK086(lu)003:3721: sogs pa'o // de'ang gnyis su 'dzin pa'i 'khrul blo'i
NK086(lu)003:3722: gnas skabs su bden pa ltar snang ba mig skyon
NK086(lu)003:3723: can la skra shad du snang ba mig dag pa
NK086(lu)003:3724: la ci yang med pa'i bzhin du blo 'khrul pa
NK086(lu)003:3725: la sna tshogs su snang ba nyid 'phags pa'i mnyam
NK086(lu)003:3726: gzhag dang 'khrul pa zad pa'i sangs rgyas la dmigs
NK086(lu)003:3727: par bya ba ci yang med pas 'khrul snang cha
NK086(lu)003:3728: dang bcas pa mi snang ste /
NK086(lu)003:3730: rab rib mthu yi skra shad la sogs pa //
NK086(lu)003:3731: dngos po log pa gang zhig rnam brtag las //
NK086(lu)003:3732: de nyid gang gis bdag nyid mig dag pas //
NK086(lu)003:3733: mthong ba gang yin de bzhin 'dir shes bya //
NK086(lu)003:3735: klu sgrub kyi dbu ma 'khrul 'joms su'ang /
NK086(lu)003:3736: de bzhin mkhas pa yang dag gis //
NK086(lu)003:3737: shes pa nyi mas mi shes pa'i //
NK086(lu)003:3738: bag chags ma lus bcom pa'i tshe //
NK086(lu)003:3739: sems dang sems byung yul mi gzigs //
NK086(lu)003:3740: zhes gsungs pa ltar gzung 'dzin spros pa thams cad
NK086(lu)003:3741: dang bral ba'i ngo bo sgra tshig la sogs pa
NK086(lu)003:3742: dngos su mi rtog pa'i cha nas gzhan las shes
NK086(lu)003:3743: pa ma yin pa sems dang sems byung gi rnyog
NK086(lu)003:3744: pa ma lus pa chos kyi dbyings su zhib /
NK086(lu)003:3745: rnam par rtog pa las 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:3746: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba /
NK086(lu)003:3747: grub pa'i mtha' ma reg pa'i chos nyid kyi gnas
NK086(lu)003:3748: lugs de ni don dam bden pa'i mtshan nyid de
NK086(lu)003:3750: gzhan las shes min zhi ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:3751: spros pa rnams kyis ma spros pa //
NK086(lu)003:3752: rnam rtog med don tha dad min //
NK086(lu)003:3753: de ni de yi mtshan nyid do //
NK086(lu)003:3755: mdor bsdu na sangs rgyas 'phags pa'i thugs sgrib pa
NK086(lu)003:3756: thams cad dang bral ba'i zab pa dang zhi ba'i
NK086(lu)003:3757: mtshan nyid can gyi dbyings dang /
NK086(lu)003:3758: de rtogs byed rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes /
NK086(lu)003:3759: byang 'phags kyi mnyam gzhag gi ye shes kyi ngo bo dang /
NK086(lu)003:3760: de'i rjes thob kyi snang ba lhag mthong gi rnam par gyur to cog don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:3761: de yang gtan tshigs lnga po rnams kyis chos thams cad rang bzhin med par 'jal mod kyi /
NK086(lu)003:3762: rang rgyud pa ltar kun rdzob bden pa bkag nas rdzun par bsgrub pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3763: don dam spros pa bkag nas spros med du sgrub pa sogs res 'jog can ma yin par /
NK086(lu)003:3764: chos thams cad yod min med min gang du'ang mi
NK086(lu)003:3765: phye bar brjod du med pa'i gnas lugs bsam gyis
NK086(lu)003:3766: mi khyab par skyel ba'i thal 'gyur ma 'khrul pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3767: dgongs pa 'dis khas blangs pa'i grub mtha' thams cad
NK086(lu)003:3769: gal te ngas dam bcas 'ga' yod //
NK086(lu)003:3770: de tshe nga la skyon 'di yod //
NK086(lu)003:3771: nga la dam bca' med pas na //
NK086(lu)003:3772: nga ni skyon med kho na yin //
NK086(lu)003:3775: yod dang med dang yod med ces //
NK086(lu)003:3776: gang la phyogs ni yod min pa //
NK086(lu)003:3777: de la yun ni rong po na'ang //
NK086(lu)003:3778: klan ka brjod par nus ma yin //
NK086(lu)003:3781: khas blangs pa yi dngos po ni //
NK086(lu)003:3782: phra rab tsam yang yod min te //
NK086(lu)003:3783: gdod nas skye ba med pa'i phyir //
NK086(lu)003:3784: mo gsham gyi ni bu bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:3786: 'o na bden pa gnyis kyi rnam gzhag kyang med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:3787: gnas lugs la bden gnyis sogs gnyis chos thams cad las 'das kyang /
NK086(lu)003:3788: 'jig rten snang lugs su sgro btags pa tsam du
NK086(lu)003:3789: de ltar 'dogs par byed pa de nyid grub mtha'i
NK086(lu)003:3790: bden zhen ltar bzung ba ma yin te /
NK086(lu)003:3792: ji ltar khyod kyis gzhan dbang dngos 'dod ltar //
NK086(lu)003:3793: kun rdzob kyang ni bdag gis khas ma blangs //
NK086(lu)003:3796: yi ge med pa'i chos rnams la //
NK086(lu)003:3797: nyan pa gang dang ston pa gang //
NK086(lu)003:3798: 'gyur ba med la sgro btags nas //
NK086(lu)003:3799: nyan cing ston par byed pa'ang yin //
NK086(lu)003:3801: de lta bu'i chos nyid la mnyam par bzhag pa
NK086(lu)003:3802: shes rab dang thabs snying rje chen po zung du
NK086(lu)003:3803: 'jug cing bsgoms pa ye shes kyi tshogs dang /
NK086(lu)003:3804: rjes thob tu chos thams cad sgyu ma lta bur shes pas bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa las /
NK086(lu)003:3805: mthar gyis chos kyi sku dang gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis 'thob par 'gyur ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:3807: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gzugs sku 'di //
NK086(lu)003:3808: bsod nams tshogs las byung ba ste //
NK086(lu)003:3809: chos kyi sku ni mdor bsdu na //
NK086(lu)003:3810: rgyal po ye shes tshogs las 'khrungs //
NK086(lu)003:3812: de yang gzhi dbu ma bden gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:3814: 'bras bu dbu ma sku gnyis zung 'jug tu 'dus pa yin no //
NK086(lu)003:3815: gnyis pa phra ba nang gi nges don dbu ma chen po'i tshul ni /
NK086(lu)003:3816: slob dpon skal ldan gyi dbu ma'i bstan bcos rin chen sgron mar /
NK086(lu)003:3817: thal rang gi dbu ma ni rags pa phyi'i dbu ma ste /
NK086(lu)003:3818: thos pa las byung ba'i rig par smra bas phyi rol pa dang rtsod pa'i dus dang /
NK086(lu)003:3819: bstan bcos chen po byed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3820: rig pa chen po'i gzhung 'dzugs pa'i tshe smra bar bya ba yin la /
NK086(lu)003:3821: phra ba nang gi dbu ma nyams su len pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3822: tshe ni rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma nyid bsgom
NK086(lu)003:3823: par bya'o // zhes dbu ma la phyi nang phra
NK086(lu)003:3824: rags gnyis su gsungs pa'i phyi ma 'khor lo tha
NK086(lu)003:3825: ma'i dgongs pa phyir mi ldog pa dang 'khor gsum
NK086(lu)003:3826: yongs su dag pa'i gtam gyis chos thams cad mtshan
NK086(lu)003:3827: nyid gsum du bstan pa'i don rgya che ba'i gnas
NK086(lu)003:3828: rnams rgyal tshab ma pham pas don gyi dgongs pa
NK086(lu)003:3830: de yang sngar smos pa sems tsam smra ba'i lugs
NK086(lu)003:3831: kyi stong gzhi gzhan dbang dgag bya kun brtags kyis
NK086(lu)003:3832: stong ba'i yongs grub tu bshad pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:3833: 'dir ni chos nyid yongs grub dgag bya kun brtags kyis stong par bzhed de /
NK086(lu)003:3834: 'di ltar gzhan dbang du rtog pa'i phung po khams
NK086(lu)003:3835: dang skye ched kun brtags bdag dang bdag gi bas
NK086(lu)003:3837: stong gzhi gzhan dbang gis stong pa'i gzhi chos nyid yongs grub yin te /
NK086(lu)003:3838: de nyid stong pa'i gzhi ni nam yang mi srid
NK086(lu)003:3839: de ngo bo dri ma dang skyon gyi dngos po
NK086(lu)003:3840: rnam par dbye ba dang bcas pa'i 'khor ba'i chos
NK086(lu)003:3841: glo bur ba'i mtshan nyid can gyis stong la /
NK086(lu)003:3842: ye nas lhun grub tu gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK086(lu)003:3843: 'das pa'i yon tan gyi tshogs kyis mi stong pa
NK086(lu)003:3845: rnam dbyer bcas pa'i mtshan nyid can //
NK086(lu)003:3846: glo bur dag gis khams stong gis //
NK086(lu)003:3847: rnam dbyer med pa'i mtshan nyid kyis //
NK086(lu)003:3848: bla med chos kyis stong ma yin //
NK086(lu)003:3851: 'dis ci bstan zhe na gang gi phyir rang bzhin
NK086(lu)003:3852: gyis yongs su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i khams
NK086(lu)003:3853: 'di la gsal bas bya ba kun nas nyon mongs
NK086(lu)003:3854: pa'i rgyu mtshan ni 'ga' yang med de glo bur
NK086(lu)003:3855: ba'i dri ma dang bral ba 'di'i rang bzhin yin
NK086(lu)003:3856: pa'i phyir ro // 'di la rnam par byang ba'i
NK086(lu)003:3857: rgyu mtshan can gzhag par bya ba cung zad yod
NK086(lu)003:3859: rnam par dbye ba med pa'i chos dag pa'i chos nyid ni rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:3860: des na de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ni rnam
NK086(lu)003:3861: par dbye ba yod pa dang bral ba shes pa
NK086(lu)003:3862: nyon mongs pa'i sbubs thams cad kyis stong pa yin
NK086(lu)003:3863: la / rnam par dbye ba med pa bral mi
NK086(lu)003:3864: shes pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK086(lu)003:3865: chos gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed las 'das pas
NK086(lu)003:3866: la / mi stong ngo // zhes gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:3867: de yang kun tu brtags pa ni mtshan nyid ngo bo nyid med pa /
NK086(lu)003:3868: gzhan gyi dbang ni skye ba ngo bo nyid med pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3869: yongs su grub pa don dam ngo bo nyid med
NK086(lu)003:3870: par gsungs pa'i snga ma gnyis ni bcos ma glo
NK086(lu)003:3871: bur bar gyur pa'i gzung 'dzin spros pa'i cha rnams
NK086(lu)003:3872: rang gi ngo bos stong zhing /
NK086(lu)003:3873: phyi ma ni rang bzhin gnyug ma dngos po med
NK086(lu)003:3874: pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid rang bzhin gyis
NK086(lu)003:3876: stong cha nas chos sku'i yon tan dang /
NK086(lu)003:3877: snang cha nas sku dang zhing khams gzhal yas khang sogs kyi 'char gzhir gnas shing /
NK086(lu)003:3878: rig pa'i cha nas stobs bcu'i mi 'jigs pa bzhi
NK086(lu)003:3879: sogs kyi rten gzhir gyur pas bral rgyu dang bral
NK086(lu)003:3880: 'bras gdod nas lhun grub tu bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK086(lu)003:3881: kyi rang bzhin bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po zhes
NK086(lu)003:3883: rgyu rkyen sogs kyi khams su mi gnas shing tha
NK086(lu)003:3884: snyad dang bsam brjod kyi yul yang ma yin pa
NK086(lu)003:3885: rtag tu gos pa med par yod pa yin te
NK086(lu)003:3886: / 'jam dpal rnam par rol pa las /
NK086(lu)003:3887: sring mo gang rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba la
NK086(lu)003:3888: glo bur gyi nyon mongs pa byung yang rang bzhin
NK086(lu)003:3889: gyi 'od gsal ba de ni glo bur gyi nyon
NK086(lu)003:3890: mongs pa des kun nas nyon mongs par byed mi
NK086(lu)003:3893: 'dus ma byas shing lhun gyis grub //
NK086(lu)003:3894: gzhan gyi rkyen gyis rtogs min pa //
NK086(lu)003:3895: mkhyen dang brtse dang nus par ldan //
NK086(lu)003:3896: don gnyis ldan pa'i sangs rgyas nyid //
NK086(lu)003:3898: gzhan du rang stong pa ltar chos thams cad rang
NK086(lu)003:3899: gi ngo bos stong pa kho nar ba zung na
NK086(lu)003:3900: mtha' gcig tu chos kyi sku yang rang stong du
NK086(lu)003:3901: 'gyur zhing sku dang ye shes zhing khams sogs kyang
NK086(lu)003:3903: der brten pa'i tshogs bsags pa dang sgrib pa sbyong ba rnams kyang med par 'gyur zhing /
NK086(lu)003:3904: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa dag gis gzhi gang
NK086(lu)003:3905: du lam gang gis dri ma sbyong ba'i thabs ji
NK086(lu)003:3906: snyed bstan pa rnams kyang nyams par 'gyur te /
NK086(lu)003:3907: sbyang gzhi med pas sbyong byed dgos pa med pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:3908: ye shes kyis stong pas gzhan don mdzad pa dang mkhyen par mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:3909: ma dag pa'i gzhan dbang kun rdzob tsam du'ang med
NK086(lu)003:3910: pas dag pa'i gzhan dbang gnas yongs su 'gyur ba'i
NK086(lu)003:3911: yon tan rnams kyang med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:3912: bcings pa dang grol ba'i gzhir gyur pa'i bdag med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:3913: so so rang gis rig par bya ba'i chos med
NK086(lu)003:3914: par 'gyur ba sogs skyon gyi rnam pa du ma
NK086(lu)003:3915: gnas shing lta ba mi bzad pa'i 'byung gnas skye
NK086(lu)003:3916: ba'i bdag nyid can du gsungs te /
NK086(lu)003:3917: 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i 'od srung gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:3918: 'od srung gang zag stong pa nyid du dmigs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:3919: stong pa nyid la rton pa de dag ni nga'i
NK086(lu)003:3921: rab tu nyams par bshad de /
NK086(lu)003:3922: 'od srung gang zag tu lta ba ri rab tsam la gnas pa sla'i /
NK086(lu)003:3923: mngon pa'i nga rgyal stong pa nyid du lta ba ni de lta ma yin no //
NK086(lu)003:3925: 'od srung lta ba gyur pa thams cad las 'byung
NK086(lu)003:3926: ba ni stong pa nyid yin na 'od srung gang
NK086(lu)003:3927: stong ba nyid kho nar blta ba de ni gsor
NK086(lu)003:3928: mi rung ngo zhes ngas bshad do //
NK086(lu)003:3929: zhes gsungs pa sogs kyis shes par nus shing /
NK086(lu)003:3930: 'o na mi stong pa yin nam zhe na de yang ma yin te /
NK086(lu)003:3931: 'phags pa lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:3932: chos thams cad kyi don dam pa 'phags pa'i ye shes chen po stong pa nyid gang zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:3934: so so rang gis rig pa 'phags pa'i ye shes
NK086(lu)003:3935: thob pa ni lta ba dang nyes pa thams cad
NK086(lu)003:3936: kyi bag chags kyis stong ste 'di ni chos thams
NK086(lu)003:3937: cad kyi don dam pa 'phags pa'i ye shes chen
NK086(lu)003:3938: po stong pa nyid ces bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:3940: de ltar don dam pa gzhan gyis stong pa'i tshul
NK086(lu)003:3941: 'di 'khor lo bar pa'i mdo sde nas kyang 'byung
NK086(lu)003:3942: ste / shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa las /
NK086(lu)003:3943: de la gzhan gyi dngos po stong pa nyid gang zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:3944: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams byung yang rung de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ma byung yang rung ste /
NK086(lu)003:3948: chos skyon med pa nyid dang /
NK086(lu)003:3950: ma nor ba de bzhin nyid dang /
NK086(lu)003:3951: gzhan ma yin pa de bzhin nyid dang /
NK086(lu)003:3952: yang dag pa'i mtha' ni de bzhin nyid du gnas pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:3953: de ltar chos nyid de dag gzhan gyis stong pa
NK086(lu)003:3954: gang yin pa de ni gzhan gyi dngos pos stong
NK086(lu)003:3956: rab 'byor 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi theg pa chen po'o //
NK086(lu)003:3959: rnam dbyer bcas pa'i mtshan nyid can /
NK086(lu)003:3960: zhes sogs sngar smos pa ltar rgya cher gsungs so //
NK086(lu)003:3961: de lta bu'i dbyings de nyid sems can gyi rgyud
NK086(lu)003:3962: la sa'i khams su rin po che'i gter gnas pa
NK086(lu)003:3963: bzhin rang gi ngo bo la dri mas ma gos
NK086(lu)003:3964: kyang glo bur 'khor ba dang rnam pa mtshungs ldan
NK086(lu)003:3965: du gnas pa chu dang chab rom gyi dpe bzhin
NK086(lu)003:3968: dag pa dwangs pa 'od gsal ba //
NK086(lu)003:3970: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste //
NK086(lu)003:3971: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK086(lu)003:3973: slob dpon klu'i chos kyi dbyings kyi bstod par /
NK086(lu)003:3974: sa yi nang na gnas pa'i chu //
NK086(lu)003:3975: dri ma med par yang dag gnas //
NK086(lu)003:3976: nyon mongs nang na ye shes kyang //
NK086(lu)003:3977: de bzhin dri ma med par gnas //
NK086(lu)003:3978: zhes sogs nges don snying po'i bzhugs tshul bsam gyis mi khyab par gsungs shing /
NK086(lu)003:3979: gshegs snying de nyid rang ngo la ltos nas 'khor 'das bzang ngan med par mnyam pa nyid de /
NK086(lu)003:3980: de bzhin nyid de thams cad la //
NK086(lu)003:3981: khyad par med cing dag gyur pa //
NK086(lu)003:3982: de bzhin gshegs nyid de yi phyir //
NK086(lu)003:3983: 'gro kun de yi snying po can //
NK086(lu)003:3984: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa rnams ni chos nyid
NK086(lu)003:3985: mi 'gyur ba'i yongs grub la dgongs pa yin te
NK086(lu)003:3987: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK086(lu)003:3988: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK086(lu)003:3990: dri ma glo bur ba de la gnas skabs kyi sgo nas dbye na gsum du 'gyur te /
NK086(lu)003:3992: ma dag ma dag dag pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:3993: shin tu rnam dag go rim bzhin //
NK086(lu)003:3994: sems can byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK086(lu)003:3995: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes brjod do //
NK086(lu)003:3998: 'di ltar ma dag pa'i gnas skabs su ni sems can gyi khams zhes bya ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:3999: ma dag pa dag pa'i gnas skabs su ni byang chub sems dpa' zhes bya ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4000: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i gnas skabs su ni de bzhin gshegs pa zhes bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:4002: de bzhin du theg pa gsum sogs tha dad pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4003: sa bcu lam lnga sogs gong 'og gi dbye bas tha dad par bzhag pa rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:4004: de bzhin du 'gro ba bzang ngan nyan rang dang
NK086(lu)003:4005: byang sems sangs rgyas 'phags pa la sogs gong 'og
NK086(lu)003:4006: bzang ngan ltar du snang ba thams cad kyang /
NK086(lu)003:4009: rin po che'i snod la sogs pa tha dad bzang
NK086(lu)003:4010: ngan ltar du snang yang snod de dag gi nang
NK086(lu)003:4011: gi nam mkha' la bzang ngan med par mnyam pa
NK086(lu)003:4012: ltar / chos kyi dbyings don dam pa'i bden pa
NK086(lu)003:4013: rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba de ni bzang ngan
NK086(lu)003:4014: dang dbri bsnan med par kun la khyab par yod
NK086(lu)003:4015: ltar / de / rgyud bla ma las /
NK086(lu)003:4016: ji ltar rtog med bdag nyid can //
NK086(lu)003:4017: nam mkha' kun tu rjes song ltar //
NK086(lu)003:4018: sems kyi rang bzhin dri med dbyings //
NK086(lu)003:4019: de bzhin kun tu 'gro ba nyid //
NK086(lu)003:4020: de spyi'i mtshan nyid nges pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:4021: yon tan mthar thug khyab pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:4022: gzugs kyi rnam pa dman pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:4023: bar pa mchog la nam mkha' bzhin //
NK086(lu)003:4025: 'o na gong du gnas skabs gsum smos pa ci zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:4026: snying po de nyid sgrib byed kyi dri ma las
NK086(lu)003:4027: grol ba dang ma grol ba'i khyad par gyis 'khor
NK086(lu)003:4028: ba dang myang 'das gnyis su phye ba yin te
NK086(lu)003:4030: nyon mongs d+r+wa bas g.yogs pa la //
NK086(lu)003:4031: sems can zhes ni nges par brjod //
NK086(lu)003:4032: de nyid nyon mongs bral gyur na //
NK086(lu)003:4033: sangs rgyas zhes ni brjod par byed //
NK086(lu)003:4035: gnas skabs gsum po de yang /
NK086(lu)003:4036: sgrib pa'i mun pa chen pos bsgribs pa'i so so
NK086(lu)003:4037: skye bo la yon tan cha shas tsam las med
NK086(lu)003:4038: pa las / snying po'i dri ma bsal stobs gnyan
NK086(lu)003:4039: po'i nus pa che chung gi dbang gis rim pa
NK086(lu)003:4040: bzhin srab tu song bas nyan rang gi dgra bcom
NK086(lu)003:4042: de dag gis kyang mi shes pa thams cad ma
NK086(lu)003:4043: spangs pa las gong mar gyur pa sa thob pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4044: byang chub sems dpa' rnams 'phags par snang ba dang
NK086(lu)003:4045: / de bas sgrib pa thams cad dang bral ba'i sangs rgyas 'phags par snang ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:4046: de lta bas na dbyings don dam pa'i bden pa
NK086(lu)003:4047: de nyid nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa'
NK086(lu)003:4048: ste 'phags pa 'og ma gsum gyis gnas lugs ji
NK086(lu)003:4049: lta ba bzhin ma mthong ste /
NK086(lu)003:4050: tshogs sbyor gyis lam la gnas pas yid dpyod kyi mos pa tsam las mngon sum du mi mthong /
NK086(lu)003:4051: mthong sgom gnyis su phyogs re mthong la /
NK086(lu)003:4052: 'on kyang lam de bas bu chung gis mthongs ka'i
NK086(lu)003:4053: nyi zhur mthong ba tsam las yongs la khyab pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4054: nyi ma ma mthong ba mthong ba bzhin dbyings kyi
NK086(lu)003:4055: yon tan cha shas tsam las yongs su rdzogs par
NK086(lu)003:4057: ngag yul min phyir don dam gyis bsdus phyir //
NK086(lu)003:4058: rtogs gnas min phyir dpe las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK086(lu)003:4059: bla na med phyir srid zhis ma bsdus phyir //
NK086(lu)003:4060: rgyal yul 'phags rnams kyis kyang bsam mi khyab //
NK086(lu)003:4061: ces sngar drangs pa ltar ro //
NK086(lu)003:4062: sangs rgyas kyi sar ni rang bzhin ci yin pa
NK086(lu)003:4063: mngon sum du gyur nas yongs su rdzogs par gzigs
NK086(lu)003:4064: pa ste / rgyud bla ma'i 'grel par /
NK086(lu)003:4065: sprin mthongs mkha' la nyi bzhin 'dir khyod phyogs gcig blo gros can //
NK086(lu)003:4066: blo mig dag pa'i 'phags rnams kyis kyang thams cad rab tu mthong ma lags //
NK086(lu)003:4067: bcom ldan 'das khyod chos sku rnam dag blo gros mtha' yas pas //
NK086(lu)003:4068: shes bya mtha' med mkha' dbyings khyab pa de dag gis kun mthong //
NK086(lu)003:4070: de ltar na sems can gyi khams la dbyings rang
NK086(lu)003:4071: bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba de rang chas su bzhugs
NK086(lu)003:4072: pas sems can rnams tshogs gnyis bsags shing sgrib gnyis
NK086(lu)003:4073: spangs pa'i sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:4074: de ma yin pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK086(lu)003:4075: spang ba la gnyis yod de /
NK086(lu)003:4079: chos nyid rang gi ngo bo gdod ma nyid nas
NK086(lu)003:4080: dag pa chen po'i gshis lugs su gnas pa la
NK086(lu)003:4082: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yul la 'jug pa ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:4083: 'jam dpal sems ni rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i
NK086(lu)003:4084: phyir te de ni glo bur ba'i nye ba'i nyon
NK086(lu)003:4085: mongs pa thams cad kyis nye bar nyon mongs par
NK086(lu)003:4086: zad kyis / rang bzhin gyis kun nas nyon mongs pa ma yin no //
NK086(lu)003:4087: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba gang yin pa de
NK086(lu)003:4088: ni kun nas nyon mongs pa med pa nyid yin
NK086(lu)003:4089: no // kun nas nyon mongs pa med pa de
NK086(lu)003:4090: la ni gnyen po gang gis kun nas nyon mongs
NK086(lu)003:4091: pa spongs bar 'gyur ba'i gnyen po med do //
NK086(lu)003:4093: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa las /
NK086(lu)003:4094: koo shi ka de ji snyam du sems /
NK086(lu)003:4095: de la sems can gang yang skye ba'am 'gag par gyur pa yod dam /
NK086(lu)003:4097: btsun pa rab 'byor de ni med de /
NK086(lu)003:4098: de ci'i phyir zhe na sems can thog ma nas rnam par dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:4101: gzugs rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i phyir rnam par dag pa kun nas nyon mongs pa med pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:4102: tshor bar dang 'du shes dang 'du byed dang rnam
NK086(lu)003:4103: par shes pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i phyir
NK086(lu)003:4104: rnam par dag pa kun nas nyon mongs pa med
NK086(lu)003:4105: pa'o // rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi
NK086(lu)003:4106: bar du rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i phyir rnam
NK086(lu)003:4107: par dag pa kun nas nyon mongs pa med pa'o
NK086(lu)003:4108: pa'o // // zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa ltar
NK086(lu)003:4109: rnam par shes pa'i chos las 'das pa dang sgrib
NK086(lu)003:4110: pa kun las nges par grol ba nyid kyi phyir
NK086(lu)003:4111: rang bzhin gyi spang ba de don dam pa'i chos
NK086(lu)003:4112: nyid la gdod nas tshang ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:4113: chos nyid yongs grub de nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:4115: glo bur gyi sgrib byed de dang 'tshams pa'i gnyen pos bsal ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:4116: lam gyis ma sbyangs par gzhi la yod pa'i yon
NK086(lu)003:4117: tan mngon du mi 'gyur ba sngar bshad pa bzhin
NK086(lu)003:4118: sems can gyi skabs su gyur kyang des grub mtha'
NK086(lu)003:4119: 'di la skyon du mi 'gyur te sems can rnams
NK086(lu)003:4120: sgrib pa kun bral gyi sangs rgyas su mi bzhed
NK086(lu)003:4121: pa'i phyir ro // de bzhin du rtogs pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:4122: gdod nas chos nyid rang gi rig pas rtogs pa rang byung ye shes dang /
NK086(lu)003:4123: lam bsgom stobs kyis rtogs pa gzhan byung ye shes so //
NK086(lu)003:4125: don dam chos nyid de rtogs byed so so rang
NK086(lu)003:4126: gi rig pa shes rab rang byung gi ye shes
NK086(lu)003:4127: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mtshan nyid can te /
NK086(lu)003:4128: bdag rig gzhan rig thams cad rig /kun shes kun rig dam pa po //
NK086(lu)003:4129: zhes gsungs pa ltar gnyug ma'i spangs rtogs gnyis po
NK086(lu)003:4130: don dam pa'i gnas lugs rang gi ngo bor tshang
NK086(lu)003:4131: ba ste / rje btsun byams pas /
NK086(lu)003:4132: 'di la bsal bya gang yang med //
NK086(lu)003:4133: gzhag par bya ba'ang cung zad med //
NK086(lu)003:4134: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK086(lu)003:4135: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK086(lu)003:4138: lam bsgom stobs kyis rtogs pa rgyas 'gyur gyi rigs de mnyam gzhag gis ye shes kyi tshogs dang /
NK086(lu)003:4139: rjes thob tu bsod nams kyi tshogs gnyis bsags pas
NK086(lu)003:4140: mthar bral stobs kyi yon tan mngon du gyur pa
NK086(lu)003:4141: la phyin ci ma log pa'i yongs grub tu gdags
NK086(lu)003:4142: pa ste / mdo sde rgyan las /
NK086(lu)003:4143: snga ma phyi ma khyad med kyang //
NK086(lu)003:4144: sgrib pa kun gyi dri med pa //
NK086(lu)003:4145: de bzhin nyid ni sangs rgyas 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:4147: de la kun rdzob rang gi ngo bo sa stong pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4148: don dam gzhan gyis stong pa'i tshul 'di nyid 'khor
NK086(lu)003:4149: lo bar tha gnyis nas ci rigs par bstan la
NK086(lu)003:4150: / khyad par stong gzhi bde gshegs snying po zab
NK086(lu)003:4151: gsal gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi bzhugs tshul
NK086(lu)003:4152: bka' tha ma'i sde snod rnams su rgyas par gsungs
NK086(lu)003:4153: pa dang chos thams cad sems kyi snang cha tsam
NK086(lu)003:4155: sngon gyi slob dpon 'ga' zhig gis dgos pa'i dbang
NK086(lu)003:4156: gis sems don dam par khas blangs pas deng sang
NK086(lu)003:4157: grub mtha' bzhir grags pa'i nang gi rnam rig smra
NK086(lu)003:4158: bar brjod pa 'di byung ba yin la /
NK086(lu)003:4159: don gyi dgongs pa ni bzhin ma longs te chos
NK086(lu)003:4160: thams cad sems kyi snang cha tsam du gsungs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4161: sems de kun gzhi'i rnam shes su dgongs pa'i skabs
NK086(lu)003:4162: dang / chos nyid yongs grub la dgongs pa'i skabs gnyis yod de /
NK086(lu)003:4163: snga ma la dgongs nas 'khrul pa'i yul dang yul
NK086(lu)003:4164: can kun rdzob pa yin pa'i phyir rtag pa mi
NK086(lu)003:4165: srid pas don dam bden par ma gsungs te /
NK086(lu)003:4166: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:4168: sems zhes bya ba ni sems dang yid kyi rnam par shes pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4174: des stong pa nyid gang zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:4175: sh+aa ra dwa ta'i bu sems ni sems kyis stong ste /
NK086(lu)003:4176: de la byed pa po gang yang med do //
NK086(lu)003:4177: gal te de'i byed pa po 'ga' zhig yod na
NK086(lu)003:4178: ni des byas na gzhan gyis myong ba de lta
NK086(lu)003:4179: bur 'gyur ro // sems kyis kyang sems mngon par 'du mi byed do //
NK086(lu)003:4181: chos thams cad sems kyi snang cha tsam du gsungs
NK086(lu)003:4182: kyang de don dam pa'i bden par gsungs pa'i skabs
NK086(lu)003:4185: rnam shes thams cad las 'das pa'i ye shes la don dam pa'i bden par bstan te /
NK086(lu)003:4186: 'phags pa lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:4189: yid kyi rnam par shes pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4191: 'du shes med par gyur pas mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob par 'gyur te /
NK086(lu)003:4192: blo gros chen po snang ba med pa rnam par
NK086(lu)003:4193: rtog pas dben pa'i chos bstan pa'i phyir don dam
NK086(lu)003:4194: pa 'di la go rim dang go rim gyi mtshams
NK086(lu)003:4197: sems dang yid dang rnam shes dang //
NK086(lu)003:4198: 'du shes rtog pa spangs pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:4199: rnam par rtog pa'i chos thob pa //
NK086(lu)003:4200: nyan thos rnams ni rgyal sras yin //
NK086(lu)003:4201: zhing dang bzod pa'i khyad par las //
NK086(lu)003:4202: de bzhin gshegs kyi ye shes dge //
NK086(lu)003:4203: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:4204: gzhan yang sems tsam pa'i grub mtha' smra ba gang
NK086(lu)003:4205: zhig /don dam bden par 'dod pa ni rnam shes
NK086(lu)003:4206: las ma 'das la de ni 'khor ba'i yul can
NK086(lu)003:4207: gyi shes pa zang ka ma ste 'jig rten las
NK086(lu)003:4208: 'phags par mi nus pa'i phyir dang /
NK086(lu)003:4209: don dam pa'i bden pa ni zag pa med pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4210: dbyings dang de rtogs pa'i sgrib bral gyi ye shes
NK086(lu)003:4211: 'phags pa rnams kyi so so rang gi rig pa
NK086(lu)003:4212: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mtshan can te /
NK086(lu)003:4213: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni theg pa chen po'i mdo sde las /
NK086(lu)003:4214: de la blo gros chen po ye shes ni rnam pa gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:4218: de las skyes nas 'jig pa ni rnam par shes pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:4219: ma skyes mi 'jig pa ni ye shes so //
NK086(lu)003:4220: gzhan yang blo gros chen po mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med par ltung ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4221: yod pa dang med par ltung ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4222: mtshan nyid sna tshogs kyi rgyu las skyes pa rnams ni rnam par shes pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:4223: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa las shin tu 'das pa'i mtshan nyid ni ye shes so //
NK086(lu)003:4224: gzhan yang blo gros chen po de la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid ni rnam par shes pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:4225: bri ba'i mtshan nyid ni ye shes so //
NK086(lu)003:4226: de la rnam pa gsum ni 'di lta ste /
NK086(lu)003:4227: rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid rtogs par byed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4228: skye ba dang 'jig pa rtogs par byed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4229: skye ba med pa dang 'gag pa med par rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:4230: de la 'jig rten pa'i ye shes ni yod pa
NK086(lu)003:4231: dang med pa'i phyogs la mngon par chags pa mu
NK086(lu)003:4232: stegs byed dang / byis pa so so'i skye bo thams cad kyi'o //
NK086(lu)003:4233: de la 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes ni
NK086(lu)003:4234: rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid du ltung ba'i bsam pa
NK086(lu)003:4235: la mngon par chags pa nyan thos dang rang sangs
NK086(lu)003:4237: de la 'jig rten las 'das pa mchog gi ye
NK086(lu)003:4238: shes ni sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK086(lu)003:4239: kyi snang ba med pa'i chos la rab tu rnam
NK086(lu)003:4242: 'gag pa med par mthong ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4243: yod pa dang med pa'i phyogs dang bral pa de
NK086(lu)003:4244: bzhin gshegs pa'i sa bdag med pa thugs su chud
NK086(lu)003:4246: gzhan yang blo gros chen po chags pa med pa'i mtshan nyid ni ye shes so //
NK086(lu)003:4247: yul sna tshogs la chags pa'i mtshan nyid can ni rnam par shes pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:4248: gzhan yang blo gros chen po gsum du 'dus pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4249: bya ba skye ba dang ldan pa'i mtshan nyid ni
NK086(lu)003:4251: mi ldan pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi mtshan nyid ni ye shes so //
NK086(lu)003:4252: gzhan yang blo gros chen po thob pa med pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4253: mtshan nyid ni ye shes te bdag gi so so
NK086(lu)003:4254: rang gi 'phags pa'i ye shes kyis rtogs pa'i spyod
NK086(lu)003:4255: yul du mi 'byung mi 'jug pa'i phyir chu la
NK086(lu)003:4257: de la 'di skad ces bya ste //
NK086(lu)003:4258: sems kyis su ni las la sogs //
NK086(lu)003:4259: ye shes kyi sa ni rnam par 'byed //
NK086(lu)003:4260: shes rab kyis kyang snang med dang //
NK086(lu)003:4261: mthu yang rab tu thob par byed //
NK086(lu)003:4262: sems ni yul dang 'brel ba ste //
NK086(lu)003:4263: zhes pa la sogs pas rgyas par gsungs pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4264: de bzhin du 'phags pa dkon mchog sprin gyi mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:4265: chos 'di ni yi ge thams cad las yang dag
NK086(lu)003:4266: par 'das pa smra ba thams cad las yang dag
NK086(lu)003:4267: par 'das pa / tshig gi spyod yul thams cad las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:4268: ngag gi lam thams cad las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:4269: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba /
NK086(lu)003:4270: blang ba dang dor ba thams cad dang bral ba /
NK086(lu)003:4271: phye ba dang btsun pa thams cad dang bral ba /
NK086(lu)003:4272: rtog ge thams cad dang bral ba /
NK086(lu)003:4273: brtag par bya ba ma yin pa /
NK086(lu)003:4274: rtog ge'i spyod yul ma yin pa /
NK086(lu)003:4275: rtog ge'i spyod yul las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:4278: mtshan ma'i spyod yul las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:4279: byis pa'i spyod yul las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:4280: bdud thams cad kyi spyod yul las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:4281: nyon mongs pa thams cad kyi spyod yul las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:4282: rnam par shes pa'i spyod yul las yang dag par 'das pa /
NK086(lu)003:4286: 'phags pa'i ye shes kyi spyod yul te /
NK086(lu)003:4287: de dag nyid kyi so so rang gis rig pa /
NK086(lu)003:4296: ther zug /mi 'jig pa'i chos can te /
NK086(lu)003:4297: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams byung yang rung /
NK086(lu)003:4298: ma byung yang rung ste chos kyi dbyings 'di ni 'dug pa kho na'o //
NK086(lu)003:4299: zhes pa la sogs pas don dam 'phags pa'i ye
NK086(lu)003:4300: shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshul rgyas par bstan
NK086(lu)003:4301: pa dag ni sems tsam pa 'dod pa'i lam du
NK086(lu)003:4302: mi gnas te / gzung 'dzin gnyis med shes pa
NK086(lu)003:4303: rang rig rang gsal de nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyu
NK086(lu)003:4304: grung por khas blangs shing yul can gzhan dbang bden
NK086(lu)003:4305: par 'dod pas rnam shes rdzas grub don dam par
NK086(lu)003:4306: 'dod pa gang zhig chos kyi bdag med sgra ji
NK086(lu)003:4307: bzhin pa yang rtogs par dkar ba'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:4308: de ltar yang lang gshegs las /
NK086(lu)003:4309: sems tsam yin te snang ba med //
NK086(lu)003:4310: snang ba med pas mi skye ste //
NK086(lu)003:4311: dbu ma yi ni lam 'di dag /nga dang gzhan dag gis kyang bshad //
NK086(lu)003:4312: sems tsam du ni rtogs pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:4313: phyi rol dngos po rnam bsal ba //
NK086(lu)003:4314: rnam par rtog pa rnam ldog pas //
NK086(lu)003:4315: lam de nyid ni dbu ma'o //
NK086(lu)003:4316: zhes gsungs pa bzhin bka' tha ma'i dgongs pa 'di
NK086(lu)003:4317: nyid nges don dbu ma chen por gnas pa ni
NK086(lu)003:4318: byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi 'grel ba
NK086(lu)003:4319: dang theg chen gyi slob dpon shing rta gnyis rjes
NK086(lu)003:4320: 'brangs dang bcas pas rang gzhung rnams su gsal bar
NK086(lu)003:4322: 'on kyang slob dpon 'ga' zhig gis dgos dbang la
NK086(lu)003:4323: brten nas rnam gzhag gzhan dang gzhan du smra ba
NK086(lu)003:4324: dag byung srid na'ang de dag rnams skye 'phags ji
NK086(lu)003:4325: ltar yin tshad gzung bar dka' zhing /
NK086(lu)003:4326: 'phags pa'i sar bzhugs par grub na dgongs gzhi gzhan
NK086(lu)003:4327: dang gzhan gyis de ltar gsungs pa'i skabs srid pa
NK086(lu)003:4328: / rang re byis pa rnams kyis mtha' gcig tu
NK086(lu)003:4329: bzung nas chos spang gi las ngan mi gsog pa
NK086(lu)003:4331: gal te 'dir ngo bo nyid gsum bstan pa'i phyir sems tsam pa'o zhes smras kyang /
NK086(lu)003:4334: yongs su brtags pa'i gzugs gang yin pa de ni rdzas med par blta'o //
NK086(lu)003:4335: rnam par brtags pa'i gzungs gang yin pa de ni
NK086(lu)003:4336: rnam par rtog pa rdzas yod pa'i phyir rdzas yod
NK086(lu)003:4337: par blta yi rang dbang du 'jug pa ni ma
NK086(lu)003:4338: yin no // chos nyid kyi gzugs gang yin de
NK086(lu)003:4339: ni rdzas med pa yang ma yin rdzas med pa
NK086(lu)003:4340: yang ma yin don dam pas rab tu phye ba
NK086(lu)003:4344: shes rab pha rol phyin pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:4345: bstan pa gsum la yang dag brten //
NK086(lu)003:4346: brtags pa dang ni gzhan dbang dang //
NK086(lu)003:4347: yongs su grub pa kho na'o //
NK086(lu)003:4348: med ces bya ba sogs tshig gis //
NK086(lu)003:4349: brtags pa thams cad 'gog pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:4350: sgyu ma la sogs dpe rnams kyis //
NK086(lu)003:4351: gzhan gyi dbang ni yang dag bstan //
NK086(lu)003:4352: rnam par byang ba bzhi yis ni //
NK086(lu)003:4353: yongs su grub par rab tu bsgrags //
NK086(lu)003:4354: shes rab pha rol phyin pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:4355: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gzhan bstan med //
NK086(lu)003:4356: ces pa la sogs pa ngo bo nyid gsum gyi
NK086(lu)003:4357: tshul bka' bar pa nas kyang rgyas par bstan pa
NK086(lu)003:4358: dang / de bzhin du gzhan yang slob dpon klu'i
NK086(lu)003:4359: bshes gnyen gyi sku gsum la 'jug pa'i sgor yang
NK086(lu)003:4360: dang / / ngo bo nyid gsum gyis sku gsum 'thob pa'i rgyur bsdus pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4361: de'i 'grel ba dbu ma pa chen po ye shes
NK086(lu)003:4362: zla bas mdzad par yang de dang don gcig par
NK086(lu)003:4363: bshad pa sogs dbu ma'i gzhung chen po thams cad
NK086(lu)003:4364: du ngo bo nyid gsum gyi rnam gzhag mdzad pa
NK086(lu)003:4365: thams cad kyang dbu ma'i lugs su de med cing
NK086(lu)003:4366: sems tsam gyi lugs kho na'o zhes smra ba rnams
NK086(lu)003:4367: kyis gzhung de dang de ma mthong bar zad la
NK086(lu)003:4369: sems tsam la ni bstan nas su //
NK086(lu)003:4370: phyi rol don ni mi brtag go //
NK086(lu)003:4371: snang ba med pa la brten nas //
NK086(lu)003:4372: sems tsam las ni 'da' bar bya //
NK086(lu)003:4373: yang dag dmigs pa la brten nas //
NK086(lu)003:4374: snang ba med las 'da' bar bya //
NK086(lu)003:4375: rnal 'byor snang ba med gnas na //
NK086(lu)003:4376: theg pa chen po mi mthong ngo //
NK086(lu)003:4377: zhes gnas skabs su sems tsam du bstan nas mthar
NK086(lu)003:4378: de las yang dag par 'das nas snang med du
NK086(lu)003:4379: dbu ma dang / de las kyang 'das nas snang bcas dbu ma ston cing /
NK086(lu)003:4380: de la ma sleb na theg chen gyi don zab mo mi mthong bar gsungs pa yin /
NK086(lu)003:4381: sbyin sems kyi sgras smos pa thams cad sems tsam du smra ba'ang nongs te /
NK086(lu)003:4384: rang bzhin gyis mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4387: kun tu bzang po'i yid la sogs pa mtha' thams
NK086(lu)003:4388: cad dang bral ba'i gnas la sems kyi sgras bstan
NK086(lu)003:4391: rab 'byor sems de ni sems ma mchis te sems kyi rang bzhin ni 'od gsal ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:4392: zhes 'khor ba'i sems dang sems byung las 'das pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4393: 'od gsal ba'i sems nyid gsungs pa rnam shes las
NK086(lu)003:4394: 'das pa'i sems tsam du nor bar mi bya ste
NK086(lu)003:4397: rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags 'brel //
NK086(lu)003:4398: sems las byung ba sna tshogs pa //
NK086(lu)003:4399: mi las phyi rol snang ba ni //
NK086(lu)003:4400: 'jig rten pa yi sems tsam mo //
NK086(lu)003:4402: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sems tsam
NK086(lu)003:4403: gyi khyad par bstan pa sngar bshad pa'i rnam shes
NK086(lu)003:4404: ye shes kyi khyad par dang don gcig cing /
NK086(lu)003:4405: de bzhin du shin tu zab pa'i theg chen rnams
NK086(lu)003:4406: su bstan pa'i ming gzhan gyis bsnyad pa'i sems kyi
NK086(lu)003:4407: don can rnams kyang de bzhin du shes dgos la
NK086(lu)003:4408: / der ma zad zag pa med pa'i dbyings dang /
NK086(lu)003:4409: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbyings dang /
NK086(lu)003:4410: don dam pa'i dge ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4411: chos nyid mi 'gyur zhing brtan pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4412: don dam pa'i gnas lugs su bden pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4413: gdod nas rnam par grol ba'i sku dang /
NK086(lu)003:4414: mtha' bzhi'i spros pa thams cad dang bral ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4415: bdag gnyis spangs pa sogs thub pa chen po'i chos
NK086(lu)003:4416: kyi sku dang dbyer med pa'i yon tan gyi tshogs
NK086(lu)003:4417: gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed las 'das pa rnams
NK086(lu)003:4418: kyang rnam shes kyi chos las shin tu 'das par
NK086(lu)003:4419: lhun grub tu gnas pa'i phyir 'jig rten pa'i sems
NK086(lu)003:4420: tsam smra ba dang rnam pa rab tu 'gal ba
NK086(lu)003:4421: can no // spyir phyogs su ma lhung ba'i blo
NK086(lu)003:4422: gros tshad mar gyur pa dag gis stong lugs gnyis
NK086(lu)003:4423: ka yang shing rta'i srol so so la brten pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4424: grub mtha' bzhir grangs nges pa dag gi rtse mor
NK086(lu)003:4425: gyur ba'i dbu mar gnas pa la khyad par med
NK086(lu)003:4426: can no // de / nges don gyi dgongs pa
NK086(lu)003:4427: 'grel ba la rgyal bas lung bstan pa'i slob dpon
NK086(lu)003:4428: chen po klu thogs rnam gnyis so so'i bstan bcos
NK086(lu)003:4430: de dang mthun par rtsod dus kyi thams cad mkhyen pa rin chen 'byung gnas zhi ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4433: jo bo rje sogs kyis kyang bshad la /
NK086(lu)003:4434: slob dpon seng ge bzang pos kyang zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK086(lu)003:4435: des rgyan gyi dgongs pa 'chad pa na /
NK086(lu)003:4436: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes 'ba' zhig 'di yang
NK086(lu)003:4437: dag par yod pa'i ngo bo yin no snyam du
NK086(lu)003:4438: nges par byas nas zhes pa 'di rnal 'byor gyis
NK086(lu)003:4439: gsum pa'i sgom byung gi rnal 'byor ram bsam byung
NK086(lu)003:4440: gi rim pa gang rung du bzhed pa'i phyir dang
NK086(lu)003:4441: / de bzhin nyid gyi ngos 'dzin ye shes la bshad pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4442: ngo bo nyid sku'i 'grel pa gnas tshul gyi sku
NK086(lu)003:4443: lhag ma gsum po chos nyid du bshad pa'i phyir
NK086(lu)003:4444: ro // de'i phyir 'khor lo bar pa nas dngos
NK086(lu)003:4445: su bstan pa'i stong nyid kyis lus can rnams kyi
NK086(lu)003:4446: blo lhan skyes kyi ngar 'dzin dang /
NK086(lu)003:4447: mu stegs byed rnams kyis grub mtha' gsar du btags pa'i bdag tu lta ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4448: rang sde dngos por smra ba'i grub mtha'i 'dzin zhen
NK086(lu)003:4449: gyi spros pa gcod pa'i don du nges don med
NK086(lu)003:4451: ci yang mi bsgom pa la stong nyid bsgom pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4452: ci yang mi mthong ba la de kho na nyid
NK086(lu)003:4453: rtogs par bstan pas de dang de'i don mthong bas
NK086(lu)003:4454: bdag med tshul bzhin du rtogs par byed pa'i go
NK086(lu)003:4456: mtshan 'dzin gzhig par dka' ba yang thos bsam las
NK086(lu)003:4457: byung ba'i shes rab kyis 'gog par byed pa la
NK086(lu)003:4458: thal rang gi rig pa spros pa gcod byed la
NK086(lu)003:4459: rno ba dang / bsgom pa nyams myong gis gtan
NK086(lu)003:4460: la 'bebs pa'i tshe ni 'khor lo gsum par gsungs
NK086(lu)003:4461: pa'i dbu ma chen po'i lugs 'di nyid mchog tu
NK086(lu)003:4462: zab la rgya che ba yin te /
NK086(lu)003:4463: dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa don dam
NK086(lu)003:4464: pa'i bden pa rang byung gi ye shes 'di nyid
NK086(lu)003:4465: ni chos thams cad kyi thog ma'i gnas lugs yin
NK086(lu)003:4466: pa gang zhig /so so rang gi rig pas nyams
NK086(lu)003:4467: su myong byar yod pa'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir
NK086(lu)003:4468: te / sgra gcan zin gyis yum la bstod par /
NK086(lu)003:4469: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin /
NK086(lu)003:4470: ma skyes mi 'gag nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid /
NK086(lu)003:4471: so so rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba /
NK086(lu)003:4472: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK086(lu)003:4474: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK086(lu)003:4475: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig bdag gis rnyed //
NK086(lu)003:4476: ces gsungs pa sogs kyis bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4477: ye shes mtshon par byas shing 'di nyid kyi rang
NK086(lu)003:4478: bzhin mthong bas don dam bden pa mthong ba zhes
NK086(lu)003:4479: bya yi ci yang med pa'i stong nyid tsam la
NK086(lu)003:4480: don dam bden par mi rung ngo //
NK086(lu)003:4481: de'i phyir chos nyid yongs grub ni gnyis su med
NK086(lu)003:4482: pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes yin pa'i phyir
NK086(lu)003:4483: rnam shes kyi chos las yang dag par 'das pa
NK086(lu)003:4484: sangs rgyas chos kyi sku dang /
NK086(lu)003:4485: ngo bo nyid sku'i sgras bstan pa /
NK086(lu)003:4486: gsang sngags su gsungs pa'i rgyud gsum gyi rnam par gzhag pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4491: rnam par kun gyi mchog dang ldan pa'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK086(lu)003:4492: gnyug ma'i lus ngag yid gsum gyi rten mi shigs
NK086(lu)003:4493: pa'i theg le chen po sogs rgyu 'bras kyi theg
NK086(lu)003:4494: pa chen po bdag gis sbyang gzhi dang sbyong byed
NK086(lu)003:4495: dang sbyangs 'bras sogs kyi rnam par gzhag pa dang
NK086(lu)003:4496: / gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rnam gzhag thun mong ma
NK086(lu)003:4497: yin pa rnams kyang sems tsam par grags pa'i grub
NK086(lu)003:4498: mtha' dang 'gal ba'i chos su gnas shing /
NK086(lu)003:4499: rang stong pa ltar 'dod pa'i lam du'ang mi gnas
NK086(lu)003:4500: par 'khor lo tha ma'i dgongs pa sa bcu'i dbang
NK086(lu)003:4501: phyug chen po rnams kyis bkral ba dang sngags kyi
NK086(lu)003:4502: rgyud sde rnams kyis bstan pa gcig la gcig ltos
NK086(lu)003:4503: kyis mi 'gal bar gnas pa'ang shes par bya dgos
NK086(lu)003:4504: la / de phyir bka' tha ma'i dgongs pa 'jig
NK086(lu)003:4505: rten pa'i sems tsam smra ba dang rnam pa kun
NK086(lu)003:4506: tu gcig pa ma yin par theg pa'i rim pa
NK086(lu)003:4507: 'og ma 'og ma'i dgos pa gong ma gong ma'i
NK086(lu)003:4508: nang du rim gyis 'du zhing mtha' gcig tu grub
NK086(lu)003:4510: 'og ma las gong ma ches khyad par du 'phags
NK086(lu)003:4511: pa bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa rin po che'i
NK086(lu)003:4512: khyad par du nges pa khong du chud dgos te
NK086(lu)003:4513: / de ltar min na 'khor lo dang por sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4516: mi rtog pa zhes bstan nas /
NK086(lu)003:4517: bka' bar par thams cad stong pa nyid du gtan la phab ste /
NK086(lu)003:4522: bdag dam par bstan pa'i don gyi dgongs pa nyid /
NK086(lu)003:4523: rton pa bzhi la gding du gyur pa'i blo gros
NK086(lu)003:4524: kyis blangs ma shes par sgra ji bzhin par bzung
NK086(lu)003:4525: na gdul bya mgo rmongs par 'gyur ba dang bstan
NK086(lu)003:4526: pa 'gal bar dpyod pa'i rnam par rtog pa can
NK086(lu)003:4527: du 'gyur te / 'di la dgongs nas rgyud bla ma'i 'grel par /
NK086(lu)003:4528: mdor bsdu na gang zag bzhi po 'di ni de
NK086(lu)003:4529: bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po mthong ba la mig dang
NK086(lu)003:4531: bzhi gang zhe na 'di lta ste /
NK086(lu)003:4535: theg pa la ga sar du zhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ste /
NK086(lu)003:4537: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po 'di ni /
NK086(lu)003:4538: 'jig tshogs la blta bar lhung ba rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:4539: phyin ci log la mngon par dga' ba rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:4540: stong pa nyid la sems rnam par g.yengs pa rnams kyis spyod yul ma lags so //
NK086(lu)003:4542: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa bzhin dang /
NK086(lu)003:4543: gzhan yang tshul 'di nyid bka' dang bstan bcos thams
NK086(lu)003:4544: cad nas shin tu sgrub tu yod kyang 'dir re
NK086(lu)003:4546: bstan pa de dag drang nges gnyis su rnam pa gzhag na /
NK086(lu)003:4547: chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum po de dag
NK086(lu)003:4548: gis gang du sgrib byed glo bur ba'i dri ma
NK086(lu)003:4549: rags pa dang / phra ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4550: shin tu phra ba'i tshul rnams sbyong byed kyi thabs
NK086(lu)003:4551: rgya che chung las don du gshegs snying gcig pu'i
NK086(lu)003:4552: steng gi dri ma sbyong ba la gsum ka mthun
NK086(lu)003:4553: zhing / 'di ltar dang pos mi rtag pa sogs
NK086(lu)003:4554: kyis 'khor ba las yid 'byung zhing mya ngan las
NK086(lu)003:4556: gnyis pa rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum gyis 'jig
NK086(lu)003:4557: rten pa'i bdag tu lta ba sogs mtshan 'dzin gyi
NK086(lu)003:4559: gsum pa phyir mi ldog pa'i gtam gyis bde bar
NK086(lu)003:4560: gshegs pa'i tshul rgya chen po khong du chud par
NK086(lu)003:4561: byed pa la dgongs pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:4562: gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:4563: rigs kyi bu 'di ltar dper na nor bu mkhan
NK086(lu)003:4564: mkhas pas nor bu sbyong ba'i tshul legs par shes
NK086(lu)003:4565: pa des / nor bu rin po che'i rigs nas
NK086(lu)003:4566: yongs su ma dag pa'i nor bu blangs te lan
NK086(lu)003:4567: tsh+wa'i chu rnyog por spangs nas skra'i re bas yongs
NK086(lu)003:4569: de bzhin du de'i 'og tu zas kyi khu bar
NK086(lu)003:4570: sbyongs te bal gyi lu bas yongs su sbyong bas
NK086(lu)003:4571: yongs su sbyong bar byed do //
NK086(lu)003:4572: de bzhin du de'i 'og tu sman bzang po'i khu
NK086(lu)003:4573: bas spangs te ras srab mos yongs su sbyong bas
NK086(lu)003:4574: yongs su sbyong bar byed do //
NK086(lu)003:4575: yongs su sbyangs te dri ma dang bral ba ni beed+aur+ya rigs chen po zhes brjod do //
NK086(lu)003:4576: de bzhin du sems can la dang po mi rtag
NK086(lu)003:4577: pa dang sdug bsngal ba sogs yid 'byung ba'i gtam
NK086(lu)003:4578: gyis 'dul ba la 'dzud par mdzad pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4579: de'i 'og tu rnam par thar pa gsum gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshul rtogs par mdzad pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4580: de'i 'og tu phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i gtam
NK086(lu)003:4581: gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i yul la 'jug par mdzod
NK086(lu)003:4582: do // zhugs par gyur cing chos nyid rtogs na ni bla na med pa'i yon gnas so //
NK086(lu)003:4583: zhes pa la sogs pas rgyas par gsungs shing /
NK086(lu)003:4584: de bzhin du bka' rim pa gsum po drang don dang nges don du rnam par dbye ba yang /
NK086(lu)003:4585: dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba'i mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:4586: bcom ldan 'das kyis nyan thos kyi theg pa la
NK086(lu)003:4587: zhugs pa rnams la 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi ston
NK086(lu)003:4588: pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo dang po bskor ba de
NK086(lu)003:4592: rtsod pa'i gzhi'i gnas su gyur pa lags la /
NK086(lu)003:4593: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos rnams kyi ngo bo nyid ma mchis pa nyid las brtsams te /
NK086(lu)003:4594: theg pa chen por yang dag par zhugs pa rnams la /
NK086(lu)003:4595: stong pa nyid ston pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo gnyis pa bskor ba de yang bla na mchis pa /
NK086(lu)003:4598: rtsod pa'i gzhir gyur pa lags kyi /
NK086(lu)003:4599: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos rnams ngo bo nyid ma mchis pa nyid las brtsams te /
NK086(lu)003:4600: theg pa thams cad la yang dag par zhugs pa rnams la /
NK086(lu)003:4601: legs par rnam par phye ba dang ldan pa'i shin
NK086(lu)003:4602: tu ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos kyi 'khor
NK086(lu)003:4604: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba de ni bla na ma mchis pa /
NK086(lu)003:4607: rtsod pa'i gzhir ma gyur ba lags so //
NK086(lu)003:4608: zhes pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas drang nges kyi rnam par bzhag par mdzad la /
NK086(lu)003:4609: de ltar 'khor lo bar pa drang don du bzhag pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK086(lu)003:4610: chos 'khor 'dir dgos pa'i dbang gis bde bar gshegs
NK086(lu)003:4611: pa'i stobs sogs don dam gyis yon tan rang stong
NK086(lu)003:4612: ma yin pa rnams kyang phal cher rang stong du
NK086(lu)003:4613: ston pa dang / de dag legs par phye ste
NK086(lu)003:4614: nang 'gal med par ma bstan pa sogs kyis bla
NK086(lu)003:4615: na mchis pa la sogs pa gsungs la /
NK086(lu)003:4616: gsum par ni kun rdzob kyi chos rnams rang stong
NK086(lu)003:4617: dang don dam pa'i chos gzhan gyis stong bas de
NK086(lu)003:4618: dag gi tshul nyid legs par rnam par ji lta
NK086(lu)003:4619: bar phyes nas bstan pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis de ltar
NK086(lu)003:4620: du bzhag go // gal te 'khor lo bar par
NK086(lu)003:4621: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bstan pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4623: de las bzlog nas ston pa'i phyir tha ma drang
NK086(lu)003:4624: don dgongs pa can yin no zhes smra ba ni
NK086(lu)003:4625: legs par ma brtags pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:4626: ma skyes mi 'gag gdod nas zhi ba la sogs
NK086(lu)003:4627: pa sher phyin sgra ji bzhin ba ni 'khor lo
NK086(lu)003:4628: tha ma nyid du mchog tu rgyas shing /
NK086(lu)003:4629: shin tu zab pa'i tshul ni rdo rje theg par bstan la /
NK086(lu)003:4630: de nyid mi gsal ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:4632: rab tu gsal bar ston pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis bla
NK086(lu)003:4633: na yod med kyi khyad par gsungs pa yin gyi
NK086(lu)003:4634: sher phyin gyi ngo bo la khyad par yod pa
NK086(lu)003:4635: ma yin te / gang bde gshegs snying po dang /
NK086(lu)003:4638: rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i rigs dang /
NK086(lu)003:4640: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid
NK086(lu)003:4641: la sogs pa ming gis bstan pa mtha' yas pa
NK086(lu)003:4642: thams cad rang byung gnyis su med pa'i ye shes
NK086(lu)003:4644: de nyid shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:4645: slob dpon phyogs kyi glong pos /
NK086(lu)003:4646: shes rab pha rol phyin gnyis med //
NK086(lu)003:4647: ye shes de ni de bzhin gshegs //
NK086(lu)003:4648: bsgrub bya don de dang ldan pas //
NK086(lu)003:4649: gzhung lam dag la de'i sgra yin //
NK086(lu)003:4651: des na bka' tha ma nges don mtha' thug tu
NK086(lu)003:4652: lung dang rigs pa thams cad kyis 'grub ste rgyal
NK086(lu)003:4653: ba nyid kyis drang nges dbye bar mdzad pa dang
NK086(lu)003:4655: thogs med ces bya'i dge slong ni //
NK086(lu)003:4656: bstan bcos de yi don la mkhas //
NK086(lu)003:4657: mdo sde drang don nges pa'i don //
NK086(lu)003:4658: rnam pa mang po rab tu 'byed //
NK086(lu)003:4659: ces rgyal bas drang nges 'byed pa por lung du
NK086(lu)003:4660: bstan pa'i 'phags pa de nyid kyis tha ma nges
NK086(lu)003:4661: don mthar thug tu bzhag pa yin cing /
NK086(lu)003:4663: tha ma drang don yin pa'i lung gang yang med mod kyi /
NK086(lu)003:4664: 'on te bka' tha ma 'di nyid rnam rig smra
NK086(lu)003:4665: bar 'dod pa dag gis de ltar byas pa yin
NK086(lu)003:4666: srid kyang gong du drangs ba'i nor bu sbyong ba'i
NK086(lu)003:4667: dpe dang nad pa'i sman dang yi ge slob pa'i
NK086(lu)003:4668: dpe sogs kyis bstan pa'i go rim dang 'gal ba
NK086(lu)003:4669: dang / rgyal ba nyid dang 'phags pas rnams par
NK086(lu)003:4670: gzhag pa la'ang dgos pa med par 'gyur ba sogs
NK086(lu)003:4672: der ma zad gdul bya rnams la dang po drang don dang /
NK086(lu)003:4673: bar du nges don bstan nas /
NK086(lu)003:4674: slar yang drang don zlos te bstan pa la dgongs
NK086(lu)003:4675: pa'i len lugs dang dgos pa ci yod kyang bsam
NK086(lu)003:4676: dgos so // des ni nges don mthar thug la dngos por smra ba'i grub mthar bzhag pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:4677: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams la kun rdzob bstan pa'i skur zhus dang /
NK086(lu)003:4678: snying po'i chos 'di spang bar 'gyur ba sogs sdig to mi bzad par shes par bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:4679: gzhan yang theg pa gsum gyi sgo nas nges don
NK086(lu)003:4680: 'khor lo tha mar 'du ba'i dbang du mdzad pas
NK086(lu)003:4681: kyang nges don mthar thug tu grub ste /
NK086(lu)003:4682: phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i mdo las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:4683: de nas bcom ldan 'das de'i bsnyen bkur ba byang
NK086(lu)003:4684: chub sems dpa' chen po sgra dbyangs snyan pa zhes
NK086(lu)003:4685: pa de pad+ma'i stan las langs te gsol ba /
NK086(lu)003:4687: 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed 'di ji srid cig na mchis /
NK086(lu)003:4689: rigs kyi bu 'jig rten gyi khams 'di nas nub
NK086(lu)003:4690: phyogs logs su 'jig rten gyi khams gang+g+aa'i klung gi
NK086(lu)003:4691: bye ma snyed las 'das pa na'o //
