NK086(lu)003:9367: a nu man chad kyi rim pa brgyad po rnams
NK086(lu)003:9368: ni blos btags pas gzhi las gol ba yin la
NK086(lu)003:9369: / 'dir ni rang byung gi ye shes blo dang
NK086(lu)003:9370: bral bas rgyu rkyen la bzla bas chos nyid ye
NK086(lu)003:9371: stong chen po dran bsam phyogs 'dzin byung tshor sogs
NK086(lu)003:9372: las 'das pa'i gshis su ma bsgribs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9373: gsum pa gtan tshigs khungs rdib pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:9374: gzhi sems nyid spros bral chen po la bcos su
NK086(lu)003:9375: med pa'i don rtogs pas ngo bo skye med du
NK086(lu)003:9376: grol / rtsal 'gag med rgya yan chen por phyam
NK086(lu)003:9377: gdal bas na bag chags kyi rten med pas rnam
NK086(lu)003:9378: smin dkar nag gnyis ma grub pas chos nyid ye
NK086(lu)003:9380: mtha' grol chen po'i gtan tshigs kyis 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du grol bar 'dod pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9381: bzhi pa rgya chad phyogs lhung med par 'dod pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:9382: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes kyis 'khor 'das kun la khyab kyang /
NK086(lu)003:9383: snang ba dngos por rgya ma chad /
NK086(lu)003:9384: stong ba dngos med du rgya ma chad /
NK086(lu)003:9385: gnyis ka ma yin pas zung 'jug gi phyogs su'ang ma lhungs /
NK086(lu)003:9386: ngo bo stong pas rtag pa'i mtha' las grol /
NK086(lu)003:9387: rtsal ma 'gags pas chad pa'i mtha' las grol bas
NK086(lu)003:9388: bya bral bde sdug las 'das pa'i chos nyid do
NK086(lu)003:9389: // lnga pa phyogs 'dzin grub mtha'i sa ni /
NK086(lu)003:9390: sems kyi ngo bo gang du'ang mi gnas shing gang
NK086(lu)003:9391: du'ang ma grub par cir yang snang la cir yang
NK086(lu)003:9394: cir yang med la cir yang snang //
NK086(lu)003:9395: ma skyed sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs snang //
NK086(lu)003:9396: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor sna tshogs kyang //
NK086(lu)003:9397: sems kyi cho 'phrul chen po yin //
NK086(lu)003:9398: zhes gsungs pa ltar shar yang mi dgag mi 'dzin mi rtog pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9399: drug pa blo bral phyogs 'dzin las 'das pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:9400: rang byung gi ye shes blo dang bral bas ji
NK086(lu)003:9401: ltar snang yang bden rdzun gang du'ang ma grub pas
NK086(lu)003:9402: yod med mtha' grol chen po'i rol pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9403: bdun pa sems kyi phyogs yin tu smra ba ni /
NK086(lu)003:9404: 'di ltar snang ba thams cad sems kyi rol pa
NK086(lu)003:9405: yin pas sna tshogs su snang yang sems nyid ngo
NK086(lu)003:9406: bo med pas snang ba sna tshogs kyang ngo bo
NK086(lu)003:9408: gang shar sems kyi rnam pa 'dzin byed dang /
NK086(lu)003:9409: snang ba gzung bar byung ba gnyis ka'ang snang ba tha dad du snang yang /
NK086(lu)003:9410: yin gang yang ma yin pa'i chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes su dbyer med pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:9411: rang rtsal lhun grub kyi gdangs las 'khor 'das gnyis
NK086(lu)003:9412: su shar yang shar mkhan la ngo bo med pas
NK086(lu)003:9413: shar sa rang grol du 'gro ba 'di'i khyad par
NK086(lu)003:9414: gyi chos te / kun byed las /
NK086(lu)003:9415: snang srid snod bcud sangs rgyas sems can kun //
NK086(lu)003:9416: sems kyis byas shing sems kyi ngang du gcig /ces so //
NK086(lu)003:9417: de ltar sems kyi sde la rjod byed kyi rgyud
NK086(lu)003:9418: shwa lo ka 'bum phrag nyi shu rtsa gnyis yod
NK086(lu)003:9420: chos nyid brjod du med pa'i klong dang /
NK086(lu)003:9421: lta ba med pa med pa'i klong dang /
NK086(lu)003:9422: spyod pa yin pa med pa'i klong gsum po la
NK086(lu)003:9423: bam po drug stong sum brgyar gnas pa yin la
NK086(lu)003:9425: gnas pa gzhi thog phebs pa'i 'phyong /
NK086(lu)003:9426: snang ba rang sar grol ba'i 'phyong /
NK086(lu)003:9427: ngo mnyam tha dad med pa'i 'phyong gsum du 'du la /
NK086(lu)003:9428: chos nyid la 'chugs pa med pa'i gzer bu lnga bcu /
NK086(lu)003:9429: yul sems la lta ba'i gnas lnga brgya bcu gcig
NK086(lu)003:9430: /snang sems cig car du shan 'byed pa khri phrag
NK086(lu)003:9431: gnyis / lta ba thod rgal du la bzla ba lnga khri /
NK086(lu)003:9432: sgom yod rtog pa gcod pa'i gnas chig stong rnams
NK086(lu)003:9433: mtshan thogs pa'i rgyud sde chen po stong dang gsum
NK086(lu)003:9435: mdo 'gag tu dril na sems sde'i grub mtha' 'dis
NK086(lu)003:9436: chos su ji ltar snang ba la chos nyid kyi
NK086(lu)003:9437: phyag rgyas phar rgyas mi 'debs par chos can ji
NK086(lu)003:9438: ltar snang ba thams cad chos nyid byang chub sems
NK086(lu)003:9439: kyi dbyings su rdzogs pas rtsal lam rol pa tsam
NK086(lu)003:9440: du snang rig ngos bzung dang bral bar skyel ba
NK086(lu)003:9441: ste / dpa' n+aa ro ta pas kyang /
NK086(lu)003:9442: sna tshogs snang ba'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK086(lu)003:9443: chos nyid yin par dbyer med pas //
NK086(lu)003:9444: zung du 'jug pa gang dgongs pa //
NK086(lu)003:9445: gsal ba'i sems de nyid la ni //
NK086(lu)003:9446: chos nyid ma yin bag mi snang //
NK086(lu)003:9447: thams cad snang ba'i ngo bo 'di //
NK086(lu)003:9448: ye shes snying po nyid du mthong //
NK086(lu)003:9449: ngo bo nyid la brjod pa bral //
NK086(lu)003:9451: gnyis pa klong gi sde ni /
NK086(lu)003:9452: rang byung gi ye shes chos nyid kun tu bzang
NK086(lu)003:9453: mo'i klong yangs par chos can ji ltar snang ba
NK086(lu)003:9454: thams cad rang snang bkod pa'i rgyan tsam las /
NK086(lu)003:9455: 'ching grol dang shar bya shar byed du ma grub pas /
NK086(lu)003:9456: sems sde ltar rtsal dang rol par snang bar mi bzhed cing /
NK086(lu)003:9460: dag ma dag gang du'ang mi dpyod par ye grol
NK086(lu)003:9461: phyogs 'byams chen por gtan la phab pa klong sde
NK086(lu)003:9463: de yang slob dpon n+aa ro pa'i de kho na nyid sgrub pa'i thabs las /
NK086(lu)003:9464: rtsol bral rig pa mi rtog pa //
NK086(lu)003:9465: ma bcos rang snang bde ba'i klong //
NK086(lu)003:9466: ye shes lhun grub klong du shar //
NK086(lu)003:9467: rang byung nam mkha' lta bur khyab //
NK086(lu)003:9468: rang snang rol ba byang chub sems //
NK086(lu)003:9469: sgyu ma'i ye shes bde ba'i klong //
NK086(lu)003:9470: rang rig ye shes 'dzin pa yi //
NK086(lu)003:9471: rang byung sgyu mar mngon sum gsal //
NK086(lu)003:9474: dang po klong nag po rgyu med du smra ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK086(lu)003:9475: rang byung gnyug ma'i ye shes de nyid 'gyur med
NK086(lu)003:9476: rgyu dang rkyen las 'das pa'i rang bzhin phyogs char
NK086(lu)003:9477: med pas chos can dang chos nyid gnyis kar mi
NK086(lu)003:9480: mdzad pa klong nag /thugs rje klong nag /sprul pa klong nag gi sde dang gsum mo //
NK086(lu)003:9481: gnyis pa klong khra bo sna tshogs su smra ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK086(lu)003:9482: rang byung gi ye shes de nyid kyi rol par snang ba rnams /
NK086(lu)003:9483: yin sna tshogs rang shar du snang ba chos nyid kyi rgyan dang rol pa la /
NK086(lu)003:9484: min phyogs mid kun khyab tu shar ba rol pa dgag sgrub las 'das par 'dod pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9486: yod smra sems sde dang mthun pa'i klong khra bo dang /
NK086(lu)003:9487: med smra rang gnas dang mthun pa'i klong khra bo dang /
NK086(lu)003:9488: yod med man ngag dang mthun pa'i klong khra bo gsum mo //
NK086(lu)003:9489: gsum pa klong dkar po sems su smra ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK086(lu)003:9490: rang byung rig pa'i ngang las phyi snang ba dang
NK086(lu)003:9491: nang rig pa shar ba thams cad sems kyi rol
NK086(lu)003:9492: pa ste / snang ba dang rkyen rang sar grol
NK086(lu)003:9493: bas byar med rgyu nas dag ste gnas lugs la
NK086(lu)003:9496: brjod med rang shar chen po'i klong dkar po dang /
NK086(lu)003:9497: lta sgom gnyis su med pa'i klong dkar po gnyis so //
NK086(lu)003:9498: bzhi pa klong rab 'byams rgyu 'bras la bzla ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK086(lu)003:9499: rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngang las shar ba'i chos thams cad snang bar sems kyis shes la /
NK086(lu)003:9500: mi snang bar gnas lugs kyis shes par 'dod do //
NK086(lu)003:9502: bya ba dang bral ba phyi'i rab 'byams /
NK086(lu)003:9503: grub mtha' rang gzhung du smra ba nang gi rab 'byams /
NK086(lu)003:9504: gegs bsal ba gsang ba'i rab 'byams /
NK086(lu)003:9505: gnad bkrol ba de kho na nyid kyi rab 'byams dang bzhi'o //
NK086(lu)003:9510: bya bral gyi klong bzhi las /
NK086(lu)003:9512: sems nyid kyi rol pa 'gag med du shar ba'i ngang nas 'pho 'gyur med pas yin la /
NK086(lu)003:9513: dngos med kyi rol pa mtha' 'dzin du ma grub pas min /
NK086(lu)003:9514: phyogs yan nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i dgongs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9519: bcos bslad med pa bzhi rim pa bzhin ye nas
NK086(lu)003:9520: rgyan du shar ba skye med kyi ngang las 'gag
NK086(lu)003:9523: rang 'gro sa rang gsal chen po'i dgongs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9525: thams cad gang nas kyang ma 'ongs /
NK086(lu)003:9527: mi 'gag /chos nyid kyi ngang las de'i rol rtsal
NK086(lu)003:9528: thams cad snang yang 'byung bzhi nam mkha'i dbyings las
NK086(lu)003:9529: ma g.yos pa ltar chos nyid kyi ngang du phyam
NK086(lu)003:9531: gang la'ang 'bad rtsol gyis blang dor mi dgos te /
NK086(lu)003:9534: ma sbyangs ye dag /ma bsgrubs ye grub tu gnas
NK086(lu)003:9535: pas nam mkha' ltar 'dus ma byas kyi khams su
NK086(lu)003:9536: gnas pa'o // de ltar klong gi sde de rnams bsdu na dgur 'dus te /
NK086(lu)003:9538: bsgom pa yin min med pa'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:9539: 'bras bu re dogs med pa'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:9540: ngo bo grub bsal med pa'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:9542: mtshan nyid la snang sems grol ba'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:9544: rol pa 'gag med rang shar gyi klong /
NK086(lu)003:9545: lhun mnyam ye grol cog bzhag gi klong dang dagu'o //
NK086(lu)003:9547: lhun grub yangs pa chen po'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:9548: rang gsal bya rtsol med pa'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:9549: ma byas ye nas grub pa'i klong dang gsum du 'dus so //
NK086(lu)003:9550: de dag gi tshul rgyas par ston pa'i rgyud stong phrag gsum gyi mtshan gyis bsdus pa la /
NK086(lu)003:9552: shwa lo ka 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi yod
NK086(lu)003:9553: pa rnams kyang la bzla ba khri phrag brgyad du
NK086(lu)003:9554: 'dus la / de'ang shan 'byed khri phrag gnyis su 'du /
NK086(lu)003:9556: gnad nyis stong gzer bu lnga bcu dang bcas pa thams cad kyang bsdu na /
NK086(lu)003:9560: mnga' bdag me tri pas bsdebs pa'i do ha las /
NK086(lu)003:9561: mi rtog rtog med rtog dpyod yul las 'das //
NK086(lu)003:9562: mi sems sems med bsam du ci yang med //
NK086(lu)003:9563: rten dang rten med 'gro 'ong gnas dang bral //
NK086(lu)003:9564: 'khor 'das bde sdug bde chen klong du sad //
NK086(lu)003:9565: ma bcos yengs med rang bzhin lhug pa la //
NK086(lu)003:9566: sems byung rgyun chad 'od gsal 'gro 'ong bral //
NK086(lu)003:9567: snang ba smrar med slob dpon su yang med //
NK086(lu)003:9568: chos nyid rang gsal rig pa chos skur 'phrod //
NK086(lu)003:9569: ces gsungs pas kyang 'di'i grub mtha' lhongs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9570: gsum pa man ngag gi sde ni /
NK086(lu)003:9571: 'og ma gnyis las khyad par du gyur pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:9572: 'di ltar sems sdes sems yin pas gsal ba las zab mo'i phyogs shas che bar bsgrub kyang /
NK086(lu)003:9573: gsal ba'i rtsal chos nyid du ma rtogs pas yid dpyod du 'dzin par nye zhing /
NK086(lu)003:9574: klong sdes zab gsal mnyam par ba sgrubs kyang chos
NK086(lu)003:9575: nyid la 'dzin pa'i yid dpyod las stong phyogs kyi
NK086(lu)003:9577: man ngag sde ni ngo bo ka nas dag pa
NK086(lu)003:9578: brjod bral blo 'das chen po'i gdangs rang snang lhun
NK086(lu)003:9579: grub kyi rang rtsal las chos can gyi snang ba
NK086(lu)003:9580: thams cad chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i dbyings
NK086(lu)003:9581: su sdud pa'i don gyis khyad par du 'phags par
NK086(lu)003:9582: ste / a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK086(lu)003:9584: de ltar gtan la ma phab na //
NK086(lu)003:9585: yid dpyod 'dzin pa rnams dang ni //
NK086(lu)003:9586: khyad par ci yang med par 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:9587: de phyir nges gsang snying po 'di //
NK086(lu)003:9588: mun pa las ni mar me'am //
NK086(lu)003:9589: ba lang rnams las glang chen nam //
NK086(lu)003:9590: gcan gzan rnam las seng ge'am //
NK086(lu)003:9591: rkang thang rnams las rta pa bzhin //
NK086(lu)003:9592: kun gyi nang nas khyad par 'phags //
NK086(lu)003:9594: 'di'i ngo bo ni gdod ma nyid nas grol zhing
NK086(lu)003:9595: ka nas dag pa'i chos nyid la nyi tshe ba'i
NK086(lu)003:9597: lta byed kyi shes pa gnyis su chad pas 'khrul ma 'khrul dang /
NK086(lu)003:9598: rtogs ma rtogs su bsgrubs pa'i ltos gzhi dang /
NK086(lu)003:9599: ltos pa'i chos las log pas /
NK086(lu)003:9600: rang gi ngo bo spros bral gyi cha nas shes
NK086(lu)003:9601: bya shed byed kyi yul yul can gnyis ka yang
NK086(lu)003:9602: dag pa ma yin par mnyam zhing /
NK086(lu)003:9603: tha snyad tsam du btags pa las de 'dzin gyi bsam brjod las yang dag par 'das pas na /
NK086(lu)003:9607: yid dpyod las 'das pa'i don gnas thog tu phebs pa'i me btsa' lta bu ste /
NK086(lu)003:9609: rang bzhin gyis ni 'od gsal ba //
NK086(lu)003:9610: gdod nas dag pa nam mkha' bzhin //
NK086(lu)003:9611: ye nas chos rnams mtshan nyid spangs //
NK086(lu)003:9612: chos dang chos nyid yang med de //
NK086(lu)003:9613: dngos po med pa'i mkha' dang mtshungs //
NK086(lu)003:9614: tshig dang yi ge kun las grol //
NK086(lu)003:9616: 'di las gzhan du lta bar 'dogs pa'i yul du
NK086(lu)003:9617: dmigs pa de srid du yul can sems kyi 'dzin
NK086(lu)003:9618: stangs spang par mi nus shing /
NK086(lu)003:9619: de ma sbangs pas mi zad pa dang skye ba'i
NK086(lu)003:9620: bdag nyid can du 'gyur bas srid pa'i rtsa ba
NK086(lu)003:9623: rgyal ba rnams kyi stong nyid ni //
NK086(lu)003:9624: lta kun nges par 'byin par gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:9629: rgyud rang gzhung du bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK086(lu)003:9630: dang po kha 'thor gyi ngo bo ni /
NK086(lu)003:9631: blo las 'das pa'i ye shes dbye bsal gzhan ltos med par skad cig nyid la 'char ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:9633: bzhag pa lam gyi mtha' gcod pa'i man ngag dang /
NK086(lu)003:9634: grol ba stobs dag pa lam mngon gyur gyi man ngag gnyis so //
NK086(lu)003:9635: gnyis pa kha gtam gyi tshul du gsungs pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:9636: ngo bo blo bral ma 'khrul pa /
NK086(lu)003:9637: rang bzhin rnam rtog gi khungs rdib pa /
NK086(lu)003:9638: mtshan nyid ngos bzung dang bral ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:9640: gleng ba yongs la bor ba'i kha gtam dang /
NK086(lu)003:9641: khar phog dus med pa'i kha gtam gnyis so //
NK086(lu)003:9642: gsum pa rgyud dang gzhung du bstan pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:9643: ngo bo bka' thams cad kyi byung sar gyur /
NK086(lu)003:9644: rang bzhin 'khor 'das dang bral bas spang blang bya rtsal med /
NK086(lu)003:9645: chos nyid sgra dang tshig tu mi gnas pas stong nyid la rtsod pas mi reg ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:9647: lta ba sgang dril ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:9648: gtar ga gegs sel ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:9649: gab pa mngon du phyung ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:9650: bshad pa rang gsal gyi tshul dang bzhi'o //
NK086(lu)003:9651: 'di dag la'ang lta sgom spyod gsum gyi gnas gab pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:9654: yul shes gnad la bor nas rig pa ther la 'byin pa'i gnad /
NK086(lu)003:9656: theg le gnad la dbab pa sogs zab la rgya
NK086(lu)003:9657: che ba'i nang gses kyi dbye ba mang du yod
NK086(lu)003:9662: thams cad rdzogs pa dang 'dra ba yang gsang bla na med pa'i skor te bzhi'o //
NK086(lu)003:9664: ngo bo la nyon mongs ma grub pas dug lnga lam du khyer /
NK086(lu)003:9665: rang bzhin la rtsol sgrub med pas cir snang chos nyid du shar /
NK086(lu)003:9666: mtshan nyid la phyogs cha med pas stong nyid gang du'ang phye ba med pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9668: ngo bo gzugs can las 'das pas mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid /
NK086(lu)003:9669: rang bzhin 'gro 'ong med pas rtag pa rgyun gnas kyi ye shes so //
NK086(lu)003:9671: 'khor 'das gnyis ka la zug pas rtsa ba /
NK086(lu)003:9672: rang ngo tha dad du 'dril bas sdong po /
NK086(lu)003:9673: rtsal snang cir yang rgyas pas yal ga /gsal cha
NK086(lu)003:9674: mi 'gag pas me tog /sna tshogs gcig tu smin
NK086(lu)003:9677: ngo bo ngo sprod pa dang rtogs pa dus mnyam pas shes rab gsum la ma ltos /
NK086(lu)003:9678: rang bzhin dbugs chad pa dang grol ba dus mnyam pas goms stobs la ma ltos /
NK086(lu)003:9679: mtshan nyid sangs rgyas pa dang thugs rje 'byung ba
NK086(lu)003:9680: dus mnyam pas rgyu tshogs gnyis la mi ltos pa'o
NK086(lu)003:9681: // bzhi pa yang gsang bla na med pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:9682: ngo bo shes bya ma yin pas shes byed la mi ltos /
NK086(lu)003:9683: rang bzhin mngon sum mthong bas chos nyid yid dpyad du mi gnas /
NK086(lu)003:9684: mtshan nyid snang ba bzhis 'bras bu phyi dus la
NK086(lu)003:9685: re ba mi 'cha' bar tshe 'di nyid kyis gdod
NK086(lu)003:9686: ma'i gzhi dbyings su sbyor ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:9687: de lta bu'i tshul la rjod byed tshig gi rgyud khri phrag gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:9688: le'u stong phrag sum cu rtsa lnga /
NK086(lu)003:9689: sh+aa lo ka 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK086(lu)003:9692: gzer bu brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK086(lu)003:9695: la bzla ba 'bum phrag phyed dang gnyis sogs brjod
NK086(lu)003:9696: bya dang rjod byed nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam par
NK086(lu)003:9697: bka' stsal / man ngag gi sde de bzhi ka'ang klong gsum du 'du ste /
NK086(lu)003:9698: rol pa 'gag pa med pa'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:9699: blo la ma grol ba med pa'i klong /
NK086(lu)003:9700: ngo bo la bzang ngan med pa'i klong gsum mo //
NK086(lu)003:9705: mngon sum rang gnad la dbab pa dang bzhi'o //
NK086(lu)003:9706: de ltar bstan pa thams cad kyi snying po rdzogs
NK086(lu)003:9707: pa chen po man ngag sde pa'i lugs 'dis so
NK086(lu)003:9708: so rang gi rig pa ni ye shes kyi nyams
NK086(lu)003:9709: su myong bya'i yul yin la /
NK086(lu)003:9710: zag pa dang bcas pa'i nye bar len pa'i rnam
NK086(lu)003:9711: shes tshogs brgyad po'i rang bzhin can gyi sems las
NK086(lu)003:9714: sems dang ye shes bag chags dngos ma yin //
NK086(lu)003:9715: ye shes bag chags kun dang bral gyur kyang //
NK086(lu)003:9716: sems kyis sna tshogs bag chags sdud par byed //
NK086(lu)003:9717: sems dang ye shes gnyis su ma phye na //
NK086(lu)003:9718: snang ba yul gyi rtsa ba mi chod pas //
NK086(lu)003:9719: rkyen bral chos nyid dag kyang rtogs par dka' //zhes dang /
NK086(lu)003:9720: n+aa ro ba'i de kho nyid sgrub pa'i thabs las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:9721: byang chub sems kyi rang rig 'di //
NK086(lu)003:9722: bag chags 'khrul pa'i dbang gis na //
NK086(lu)003:9723: brtags pas sna tshogs med bzhin 'grub //
NK086(lu)003:9724: sems kyi bag chags phyir snang yang //
NK086(lu)003:9727: rnam rtog sems kyi rgyu ba bral //
NK086(lu)003:9730: mdor na snang grags bsam yul du gnas so cog
NK086(lu)003:9731: thams cad ni sems kyi snang ba 'khor ba'i chos
NK086(lu)003:9732: thams cad kyi rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i sems
NK086(lu)003:9733: te / 'phags pa stong phrag brgya pa las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:9734: sems la sems ma mchis te sems kyi rang bzhin ni 'od gsal ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:9735: zhes 'jig rten pa'i sems sems byung las 'das pa'i
NK086(lu)003:9736: sems nyid kyi don du gsungs pa'ang snga ma dang
NK086(lu)003:9737: don gcig go // gzhan yang 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK086(lu)003:9738: sems dang yid dang rnam par shes pa dang yang bral ba /
NK086(lu)003:9739: ting nge 'dzin gyi gnas kyang mi 'dor ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:9740: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa yin no //
NK086(lu)003:9743: sems med pas na chos kyang med //
NK086(lu)003:9744: de ltar lus dang khams kyang med //
NK086(lu)003:9745: de ltar gnyis med lam gyis ni //
NK086(lu)003:9746: de nyid du ni rab tu bshad //
NK086(lu)003:9747: ces sogs rgya cher gsungs pa rnams kyang sems las 'das pa'i rig pa la dgongs pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:9748: de lta bu'i rig pa de nyid kyang thog ma
NK086(lu)003:9749: med pa nas rang ngo la 'khor ba'i chos gang
NK086(lu)003:9750: gis kyang ma gos pas srid pa'i nyer len gyi
NK086(lu)003:9752: gnyen po gang gis kyang ma bcos par gang shar
NK086(lu)003:9753: thams cad sprul mdud rang zhig pa bzhin 'grol byed
NK086(lu)003:9754: gzhan la ma ltos pas rang grol /
NK086(lu)003:9755: tshogs brgyad kyi shes pa thams cad kyang yul yul
NK086(lu)003:9756: can gnyis su med pa skad cig nyid la thog
NK086(lu)003:9757: babs chen por rang bzhin gyis grol bas cer grol
NK086(lu)003:9758: / dus gsum dang shes bya gang du'ang mi gnas pas mtha' grol te /
NK086(lu)003:9759: de ltar grol lugs chen po bzhi'i ngang du gnas
NK086(lu)003:9760: pa rang gi rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK086(lu)003:9761: de nyid lam 'di nyid kyi khyad chos su nges
NK086(lu)003:9762: par byas nas / de tshul bzhin rtogs par bya ba la /
NK086(lu)003:9763: stong ngos ka dag gis rig pa spros bral du
NK086(lu)003:9764: gyur pas stong pa'i chos zad par byed pa khregs
NK086(lu)003:9765: chod dang / snang ngos lhun grub kyis gdos bcas
NK086(lu)003:9766: 'od gsal du dwangs pas snang ba'i chos nyid zad
NK086(lu)003:9767: par byed pa thod rgal gyi lam gnyis su yod
NK086(lu)003:9768: chod dang / pa las / dang po ka dag
NK086(lu)003:9769: gi gnas lugs gtan la phab pa khregs chod ni
NK086(lu)003:9770: chod dang / pa las / / theg pa'i mchog
NK086(lu)003:9771: 'di'i dgongs pa rig pa 'ching grol med pa'i gshis
NK086(lu)003:9772: lugs ka nas dag pa'i ngo bo de nyid ma
NK086(lu)003:9773: bcos pa rgya gang du'ang ma chad /
NK086(lu)003:9774: rang gi rang bzhin la ngo bo 'di zhes gdags su med pas phyogs gang du'ang ma lhungs shing /
NK086(lu)003:9775: rtog pa'i blo dang bral bas bsam brjod las 'das
NK086(lu)003:9776: pa'i zang thal rjen pa'i rig pa de nyid stong
NK086(lu)003:9777: pa nyid dang / lam dus tshig dang yi ges mi mtshon pas mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:9778: 'bras bu'i ngos nas thob byar re dogs med pas smon pa med pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:9779: rig pa'i cha las byang chub kyi yon tan rnams
NK086(lu)003:9780: rdzogs shing 'od gsal ba'i rang bzhin gyi rnam par
NK086(lu)003:9781: thar pa gsum gyi bdag nyid can gyi rig pa
NK086(lu)003:9782: gang la lta sgom spyod 'bras rtogs bcas rtog med
NK086(lu)003:9783: kyi shes pas bsdus pa'i chos rnams mi 'grub cing
NK086(lu)003:9788: de med pas sa la sbyang ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:9791: de dang de'i rim pa'ang byar med pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:9793: kye ma rgyu dang 'bras bu gnyis la ma lta
NK086(lu)003:9794: zhig /dngos por skye ba'i rgyu dang 'bras bu yod
NK086(lu)003:9795: min te // re dang dogs pa'i sems kyis rnal 'byor sems myos na //
NK086(lu)003:9796: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes gnas der 'ching bar 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:9797: kye ma rang bzhin bral bas de nyid bsgom du yod ma zer //
NK086(lu)003:9798: gal te bsgom par bya dang sgom byed gnyis rtogs nas //
NK086(lu)003:9799: gnyis su 'dzin pa'i yid kyis byang chub tu sems na //
NK086(lu)003:9800: skyes bu de yi rang gis rang la sdig pa byas //
NK086(lu)003:9802: gnas tshul de lta bu blor ma chud pa kha
NK086(lu)003:9803: cig gis rgyu bskyed rim sogs tshogs gnyis ma bsags
NK086(lu)003:9804: na 'bras bu gzugs sku mi 'grub par 'dod pa
NK086(lu)003:9805: sogs rdzogs rim zab mo rnams la skur pa gdab
NK086(lu)003:9806: pa chos spang gi las te /
NK086(lu)003:9807: lam 'dis sangs rgyas rnams kyi mthar thug pa chos kyi sku yin na de ni thob la /
NK086(lu)003:9809: gang dag nga la gzugs su mthong //
NK086(lu)003:9810: gang dag nga la sgrar shes pa //
NK086(lu)003:9811: log pa'i lam du zhugs pa yi //
NK086(lu)003:9812: skye bo de dag nga mi mthong //
NK086(lu)003:9813: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos kyi sku //
NK086(lu)003:9815: de'i phyir rdo rje snying po ka dag gi rig
NK086(lu)003:9816: pa ni gdod ma'i chos kyi sku'i yin lugs ji
NK086(lu)003:9817: lta ba la goms su 'jug pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:9818: spros pa'i sgrib byed las grol ba nyi ma ngang bzhin gyis gsal ba lta bu yin la /
NK086(lu)003:9819: rim pa brgyad po'i nyer len sems kyi kun tu
NK086(lu)003:9820: rtog pa 'ba' zhig gis bskyed pa'i mtshan bcas kyi
NK086(lu)003:9821: rim pa la brten pa sgrib byed kyis sgrib pa
NK086(lu)003:9822: sbyangs nas gzod nyi ma mthong bar 'dod pa lta
NK086(lu)003:9824: rang byung gi ye shes la rtog pa'i lta sgom
NK086(lu)003:9825: spyod 'bras kyis ma bcos par rang gzhag nyid du
NK086(lu)003:9827: rig pa de nyid rgya yan /
NK086(lu)003:9836: lhod de bar rang bab tu bzhag pa tsam la
NK086(lu)003:9837: lta ba dang sgom pa'i bla dwags btags pa tsam
NK086(lu)003:9839: rig pa spros dang bral ba la //
NK086(lu)003:9840: 'khrul dang ma rig ga la yod //
NK086(lu)003:9841: ye shes sems dang bral ba la //
NK086(lu)003:9842: ma rig bag chags ga la yod //
NK086(lu)003:9844: de ltar mnyam par bzhag pa nyid kyis rig pa
NK086(lu)003:9845: ka dag chen po'i gshis ma bcos pa'i gnas lugs
NK086(lu)003:9846: bcar phog tu ngo 'phrod pa la gzung 'dzin gyis
NK086(lu)003:9848: de la bsgom bya sgom byed kyi bslad mi gzhug
NK086(lu)003:9849: pa'i tshul rdo rje'i gad mo chen po bcu gnyis
NK086(lu)003:9850: sogs kyis legs par ston la /
NK086(lu)003:9851: lam 'di nyid la goms pa brtan par gyur pa
NK086(lu)003:9852: na mthar gyis grol sa'i ka dag chen por sdud
NK086(lu)003:9853: pa ni 'byung bzhi rags pa'i rdul phran ye shes
NK086(lu)003:9854: kyi me stobs su gyur pas sbyongs te cho 'phrul
NK086(lu)003:9855: chen po dang bcas te thim par 'gyur zhing /
NK086(lu)003:9856: gzhan don du 'gyur na rdul phran dengs pa de
NK086(lu)003:9857: ring bsrel rnam bzhir sprul nas 'jog pa'ang yod la
NK086(lu)003:9858: / rig pa ni chos sku'i dbyings su 'khyil nas
NK086(lu)003:9859: sprul pa'i sku rgyun chad med pas 'gro don mdzad
NK086(lu)003:9860: / pa'o // gnyis pa lhun grub kyi snang ba
NK086(lu)003:9861: gtan la phab pa thod rgal gyi man ngag ni
NK086(lu)003:9862: / pa'o // / de yang khregs chod kyis gzung
NK086(lu)003:9863: yul 'khrul pa'i snang ba gzhi med rtsa bral gshis
NK086(lu)003:9864: thog tu grol ba yin la /
NK086(lu)003:9865: 'dir ni khams gsum gyi snang cha de dag thams
NK086(lu)003:9866: cad rig pa'i rang gdangs 'od lnga'i thig le chen
NK086(lu)003:9867: po'i 'od gsal du grol ba'i phyir 'og ma las
NK086(lu)003:9870: 'di ni ngang yul bstan pa las //
NK086(lu)003:9872: zang ma nyid dang thal byung du //
NK086(lu)003:9873: yul dang shes pa'i snang cha las //
NK086(lu)003:9874: thad ka so so'i gzhi las grol //
NK086(lu)003:9877: dngos po rang bzhin thams cad ni //
NK086(lu)003:9878: chos kyi dbyings kyi thig le yin //
NK086(lu)003:9879: de nyid sgrub pa'i thabs su ni //
NK086(lu)003:9880: snying po rig pa nyid shar bas //
NK086(lu)003:9881: mtha' yi mun pa ngang gis dag /sgrub med rang byung sgrub pa 'dis //
NK086(lu)003:9882: khams gsum 'od gsal thugs su sgrub //
NK086(lu)003:9883: ces bshad pa 'dis dbyings kyi snang ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:9884: snying po rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud smin
NK086(lu)003:9885: pa'i mtha' chos nyid zad pa'i snang bas khams gsum
NK086(lu)003:9886: phyi nang gi 'byung ba rnams 'od gsal du dengs
NK086(lu)003:9887: pa'i lam mdor bstan pa yin cing /
NK086(lu)003:9888: 'di la'ang bca' ba lus kyi gnad gsum /
NK086(lu)003:9890: snang ba yul gyi gnad gsum du bsdus te nyams su blang bar bya ba las /
NK086(lu)003:9891: phyi ma 'di la sgron ma bzhir dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:9893: rig pa dbyings kyi sgron ma /
NK086(lu)003:9894: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma /
NK086(lu)003:9895: shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma bzhi las /
NK086(lu)003:9896: dang po ni 'char byed kyi sgo ste rig cha'i
NK086(lu)003:9897: gdangs phyi rol gyi lam la mthong ba'i phyir dang
NK086(lu)003:9898: / gnyis pa ni nang dbyings phyi ru gsal ba'i gdangs 'char gzhi /
NK086(lu)003:9899: gsum pa ni 'char ba'i rnam pa rtsol byed kyi rten dang /
NK086(lu)003:9900: bzhi pa ni dwangs la yul med du 'char ba'i
NK086(lu)003:9901: rig ngo lhag mthong gi gnas lugs ma nor ba
NK086(lu)003:9902: ste / de dag gi dbye ba'ang /
NK086(lu)003:9904: nam mkha' stong pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK086(lu)003:9905: bcos med sgron ma rnam pa bzhi //
NK086(lu)003:9906: ma 'gags pa yi don gyis gsal //
NK086(lu)003:9907: rig pa dbyings kyi sgron ma ni //
NK086(lu)003:9908: nam mkha' stong pa'i klong dkyil du //
NK086(lu)003:9909: dbyings kyi rang bzhin 'od kyi sku //
NK086(lu)003:9911: ye shes lnga ldan thugs kyi sku //
NK086(lu)003:9912: lu gu rgyud kyi tshul du 'char //
NK086(lu)003:9915: rig pa dbyings kyi sgron ma ru //
NK086(lu)003:9916: bcug ste rig pa ma 'gul na //
NK086(lu)003:9917: 'gyur med rtogs pa'i rab tu bshad //
NK086(lu)003:9918: shes rab rang byung sgron ma ni //
NK086(lu)003:9919: sgro 'dogs thams cad gcod pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:9920: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma ni //
NK086(lu)003:9921: rtsol ba med par shar gyur na //
NK086(lu)003:9922: rgyangs zhag chu yi sgron ma yis //
NK086(lu)003:9923: de la blta ba ma yengs na //
NK086(lu)003:9924: mthar phyin bsgom pa'i tshad du gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:9926: lhag mthong gi rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK086(lu)003:9927: la bltas pas goms pa'i rim pas snang ba bzhir
NK086(lu)003:9928: 'byongs shing / chos nyid mngon sum gyis zhing khams kyi sgo phye /
NK086(lu)003:9929: de las thig le sku ru smin du nye ba nyams gong 'phel sprul sku /
NK086(lu)003:9930: sku ru smin pa rig pa tshad phebs longs sku /
NK086(lu)003:9931: de nas snang ba thams cad thig le chen po
NK086(lu)003:9932: gcig gi dkyil 'khor du dag nas blos btags pa'i
NK086(lu)003:9933: chos so cog thams cad zad cing chos nyid du
NK086(lu)003:9934: 'dzin pa tsam yang zad pas chos sku'i snang ba
NK086(lu)003:9936: chos nyid mngon sum mthong ba yis //
NK086(lu)003:9938: nyams snang gong du 'phel ba yis //
NK086(lu)003:9939: 'khrul pa'i snang ba nub pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:9940: bar do'i ye shes mngon du byed //
NK086(lu)003:9941: rig pa tshad phebs snang ba yis //
NK086(lu)003:9942: sku gsum rtogs pa'i lam snang 'das //
NK086(lu)003:9943: chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba yis //
NK086(lu)003:9944: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgyun thag chad //
NK086(lu)003:9946: thig le skur smin pa'i tshul 'di dang phyogs mtshungs
NK086(lu)003:9947: tsam dus kyi 'khor lor yang gsungs pa yod de
NK086(lu)003:9948: / nam mkhar kun nas zhen pa'i sems dang mig
NK086(lu)003:9949: ni mi 'dzum rdo rje'i lam du rab tu zhugs
NK086(lu)003:9950: / pa yis // stong pa las ni du ba
NK086(lu)003:9951: smig rgyu rab gsal dri ma med pa'i mkha' snang
NK086(lu)003:9953: 'bar ba dang ni zla ba nyi ma rdo rje
NK086(lu)003:9954: rnams dang mchog gi cha dang thig le mthong bar
NK086(lu)003:9955: 'gyur // de yi dbus su sangs rgyas gzugs ni
NK086(lu)003:9956: yul dang rnam par bral ba du ma longs spyod
NK086(lu)003:9957: 'gyur // rdzogs pa'i sku // zhes gsungs so //
NK086(lu)003:9958: 'di ltar gsang ba bla na med pa 'dir thog
NK086(lu)003:9959: ma nas 'khor ba'i sems las 'das pa'i rang byung
NK086(lu)003:9960: gi rig pa nyid bcar phog tu lam du byed
NK086(lu)003:9961: pa la mkhas pas myur du 'bras bu rang thog
NK086(lu)003:9962: tu phebs pa'i gnad kyang de yin cing /
NK086(lu)003:9963: de ltar ma yin na nyams su len dus 'khor
NK086(lu)003:9964: ba'i sems dang sems byung las ma 'das pas 'bras
NK086(lu)003:9965: bu 'khor ba nyid de rgyu 'bras mi bslu bar
NK086(lu)003:9966: gcig pa'i phyir 'gal bar 'du ba'i skabs med la
NK086(lu)003:9967: / khyad par mngon sum 'od gsal la blta ba'i
NK086(lu)003:9968: rig pa skad cig ma de nyid ni khams gsum
NK086(lu)003:9969: pa'i sems sems byung kun gzhi dang bcas pa ldog
NK086(lu)003:9970: / pa ste / mngon sum la bltas pas nang
NK086(lu)003:9971: kun rtog gi 'phro 'du med pas 'dod pa'i khams
NK086(lu)003:9972: las log /gsal ba'i ngang la gsal bar 'jog byed
NK086(lu)003:9973: kyi gnyen po med pas gzugs kyi khams las log
NK086(lu)003:9974: /rtog med rtse gcig la chos nyid kyi ngang du
NK086(lu)003:9975: zhen pa'i blo med pas gzugs med kyi khams las
NK086(lu)003:9976: log /dwangs la rig pa'i phyir kun gzhi las log
NK086(lu)003:9977: /rang byung gi ye shes su thag chod pas kun
NK086(lu)003:9978: gzhi'i rnam shes las log /snang ba 'od gsal gyi
NK086(lu)003:9979: yul las tha mal gyi rjes su snang ba med
NK086(lu)003:9980: pas sgo lnga'i rnam shes las log /de'i tshe dpyod
NK086(lu)003:9981: byed kyi rtog pa dang chags sdang gi kun rtog
NK086(lu)003:9982: med pas yid shes dang nyon shes las log ste
NK086(lu)003:9983: / pa ste / / mdor na khams gsum gyi
NK086(lu)003:9984: sems dang sems byung thams cad las rnam par grol
NK086(lu)003:9985: ba sangs rgyas kyi ye shes zhi ba nyid las
NK086(lu)003:9986: gzhan ma yin pa'i mthar thug pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:9987: dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs las /
NK086(lu)003:9989: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi gsang ba 'di sems dang /
NK086(lu)003:9990: yid dang rnam par shes pa dang yang bral la /
NK086(lu)003:9991: ting nge 'dzin gyis gnad kyang mi 'dor la /
NK086(lu)003:9992: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:9994: gang dag gsang sngags kyi grub mtha' rgyud sde 'og
NK086(lu)003:9995: ma rnams su ro rkyang gi rlung dbu mar tshud
NK086(lu)003:9996: pas bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes la lhan
NK086(lu)003:9997: cig skyes pa'i ye shes su 'dod pa gang zhig
NK086(lu)003:9998: tshogs brgyad kyi rnam shes las ma log ste /
NK086(lu)003:9999: tshor ba bde ba ni yid dang nyon yid kyis rjes su bskyed cing /
NK086(lu)003:10000: sems rtog kyi cha ni kun gzhi las gzhan du ma 'das la /
NK086(lu)003:10001: rlung dang khams rnams ro rkyang gi lam nas dbu
NK086(lu)003:10002: mar 'jug cing de'i rtsa bdud re re grol stobs
NK086(lu)003:10003: kyis sa bcu'i spangs rtogs 'char bar 'dod pas 'gro
NK086(lu)003:10004: drug gi rtsa 'dab tu rlung sems zhugs pas ma
NK086(lu)003:10005: dag pa'i 'khrul snang 'char ba'i phyir gol ma gol
NK086(lu)003:10006: gyi gnad kyang de yin la /
NK086(lu)003:10007: 'dir ni rlung rnams rang zhir 'jog pa las dbu
NK086(lu)003:10008: mar 'jug pa sogs med cing rtsa 'dab so so'i
NK086(lu)003:10009: rlung rang dag la song dus 'od kyi rtsa'i ye
NK086(lu)003:10010: shes kyi rlung rang sa na rang gsal bas /
NK086(lu)003:10011: dag pa ye shes kyi snang ba sku dang zhing
NK086(lu)003:10012: khams ngang 'od kyi rang bzhin las ma dag pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10014: dbu ma'i 'od kyi rtsa rnams 'phel bas rtsa bas
NK086(lu)003:10015: rtsa bdud kyi rnam rnams rim gyis 'od du yang
NK086(lu)003:10016: ba'i yon tan las sa'i mngon rtogs rnams rang snang
NK086(lu)003:10017: du 'char ro // de yang rtsa mdud dang po gnyis 'od du yal bas /
NK086(lu)003:10018: phyir snang 'od kyi nang du sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams brgya phrag 'char la /
NK086(lu)003:10019: de dag tu 'od zer 'gyed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10020: rang snang du 'dus pas bgrod pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10021: lus 'gul bas zhing brgya g.yo ba dang /
NK086(lu)003:10022: nang du chos nyid mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK086(lu)003:10023: brgya la 'jug cing ldang ba la sogs 'byung ba'i
NK086(lu)003:10024: phyir / de dag gis mtshon pa'i lam gong ma
NK086(lu)003:10025: rnams kyang theg pa 'og ma las ches khyad par
NK086(lu)003:10026: du 'phags par shes par bya dgos la /
NK086(lu)003:10027: de ltar snang ba bzhi'i lam mthar phyin pa de'i
NK086(lu)003:10028: tshe khregs chod kyis lus rdul phran du dengs pa
NK086(lu)003:10029: yod kyang des rdo rje'i sku mi 'grub /
NK086(lu)003:10030: de ma 'grub pas rten des 'khor ba ma stongs
NK086(lu)003:10031: kyi bar gzhan don rlabs po che sgrub pa'i thabs
NK086(lu)003:10032: med pas / gzugs sku de nyid chu'i zla ba
NK086(lu)003:10033: ltar snang gzugs yod kyang rig gzugs med par bzhugs
NK086(lu)003:10034: nas sems can gyi don dpag tu med par mdzad
NK086(lu)003:10035: pa la 'pho ba chen po'i sku zhes slob dpon
NK086(lu)003:10037: bi ma la mi tra lta bu'o //
NK086(lu)003:10038: gal te rten des re zhig gdul bar bya ba
NK086(lu)003:10039: med na phyir gsal zung 'jug gzugs kyi sku'i rang
NK086(lu)003:10040: snang de nyid nang dbyings spros pa dang bral ba
NK086(lu)003:10041: chos sku'i ngang du thim nas so so rang gi
NK086(lu)003:10042: rig pa phra ba'i ye shes nang gsal gzhon nu
NK086(lu)003:10043: bum pa sku'i tshul gyis 'khyil pa las /
NK086(lu)003:10044: de'i ngang du gdul bya 'dul byed kyi rol pa
NK086(lu)003:10045: bkye ba 'gag pa med pa'i thugs rje chen po'i
NK086(lu)003:10046: ye shes 'phro ba'i gzhir shin tu mnyam par bzhag
NK086(lu)003:10047: pa las ma g.yos bzhin du bzhugs pa'i chos nyid
NK086(lu)003:10048: de ni dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10049: chos kyi sku'i mthar thug pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10050: ka dag dang lhun grub gnyis med kyi grol sa
NK086(lu)003:10051: ka dag chen po gdod ma'i gzhi'i gnas lugs su
NK086(lu)003:10053: ngo bo nyid med par smra ba'i dbu ma pa
NK086(lu)003:10054: rnams kyis 'di skabs su 'jug pa thams cad zhi
NK086(lu)003:10055: ba'i 'gog pa dam pa la gnas pas rang snang
NK086(lu)003:10056: gi sku dang ye shes kyang mi 'dod de spros
NK086(lu)003:10057: pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba nyid kyang stong
NK086(lu)003:10058: pa mtha' gcig tu bzhed pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:10059: 'di ltar rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK086(lu)003:10060: yul yul can du rnam par mi rtog pa la
NK086(lu)003:10061: rang rang gi bzhed tshul tha dad pa byung yang
NK086(lu)003:10062: gdod ma'i mgon po'i dgongs pa rdzogs chen rang lam
NK086(lu)003:10063: gyis khyad par 'di ltar bzhag ste /
NK086(lu)003:10064: ngo bo ka dag gi cha nas dbyings stong pa nyid spros pa thams cad dang bral bar /
NK086(lu)003:10065: lhun grub kyi cha nas rang snang longs spyod rdzogs
NK086(lu)003:10066: pa'i zhing dang sku'i 'char gzhi phra ba'i ye shes
NK086(lu)003:10067: gsum dang / de'i rtsal las mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:10068: shes bya mkhyen pa'i ye shes 'char gzhi'i chu shel
NK086(lu)003:10069: 'od nang du gsal ba phyi rol du mi mngon
NK086(lu)003:10070: pa bzhin gnas pa yin la /
NK086(lu)003:10071: ye shes de nyid yod pas sku dang ye shes thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10072: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos bzhin du gzugs sku
NK086(lu)003:10073: gnyis phrin las dang bcas pa gdul bya la snang
NK086(lu)003:10074: ba'i nus pa 'di nyid las byung ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:10075: de ltar min na ye shes yod pas gdul bya'i don dang /
NK086(lu)003:10076: thams cad mkhyen pa'i yon tan tshad med pa rnams kyang mi 'byung bar 'gyur te /
NK086(lu)003:10078: ye shes med na yon tan 'phel med byang chub dang //
NK086(lu)003:10079: rgya mtsho 'dra ba'i sangs rgyas chos kyang med par 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:10082: de ltar ye shes cha med na //
NK086(lu)003:10083: phyi rol nam mkha' stong pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:10084: khyad par nyid ni yod ma yin //
NK086(lu)003:10085: de phyir gzhi nas ye shes khyab //
NK086(lu)003:10086: ye shes med na chad pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:10087: khyad par ci yang yod mi 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:10088: zhes pa la sogs mtha' yas par gsungs so //
NK086(lu)003:10089: yon tan lhun grub kyi tshul 'di la mnyam sbyor 'grel chen las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:10090: thams dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i mtshan nyid
NK086(lu)003:10091: bde ba chen po'i sku 'di ni rnal 'byor gyi
NK086(lu)003:10092: bdag nyid can te gnyis can du rtog pa'i mtshan
NK086(lu)003:10093: ma bdud la sogs pa'i tshogs rnams ngang gis bcom
NK086(lu)003:10094: zhing / legs pa'i yon tan gyi bkod pa thams
NK086(lu)003:10095: cad la mnga' brnyes pas yon tan gyi bye brag
NK086(lu)003:10096: gzhan med de rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa dang
NK086(lu)003:10097: rtogs pas mngon du gyur pa'i tshul du bzhugs shing
NK086(lu)003:10098: zhing / / zhes pa la sogs pa rnams kyis legs par bshad do //
NK086(lu)003:10099: chos kyi sku de'i ngang las rang snang longs spyod
NK086(lu)003:10100: rdzogs pa'i skur bzhengs pa'i byin rlabs las dag pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10101: zhing khams su de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga dang
NK086(lu)003:10102: / ma dag pa'i zhing du mchog gi sprul sku
NK086(lu)003:10103: sogs phrin las rgyud mi 'chad du 'byung ba yin
NK086(lu)003:10104: / no // rjes mtha' rten bzhi'i man ngag kyang /
NK086(lu)003:10105: mi 'gul ba gsum la gzhi bca' ba /
NK086(lu)003:10106: sdod pa gsum gyis tshad bzung ba /
NK086(lu)003:10107: thob pa gsum gyis gzer gdab pa /
NK086(lu)003:10108: gding bzhis grol tshad bstan pas mjug bsdu ba yin la /
NK086(lu)003:10109: mdor na rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs ni lta ba yongs grub /
NK086(lu)003:10113: spros pa spros kyi mthar ma lhungs /
NK086(lu)003:10117: bar du mi gzhag /brjod tshad thams cad tshig dang tha snyad kyi spun pa /
NK086(lu)003:10118: bsam tshad dpyod tshad thams cad rtog pas btags pa
NK086(lu)003:10119: kho nar song bas rang ngo khas len gyi mthar
NK086(lu)003:10120: mi gnas pa'i ngang du la bzla ba zhig ste
NK086(lu)003:10121: / rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me long las /
NK086(lu)003:10122: rig pa'i chos thams cad bdag rtog gi blo dang bral bar shes par gyis shig /ces so //
NK086(lu)003:10123: 'on kyang snga phyi ci rigs pa rnams su chos
NK086(lu)003:10124: nyid zab mo blos byas kyis sgrub par rlom pa
NK086(lu)003:10125: rnams ni chos nyid blo bral gyi gtam zab mos
NK086(lu)003:10127: 'di sa lam gyi rim pa 'og ma rnams sun
NK086(lu)003:10128: phyung ba ltar snang ba la zab mo'i phyogs dang
NK086(lu)003:10129: rgya che ba'i gnas la shin tu mdza' ba ma
NK086(lu)003:10130: yin pa'i rtog ge'i blo gros ltar snang dang lhan
NK086(lu)003:10131: cig tu dus snga phyi tsam la'ang phrag ba dog
NK086(lu)003:10132: pa'i bka' thub res 'ga' ma yin par lhur len
NK086(lu)003:10135: bya ba rnams la rnal 'byor ba //
NK086(lu)003:10136: lam chen dag tu yongs 'dzin pa //
NK086(lu)003:10137: ri dwags smin rgyu bsnyeg pa ltar //
NK086(lu)003:10138: rtag tu snang yang mi zin no //
NK086(lu)003:10139: de bas de dag thams cad kyang //
NK086(lu)003:10140: yang dag min pa'i blo dang bcas //
NK086(lu)003:10142: gong ma gong ma'i khyad par 'phags //
NK086(lu)003:10143: 'og ma'i blo ni gong ma yi //
NK086(lu)003:10144: shes rab kyis ni sun 'byin no //
NK086(lu)003:10145: zhes gsungs pa bzhin shes par bya zhing rtsod pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10146: kun lhongs chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ngang
NK086(lu)003:10147: du zhib la mkhas par bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:10148: gzhan yang rdzogs pa chen po'i gdams pa lag len
NK086(lu)003:10149: du 'dril ba'i man ngag tu 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK086(lu)003:10150: thams cad bar do rnam pa bzhi'i rol par gtan
NK086(lu)003:10151: la phab ste / skye gnas kyi bar dor gdams
NK086(lu)003:10152: ngag la thos bsam gyi sgro 'dogs chod pa'i bya
NK086(lu)003:10154: 'chi kha'i bar dor gdams ngag gsal 'debs pa sgeg mo me long la blta ba lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:10155: chos nyid kyi bar dor rang snang la yid ches pa ma pang du bu 'jug pa lta bu /
NK086(lu)003:10156: srid pa bar dor las kyi 'phro mthud pa yur
NK086(lu)003:10157: ba rkang chad la wa 'dzug pa lta bu'i gdams
NK086(lu)003:10158: ngag la brten nas skal ldan rnams gdod ma'i grol
NK086(lu)003:10160: gnad kyi snying po gnas lugs rtogs pa'i ye shes
NK086(lu)003:10161: ji bzhin pa dngos ni go yul gyi lta ba
NK086(lu)003:10162: kha khyer tsam gyis nam yang mthong zhing thob pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10165: don dang lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni //
NK086(lu)003:10166: tshogs bsags sgrib pa dag pa'i lag rjes dang //
NK086(lu)003:10167: rtogs ldan bla ma'i byin rlabs kho na las //
NK086(lu)003:10168: thabs gzhan bstan pa rmongs par shes par bya //
NK086(lu)003:10171: gzhan gyis brjod min lhan cig skyes //
NK086(lu)003:10172: gang du yang ni mi rnyed de //
NK086(lu)003:10173: bla ma'i dus thabs bsten pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:10174: rang gi bsod nams las shes bya //
NK086(lu)003:10177: bla mas smras pa gang gi snying zhugs pa //
NK086(lu)003:10178: lag pa'i mthil na gnas pa'i gter mthong 'dra //
NK086(lu)003:10180: bla slob snod bcud kyi rten 'brel tshogs pa na
NK086(lu)003:10181: byin rlabs 'pho ba'i stobs kyis ye shes rgyal thabs
NK086(lu)003:10182: spyi blugs kyi dbang chen nos te mngon sum rang
NK086(lu)003:10183: thog tu dbab / dbab pa'i don rtsol med ngang
NK086(lu)003:10184: bzhag chu bo'i rgyun gyi rnal 'byor la goms par
NK086(lu)003:10185: thog tu dbab / byas te / lam rtags nyams
NK086(lu)003:10186: kyi so mtshams ngos bzung zhing bde rtsub nyams bzhes
NK086(lu)003:10188: nyams myong rtogs pa'i yon tan bogs dbyung ba la brten nas /
NK086(lu)003:10189: 'bras bu phyi dus su mi re bar tshe lus
NK086(lu)003:10190: 'di nyid la mngon du byed pa'i gding dang ldan
NK086(lu)003:10191: pa yin no // de ltar go don spyir dbye
NK086(lu)003:10192: ba'i sgo nas bshad pa nyid nges par byas te
NK086(lu)003:10193: pa yin no // / da ni gnyis pa blo
NK086(lu)003:10194: la 'jug bde ba'i phyir skabs don bye brag tu
NK086(lu)003:10195: bsdu ba'i sgo nas slar yang 'chad par bya ste
NK086(lu)003:10196: pa yin no // / / de la gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:10197: phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10198: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10199: de gnyis kyi khyad par la snga rabs pa rnams kyi bzhed pa mi mthun pa mang na'ang /
NK086(lu)003:10200: 'dir thugs su sras ka ba bzhi'i dgongs pa rje sgro phug pas bsdus nas lngar gsungs te /
NK086(lu)003:10201: dang po lta ba'i khyad par ni /
NK086(lu)003:10202: sngags kyi theg pa gang zhig sems nyid bdag nyid chen por rtogs pa nang pa /
NK086(lu)003:10203: ma rtogs pa phyi pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10204: in+d+ri b+hu ti'i lam rnam bkod las /
NK086(lu)003:10205: rigs gsum rigs lngar 'dod pa dag /bdag nyid chen po ma rtogs phyir //
NK086(lu)003:10206: thun mong mnyam par nga smra'o //
NK086(lu)003:10208: gnyis pa dngos grub len tshul gyi khyad par ni /
NK086(lu)003:10209: ye shes kyi lha la re zhing bka' la sdod pas dngos grub zhu ba ni phyi pa /
NK086(lu)003:10210: bdag nyid chen por rtogs pas sems nyid sku dang
NK086(lu)003:10211: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'i phyir
NK086(lu)003:10212: dngos grub rang la yod par mthong ba ni nang
NK086(lu)003:10213: pa ste / rdo rje sems dpa'i zhus lan las /
NK086(lu)003:10214: sngags phyi nang gi rnal 'byor pa gnyis dngos grub len pa la khyad par ci mchis /
NK086(lu)003:10216: dper na rgyal pos blon por bsgos pa ltar //
NK086(lu)003:10217: grub pa gong nas 'byin pa phyir ba'i tshul //
NK086(lu)003:10218: 'bangs kyis rgyal srid phul nas dbang bsgyur ltar //
NK086(lu)003:10219: rang byung rdzogs chen bla na med pa tshul //
NK086(lu)003:10222: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK086(lu)003:10223: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK086(lu)003:10224: gsum pa dbang gi khyad par ni /
NK086(lu)003:10225: mchog dbang gong ma gsum bskur thob mi nus pa phyir pa /
NK086(lu)003:10226: de gsum la gtso bor 'dzin pa nang pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10227: bzhi pa sbyod pa'i khyad par ni /
NK086(lu)003:10228: 'khor ba'i chos nyi shu la thabs kyis zin nas spyod nus pa nang pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10230: lnga pa 'bras bu'i khyad par ni /
NK086(lu)003:10231: mi tshe bdun dang lnga dang gsum sogs nas sbyor nus pa phyi pa /
NK086(lu)003:10232: tshe 'di la sbyor nus pa nang pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10234: lha rje kha rag pa dang blo ma rog ni /
NK086(lu)003:10235: rgyud gzhung gi skabs su rgyud kyi dngos po bcu phyi nang gis bsgyur ba'i khyad par dang /
NK086(lu)003:10236: bye brag dbang gi skabs su zab dbang gsum ston nus mi nus dang /
NK086(lu)003:10237: lta ba'i skabs su rang byung ye shes smra nus mi nus dang /
NK086(lu)003:10238: bsgom pa'i skabs su lha zhal sbyor du bsgom nus mi nus dang /
NK086(lu)003:10239: sbyod pa'i skabs su dam rdzas lnga la spyod nus mi nus dang /
NK086(lu)003:10240: lha dang bdag tha mi dad du bltas nas 'jug nus mi nus dang /
NK086(lu)003:10241: dngos grub kyi skabs su dus nye ring dang phyi nang nas re ba'i khyad par yod ces gsungs /
NK086(lu)003:10243: khyad par de rnams kyang phyogs re ba tsam yin pas /
NK086(lu)003:10245: shes byed lam gyi khyad par /
NK086(lu)003:10246: thob bya 'bras bu'i khyad par gsum du phye na 'thad gsungs /
NK086(lu)003:10247: rje sgrol g.yung gnyis kyi zhal nas /
NK086(lu)003:10248: lta spyod dang ting nge 'dzin gsum dbyer med du 'dod pa sngags nang pa /
NK086(lu)003:10250: 'o na rgyu'i theg pa dang sngags phyi ba la khyad par med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:10252: kun rdzob lam du byed nus mi nus kyi khyad par yod pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK086(lu)003:10254: dang po phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa la dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:10256: phyi ba rgyud la rnam gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:10257: kri ya u pa yo ga'o //
NK086(lu)003:10266: don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i dag par
NK086(lu)003:10267: rtogs pas kun rdzob tu dngos grub gzhan la re
NK086(lu)003:10268: zhing rtsol ba'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10270: gnyis med mnyam par ma shes pas //
NK086(lu)003:10271: don dam dag pa chos nyid tsam //
NK086(lu)003:10272: ye shes bzhi yon kun rdzob lha //
NK086(lu)003:10273: res bsgom bya ba las kyi sa //
NK086(lu)003:10276: kri ya'i sgra bya ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:10277: phyi'i bya ba gtso bor ston pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:10278: de ltar yang bsam gtan phyi ma'i 'grel ba las /
NK086(lu)003:10279: rgyud 'di ni lus ngag gi bya ba gtso bor ston pas na bya ba'i rgyud ces bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:10281: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK086(lu)003:10283: thog ma'i 'jug sgo smin byed dang /
NK086(lu)003:10286: chu dang cod pan gyi dbang 'khor bcas bskur bas slob ma snod rung du byed pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10288: chu yi dbang bskur dbu rgyan dag /bya ba'i rgyud la rab tu grags //
NK086(lu)003:10291: khrus dang gtsang sbra dang dag pa gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK086(lu)003:10293: 'jug pa'i sgo ni dag pa gsum //
NK086(lu)003:10296: de yang dag pa gsum ni /
NK086(lu)003:10298: dag pa rnam gsum gang zhe na //
NK086(lu)003:10299: lha dang dkyil 'khor dag pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:10300: rdzas dang longs spyod dag pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:10305: kri ya don dam chos nyid blta //
NK086(lu)003:10306: kun rdzob rang rig yon tan lha //
NK086(lu)003:10307: rigs gsum dkyil 'khor snang ba la //
NK086(lu)003:10309: ces pas bden pa gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:10311: sems nyid dag pa stong gsal gyi ye shes yod
NK086(lu)003:10312: med snang stong gi mtha' bzhi dang bral bar 'dod
NK086(lu)003:10314: rang sems mtha' bzhi yongs bral ba //
NK086(lu)003:10315: rig phyir ye shes gzhan las min //
NK086(lu)003:10320: dbu ma pa man chad kyis yang dag dang log par brtags pa'i kun rdzob thams cad yin la /
NK086(lu)003:10322: chos nyid rtogs pa'i yon tan rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang bar 'dod pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10324: skyed bslang snang ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK086(lu)003:10325: snang ba'i dngos po mtho 'jam rtsub //
NK086(lu)003:10326: drug phyed rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK086(lu)003:10327: mthong ba rnam par dag ces bya //
NK086(lu)003:10331: dkon mchog gsum dang byang chub sems //
NK086(lu)003:10332: sngags dang phyag rgya mi spang zhing //
NK086(lu)003:10333: rdo rje dril bu spang mi bya //
NK086(lu)003:10334: lha dang bla ma de bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:10335: de ni yan lag dam tshig yin //
NK086(lu)003:10336: rtse ba'i dam tshig lnga po ni //
NK086(lu)003:10337: khri la nyal bar mi bya zhing //
NK086(lu)003:10338: sha mi za zhing chang mi btung //
NK086(lu)003:10339: zhes dam tshig bcu gcig tu gsungs /
NK086(lu)003:10340: gsang ba spyi rgyud las spyi'i dam tshig gsum dang /
NK086(lu)003:10341: bye brag gi dam tshig bcu gsum du bshad pa la sogs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10346: he ru ka gal po las /
NK086(lu)003:10347: chos nyid sgra dang yid gzugs thugs //
NK086(lu)003:10348: ye shes yongs rdzogs skur sgrub bsgom //
NK086(lu)003:10349: zhes pas kri ya don gyi lha drug gi sgo nas dam tshig pa bskyed par bya ste /
NK086(lu)003:10350: de'ang stong pa nyid kyi lha dang /
NK086(lu)003:10357: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang //
NK086(lu)003:10358: phyag rgya mtshan ma drug yin te //
NK086(lu)003:10359: zhes rnam 'joms kyi rgyud rgyas pa las gsungs so //
NK086(lu)003:10360: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs te /
NK086(lu)003:10361: mchod bstod dang bzlas pa sogs byas la /
NK086(lu)003:10362: rje khol gyi tshul du bltas nas dngos grub blang ste /
NK086(lu)003:10364: lha dang rnal 'byor dag pa gnyis //
NK086(lu)003:10365: rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul du blta //
NK086(lu)003:10367: rigs thams cad pa'i dngos grub len pa'i rgyud las /
NK086(lu)003:10368: rje dpon rgyal po'i tshul bltas la //
NK086(lu)003:10369: rang nyid bron gyi 'du shes kyis //
NK086(lu)003:10370: sngags bsgrub dngos grub snying po ni //
NK086(lu)003:10371: bla na med pa'i mchog tu blang //
NK086(lu)003:10374: mtshan bcas lha dang yig 'bru la sogs par bsgom
NK086(lu)003:10375: pa'i snang ba de'ang mi dmigs pa dag pa mtha'
NK086(lu)003:10376: bzhi dang bral ba'i ngang du 'jog pas bden gnyis
NK086(lu)003:10377: res bsgom ste / la shan las /
NK086(lu)003:10378: snang stong rim gyis brtan par byed //
NK086(lu)003:10387: bzlas brjod sngags kyi bya ba rnams so //
NK086(lu)003:10390: gza' skar dus tshigs zas gos gtsang //
NK086(lu)003:10391: brtul zhugs dka' thub spyad pa spyod //
NK086(lu)003:10399: mi tshe bdun na rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10400: sa sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can 'thob
NK086(lu)003:10403: mi tshe bdun na sangs rgyas sa //
NK086(lu)003:10406: gnyis pa u pa ya'i theg pa la /
NK086(lu)003:10411: spyod pa bya ba ltar spyod pas dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10413: gnyis ka la brten pa las grub pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10416: u pa'i sgras phyi lus ngag gi bya ba dang
NK086(lu)003:10417: nang gi rnal 'byor gnyis cha mnyam du spyod pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10418: phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces bya ste /
NK086(lu)003:10420: u pa ya ni 'di lta ste //
NK086(lu)003:10421: lta ba yo gar blta ba la //
NK086(lu)003:10422: spyod pa kri yar spyod pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10423: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags //
NK086(lu)003:10425: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK086(lu)003:10426: dang po 'jug sgo la'ang gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:10428: chu cod pan gnyis kyi steng du rdor dril ming gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:10430: rdo rje dril bu de bzhin ming //
NK086(lu)003:10431: spyod pa'i rgyud du rab tu gsal //
NK086(lu)003:10435: lnga pa spyod pa rnams bya rgyud dang /
NK086(lu)003:10437: bzhi pa sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni yo ga dang shas cher mthun pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10439: gnyis ka rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:10440: spyod pa bya ba'i rjes mthun yang //
NK086(lu)003:10441: lta ba rnal 'byor rjes mthun phyir //
NK086(lu)003:10442: rigs dang lta bas khyad par 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:10445: gnyis ka rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:10446: lta spyod gong 'og rjes su mthun //
NK086(lu)003:10448: 'o na kyang rgyal ba rigs bzhir blta zhing bsgom pa sogs khyad par cung zad snang ngo //
NK086(lu)003:10450: mi tshe lnga na rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob par 'dod pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10451: rigs bzhi ni las kyi rigs rin chen rigs la bsdus pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10453: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang bar nas //
NK086(lu)003:10456: gnyis su med la mi tshe lngas sgrib gol //
NK086(lu)003:10458: gsum pa yo ga'i theg pa la /
NK086(lu)003:10462: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid kyi byin
NK086(lu)003:10463: rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi lhar brtags te
NK086(lu)003:10464: rtog pa bzang ngan blang dor gyi rtsol bas 'bras
NK086(lu)003:10467: lhun grub mnyam pa ma mthong bas //
NK086(lu)003:10468: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyi //
NK086(lu)003:10469: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings sprul pa //
NK086(lu)003:10473: yo ga'i sgra las nang gi rnal 'byor gtso bor
NK086(lu)003:10474: byed pa'am ston pas na rnal 'byor rgyud ces bya
NK086(lu)003:10476: rnal 'byor gtso bor byas pas 'grub pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10478: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK086(lu)003:10479: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:10481: rig pa'i dbang lnga'i steng du rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang drug bskur te /
NK086(lu)003:10483: phyir mi ldog pa bum pa'i dbang /
NK086(lu)003:10484: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsal bar byas //
NK086(lu)003:10485: de ni drug gi bye brag dbang //
NK086(lu)003:10486: de ni slob dpon dbang zhes bya //
NK086(lu)003:10488: gnyis pa bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK086(lu)003:10489: mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK086(lu)003:10491: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pa //
NK086(lu)003:10492: mtshan ma yod med sgor zhugs nas //
NK086(lu)003:10496: don dam pa bden pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:10497: chos thams cad spros pa'i mtshan ma dang bral ba'i rang bzhin 'od gsal stong pa nyid de /
NK086(lu)003:10499: chos rnams rang bzhin 'od gsal bas //
NK086(lu)003:10500: ngo bo nyid kyis gdod nas dag /ces so //
NK086(lu)003:10502: log pa'i kun rdzob sngar dang 'dra la /
NK086(lu)003:10504: cir snang thams cad chos nyid rtogs pa'i byin rlabs
NK086(lu)003:10505: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba'i phyir
NK086(lu)003:10506: / skye bos snang bar rang rgyud du brtags pa 'di med par 'dod do //
NK086(lu)003:10507: de ltar yang gal po las /
NK086(lu)003:10508: yo ga'i theg par gnas 'dod pa //
NK086(lu)003:10509: 'og min rdo rje dbyings su blta //
NK086(lu)003:10512: yo ga don dam rnam dag pa'i //
NK086(lu)003:10513: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su //
NK086(lu)003:10514: rtogs pa'i byin rlabs lhar snang ba //
NK086(lu)003:10515: de phyir skye bo ltar mthong 'khrul //
NK086(lu)003:10518: rang rig dngos mthong mtshan ma gnyis //
NK086(lu)003:10519: dbyer med dbyings dag ye shes las //
NK086(lu)003:10520: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings kyi lha //
NK086(lu)003:10521: shar ltar grogs po'i tshul du blta //
NK086(lu)003:10524: rtse mor gsungs pa'i rigs lnga spyi'i dam tshig /byang chub kyi sems dang por bskyed cing /
NK086(lu)003:10525: de'i rjes su tshul khrims gsum gyi bslab pa la nan tan byed pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10526: bye brag gi dam tshig /snang mdzad dam tshig gsum /
NK086(lu)003:10527: mi bskyod rin 'byung gnyis la bzhi bzhi /
NK086(lu)003:10528: mtha' yas kyi gcig /don grub gnyis te bcu bzhir gsungs la /
NK086(lu)003:10530: bya rgyud kyi dam tshig bcu gcig po'i steng du
NK086(lu)003:10531: thun min gnyis bsnyan nas bcu gsum du bshad de
NK086(lu)003:10533: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi bsrung mtshams ni //
NK086(lu)003:10534: gong gi bsrung 'tshams steng du ni //
NK086(lu)003:10535: lung gcig chu la mi btung zhing //
NK086(lu)003:10536: nyams dang kha mi bsre ba bsrung //
NK086(lu)003:10542: mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi'i sgo nas lha
NK086(lu)003:10543: dang lha mo'i rnal 'byor phyag rgya bzhi ldan du
NK086(lu)003:10544: bsgom pa ste / lta phreng las /
NK086(lu)003:10545: phyi yo byad la gtso bor mi 'dzin par don
NK086(lu)003:10546: dam par skye 'gag med pa'i lha dang lha mo
NK086(lu)003:10547: dang / de dang 'dra ba'i rgyud yongs su dag
NK086(lu)003:10548: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'phags pa'i gzugs kyi sku
NK086(lu)003:10549: phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan par bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor
NK086(lu)003:10552: de'ang dam tshig pa bskyed la /
NK086(lu)003:10553: ye shes pa spyan drangs nas /
NK086(lu)003:10554: spun nam grogs po'i tshul du bzang ngan med par bltas te /
NK086(lu)003:10555: mchod bstod bzlas pa la sogs pa bya'o //
NK086(lu)003:10556: de ltar yang rang shar las /
NK086(lu)003:10557: lha dang rnal 'byor bdag nyid kyang //
NK086(lu)003:10558: spun dang grogs po'i tshul du 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:10560: de la mngon byang lnga ni /
NK086(lu)003:10565: sku yongs su rdzogs pa las mngon par byang chub pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10571: de dag kyang gal po las /
NK086(lu)003:10572: mi rtogs zla ba gsung rdo rje //
NK086(lu)003:10573: spro bsdus bsgom pa'i sku ru gsal //
NK086(lu)003:10574: ting 'dzin byin rlob dbang bskur mchod //
NK086(lu)003:10575: mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi //
NK086(lu)003:10576: bsgom zhing mchod pa bya ba yang //
NK086(lu)003:10577: bsod nams ldan phyir bya ba yin //
NK086(lu)003:10580: lus ngag yid dang bya ba bzhi la /
NK086(lu)003:10582: me long kun gzhi sku phyag chen /
NK086(lu)003:10583: sor rtog yid gsung chos rgya mnyam nyid nyon yid /
NK086(lu)003:10585: bya ba sgo lnga phrin las las rgya rnams kyis rgyas btab nas bsgom pa'i phyir phyag rgya ste /
NK086(lu)003:10586: me long lta bu la sogs pa'i ye shes bzhi mngon du bya ba dang sbyar zhing /
NK086(lu)003:10587: chos dbyings ye shes ni de thams cad kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10589: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i ngo bo nyid dang
NK086(lu)003:10590: de'i byin rlabs lhar snang ye shes kyi snang cha
NK086(lu)003:10591: gnyis gnyis su med pa'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog
NK086(lu)003:10592: pa ste / rdo rje 'byung ba las /
NK086(lu)003:10593: gnyis su med pa'i chos dbyings dang //
NK086(lu)003:10594: bla med dngos grub dam pa blang //
NK086(lu)003:10597: gtsang sbra sogs phyi'i kun spyod kyi grogs dang ldan
NK086(lu)003:10598: pa'i sgo nas gtso bor lha'i rnal 'byor la gnas
NK086(lu)003:10599: pas rang gzhan gyi spyod pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10601: lha yi ting 'dzin la gnas te //
NK086(lu)003:10602: sems can thams cad yongs mi gtong //
NK086(lu)003:10603: rtag tu sangs rgyas yid la byed //
NK086(lu)003:10604: rtag tu sangs rgyas mchod pa mchog /ces so //
NK086(lu)003:10606: mi tshe gsum na stug po bkod pa'i sa la
NK086(lu)003:10607: sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can du 'tshang
NK086(lu)003:10610: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pas //
NK086(lu)003:10611: mi tshe gsum na grol bar 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:10614: gzung 'dzin bag chags lnga byang nas //
NK086(lu)003:10615: ye shes lnga yi rtsal dag gis //
NK086(lu)003:10616: stug po bkod pa'i sa bon nas //
NK086(lu)003:10618: skye med chos sku dag pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:10619: skye med sgo nas 'gro don mdzad //
NK086(lu)003:10620: phyag rgya rigs lnga longs spyod rdzogs //
NK086(lu)003:10621: byang chub sems dpa'i 'gro don rdzogs //
NK086(lu)003:10622: sprul pa bye ba sa ya yis //
NK086(lu)003:10623: rigs drug ngo la cir yang ston //
NK086(lu)003:10625: gnyis pa nang pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa la /
NK086(lu)003:10627: nang pa la ni gsum du 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:10628: ma h+aa a nu a ti'o //
NK086(lu)003:10630: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /lung a nu yo ga /man ngag a ti yo ga'o //
NK086(lu)003:10631: de gsum gyi khyad par la /
NK086(lu)003:10632: glan chab par bas rje zur chung pa la zhus pa'i lan du /
NK086(lu)003:10633: rig pa'i cho 'phrul du snang ba ma h+aa /
NK086(lu)003:10634: rang rig pa'i rtsal du snang ba a nu /
NK086(lu)003:10635: rig pa rang snang ba a ti ste /
NK086(lu)003:10637: cho 'phrul rtsal dang rang snang ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:10638: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir gsungs skad /
NK086(lu)003:10640: chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer med kyi
NK086(lu)003:10641: cho 'phrul du rtogs pa ma h+aa yo ga /chos
NK086(lu)003:10642: thams cad sems nyid dbyings ye gnyis su med pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10643: rtsal du rtogs pa a nu /
NK086(lu)003:10644: chos thams cad sems nyid ye nas skye 'gag med
NK086(lu)003:10645: pa'i rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bar rtogs
NK086(lu)003:10646: pa a ti ste lta ba'i sgo nas khyad par
NK086(lu)003:10647: phye ba'o // de la mda' glan gnyis ka gces nor du bzhed do //
NK086(lu)003:10648: yang skyo gong bu pa'i zhal nas /
NK086(lu)003:10650: spyod pa gtso che ba ma h+aa /
NK086(lu)003:10651: ting nge 'dzin gtso che ba a nu /
NK086(lu)003:10652: lta ba gtso che ba a ti'o gsungs /
NK086(lu)003:10653: yang lha rje rog /ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis lha rim par bskyed pa'i phyir bskyed pa ma h+aa /
NK086(lu)003:10654: de la mi brten par lha rdzogs tshul du bskyed pa rdzogs pa a nu /
NK086(lu)003:10655: bskyed rdzogs gnyis las grol bas bskyed du med pa ni rdzogs pa chen po a ti'am /
NK086(lu)003:10657: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu la ched 'dzin che ba ma h+aa /
NK086(lu)003:10658: de bas chung pa a nu /
NK086(lu)003:10659: ched 'dzin las grol ba a ti'o gsungs /
NK086(lu)003:10660: me nyag 'byung grags kyi zhal nas /
NK086(lu)003:10661: yod bskyed rdzogs gsum ka yod kyang /
NK086(lu)003:10662: bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa ma h+aa /
NK086(lu)003:10663: rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa a nu /
NK086(lu)003:10664: de gnyis kyi rtsol ba dang bral ba rdzogs pa chen po ste /
NK086(lu)003:10665: dpyal lo kun rdor yang nges tshig gi khyad par la 'di legs par bzhed do //
NK086(lu)003:10667: gdul bya zhe sdang shas che zhing rtog pa mang
NK086(lu)003:10668: ba'i don du snang ba thabs kyi rang bzhin pha
NK086(lu)003:10669: rgyud ma h+aa / 'dod chags shas che zhing sems
NK086(lu)003:10670: gnas pa la dga' ba'i don du stong pa de
NK086(lu)003:10671: kho na nyid kyi rdzogs rim shes rab ma rgyud
NK086(lu)003:10672: rgyud ma h+aa / a nu / gti mug shas
NK086(lu)003:10673: che zhing bya rtsol can gyi don du gnyis su
NK086(lu)003:10674: med pa'i rang bzhin a ti yo ga bstan te
NK086(lu)003:10675: rgyud ma h+aa / a nu / / bkod pa chen po las /
NK086(lu)003:10676: sems yas pa la bskyed pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:10677: sems bcud can la rdzogs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10678: mchog gsang rab la rdzogs pa che //
NK086(lu)003:10679: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir gsungs shing /
NK086(lu)003:10680: sems nyid ngal gso las kyang /
NK086(lu)003:10681: ma h+aas rlung dang bskyed rim thabs gtso la //
NK086(lu)003:10682: a nus khams dang rdzogs rim shes rab gtso //
NK086(lu)003:10683: a tis thams cad gnyis med ye shes gtso //
NK086(lu)003:10686: dang po ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa la /
NK086(lu)003:10690: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa la gtso bor brten pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10691: sgo nas lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi don
NK086(lu)003:10692: la rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas grol ba thob pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10693: rang bzhin no // gnyis pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:10694: ma h+aa yo ga'i sgra las rnal 'byor chen po ste /
NK086(lu)003:10695: gnyis med kyi don la blo 'byor bas yo ga phyi ba las ches 'phags pa'i phyir ro //
NK086(lu)003:10696: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK086(lu)003:10697: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:10699: thun mong ba bum dbang gi steng du thun min
NK086(lu)003:10700: mchog dbang gong ma gsum bsnan pas dbang bzhi bskur
NK086(lu)003:10701: bar bya ste / sgyur 'phrul rtsa rgyud phyi ma las /
NK086(lu)003:10702: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK086(lu)003:10703: de ma thag pa bzhi ba ste //
NK086(lu)003:10705: de yang bum dbang la phan nus gnyis su phye bas lngar 'gyur te /
NK086(lu)003:10707: dbye ba rnam pa lnga ru 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:10708: bdag phan nus pa gnyis ka'i las //
NK086(lu)003:10710: gnyis pa bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK086(lu)003:10711: shes rab stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK086(lu)003:10712: thabs snying rje sgyu ma dang /
NK086(lu)003:10714: ting 'dzin gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK086(lu)003:10715: bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa'i lam yin pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:10716: de ltar yang rang shar las /
NK086(lu)003:10717: 'jug pa'i sgo ni ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum //
NK086(lu)003:10720: ma h+aa yo ga'i 'jug sgo ni //
NK086(lu)003:10721: ting 'dzin rnam gsum sgo nas 'jug /ces so //
NK086(lu)003:10723: rig pa spros bral la snang ba ngo bo nyid
NK086(lu)003:10724: kyi rgyur lhun grub tu 'dod pa'i don dam bden
NK086(lu)003:10725: pa dang / de nyid kyi rtsal rtog tshogs thams
NK086(lu)003:10726: cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang
NK086(lu)003:10727: snang ba kun rdzob kyi bden par 'dod la /
NK086(lu)003:10728: de gnyis kyang snang stong phyogs re ba ma yin te /
NK086(lu)003:10729: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed par mnyam pa nyid du snang ba'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:10730: tha snyad du dbyer med ces brjod na'ang /
NK086(lu)003:10731: der 'dzin pa'i bsam brjod kyi yul las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK086(lu)003:10732: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:10733: de ltar yang rnam bkod las /
NK086(lu)003:10734: lhag pa'i mnyam nyid dbyer med don //
NK086(lu)003:10735: mi grangs cir yang bstan mod kyang //
NK086(lu)003:10736: don du smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK086(lu)003:10739: de ming zhen pa grol phyir las //
NK086(lu)003:10740: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK086(lu)003:10744: bsrung bya'i dam tshig rtsa ltung bcu bzhi la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK086(lu)003:10745: spyad bya'i dam tshig sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i rang bzhin du shes nas spyod pa gnyis su bzhed /
NK086(lu)003:10747: rnal 'byor chen po'i dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad gsungs te /
NK086(lu)003:10749: rnal 'byor chen po'i bsrung mtshams ni //
NK086(lu)003:10750: rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum po dang //
NK086(lu)003:10751: yan lag nyi shu rtsa lnga bsrung //
NK086(lu)003:10754: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gsum mo //
NK086(lu)003:10757: spyad dang mi spang dang du blang //
NK086(lu)003:10758: shes dang bsgrub par bya ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:10761: sgrub sde gtso bor byas pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10762: rgyud sde gtso bor byas pa'i lugs gnyis /
NK086(lu)003:10764: 'jam dpal gyi sku 'khor lo bzhi la brten nas bde gshegs sku'i sgrub pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10765: rta mgrin gyi rta skad thengs gsum la brten nas pad+ma gsung gi sgrub pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10766: yang dag gi thugs rig pa rang byung gi ye
NK086(lu)003:10767: shes yang dag grub pa gcig pu la brten nas
NK086(lu)003:10768: thugs rdo rje'i sgrub pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:10769: che mchog gi 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad yon
NK086(lu)003:10770: tan du rdzogs par ston pa bdud rtsi yon tan
NK086(lu)003:10772: phur pa'i mngon spyod kyi las kyis gdug pa can
NK086(lu)003:10773: 'dul pa'i thabs gtso bor ston pa phur pa phrin
NK086(lu)003:10774: las kyi sgrub pa ste ye shes lha'i sgrub sde
NK086(lu)003:10775: lnga dang / ma mo rbod gtong /
NK086(lu)003:10777: 'jig rten mchod bstod kyi sgrub pa ste thun mong gi sgrub sde gsum mo //
NK086(lu)003:10779: spyir ma h+aa yo ga la'ang pha ma gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum gyi dbye bas /
NK086(lu)003:10780: gsang 'dus la sogs pa pha rgyud du bskyed rim thabs kyi cha dang /
NK086(lu)003:10781: de'i rdzogs rim kyang rlung gtso bor byed pas gsal
NK086(lu)003:10782: stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis nyams su
NK086(lu)003:10783: len par 'dod / bde dgyes yang dag sogs ma
NK086(lu)003:10784: rgyud rnams su bskyed rim gyi spros pa shas chung
NK086(lu)003:10785: len par 'dod / zhing / shes rab rdzogs pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10786: rim pa khams byang chub kyi sems thig le gtso
NK086(lu)003:10787: bor byed pa'i bde stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK086(lu)003:10788: tshul gyis nyams su len par 'dod /
NK086(lu)003:10789: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs ma ning gi rgyud rnams su bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug cing /
NK086(lu)003:10790: de'ang rdzogs rim rtsa thig rlung gsum las skyes pa'i bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK086(lu)003:10791: khyad par 'od gsal ye shes chen po la gtso
NK086(lu)003:10792: bor byed pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len par 'dod
NK086(lu)003:10793: do // 'dir rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po'i dbang du byas te bshad na /
NK086(lu)003:10795: mtshan ma bsgom pa'i rim pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:10796: de bzhin nyid ni bsgom pa yi //
NK086(lu)003:10797: bye brag rnam pa gnyis su gsungs //
NK086(lu)003:10804: ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas dkyil 'khor rim
NK086(lu)003:10805: gyis bskyed pa gtso bor byed pa'i sgo nas lha
NK086(lu)003:10806: rtog dbyer med du bsgom pa'i nyams len /
NK086(lu)003:10811: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob kyang rnam
NK086(lu)003:10812: pa tsam bsgom pa nub gcig la bskyed rim gyi
NK086(lu)003:10813: cho ga'i yan lag tshang ba nyams su len pa
NK086(lu)003:10815: zag bcas tshogs sbyor gyi rnal 'byor lnga dang /
NK086(lu)003:10816: zag med rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'o //
NK086(lu)003:10818: steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag dang /
NK086(lu)003:10819: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag gnyis te /
NK086(lu)003:10821: gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo //
NK086(lu)003:10824: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10826: thabs la mkhas pa'i gding gis zin pas 'khor ba'i chos ci la'ang ma chags par spyod pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:10828: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni /
NK086(lu)003:10829: ta na dang ni ga na dang //
NK086(lu)003:10830: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga po la //
NK086(lu)003:10831: thabs chen lta ba'i spyod pa spyad //
NK086(lu)003:10834: tshe 'adi'am bar dor sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid mngon du byed pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:10836: 'di ni bcom ldan bdag nyid che //
NK086(lu)003:10837: sku gsum mi phyed las byung ba //
NK086(lu)003:10838: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par brgyan //
NK086(lu)003:10842: yang na lus ni spangs ma thag /brtson pa mi ldan pas kyang 'grub //
NK086(lu)003:10844: gnyis pa lung a nu yo ga'i theg pa la /
NK086(lu)003:10848: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa la gtso bor brten
NK086(lu)003:10849: pa'i sgo nas dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med
NK086(lu)003:10850: pa'i don la rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas grol ba
NK086(lu)003:10853: a nu yo ga ste shes rab rjes chags kyi
NK086(lu)003:10854: lam gtso bor ston pa'i phyir rjes su rnal 'byor
NK086(lu)003:10855: ro // gsum pa dbye ba drug gi /
NK086(lu)003:10856: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:10858: a nu'i dkyil 'khor du phyi nang sgrub gsang bzhis bsdus pa'i dbang chog sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK086(lu)003:10860: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK086(lu)003:10861: sgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK086(lu)003:10862: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK086(lu)003:10863: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:10865: de la kha cig /de ltar smos pa'i rtsa ba
NK086(lu)003:10866: sa drug las yan lag gi dbang brgyad brgya po
NK086(lu)003:10867: gcig tu phye ba ni theg pa dgu ka'i dbang
NK086(lu)003:10868: yin te / dbang don bsdus pa las /
NK086(lu)003:10869: yo ga sogs theg drug las //
NK086(lu)003:10870: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK086(lu)003:10872: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las //
NK086(lu)003:10873: bcu yis byang chub rigs can 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:10874: bcu gcig gsang ba nang par 'gyur //
NK086(lu)003:10875: bcu gsum bla ma chen por grags //
NK086(lu)003:10876: gnyis kyis theg dgu'i dbang rdzogs pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:10878: a nu'i sgos dbang du ji ltar 'gyur zhe na /
NK086(lu)003:10880: theg rim dgu dang tshul mthun pas theg dgu'i dbang
NK086(lu)003:10881: du ming btags par bla ma mkhas pa rnams bzhed
NK086(lu)003:10883: mdo dbang 'chad pa po phal gyi 'dod pa ltar ma yin te /
NK086(lu)003:10885: a nu yo ga'i dbang gi nang du gong ma
NK086(lu)003:10886: a ti yo ga'i dbang 'du bar khas len dgos
NK086(lu)003:10887: pa'i phyir ha cang thal te /
NK086(lu)003:10888: phyi rgyud kyi nang du nang pa'i thun min gyi chos skad mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK086(lu)003:10889: de ltar yang rig 'dzin chen po gter bdag gling pa'i zhal nas /
NK086(lu)003:10890: rtsa ba a nu cho ga la //
NK086(lu)003:10891: theg brgyad sgos chos bye brag tu //
NK086(lu)003:10892: sbyar ba nyid la ltos dgos na //
NK086(lu)003:10893: a nu'i mtshan gzhir ji ltar nges //
NK086(lu)003:10894: zhes gsungs pas phyogs snga ma nyid du gnas pa'i phyir skyon yod pa ma yin no //
NK086(lu)003:10895: gnyis pa bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK086(lu)003:10896: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK086(lu)003:10898: a nu dbyer med pa 'dod pa'i //
NK086(lu)003:10899: dbyings dang ye shes sgor zhugs nas //
NK086(lu)003:10902: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul gyis te //
NK086(lu)003:10904: skye med dbyings nyid ye shes te //
NK086(lu)003:10905: ye shes rig pa dbyings nyid tshul //
NK086(lu)003:10906: gnyis med rol pa bde ba che //
NK086(lu)003:10907: rim par 'jug pa ma yin te //
NK086(lu)003:10908: snang srid phyag rgya thams cad la //
NK086(lu)003:10909: chu la nya ldang ji bzhin du //
NK086(lu)003:10910: thug phrad snang srid phyag rgya che //
NK086(lu)003:10913: chos thams cad rang gi sems yin la /
NK086(lu)003:10914: de nyid skye med spros pa dang bral ba'i rang
NK086(lu)003:10915: bzhin yul kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnam par
NK086(lu)003:10916: dag pa ste / ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes kyang bya'i /
NK086(lu)003:10917: de ltar yang spyi mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:10918: sems las byung ba stong nyid pas //
NK086(lu)003:10919: de las byung ba thams cad stong //
NK086(lu)003:10921: skye med de nyid thams cad du mi 'gag par
NK086(lu)003:10922: rig pa rang byung 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK086(lu)003:10923: ba ni ye shes kun tu bzang po'am /
NK086(lu)003:10924: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK086(lu)003:10926: brtag na ma mthong cir yang snang ba nyid //
NK086(lu)003:10928: de gnyis ngo bo tha mi dad par gsal ba
NK086(lu)003:10929: ni dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sras bde
NK086(lu)003:10930: ba chen po ste rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi
NK086(lu)003:10931: dkyil 'khor ro // de ltar yang snga ma las /
NK086(lu)003:10932: gsang sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK086(lu)003:10933: snang ba dang mi snang ba gnyis su med pa /
NK086(lu)003:10934: gnyis kyi ngo bo las grol ba /
NK086(lu)003:10935: dbu mar mi dmigs pa gang yin pa de kho na nyid do //
NK086(lu)003:10937: de'i phyir chos thams cad dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum
NK086(lu)003:10938: dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin rtsa ba byang chub sems
NK086(lu)003:10939: kyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas par blta
NK086(lu)003:10941: thams cad de nyid der gcig pas //
NK086(lu)003:10942: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK086(lu)003:10943: skye 'gag med pa'i snying po yin //
NK086(lu)003:10944: bya byed med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK086(lu)003:10945: ye nas grub zin lhun gyis grub //
NK086(lu)003:10948: snang srid bzang mo'i mkha' klong las //
NK086(lu)003:10949: ma bskyed dkyil 'khor kun bzang shar //
NK086(lu)003:10950: shar ba nyid na shar ba med //
NK086(lu)003:10951: yab yum sras bcas bde chen po //
NK086(lu)003:10954: de'ang kun tu bzang po'i rol pa ma 'gags pa'i rtsal lha skur 'char bar 'dod de /
NK086(lu)003:10956: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba las //
NK086(lu)003:10957: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK086(lu)003:10958: snang srid rnam dag lha mo'i dbyings //
NK086(lu)003:10961: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga ni //
NK086(lu)003:10962: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK086(lu)003:10963: lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK086(lu)003:10964: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul du 'dod //
NK086(lu)003:10968: gzhi 'dzin pa ni dam tshig ste //
NK086(lu)003:10969: sgo gsum sdom bar gnas pa'i don //
NK086(lu)003:10970: rtsa ba yan lag la sogs pa'i //
NK086(lu)003:10971: bsrung dang bsgrub pa de nyid do //
NK086(lu)003:10972: zhes pas sgo gsum gyis rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK086(lu)003:10973: la sogs pa'i dam tshig bsrung zhing bsgrub par bya
NK086(lu)003:10974: ba rnams te / de'ang dbye na /
NK086(lu)003:10975: gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig bzhi /
NK086(lu)003:10976: thun mong gi nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK086(lu)003:10983: lta ba'i dam tshig ste rnam grangs dgur spyi mdo'i le'u re drug par gsungs mod kyang /
NK086(lu)003:10985: bsrung mtshams med pa cig car ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK086(lu)003:10986: bsrung mtshams can rim gyis pa'i dam tshig gnyis su 'du ste /
NK086(lu)003:10988: bsrung bya bsrung du med pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:10989: chos nyid dam tshig dam pa yin //
NK086(lu)003:10991: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK086(lu)003:10992: kun gyi thun mong ma yin phyir //
NK086(lu)003:10993: mos pa chung ngu thams cad la //
NK086(lu)003:10994: bsrung ba'i mtshams dag bzung bar byas //
NK086(lu)003:10998: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK086(lu)003:11003: steng sgo 'khor lo bzhi'am drug bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK086(lu)003:11004: 'og sgo mkhar gsang gnyis kyi snyoms 'jug la brten
NK086(lu)003:11005: nas lhan skyes kyi ye shes bskyed pa'i thabs te
NK086(lu)003:11007: rol pa'i ka ra la sogs pa //
NK086(lu)003:11008: man ngag thabs kyis der 'jug dang //
NK086(lu)003:11014: spros med rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK086(lu)003:11015: chos nyid snying po ji bzhin pa'i ngang las sgom byed kyi blo ma bcos par 'jog pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:11016: de ltar yang spyi mdo las /
NK086(lu)003:11017: ji bzhin pa yi chos nyid la //
NK086(lu)003:11018: de bzhin pa yi blo bzhag nas //
NK086(lu)003:11019: brjod pa med pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK086(lu)003:11020: ma yengs rgyun du dran pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:11023: spros bcas lha yi ting nge 'dzin te /
NK086(lu)003:11024: sngags brjod pa tsam gyis chu las nya ldang ba ltar /
NK086(lu)003:11025: snod bcud lha'i dkyil 'khor gsal lam 'dres par cig
NK086(lu)003:11026: car du bsgom pa gtso bor byed pa'i nyams len
NK086(lu)003:11027: no // de ltar yang bang mdzod 'phrul lde las /
NK086(lu)003:11028: a nu yo ga'i theg par ni //
NK086(lu)003:11029: snying po tsam zhig brjod byas nas //
NK086(lu)003:11030: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i lha ru bsgom //
NK086(lu)003:11033: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK086(lu)003:11034: 'byung dang 'byung gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK086(lu)003:11036: de'ang spyir nges rdzogs bsgom pa'i lam la /
NK086(lu)003:11045: rtsa chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK086(lu)003:11047: spyir mnyam pa nyid la gtso bor spyod pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:11049: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga ni //
NK086(lu)003:11050: dbyings dang ye shes longs spyod rdzogs //
NK086(lu)003:11055: thabs kyi spyod pa gsum ste /
NK086(lu)003:11057: byin gyis rlob kyi spyod pa dang //
NK086(lu)003:11058: dbang sgyur thabs kyi spyod pa ste //
NK086(lu)003:11059: dper na nam mkha' rgyal po'am //
NK086(lu)003:11060: ji ltar me dpung chu bo 'dra //
NK086(lu)003:11063: tshe gcig gis 'bras chos nyer lnga dbyer med lhun
NK086(lu)003:11064: grub kyi ngo bo sku bzhi'i bdag nyid bde ba
NK086(lu)003:11065: chen po'i sku mngon du byed de /
NK086(lu)003:11066: thig le mchog gi rgyud las /
NK086(lu)003:11067: 'od gsal ba yi sems nyid ni //
NK086(lu)003:11068: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med par //
NK086(lu)003:11069: bde ba che de su bsgom pa //
NK086(lu)003:11073: a nu yo ga'i theg pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:11074: bar ma chod pa'i tshe gcig gis //
NK086(lu)003:11075: sangs rgyas sa la nges par 'gro //
