NK086(lu)003:11077: gsum pa man ngag a ti yo ga'i theg pa la /
NK086(lu)003:11081: ye sangs rgyas pa'i don rang thog tu grol bar byed pa'i thabs /
NK086(lu)003:11082: spang blang re dogs dang bral ba'i rang bzhin can no //
NK086(lu)003:11085: bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i rdzogs rim mthar thug sa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK086(lu)003:11086: theg pa thams cad kyi rtse mor gyur pa'i phyir shin tu rnal 'byor ro //
NK086(lu)003:11087: gsum pa dbye na drug gi //
NK086(lu)003:11088: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis las /
NK086(lu)003:11090: rig pa'i rtsa dbang la sogs pas smin par byas pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:11091: gnyis pa bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK086(lu)003:11092: ci yang 'jug tu med pa'i sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK086(lu)003:11094: chos la bya ru med pa'i phyir //
NK086(lu)003:11095: rtsol ba med pa'i sgo nas 'jug /ces so //
NK086(lu)003:11097: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK086(lu)003:11098: thig le chen po chos kyi sku rang byung gi
NK086(lu)003:11099: ye shes chen po'i ngo bor bya rtsol med par
NK086(lu)003:11100: ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK086(lu)003:11102: rang byung ye shes rtsol med las //
NK086(lu)003:11103: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK086(lu)003:11106: rang byung ye shes mi rtog kun tu ji bzhin gnas //
NK086(lu)003:11109: med pa dang phyal ba la sogs pa'i dam tshig las mi 'da' bar bya ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:11111: a ti yo ga'i dam tshig ni //
NK086(lu)003:11112: med pa dang ni phyal ba dang //
NK086(lu)003:11113: gcig pu dang ni lhun gyis grub //
NK086(lu)003:11114: de yi don las 'da' mi bya //
NK086(lu)003:11117: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK086(lu)003:11118: yid can rnams la sems kyi sde //
NK086(lu)003:11119: nam mkha' can la klong gi sde //
NK086(lu)003:11120: rim rtsol bral la man ngag sde //
NK086(lu)003:11122: rig stong chos sku'i ngang du 'jog pa sems sde /
NK086(lu)003:11123: chos nyid bya rtsol med pa'i ngang du 'jog pa klong sde /
NK086(lu)003:11124: ye grol spang blang bral ba'i chos nyid kyi ngang du 'jog pa man ngag sde'o //
NK086(lu)003:11125: de'ang spyir rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyi bsgom pa ni /
NK086(lu)003:11129: nyams blangs khred chod thod rgal lo //
NK086(lu)003:11132: ka dag gi lta ba'i ngang las ma g.yos par 'jog pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:11134: lhun gyi gnas pas bzhag pa yin //
NK086(lu)003:11136: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK086(lu)003:11137: sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas bud+d+ha ste /
NK086(lu)003:11138: sems la skye 'gag med pa nam mkha' 'dra //
NK086(lu)003:11139: chos kun mnyam nyid yang dag don rtogs nas //
NK086(lu)003:11140: de nyid ma btsal bzhag na bsgom pa yin //
NK086(lu)003:11142: de ltar bsgoms pa sa lam gyi bskyed rim bzhi ste /
NK086(lu)003:11143: gnas dang mi g.yo mnyam nyid lhun gyis grub //
NK086(lu)003:11146: gnad drug la brten nas snang bzhi rim par 'char ba ste /
NK086(lu)003:11150: chos nyid zad pa'i snang bas mthar phyin pa'o //
NK086(lu)003:11152: cir snang chos nyid kyi rol par shar bas blang dor med par spyod pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:11154: bya ba med pas las rnams zin //
NK086(lu)003:11157: a ti yo ga'i spyod pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:11158: lta sgom srog dang ldan pa yis //
NK086(lu)003:11159: shugs las byung ba'i spyod pa ni //
NK086(lu)003:11160: ji ltar smyon pa'i spyod pa bzhin //
NK086(lu)003:11161: gang la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK086(lu)003:11164: lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i sa la da lta nyid nas gnas pa mthar phyin pa ste /
NK086(lu)003:11165: gding bzhi tshad du phyin pas 'khor ba myang 'das su grol ba'o //
NK086(lu)003:11167: rdzogs chen a ti'i 'bras bu ni //
NK086(lu)003:11168: gdod nas snying po byang chub tu //
NK086(lu)003:11169: thob med 'bras bu rang la smin //
NK086(lu)003:11171: snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa rin po
NK086(lu)003:11172: che'i rnam gzhag legs bshad snang ba'i dga' ston ces
NK086(lu)003:11173: bya ba las / 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rnam gzhag bshad pa'i tshoms te /
NK086(lu)003:11174: skabs bzhi pa'i bdag nyid can gyis re zhig bshad zin to //
NK086(lu)003:11175: de ltar 'dir ji skad smos pa'ang rjes su 'jug
NK086(lu)003:11176: pa'i gang zag blo gros gsar bu pa rnams la
NK086(lu)003:11177: cung zad phan du re bas /
NK086(lu)003:11178: chos rje kun mkhyen klong chen pa dang /
NK086(lu)003:11179: smin gling lo chen chos dpal rgya mtsho /
NK086(lu)003:11180: kahthoga pan+di ta 'gyur med tshe dbang mchog grub /
NK086(lu)003:11182: rdo grub 'jig med bstan pa'i nyi ma /
NK086(lu)003:11183: ze chen rgyal tshab 'gyur med pad+ma rnam rgyal rnams
NK086(lu)003:11184: kyi gsung gi bcud bsdus shing yig tshogs nyung ba
NK086(lu)003:11185: gtso bor byas / mdo sngags kyi rnam gzhag la
NK086(lu)003:11186: spyi'i go don dang skabs kyi bsdus don gnyis su
NK086(lu)003:11187: phyes ba zlos pa lta bur snang na'ang skabs bab
NK086(lu)003:11188: khol 'don blo la 'jug bde ba'i dbang du byas
NK086(lu)003:11189: te go sla khyer bde'i tshul du sbyar ba yin
NK086(lu)003:11190: gtso bor byas / la / gzhan du thos bsam
NK086(lu)003:11191: gyi mtha' rgya rab tu gcod par 'dod pa'i blo
NK086(lu)003:11192: ldan rnams da dung 'di tsam gyis blo kha mi
NK086(lu)003:11193: gtso bor byas / la / tshim par / snga
NK086(lu)003:11194: 'gyur che ba drug ldan rgyud lung man ngag nges
NK086(lu)003:11195: pa'i zab gnad mtha' dag gzhan dring du mi 'jog
NK086(lu)003:11196: pa'i chos nyid ji bzhin gzigs pa'i rnam dpyod kyis
NK086(lu)003:11197: legs par bkral ba kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer
NK086(lu)003:11198: gyi gsung rab rin po che'i gan mdzod rgyal srid
NK086(lu)003:11199: kyi 'byor pa khyad par can gyi grangs ldan dang
NK086(lu)003:11200: gtso bor byas / la / tshim par / / snying thig ma bu'i skor /
NK086(lu)003:11201: rig 'dzin chen po gter bdag gling pa sku mched
NK086(lu)003:11202: kyi 'dus pa mdo dang sgyu 'phrul skor gyi yig
NK086(lu)003:11203: cha / 'jam mgon mi pham smra ba'i seng ge'i
NK086(lu)003:11204: gsung rab sogs mkhas grub gong ma rnams kyis legs
NK086(lu)003:11205: par bshad pa'i snang ba rgya chen po la brten
NK086(lu)003:11206: nas blo gros kyi 'dab stong phyogs med du grol
NK086(lu)003:11207: cha / bar bya'o // slar smras pa /
NK086(lu)003:11208: rgyal bstan yongs rdzogs phyi mo snga 'gyur ba'i //
NK086(lu)003:11209: ring lugs dri med zab yangs chu gter las //
NK086(lu)003:11210: shes 'dod gsar bu'i skal 'tshams bdud rtsi'i rgyun //
NK086(lu)003:11211: rnam bshad bum bzang bcud du kho bos blangs //
NK086(lu)003:11212: sngon rabs dam pa'i legas bshad la brten nas //
NK086(lu)003:11213: lhag bsam snang ba'i 'dzum gyis nyer bsus te //
NK086(lu)003:11214: bstan pa'i rnam gzhag gtam gyi dag'a ston gang //
NK086(lu)003:11215: skal bzang tshogs rab kun dag'i dpyid du spros //
NK086(lu)003:11216: tshul 'dir nyes bshad mchis na bdag skyon phyir //
NK086(lu)003:11217: gzur gnas mkhas rnams bzod bzhes brtser dgongs 'os //
NK086(lu)003:11218: legs bshad cha kun bla ma'i drin las te //
NK086(lu)003:11219: bstan la rim gro bgyi ba'i stib stangs tsam //
NK086(lu)003:11220: bla med theg rtse'i thab gnad rdo rje tshig /rjen phyungs gsang ba bsgrags sogs nongs pa'i sprin //
NK086(lu)003:11221: gang mchis rtsa gsum byin rlabs 'thor rlung gis //
NK086(lu)003:11222: brjod bral chos dbyings mkha' ru stim mdzod gsol //
NK086(lu)003:11223: 'dir 'bad bdag gis bsod nams gang thob pa //
NK086(lu)003:11224: de kun bstan pa rgyas pa'i phyir du bsngo //
NK086(lu)003:11225: bstan pa'i snying po srid na yun gnas te //
NK086(lu)003:11226: zhing rnams yon tan rgya mtshos mdzes byed shog /bdag kyang tshe rabs kun tu rgyal bstan gyi //
NK086(lu)003:11227: gsang mdzod 'dzin la gsang bdag dpa' bo ltar //
NK086(lu)003:11228: zab don seng ge'i sgrogs bzhin du //
NK086(lu)003:11229: srid na rgyu bas srid pa gting sprugs shog /
NK086(lu)003:11230: 'pho 'gyur 'jigas tshogs dang bral gnyug ma'i gshis //
NK086(lu)003:11231: bstan g.yo kun khyab ye shesa snying po can //
NK086(lu)003:11232: mi shigs sems kyi rdo rje'i phyag rgya yis //
NK086(lu)003:11233: dngos kun bde ba chen por sdom gyur cig /de
NK086(lu)003:11234: ltar gsang sngags snga 'gyur rnying ma'i bstan pa'i rnam
NK086(lu)003:11235: gzhag mdo tsam brjod pa legs bshad snang ba'i dga'
NK086(lu)003:11237: rgyal khams pa 'jigs bral ye shes rdo rjes rang
NK086(lu)003:11238: lo drug rtsa gsum pa'i thog tu son pa zil
NK086(lu)003:11239: gnon me khams shugs 'chang gi lo sa ga zla
NK086(lu)003:11240: ba'i tshes bco lnga la dbu brtsams te skabs ci
NK086(lu)003:11242: yongs su rdzogs pa khrum stod kyi bkra shis pa'i zla ba yar ngo'i tshes bco lnga la /
NK086(lu)003:11243: sbas yul 'bras mo gshongs kyi yan lag gi gnas
NK086(lu)003:11244: mchog ka p+aa la spungs par grags pa'i ri bo
NK086(lu)003:11245: rin chen spungs kyi rtse mo pad+ma 'od kyi grong
NK086(lu)003:11246: khyer du grub par sbyar ba las /
NK086(lu)003:11247: thog ma'i yi ge pa ni mon kha ku re
NK086(lu)003:11248: lung gi sngags btsun rig 'dzin rdo rjes bgyis pa'o
NK086(lu)003:11249: // 'dis kyang bstan pa'i snying po mi nyams yun
NK086(lu)003:11250: du gnas par byed pa'i cha rkyen dam par gyur
NK086(lu)003:11251: cig /sarba d+aa mang+ga la sh+r+ai dza yan+tu ////
NK086(lu)003:11253: nyung ngu'i ngag gis rgya che'i don bston pa //
NK086(lu)003:11254: snga 'gyur bstan pa rgya mtsho'i rnam gzhag gang //
NK086(lu)003:11255: bdud 'jom sras mo bde chen g.yu sgron gyis //
NK086(lu)003:11256: chos sbyin mi mdzad spar gyi phyi mor bsgrubs //
NK086(lu)003:11257: bsod nams de mthus bstan pa rin po che //
NK086(lu)003:11258: dus kyi mthar yang mi nub 'phel zhing rgyas //
NK086(lu)003:11259: nges gsang bshad sgrub chos kyi rnga chen sgra //
NK086(lu)003:11260: 'dzam gling khyon kun 'gengs par sgrogs byed shog /rgyu sbyor gang de'i lus bskyed pha mas gtsos //
NK086(lu)003:11261: 'brel bcas 'gro kun sgrib gnyis rang grol nas //
NK086(lu)003:11262: tshogs gnyis myur rdzogs sku gnyis mngon gyur te //
NK086(lu)003:11263: don gnyis lhun grub bkra shis dpal 'bar shog //
NK086(lu)003:11264: ces pa'ang 'jigs bral ye shes rdo rjes ched du brjod pa dza yan+tu /
